hadiths[525]{hadithnumber,text}:
3949,main aik waqt Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ke pahlu mein betha hua tha. unse puchha gaya tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kitney ghazwey kiye? unhon-ne kaha unnees. maine puchha aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kitney ghazawaat mein Sharik rahe ? to unhon-ne kaha ke satrah mein. maine puchha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sabse pehli jang kon si thi? kaha ke Usaira ya Ushaira. phir maine iska zikr Qatada se kya to unhon-ne kaha ke (saheeh lafz) Ushaira hai.
3950,"wo Umayya-bin-Khalaf ke (jaahiliyat ke zamaney se) dost they aur jab bhi Umayya Madina se guzarta to unke yahan qiyam karta tha. isi tarah Sad (Raziallahu anhu) jab Makka se guzartey to Umayya ke yahan qiyam kartey. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina hijrat karke tashrif laey to aik martaba Sad (Raziallahu anhu) Makka Umra ke iraadey se gaey aur Umayya ke paas qiyam kya. unhon-ne Umayya se kaha ke mere liye koi tanhai ka waqt bataao taake main Baitullah ka tawaaf karun. chunanche Umayya unhein do-pahar ke waqt sath lekar nikla . unse abu-Jahal ki mulaqat ho gaee. us ne poochha, abu-Safwaan ! ye tumharey sath kon hain? Umayya ne bataya ke ye Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) hain. abu-Jahal ne kaha, main tumhen Makka mein amn ke sath tawaaf karta hua na dekhun . tum ne be diinon ko panah de rakhi hai aur is khayal mein ho ke tum log unki madad karogey. khuda ki qasam! agar us waqt tum, abu-Safwaan! Umayya ke sath na hotey to apne ghar salamati se nahi ja saktey they. is par Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, us waqt unki awaz buland ho gaee thi ke Allah ki qism ! agar aaj tum ne mujhey tawaaf se rokaa to main bhi Madina ki taraf se tumhara rasta band kar doonga aur ye tumharey liye bahut si mushkilaat ka baais bin jaeyga Umayya kehney laga, Sad ! abul-Hakam ( abu-Jahal (ke samney buland awaz se na bolo . ye wadi ka sardaar hai. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Umayya ! is tarah ki guftgu na karo. Allah ki qism ! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sun chuka hun ke to inke hathon se maara jaeyga Umayya ne poochha. kya Makka mein mujhey qatl karengey? unhon-ne kaha ke iska mujhey ilm nahi. Umayya ye sun kar bahut ghabraa gaya aur jab apne ghar lota to (apni biwi se) kaha, Umme- Safwan ! dekha nahi Sad mere mutaalliq kya keh rahe hain. us ne poochha, kya keh rahe hain? Umayya ne kaha ke wo ye bata rahe they ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein khabar di hai ke kisi na kisi din wo mujhey qatl kar dengey. maine puchha kya Makka mein mujhey qatl karengey ? to unhon-ne kaha ke iski mujhey khabar nahi. Umayya kehney laga : khuda ki qasam! ab Makka se bahar mein kabhi nahi jaaunga . phir badr ki ladai ke mauqe par jab abu-Jahal ne Quraish se ladai ki taiyaarii ke liye kaha aur kaha ke apne qaafile ki madad ko chalo to Umayya ne ladai mein shirkat pasand nahi ki, lekin abu-Jahal uske paas aaya aur kehney laga, aey Safwan ! tum wadi ke sardaar ho. jab log dekhengey ke tum hi ladai mein nahi nikaltey ho to doosrey log bhi nahi niklengey. abu-Jahal yun hi barabar usko samjhaataa raha. aakhir majbur ho kar Umayya ne kaha jab nahi maantaa to khuda ki qasam (is ladai ke liye) mein aisa tez raftaar oont khareedoonga jiska saanii Makka mein na ho. phir Umayya ne (apni biwi se) kaha, Umme- Safwan ! mera saman taiyaar kar de. us ne kaha, abu-Safwaan ! apne Yasrabii bhai ki baat bhool gaey? Umayya bola, main bhula nahi hun. unke sath sirf thodi door tak jaaunga. jab Umayya nikla to raaste mein jis manzil par bhi thaharnaa hota, ye apna oont (apne paas hi ( baandhey rakhta . wo barabar aisa hi ehtiyat karta raha yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne usey qatl kara diya."
3951,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jitney ghazwey kiye, mein jange-Tabook ke siwa sab mein hazir raha. albatta jange-badr mein Sharik na ho saka tha lekin jo log us ghazwey mein Sharik na ho sakey they, unmein se kisi par Allah ne ghussa nahi kya. kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Quraish ke qafley ko talash karne ke liye nikley they. (ladney ki niyat se nahi gaey they) magar Allah Taala ne naa-gahaanii musalmanon ko unke dushmanon se bhidaa diya."
3952,"maine Miqdaad-bin-Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) se aik aisi baat suni ke agar wo baat meri zaban se ada ho jati to mere liye kisi bhi cheez ke muqaabley mein zyada azeez hoti . wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt mushrekeen par baddua kar rahe they. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham wo nahi kahengey jo Musa (Alaihissalam) ki qaum ne kaha tha ke jao, tum aur tumhara rab unse jang karo, balke ham aap ke daaein-baaein, aagey aur peechhey jama ho kar ladengey. maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak chamakney laga aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khush ho gaey."
3953,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badr ki ladai ke mauqe par farmaya tha ke aey Allaah! main terey ahad aur wa'de ka waasta deta hun, agar to chahey (ke ye kaafir ghalib hon to musalmanon ke khatm ho janey ke baad) teri ibadat na hogi. is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hath thaam liya aur arz kya bas keejiye, ya Rasulullah! iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne khemey se bahar tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban par ye aayat thi ( سيهزم الجمع ويولون الدبر‏ ( '' jald hi kuffaar ki jamat ki haar hogi aur ye peeth pher kar bhag niklengey.''"
3954,(sura Nisa ki us aayat se) لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين‏ jihaad mein shirkat karne waley aur is mein Sharik na hone-waale barabar nahi ho saktey. wo log murad hain jo badr ki ladai mein Sharik huey aur jo usmein Sharik nahi huey.
3955,( badr ki ladai ke mauqe par) mujhey aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko nabaligh qarar de diya gaya tha.
3956,badr ki ladai mein mujhey aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko nabaligh qarar de diya gaya tha aur us ladai mein muhajireen ki tadaad sath se kuchh zyada thi aur Ansar 200 chalis (40) se kuchh zyada they.
3957,"Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ne jo badr mein Sharik they mujh se bayan kya ke badr ki ladai mein unki tadaad itni hi thi jitni Talut (Alaihissalam) ke un ashaab ki thi jinhoney unke sath nehar Palestine ko paar kya tha. taqriban teen so das . Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha nahi, Allah ki qism ! Talut ke sath nehar Palestine ko sirf wahi log paar kar sakey they jo momin they."
3958,ham As'haabe-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aapas mein ye guftgu kartey they ke As'haabe-badr ki tadaad bhi itni hi thi jitni ashaab Talut ki. jinhoney aap ke sath nehar Palestine paar ki thi aur unke sath nehar ko paar karne waley sirf momin hi they yani teen so das se kuchh zyada aadmi .
3959,"ham aapas mein ye guftgu kya kartey they ke jange-badr mein ashaab badr ki tadaad bhi teen so das se kuchh uper thi, jitni un ashaab Talut ki tadaad thi jinhoney unke sath nehar Palestine paar ki thi aur usey paar karne waley sirf emaandaar hi they."
3960,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kaba ki taraf munh karke kuffaare-Quraish ke chand logon Sheba-bin-Rabee'a, Utba-bin-Rabeea, Waleed bin Utba aur abu-Jahal bin Hisham ke haq mein baddua ki thi. main uske liye Allah ko gawah banata hun ke maine ( badr ke maidan mein) unki laashein padi hui paaein . suraj ne unki laashon ko badbudar kar diya tha. us din badi garmi thi."
3961,badr ki ladai mein wo abu-Jahal ke qareeb se guzrey abhi usmein thodi si jaan baqi thi us ne unse kaha us se bada koi aur shakhs hai jis ko tum ne maara hai?
3962,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (aur dusri sanad) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne farmaya, mujh se Amr bin Khalid ne bayan kya, ham se Zuhair bin Muawiya ne bayan kya, unse Sulaiman Taimi ne aur unse Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii hai jo malum karey ke abu-Jahal ka kya hashr hua?'' ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) haqeeqate-haal malum karne aaey to dekha ke Ifra ke beton (Muaaz aur Muawwiz (Raziallahu anhu)) ne usey qatl kar diya hai aur uska jism thanda padaa hai. unhon-ne malum kya, kya to hi abu-Jahal hai? Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski dadhi pakad li. abu-Jahal ne kaha, kya is se bhi bada koi aadmi hai jisey tum ne aaj qatl kar daala hai? ya (is ne ye kaha ke kya us se bhi badaa) koi aadmi hai jisey uski qaum ne qatl kar daala hai? Ahmed bin Yunus ne (apni riwayat mein) ( أنت ( Abu-Jahal ke alfaz bayan kiye hain. yani unhon-ne ye poochha, kya to hi abu-Jahal hai."
3963,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badr ki ladai ke din farmaya '' kon dekh kar aayega ke abu-Jahal ka kya hua? '' ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) malum karne gaey to dekha ke Ifra ke donon ladkon ne usey qatl kar diya tha aur uska jism thanda padaa hai. unhon-ne uski dadhi pakad kar kaha, to hi abu-Jahal hai? us ne kaha, kya us se bhi bada koi aadmi hai jisey aaj uski qaum ne qatl kar daala hai ya (is ne yun kaha ke) tum logon ne usey qatl kar daala hai? mujh se ibne- Musanna ne bayan kya, ham ko Muaaz-bin-Muaaz ne khabar di, kaha ham se Sulaiman ne bayan kya aur unhein Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di, isi tarah aagey hadis bayan ki."
3964,"unhon-ne Saleh ke dada ( Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf) se, badr ke barey mein Ifra ke donon beton ki hadis murad letey they."
3965,"qiyamat ke din mein sabse pahlaa shakhs hunga jo Allah Taala ke darbar mein jhagdaa chukaaney ke liye 2 zaanu ho kar baitheyga. Qais-bin-ibaad ne bayan kya ke unhein hazraat ( Hamza , Ali aur Ubeda (Raziallahu anhu)) ke barey mein sura Haj ki ye aayat nazil hui thii (هذان خصمان اختصموا في ربهم‏)''ye 2 fareeq hain jinhoney Allah ke barey mein ladai ki.'' bayan kya ke ye wahi hain jo badr ki ladai mein ladney nikley they, musalmanon ki taraf se Hamza , Ali aur Ubeda ya abu-Ubaida bin-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) (aur kaafiron ki taraf se) Sheba bin Rabee , Utba-bin- Rabee aur Waleed bin Utba they."
3966,"aayate-karima (هذان خصمان اختصموا في ربهم‏) ''ye 2 fareeq hain jinhoney Allah ke barey mein muqaabla kya'' Quraish ke chh shakhson ke barey mein nazil hui thi ( teen musalmanon ki taraf ke yani Ali , Hamza aur Ubaida-bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) aur) teen kuffaar ki taraf ke yani ( Sheba bin Rabee , Utba-bin- Rabee aur Waleed bin Utba ."
3967,Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ye aayat (هذان خصمان اختصموا في ربهم‏) hamarey hi barey mein nazil hui thi.
3968,"ye aayat (هذان خصمان اختصموا في ربهم‏) unhiin chh aadmiyon ke barey mein, badr ki ladai ke mauqe par nazil hui thi. pehli hadis ki tarah rawi ne usey bhi bayan kya."
3969,"ye aayat (هذان خصمان اختصموا في ربهم‏) unke barey mein utri jo badr ki ladai mein muqaabley ke liye nikley they yani Hamza , Ali aur Ubaida-bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu)) musalmanon ki taraf se) aur utba, Sheba, Rabee ke betey aur Waleed bin Utba (kaafiron ki taraf se) ."
3970,"aik shakhs ne Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha aur main sun raha tha ke kya Ali (Raziallahu anhu) badr ki jang mein Sharik they? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, unhon-ne to mubaarzat ki thi aur ghalib rahe they."
3971,Umayya-bin-Khalaf se (hijrat ke baad) mera ahad naamaa ho gaya tha. phir badr ki ladai ke mauqe par unhon-ne iske aur uske betey ( Ali (ke qatl ka zikr kya. Bilal ne (jab usey dekh liya to ( kaha ke agar aaj Umayya bach nikla to main aakhirat mein azab se bach nahi sakoonga.
3972,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eik martaba Makka mein) sura Najm ki tilawat ki aur sajda tilawat kya to jitney log wahan maujood they sab sajde mein gir gaey. siwaey aik boodhey ke ke usne hatheli mein mitti lekar apni peshani par usey laga liya aur kehney laga ke mere liye bas itna hi kafi hai. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir maine usey dekha ke kufr ki haalat mein wo qatl hua.
3973,"Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke jism par talwaar ke teen (gahrey) zakhmon ke nishanat they. aik unke mundhey par tha (aur itna gehra tha) ke main bachpan main apni ungliyan unmein dakhil kar diya karta tha. Urwa ne bayan kya ke unmein se 2 zakhm badr ki ladai mein aaey they aur aik jange-Yarmook mein. Urwa ne bayan kya ke jab Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko (Hujjaaj zaalim ke hathon se) Shahid kar diya gaya to mujh se abdul-Malik-bin-Marwaan ne kaha : aey Urwa! kya Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki talwaar tum pehchantey ho? maine kaha ke haan, pehchanta hun. us ne puchha uski nishani bataao? maine kaha ke badr ki ladai ke mauqe par uski dhaar ka aik hissey toot gaya tha, jo abhi tak usmein baqi hai. Abdul-Malik ne kaha ke tum ne sach kaha ( phir us ne naabgha shaair ka ye misra' padha ( faujon ke sath ladtey ladtey unki talwaaron ki dhaarein kai jagah se toot gii hain'' phir Abdul-Malik ne wo talwaar Urwa ko wapas kar di, Hisham ne bayan kya ke hamara andaza tha ke us talwaar ki qeemat teen hazaar dirham thi. wo talwaar hamarey aik azeez (Usman bin Urwa ( ne qeemat de kar ley li thi meri badi aarzoo thi ke kash! wo talwaar mere hissey mein aatii."
3974,Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki talwaar par chandi ka kaam tha. Hisham ne kaha ke (mere waalid) Urwa ki talwaar par chandi ka kaam tha.
3975,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se Yarmook ki jang mein kaha aap hamla kartey to ham bhi aap ke sath hamla kartey unhon-ne kaha ke agar maine un par zor ka hamla kar diya to phir tum log peechhey reh jaogey sab boley ke ham aisa nahi karengey. chunanche Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne dushman ( roomii fauj ( par hamla kya aur unki safon ko cheertey huey aagey nikal gaey. us waqt unke sath koi aik bhi) musalman ( nahi raha phir ( musalman fauj ki taraf ( aaney lagey to roomiyon ne unke ghodey ki lagaam pakad li aur mundhey par 2 kaarii zakhm lagaey , jo zakhm badr ki ladai ke mauqe par unko laga tha wo un donon zakhmon ke darmyan mein pad gaya tha. Urwa-bin-Zubair ne bayan kya ke jab main chhota tha to un zakhmon main apni ungliyan daal kar khelaa karta tha. Urwa ne bayan kya ke Yarmook ki ladai ke mauqe par Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unke sath gaey they, us waqt unki umr kal das saal ki thi isliye unko aik ghodey par Sawar karke aik sahib ki hifazat mein de diya tha."
3976,"badr ki ladai main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se Quraish ke chobis maqtool sardaar badr ke aik bahut hi andherey aur gandey kuwein mein phenk diye gaey. aadat thi ke jab dushman par ghalib hotey to maidaane-jang mein teen din tak qiyam farmatey jange-badr ke khaatme ke teesrey din aap ke hukm se aap ki sawari par kajaawa baandha gaya aur aap rawaana huey aap ke ashaab bhi aap ke sath they sahaba ne kaha, ghaaliban aap kisi zarurat ke liye tashrif ley ja rahe hain aakhir aap us kuwein ke kinarey aa kar khadey ho gaey aur kuffaare-Quraish ke maqtooleen sardaaron ke naam unke bap ke naam ke sath lekar aap unhein awaz dene lagey ke aey falan bin falan ! aey falan bin falan ! kya aaj tumharey liye ye baat behtar nahi thi ke tum ne duniya mein Allah aur uske rasool ki itaat ki hotii? beshak ham se hamarey rab ne jo wada kya tha wo hamein poori tarah hasil ho gaya to kya tumharey rab ka tumharey mutaalliq jo wada (azaab ka ( tha wo bhi tumhen poori tarah mil gayaa? abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) bol padey : ya Rasulullah ! aap un laashon se kyon Khattab farma rahe hain? jin mein koi jaan nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, jo kuchh mein keh raha hun tum log unse zyada usey nahi sun rahe ho. '' Qatada ne bayan kya ke Allah Taala ne unhein zinda kar diya tha (is waqt) taake Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein apni baat suna dein unki zillat, naamuraadii aur hasarat w nadaamat ke liye."
3977,"aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne, Quran Majeed ki aayat ( الذين بدلوا نعمة الله كفرا‏ ( ) sura Ibrahim 28) ke barey mein aap ne farmaya Allah ki qism ! ye kuffaare-Quraish they. Amr ne kaha ke us se murad Quraish they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ki nemat they. kuffaare-Quraish ne apni qaum ko jange-badr ke din (daarul-bawaar) yani dozakh mein jhonk diya."
3978,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke samney kisi ne iska zikr kya ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se bayan kartey hain ke maiyat ko qabr mein uske ghar walon ke, is par roney se bhi azab hota hai. is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne to ye farmaya tha ke azab maiyat par uski bd-amaliyon aur gunahon ki wjah se hota hai. aur uske ghar waley hain ke ab bhi uski judai par rotey rahtey hain."
3979,"unhon-ne kaha ke uski misal bilkul aisi hi hai jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badr ke us kuwein par khadey ho kar jis mein mushrekeen ki laashein daal di gain thin, unke barey mein farmaya tha ke jo kuchh mein keh raha hun, ye usey sun rahe hain. to aap ke farmaney ka maqsad ye tha ke ab unhein malum ho gaya hoga ke unse mein jo kuchh keh raha tha wo haq tha. phir unhon-ne us aayat ki tilawat ki (إنك لا تسمع الموتى‏)'' aap mardon ko nahi suna saktey. '' ( وما أنت بمسمع من في القبور‏ ( ''aur jo log qabron mein dafn ho chukey hain unhein aap apni baat nahi suna saktey. '' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke (aap un mardon ko nahi suna saktey ( jo apna thikana ab jahannam mein bana chukey hain."
3980,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badr ke kuwein par khadey ho kar farmaya ''kya jo kuchh tumharey rab ne tumharey liye wada kar rakha tha, usey tum ne sachcha pa liyaa?'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo kuchh mein keh raha hun ye ab bhi usey sun rahe hain.'' is hadis ka zikr jab Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kya gaya to unhon-ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha ke unhon-ne ab jaan liya hoga ke jo kuchh maine unse kaha tha wo haq tha. iske baad unhon-ne aayat (إنك لا تسمع الموتى‏)'' beshak aap un mardon ko nahi suna saktey.'' poori padhi."
3981,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badr ke kuwein par khadey ho kar farmaya ''kya jo kuchh tumharey rab ne tumharey liye wada kar rakha tha, usey tum ne sachcha pa liyaa?'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo kuchh mein keh raha hun ye ab bhi usey sun rahe hain.'' is hadis ka zikr jab Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kya gaya to unhon-ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha ke unhon-ne ab jaan liya hoga ke jo kuchh maine unse kaha tha wo haq tha. iske baad unhon-ne aayat (إنك لا تسمع الموتى‏)'' beshak aap un mardon ko nahi suna saktey.'' poori padhii."
3982,"Haarisa-bin-Suraaqa Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) jo abhi nau-umr ladkey they, badr ke din Shahid ho gaey they (paanii peeney ke liye hauz par aaey they ke aik teer ne Shahid kar diyaa) phir unki walida (Rabeea' binte-Nasar, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki phoophii) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aapko malum hai ke mujhey Harisa se kitna piyaar tha. agar wo ab jannat mein hai to main is par sabr karoongii aur Allah Taala ki ummeed rakhoongii aur agar kahin dusri jagah hai to aap dekh rahe hain ke main kis haal mein hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah tum par raham karey, kya deewaanii ho rahi ho, kya wahan koi aik jannat hai? bahut si jannatein hain aur tumhara betaa jannatul-firdaus mein hai.''"
3983,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha mujhey, Abu-Marsad (Raziallahu anhu) aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik muhim par bhejaa. ham sab ghud-sawaar they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log seedhey chaley jao. jab rauza khaakh par pahuncho to wahan tumhen mushrekeen ki aik aurat milegii, wo aik khat liye huey hai jisey Haatib-bin-abii-Balta' ne mushrekeen ke naam bheja hai. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jis jagah ka pata diya tha ham ne wahin us aurat ko aik oont par jatey huey pa liya. ham ne us se kaha ke khat de do. wo kehney lagi ke mere paas to koi khat nahi hai. ham ne uske oont ko betha kar uski talashi li to waqei hamein bhi koi khat nahi mila. lekin ham ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baat kabhi ghalat nahi ho sakti khat nikal warna ham tujhey nangaa kar dengey. jab us ne hamara ye sakht rawaiya dekha to izaar baandhney ki jagah ki taraf apna hath ley gaee wo aik chadar mein liptii hui thi aur us ne khat nikal kar ham ko de diya. ham usey lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke usne (yani Haatib bin abi Balta' ne) Allah aur uske rasool aur musalmanon se daghaa ki hai aap mujhey ijazat dein taake main uski gardan mar dun lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ke tum ne ye kaam kyon kya? Haatib (Raziallahu anhu) boley : Allah ki qasam! ye wjah hargiz nahi thi ke Allah aur uske rasool par mera eman baqi nahi raha tha mera maqsad to sirf itna tha ke Quraish par is tarah mera aik ehsan ho jaey aur uski wjah se wo (Makka mein baqi reh janey waale) mere ahal w ayaal ki hifazat karein. aap ke ashaab mein jitney bhi hazraat (muhaajireen) hain un sab ka qabila wahan maujood hai aur Allah unke zariey unke gharwaalon aur maal ki hifazat karta hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhon-ne sachchii baat bata di hai aur tum logon ko chahiye ke unke mutaalliq achi baat hi kaho. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne phir arz kya ke us shakhs ne Allah , iske rasool aur musalmanon se daghaa ki hai aap mujhey ijazat dijiye ke main uski gardan mar dun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke kya ye badr walon mein se nahi hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ahal badr ke halaat ko pahley hi se janta tha aur wo khud farma chuka hai ke ''tum jo chaho karo, tumhen jannat zaroor milegii.'' (ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke) maine tumhari maghfirat kar di hai ye sun kar umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki aankhon mein aansu aagey aur arz kya, Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai."
3984,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-badr ke mauqe par hamein hidayat farmai thi ke jab kuffaar tumharey qareeb aa jayen to un par teer chalaanaa aur (jab tak wo door rahein) apne teeron ko bachaaey rakhna.
3985,jange-badr main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hidayat ki thi ke jab kuffaar tumharey qareeb aa jayen yani hamla karein (itney ke tumharey nishaaney ki zad mein aa jaaein) to phir un par teer barsaey shuru karna aur (jab tak wo tum se qareeb na hon) apne teer ko mehfooz rakhna.
3986,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud ki ladai mein teerandaazon par Abdullaah-bin-Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko sardaar muqarrar kya tha us ladai mein hamarey 70 aadmi Shahid huey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaabiyon se badr ki ladai mein aik so chalis (40) mushrekeen ko nuqsan pahuncha tha. 70 unmein se qatl kar diye gaey aur 70 qaidi bana kar laey gaey is par Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha ke aaj ka din badr ke din ka badla hai aur ladai ki misal dol ki si hai.
3987,main guman karta hun ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''khair w bhalai wo hai jo Allah Taala ne hamein Uhud ki ladai ke baad ata farmai aur Khuloose-amal ka sawab wo hai jo Allah Taala ne hamein badr ki ladai ke baad ata farmaayaa.
3988,"badr ki ladai ke mauqe par main saf mein khada hua tha. maine mud ke dekha to meri dahini aur baain taraf 2 naujawaan khadey they. abhi main unke mutaalliq koi faisla bhi na kar paya tha ke aik ne mujh se chupkey se puchha taake uska sathi sunney na paaey. chachaa! mujhey abu-Jahal ko dikhaa do. maine kaha bhateejey! tum usey dekh kar kya karogey? us ne kaha, maine Allah Taala ke samney ye ahad kya hai ke agar maine usey dekh liya to ya usey qatl karke rahunga ya phir khud apni jaan de doonga. doosrey naujawaan ne bhi apne sathi se chhipaatey huey mujh se yahi baat poochhii. unhon-ne kaha ke us waqt un donon naujawaanon ke darmyan mein khadey ho kar mujhey bahut khushi hui. maine ishaarey se unhein abu-Jahal dikhaa diya. jisey dekhtey hi wo donon baaz ki tarah is par jhaptey aur fauran hi usey mar giraayaa. ye donon Ifra ke betey they."
3989,"mujhey Umar-bin Usaid bin jaariya Saqafi ne khabar di jo bani zohra ke haleef they aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke shagirdon mein shamil they ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne das jaasus bhejey aur unka ameer Aasim-bin-Saabit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya jo Aasim bin umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke naana hotey hain. jab ye log Asfan aur Makka ke darmyan maqam hada par pahunchey to banii-Huzail ke aik qabeele ko unke aaney ki itlaa mil gaee. us qabeele ka naam banii-Lahyaan tha. uske 100 teerandaaz un sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ki talash mein nikley aur unke nishaane-qadam ke andaazey par chalney lagey. aakhir us jagah pahunch gaey jahan baith kar un sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne khajoor khaaii thi. unhon-ne kaha ke ye yasrib (Madeena) ki khajoor (ki guthliyaan) hain. ab phir wo unke nishaane-qadam ke andaazey par chalney lagey. jab Aasim-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke sathiyon ne unke aaney ko malum kar liya to aik (mahfooz) jagah panah li. qabeele walon ne unhein apne gherey mein ley liya aur kaha ke nichey utar aao aur hamari panah khud qabool kar lo to tum se ham wada kartey hain ke tumharey kisi aadmi ko bhi ham qatl nahi karengey. Aasim-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, musalmaanon! main kisi kaafir ki panah mein nahi utar sakta. phir unhon-ne dua ki, aey Allah ! hamarey halaat ki khabar apne Nabi ko kar de aakhir qabeele walon ne musalmanon par teerandaazii ki aur Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ko Shahid kar diya. baad mein unke wa'de par teen sahaba utar aaey. ye hazraat khubaib, Zaid-bin-Dasna aur aik teesrey sahabi they. qabeele walon ne jab un teenon sahaabiyon par qaabu pa liya to unki kamaan se taant nikal kar usi se unhein baandh diya. teesrey sahabi ne kaha, ye tumhari pehli daghaa bazi hai main tumharey sath kabhi nahi ja sakta. mere liye to unhiin ki zindagi namoona hai. aap ka ishara un sahaba ki taraf tha jo abhi Shahid kiye ja chukey they. kuffaar ne unhein ghaseetnaa shuru kya aur zabardastii ki lekin wo kisi tarah unke sath janey par taiyaar na huey. (to unhon-ne unko bhi Shahid kar diyaa) aur Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) aur Zaid-bin dasna (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath le gaey aur (Makka mein ley ja kar) unhein beech diya. ye badr ki ladai ke baad ka waqia hai. Haaris-bin-Aamir bin Nofal ke ladkon ne Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ko khareed liya. unhon hi ne badr ki ladai mein Haris bin Aamir ko qatl kya tha. kuchh dinon tak to wo unke yahan qaid rahe aakhir unhon-ne unke qatl ka irada kya. unhiin dinon Haris ki kisi ladki se unhon-ne zere-naaf baal saaf karne ke liye ustra maangaa. usne de diya. us waqt uska aik chhota sa bachcha unke paas ( khelta hua) us aurat ki be-khabri mein chala gaya. phir jab wo unki taraf aai to dekha ke bachcha unki raan par betha hua hai. aur ustra unke hath mein hai unhon-ne bayan kya ke ye dekhtey hi wo us darja ghabraa gaee ke Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski ghabraahat ko dekh liya aur boley, kya tumhen iska khof hai ke main is bachchey ko qatl kar doonga? yaqin rakho ke aisa hargiz nahi kar sakta. un khatun ne bayan kya ke Allah ki qism ! maine kabhi koi qaidi Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) se behtar nahi dekha. Allah ki qasam! maine aik din angoor ke aik khoshe se unhein angoor khaatey dekha jo unke hath mein tha halanke wo lohey ki zanjeeron mein jakdey huey they aur Makka mein us waqt koi phal bhi nahi tha. wo bayan karti thin ke wo to Allah ki taraf se bheji hui rozii thi jo usney Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye bheji thi. phir banu-Haarisa unhein qatl karne ke liye haram se bahar ley janey lagey to Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke mujhey 2 rakaat Namaz padhney ki ijazat de do. unhon-ne uski ijazat di to unhon-ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhi aur farmaya : Allah ki qasam! agar tumhen ye khayal na honey lagta ke mujhey ghabraahat hai) maut se) to aur zyada der tak padhta . phir unhon-ne dua ki ke aey Allah ! unmein se har aik ko alag alag halaak kar aur aik ko bhi baqi na chhod aur ye ashaar padhey ''jab main Islam par qatl kya ja raha hun to mujhey koi parwah nahi ke Allah ki raah mein mujhey kis pahlu par pachhaadaa jaeyga aur ye to sirf Allah ki raza hasil karne ke liye hai. agar wo chaahega to mere jism ke eik-eik jod par sawab ata farmaeyga .'' iske baad Abu-sarooaa Aqba bin-Haaris unki taraf badha aur us ne unhein Shahid kar diya. Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne achchhey amal se har us musalman ke liye jisey qaid karke qatl kya jaey (qatl se pahley 2 rak'at) Namaz ki sunnat qaaim ki hai. idhar jis din un sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) par museebat aai thi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko isi din uski khabar de di thi. Quraish ke kuchh logon ko jab malum hua ke Aasim-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) Shahid kar diye gaey hain to unke paas apne aadmi bhejey taake unke jism ka koi aisa hissey laaein jis se unhein pehchaana ja sakey. kyonke unhon-ne bhi) badr mein) unke aik sardaar ( Aqba bin abi mueet ( ko qatl kya tha lekin Allah Taala ne unki laash par badal ki tarah bhidon ki aik fauj bhej di aur unhon-ne aap ki laash ko kuffaare-Quraish ke un aadmiyon se bacha liya aur wo unke jism ka koi hissey bhi na kaat sakey aur Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mere samney logon ne muraara bin Rabe Umri (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hilal bin Umayya waaqifii (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr kya. (jo jange-Tabook mein nahi ja sakey they) ke wo Saleh sahaabiyon mein se hain aur badr ki ladai mein Sharik huey they."
3990,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Juma ke din zikr kya ke Saeed bin Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail (Raziallahu anhu) jo Badri sahabi they, bimar hain. din chadh chuka tha, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Sawar ho kar unke paas tashrif ley gaey. itney mein Juma ka waqt qareeb ho gaya aur wo Juma ki Namaz (majbooran) na padh sakey."
3991,"unke walid ne Umar-bin-abdullaah-bin Arqam Zohri ko likha ke tum sabeeaa binte- Haris Aslamiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jao aur unse unke waqia ke mutaalliq poochho ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se masla puchha tha to aap ne unko kya jawab diya tha? chunanche unhon-ne mere walid ko iske jawab mein likha ke sabeeaa binte- Haris (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di hai ke wo Sad bin Khaula (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein thin. unka talluq bani Aamir bin looii se tha aur wo badr ki jang mein shirkat karne walon mein se they. phir Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par unki wafat ho gaee thi aur us waqt wo hamal se thin. Sad bin Khaula (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ke kuchh hi din baad unke yahan bachcha paida hua. nifaas ke din jab wo guzaar chukiin to nikah ka paigham bhejney walon ke liye unhon-ne achchhey kapdey pahney . us waqt banu- abduddaar ke aik sahabi abu-Sanaabil bin ba'kak (Raziallahu anhu) unke yahan gaey aur unse kaha, mera khayal hai ke tum ne nikah ka paigham bhejney walon ke liye ye zeenat ki hai. kya nikah karne ka khayal hai? lekin Allah ki qism ! jab tak ( Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat par) char mahiney aur das din na guzar jayen tum nikah ke qaabil nahi ho saktiin. sabeeaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab abu-Sanaabil ne mujh se ye baat kahi to maine Sham hotey hi kapdey pahney aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar iske barey mein, maine aap se masla malum kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke main bachcha paida honey ke baad iddat se nikal chuki hun aur agar main chaahoon to nikah kar sakti hun. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Asbagh ne ibne- Wahab se ki hai, unse Yunus ne bayan kya aur Leis ne kaha ke mujh se Yunus ne bayan kya, unse ibne-Shahab ne, (unhon-ne bayan kya ke) ham ne unse puchha to unhon-ne bayan kya ke mujhey banu-Aamir bin looii ke ghulam Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Sobaan ne khabar di ke Muhammad-bin-Ayaas-bin-Bukair ne unhein khabar di aur unke walid Ayas badr ki ladai mein Sharik they."
3992,"Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey aur aap se unhon-ne puchha ke badr ki ladai mein Sharik honey walon ka aap ke yahan darja kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke musalmanon mein sabse afzal ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi tarah ka koi kalima irshad farmaya, Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke jo Farishtey badr ki ladai mein Sharik huey they unka bhi darja yahi hai."
3993,"Rifaa (Raziallahu anhu) badr ki ladai mein Sharik huey they aur (unke waalid) Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) baia'te-Aqba mein Sharik huey they, to aap apne betey (Rifa'a) se kaha kartey they ke baia'te-Aqba ke barabar badr ki shirkat se mujhey zyada khushi nahi hai. bayan kya ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us barey mein puchha tha."
3994,aik Farishtey ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha aur Yahya-bin-Saeed Ansari se riwayat hai ke Yazeed bin-Haad ne unhein khabar di ke jis din Muaaz-bin-Rifa'a ne unse ye hadis bayan ki thi to wo bhi unke sath they. Yazeed ne bayan kya ke Muaz ne kaha tha ke poochhney waley Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) they.
3995,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badr ki ladai mein farmaya tha ke ye hain Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) apne ghodey ka sar thaamey huey aur hathiyar lagaey huey.
3996,"Abu-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) wafat pa gaey aur unhon-ne koi aulad nahi chhodii, wo badr ki ladai mein Sharik huey they."
3997,"abu-Saeed bin Malik Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) safar se wapas aaey to unke ghar waley qurbani ka gosht unke samney laaey, unhon-ne kaha ke main usey us waqt tak nahi khaaunga jab tak iska hukm na malum kar loon. chunanche wo apni walida ki taraf se apne aik bhai ke paas malum karne gaey. wo badr ki ladai mein Sharik honey walon mein se they yani Qatada bin Nauman (Raziallahu anhu) . unhon-ne bataya ke baad mein wo hukm mansukh kar diya gaya tha jis mein teen din se zyada qurbani ka gosht khaney ki manaahii ki gaee thi."
3998,"badr ki ladai mein meri mudbhed Ubaida-bin Saeed bin Aas se ho gaee. uska Sara jism lohey mein gharq tha aur sirf aankh dikhai de rahi thi. uski kunniyat Abu-Zaatul-karsh thi. kehney laga ke main Abu-Zaatul-karsh hun. maine chhotey barchhey se is par hamla kya aur uski aankh hi ko nishana banaya. chunanche us zakhm se wo mar gaya. Hisham ne bayan kya ke mujhey khabar di gaee hai ke Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir maine apna paon uske uper rakh kar pura zor lagaya aur badi dushwari se wo barchha uski aankh se nikal saka. uske donon kinarey mud gaey they. Urwa ne bayan kya ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ka wo barchha talab farmaya to unhon-ne wo pesh kar diya. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee to unhon-ne usey wapas ley liya. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne talab kya to unhon-ne unhein bhi de diya Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ke baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne talab kya. unhon-ne unhein bhi de diya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ke baad unhon-ne usey ley liya. phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne talab kya to unhon-ne unhein bhi de diya. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ke baad wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas chala gaya aur unke baad unki aulad ke paas aur uske baad Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey ley liya aur unke paas hi raha, yahan tak ke wo Shahid kar diye gaey."
3999,"mujhey abu-Idrees Aaizullaah bin-Abdullah ne khabar di aur unhein Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ne, wo badr ki ladai mein Sharik huey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke mujh se bait karo."
4000,"abu-Huzaifa (rz), jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath badr ki ladai mein Sharik honey walon mein they, ne Salim (Raziallahu anhu) ko apna munh bola betaa banaya tha aur apni bhateejii Hind-bint-Waleed-bin-Utba se shadi kara di thi. Salim (Raziallahu anhu) aik Ansari khatun ke ghulam they. jaisey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) ko apna munh bola betaa bana liya tha. jahiliyat mein ye dastoor tha ke agar koi shakhs kisi ko apna munh bola betaa bana leta to log usi ki taraf usey mansub karke pukaartey aur munh bola betaa uski meeraas ka bhi waaris hota. yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) ادعوهم لآبائهم‏ ( '' unhein unke baapon ki taraf mansub karke pukaaro.'' to Sehla (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin. phir tafseel se rawi ne hadis bayan ki."
4001,"jis raat meri shadi hui thi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski subah ko mere yahan tashrif laey aur mere bistar par baithey, jaisey ab tum yahan mere paas baithey huey ho. chand bachchiyaan daf bajaa rahi thin aur wo ashaar padh rahi thin jin mein unke un khandan walon ka zikr tha jo badr ki ladai mein Shahid ho gaey they. unhiin mein aik ladki ne ye misra' bhi padha ke ham mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain jo kal honey wali baat ko jantey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye na padho, balke jo pahley padh rahi thin wahi padho."
4002,mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath badr ki ladai mein Sharik they ke Farishtey us ghar mein nahi aatey jis mein tasweer ya kutta ho. unki murad jaandaar ki tasweer se thi.
4003,"jange-badr ki ghaneemat mein se mujhey aik aur ontni mili thi aur usi jang ki ghaneemat mein se Allah Taala ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka jo khums ke taur par hissey muqarrar kya tha usmein se bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey aik ontni inayat farmai thi. phir mera irada hua ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ki rukhsati kara laaun. isliye bani-Qainuqaa ke aik sunaar se baat cheet ki ke wo mere sath chaley aur ham izkhir ghaas laaein. mera irada tha ke main us ghaas ko sunaaron ke hath bech doonga aur uski qeemat waleeme ki dawat mein lagaaunga. mein abhi apni ontni ke liye paalaan, tokrey aur rassiyaan jama kar raha tha. oontniyan aik Ansari sahabi ke hujre ke qareeb baithi hui thin. main jin intizaamaat mein tha jab wo poorey ho gaey to (oontniyon ko leney aayaa) wahan dekha ke unke kohan kisi ne kaat diye hain aur kokh cheer kar andar se kalejii nikal li hai. ye haalat dekh kar main apne aansuon ko na rok saka. maine poochha, ye kis ne kya hai? logon ne bataya ke Hamza bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur wo abhi usi hujre mein Ansar ke sath sharab peeney ki aik majlis mein maujood hain. unke paas aik gaaney wali hai aur unke dost Ahbaab hain. gaaney wali ne gaatey huey jab ye misra padhaa, haan, aey Hamza! ye umda aur farba oontniyan hain, to Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ne kood kar apni talwaar thaamee aur un donon oontniyon ke kohan kaat daley aur unki kokh cheer kar andar se kalejii nikal li. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir main wahan se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein maujood they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere gham ko pahley hi jaan liya aur farmaya ke kya baat pesh aaii? main bola : ya Rasulullah! aaj jaisi takleef ki baat kabhi pesh nahi aai thi. Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ne meri donon oontniyon ko pakad ke unke kohan kaat daley aur unki kokh cheer dali hai. wo yahin aik ghar mein sharab ki majlis jamaaey baithey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni chadar Mubarak mangwai aur usey odh kar aap tashrif ley chaley. main aur Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) bhi saath-saath ho liye. jab us ghar ke qareeb aap tashrif le gaey aur Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo kuchh kya tha is par unhein tanbeeh farmai. Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) sharab ke nashey mein mast they aur unki aankhen surkh thin. unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf nazar uthaaii, phir zara aur uper uthai aur aap ke ghutnon par dekhney lagey, phir aur nazar uthai aur aap ke chehra par dekhney lagey. phir kehney lagey, tum sab mere bap ke ghulam ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) samajh gaey ke wo is waqt behosh hain. isliye aap fauran ultey paon us ghar se bahar nikal aaey, ham bhi aap ke sath they."
4004,Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) ke janazey par takbeerein kahin aur kaha ke wo badr ki ladai mein Sharik they.
4005,"jab Hafsa binte- umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke shauhar Khunais-bin-Huzaafa Sehmi (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ho gaee, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab mein they aur badr ki ladai mein unhon-ne shirkat ki thi aur Madina mein unki wafat ho gaee thi. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke meri mulaqat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se hui to maine unse Hafsa ka zikr kya aur kaha ke agar aap chaahein to uska nikah main aap se kar dun. unhon-ne kaha ke main sochoonga. isliye main chand dinon ke liye thahar gaya, phir unhon-ne kaha ke meri raey ye hui hai ke abhi main nikah na karun. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir meri mulaqat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se hui aur unse bhi maine yahi kaha ke agar aap chaahein to main aap ka nikah Hafsa-binte-Umar se kar dun Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khamosh ho gaey aur koi jawab nahi diya. unka ye tareeqae-amal Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi zyada mere liye takleef ki wajah hua. kuchh dinon main aur thahar gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ka paigham bheja aur maine unka nikah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kar diya. iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki mulaqat mujh se hui to unhon-ne kaha, shayad aapko mere us tarze-amal se takleef hui hogi ke jab aap ki mujh se mulaqat hui aur aap ne Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke mutaalliq mujh se baat ki to maine koi jawab nahi diya. maine kaha ke haan, takleef hui thi. unhon-ne bataya ke aap ki baat ka maine sirf isliye koi jawab nahi diya tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (mujh se) Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ka zikr kya tha (mujh se mashwara liya tha ke main us se nikah kar loon) aur main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka raaz faash nahi kar sakta tha. agar aap Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se nikah ka irada chhod detey to beshak main unse nikah kar letaa."
4006,"ham se Muslim-bin Ibrahim qassaab ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, unse Adii-bin Aban ne, unse Abdullah-bin Yazeed Ansari ne, unhon-ne Abu-Masood Badri (Raziallahu anhu) Aqba-bin-Amr Ansari se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' insan ka apne baal bachchon par kharch karna bhi sawab hai.''"
4007,"Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) jab Kufa ke ameer they, to unhon-ne aik din Asr ki Namaz mein der ki. is par Zaid-bin Hasan ke naana Abu-Masood Aqba-bin-Amr Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) unke yahan gaey. wo badr ki ladai mein Sharik hone-waale sahaba mein se they aur kaha : aapko malum hai ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) (namaz ka tariqa bataaney ke liye) aaey aur aap ne Namaz padhi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke peechhey Namaz padhi, panchon waqt ki namaazein. phir farmaya ke isi tarah mujhey hukm mila hai. Basheer-bin-abii-Mas'ood bhi ye hadis apne walid se bayan kartey they."
4008,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sura al-Baqara ki 2 aayatein امن الرسول se aakhir tak, aisi hain ke jo shakhs raat mein unhein padh ley wo uske liye kafi ho jati hain. Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya ke phir maine khud Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ki, wo us waqt Baitullah ka tawaaf kar rahe they. maine unse us hadis ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne ye hadis mujh se bayan ki."
4009,"Utban bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi they aur wo badr mein Sharik huey they aur Ansar mein se they, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey."
4010,"phir maine Husain bin-Muhammad Ansari se jo bani Salim ke sharif logon mein se they, Mehmood-bin-Rabeea' ki hadis ke mutaalliq puchha jiski riwayat unhon-ne Utban bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se ki thi to unhon-ne bhi uski tasdeeq ki."
4011,"mujhey Abdullaah-bin-Aamir-bin-Rabee'a (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di, wo qabila bani Adi ke sab logon mein badey they aur unke walid Aamir-bin-Rabee'a badr main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sharik they. ( unhon-ne bayan kya ke) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Qudama bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ko Bahrain ka aamil banaya tha, wo Qudama (Raziallahu anhu) bhi badr ki ladai mein Sharik they aur Abdullah-bin-Umar aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke maamun they."
4012,"unke 2 chachaon (Zaheer aur Mazahar Raafe bin Adii-bin Zaid Ansari ke beton) jinhonney badr ki ladai mein shirkat ki thi, ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zameen ko kiraaye par deney se mana kya tha. maine Salim se kaha lekin aap to kiraaya par detey hain. unhon-ne kaha ke haan, Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne uper zyadti ki thi."
4013,"unke 2 chachaon (Zaheer aur Mazahar Raafe bin Adii-bin Zaid Ansari ke beton) jinhonney badr ki ladai mein shirkat ki thi, ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zameen ko kiraaye par deney se mana kya tha. maine Salim se kaha lekin aap to kiraaya par detey hain. unhon-ne kaha ke haan, Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne uper zyadti ki thii."
4014,maine Rifaa bin Raafe Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha hai. wo badr ki ladai mein Sharik huey they.
4015,"Amr-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) jo bani Aamir-bin-Luii ke haleef they aur badr ki ladai main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sharik they. ( ne bayan kya ke) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Ubaida bin-Jarraah (Raziallahu anhu) ko Bahrain , wahan ka jiziya laney ke liye bhejaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bahrain walon se suleh ki thi aur un par Alaa bin Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) ko ameer banaya tha, phir abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) Bahrain se maal aik laakh dirham lekar aaey. jab Ansar ko abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ke aaney ki khabar hui to unhon-ne fajr ki Namaz Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz se farigh huey to tamam Ansar aap ke samney aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein dekh kar muskuraaey aur farmaya : mera khayal hai ke tumhen ye itlaa mil gaee hai ke abu-Ubaida maal lekar aaey hain. unhon-ne arz kya : ji haan, ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tumhen khushkhabri ho aur jis se tumhen khushi hogi uski ummeed rakho . Allah ki qism ! mujhey tumharey mutaalliq mohtaajii se dar nahi lagta , mujhey to uska khof hai ke duniya tum par bhi isi tarah kushaada kar di jaeygi jis tarah tum se pahlon par kushaada ki gaee thi, phir pahlon ki tarah uske liye tum aapas mein rashk karogey aur jis tarah wo halaak ho gaey they tumhen bhi ye cheez halaak karke rahegii."
4016,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) har tarah ke sanp ko mar daala kartey they.
4017,"lekin jab abu-Lubaba Bashir bin abdul-Munzir (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo badr ki ladai mein Sharik they, unse bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghar mein nikalney waley sanp ke maarney se mana farmaya tha to unhon-ne bhi usey maarna chhod diya tha."
4018,Ansar ke chand logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat chahi aur arz kya ke aap hamein ijazat ata farmaein to ham apne bhaanjey Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ka fidya maaf kar dein lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ki qasam! unke fidya se aik dirham bhi na chhodnaa.''
4019,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke agar kisi mauqe par meri kisi kaafir se takkar ho jaey aur ham donon aik doosrey ko qatl karne ki koshish mein lag jayen aur wo mere aik hath par talwaar mar kar usey kaat daaley, phir wo mujh se bhag kar aik darakht ki panah lekar kehney lagey ''main Allah par eman ley aayaa.'' to kya ya Rasulullah! iske us iqrar ke baad phir bhi mein usey qatl kar dun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tum usey qatl na karna. unhon-ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! wo pahley mera aik hath bhi kaat chuka hai? aur ye iqrar mere hath kaatney ke baad kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir bhi yahi farmaya ke usey qatl na karnaa, kyonke agar tu ney isey qatl kar daala to usey qatl karne se pahley jo tumhara maqam tha ab uska wo maqam hoga aur tumhara maqam wo hoga jo uska maqam us waqt tha jab us ne us kalime ka iqrar nahi kya tha."
4020,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badr ki ladai ke din farmaya ''kaun dekh kar aayega ke abu-Jahal ke sath kya hua? Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) uske liye rawaana huey aur dekha ke Ifra ke donon beton ne usey qatl kar diya hai aur uski laash thandii honey wali hai. unhon-ne poochha, abu-Jahal tum hi ho? ibne-Ulaih ne bayan kya ke ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha tha ke to abu-Jahal hai? is par us ne kaha, kya us se bhi bada koi hoga jisey tum ne aaj qatl kar diya hai? Sulaiman ne bayan kya, kaha ke ya us ne yun kaha, '' jisey uski qaum ne qatl kar diya hai? (kya us se bhi bada koi hoga ( kaha ke abu-Mujliz ne bayan kya ke abu-Jahal ne kaha, kash! ! aik kisaan ke siwa mujhey kisi aur ne maara hota."
4021,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee to maine Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha aap hamein sath lekar hamarey Ansari bhaiyon ke yahan chalein. phir hamari mulaqat 2 nek tareen Ansari sahaabiyon se hui jinhoney badr ki ladai mein shirkat ki thi. Ubaidullah ne kaha, phir maine us hadis ka tazkira Urwa-bin-Zubair se kya to unhon-ne bataya ke wo donon sahabi Uwaim-bin-Saaida aur Ma'n (معن) bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) they."
4022,Badri sahaba ka (saalaana) wazeefa paanch-paanch hazaar tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke main unhein (badrii sahaba ko) un sahaabiyon par fazeelat doonga jo unke baad eman laey.
4023,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine suna, aap maghrib ki Namaz mein sura taur ki tilawat kar rahe they, ye pahlaa mauqa tha jab mere dil mein eman ne qarar pakdaa."
4024,"pahlaa fasaad jab barpa hua yani Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ka to usne As'haabe-badr mein se kisi ko baqi nahi chhodaa. phir jab doosra fasaad barpa hua yani Harra ka, to usne As'haabe-Hudaibiya mein se kisi ko baqi nahi chhodaa. phir tesraa fasaad barpa hua to wo us waqt tak nahi gaya jab tak logon mein kuchh bhi khoobi ya aql baqi thi."
4025,"maine Urwa bin Zubair, Saeed-bin-Musaiyab, Alqama bin Waqas aur Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki tohmat ke mutaalliq suna. unmein se har aik ne mujh se us waaqie ka koi hissey bayan kya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya tha ke main aur umme-mistah bahar qazaey-hajat ko ja rahe they ke Umme- mistah (Raziallahu anhu) apni chadar mein ulajh kar phisal padiin. is par unki zaban se nikla, mistah ka bura ho. maine kaha, aap ne achi baat nahi kahi. aik aisey shakhs ko aap bura kehti hain jo badr mein Sharik ho chuka hai. phir unhon-ne tohmat ka waqia bayan kya."
4026,"jab ( badr ke) kuffaar maqtooleen kuwein mein daley janey lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kya tum ne us cheez ko pa liya jiska tum se tumharey rab ne wada kya tha? ''Moosaa ne bayan kya, unse Naafe ne aur unse Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chand sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! aap aisey logon ko awaz de rahe hain jo mar chukey hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo kuchh maine unse kaha hai usey khud tum ne bhi unse zyada behtar tariqa par nahi suna hoga.'' abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke Quraish ( sahaba (ke jitney log badr mein Sharik huey they aur jinka hissey bhi (is ghaneemat mein) laga tha, unki tadaad 81 thi. Urwa-bin-Zubair bayan kartey they ke Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, maine (un muhajireen ke hissey ( taqseem kiye they aur unki tadaad 100 thi aur zyada behtar ilm Allah ko hai."
4027,badr ke din muhajireen ke 100 hissey lagaey gaey they.
4028,"banu- nazeer aur banu-Quraiza ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( muaahida tod kar) ladai mol li. isliye aap ne qabila banu- nazeer ko jilaa watan kar diya lekin qabila banu-Quraiza ko jilaa watan nahi kya aur is tarah un par ehsan farmaya, phir banu-Quraiza ne bhi jang mol li. isliye aap ne unke mardon ko qatl karwaya aur unki aurton, bachchon aur maal ko musalmanon mein taqseem kar diya. sirf kuchh bani Qureza us se alag qarar diye gaey they kyonke wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki panah mein aagey they. isliye aap ne unhein panah di aur unhon-ne Islam qabool kar liya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina ke tamam yahudiyon ko jilaa watan kar diya tha. banu- qainuqaa' ko bhi jo Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ka qabila tha, yahood bani Harisa ko aur Madina ke tamam yahudiyon ko ."
4029,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney kaha, ''sura Hashr'' to unhon-ne kaha ke usey ''Sura Nazeer'' kaho (kyonke ye sura banu-Nazeer hi ke barey mein nazil hui hai) is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Hushaim se abu-Bashar ne ki hai."
4030,Ansari sahaba ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye kuchh khajoor ke darakht makhsoos rakhtey they (taake unka phal aap ki khidmat mein bhej diya jaey) lekin jab Allah Taala ne banu-Quraiza aur banu- nazeer par fateh ata farmai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke phal wapas farma diya kartey they.
4031,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bani Nazir ke khajooron ke baghaat jalwaa diye they aur unke darakhton ko katwaa diya tha. ye baghaat maqam buwera mein they. is par ye aayat nazil huii ما قطعتم من لينة أو تركتموها قائمة على أصولها فبإذن الله ''jo darakht tum ne kaat diye hain ya jinhein tum ne chhod diya hai ke wo apne jadon par khadey rahen to ye Allah ke hukm se hua hai.''
4032,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu- nazeer ke baghaat jalwaa diye they. unhon-ne kaha ke Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne usi ke mutaalliq ye sher kaha tha ( tarjama ) ''banu-Luii ( Quraish (ke sardaaron ne badi aasani ke sath bardasht kar liya. maqam buwera mein us aag ko jo phail rahi thii.'' bayaan kya ke phir iska jawab Abu-Sufiyan bin-Haaris ne in ashaar mein diyaa. ''khudaa karey ke Madina mein hamesha yun hi aag lagti rahe aur uske aas-paas mein yun hi sholey uthtey rahen. tumhen jald hi malum ho jaeyga ke ham mein se kon is maqam buwera se door hai aur tumhen malum ho jaeyga ke kis ki zameen ko nuqsan pahunchtaa hai.''
4033,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bulaya tha. (wo bhi ameerul-momineen) ki khidmat mein maujood they ke ameerul-momineen ke chaukidar Yarfaa aaey aur arz kya ke Usman-bin-Affan aur Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf, Zubair-bin-Awaam aur Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) andar aana chahtey hain. kya aap ki taraf se unhein ijazat hai? ameerul-momineen ne farmaya ke haan, unhein andar bula lo. thodi der baad Yarfaa phir aaey aur arz kya Abbas aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi ijazat chahtey hain kya unhein andar aaney ki ijazat hai? aap ne farmaya ke haan, jab ye bhi donon buzurg andar tashrif ley aaey to Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, ameerul-momineen ! mera aur in ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ka faisla kar dijiye. wo donon us jaaidaad ke barey mein jhagad rahe they jo Allah Taala ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maal banu- nazeer se faiy ke taur par di thi. us mauqe par Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik doosrey ko sakht sust kaha aur aik doosrey par tanqeed ki to haaziriin boley, ameerul-momineen ! aap un donon buzurgon ka faisla kar dein taake donon mein koi jhagdaa na rahe. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, jaldi na keejiye. mein aap logon se us Allah ka waasta de kar poochhta hun jiske hukm se aasman w zameen qaaim hain, kya aapko malum hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke ham anbiya ki wiraasat taqseem nahi hoti jo kuchh ham chhod jayen wo sadqa hota hai aur us se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad khud apni zaat se thi? haaziriin boley ke ji haan, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) Abbas aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur unse kaha, main aap donon se bhi Allah ka waasta de kar poochhta hun. kya aapko bhi malum hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye hadis irshad farmai thi? un donon buzurgon ne bhi jawab haan mein diya. iske baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, phir main aap logon se us maamle par guftgu karta hun. Allah Taala ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us maale-faiy mein se (jo banu- nazeer se mila tha) aapko khas taur par ata farma diya tha. Allah Taala ne iske mutaalliq farmaya hai ke '' banu-nazeer ke maalon se jo Allah ne apne rasool ko diya hai to tum ne uske liye ghodey aur oont nahi daudaaey . (yani jang nahi ki) Allah Taala ka irshad '' qadeer '' tak. to ye maal khas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye tha lekin Allah ki qasm ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen nazar andaz karke apne liye usey makhsoos nahi farmaya tha na tum par apni zaat ko tarjeeh di thi. pahley us maal mein se tumhen diya aur tum mein uski taqseem ki aur aakhir us faiy mein se ye jaaidaad bach gaee. to aap apni paak beeviyon ka saalaana kharch bhi usi mein se nikaaltey they aur jo kuchh usmein se baqi bachta usey aap Allah Taala ke rastey mein kharch kartey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni zindagi mein ye jaaidaad unhi raston mein kharch ki. phir jab aap ki wafat ho gaee to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khaleefa bana diya gaya hai. isliye unhon-ne usey apne qabze mein ley liya aur usey unhi maamlon mein kharch kartey rahe jis main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kharch kya kartey they aur aap log yahin maujood they. iske baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya, aap logon ko malum hai ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi wahi tariqa ikhtiyar kya, jaisa ke aap logon ko bhi iska iqrar hai aur Allah ki qasm ke wo apne us tarze-amal mein sachchey, mukhlis, sahi rastey par aur haq ki pairwi karne waley they. phir Allah Taala ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi utha liya, isliye maine kaha ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka khaleefa banaya gaya hai. chunanche main us jaaidaad par apni khilafat ke 2 saalon se qaabiz hun aur usey unhiin mamalon mein kharch karta hun jis mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kya tha aur Allah Taala janta hai ke main bhi apne tarze-amal mein sachchaa, mukhlis, sahi rastey par aur haq ki pairwi karne wala hun. phir aap donon mere paas aaey hain. aap donon aik hi hain aur aap ka mamla bhi aik hai. phir aap mere paas aaey. aap ki murad Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se thi. to maine aap donon ke samney ye baat saaf keh di thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma gaey they ke ''hamaaraa tarka taqseem nahi hota. ham jo kuchh chhod jayen wo sadqa hai.'' phir jab mere dil mein aaya ke wo jaaidaad bataur intizam mein aap donon ko de dun to maine aap se kaha ke agar aap chaahein to main ye jaaidaad aapko de sakta hun. lekin shart ye hai ke Allah Taala ke samney kiye huey ahad ki tamam zimme daariyon ko aap pura karein. aap logon ko malum hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur khud maine, jab se main khaleefa bana hun. us jaaidaad ke maamle mein kis tarze-amal ko ikhtiyar kya hua hai. agar ye shart aapko manzoor na ho to phir mujh se iske barey mein aap log baat na karein. aap logon ne is par kaha ke theek hai. aap isi shart par wo jaaidaad hamarey hawale kar dein. chunanche maine usey aap logon ke hawale kar diya. kya aap hazraat iske siwa koi aur faisla is silsiley mein mujh se karwaanaa chahtey hain? us Allah ki qasam! jiske hukm se aasman w zameen qaaim hain, qiyamat tak main iske siwa koi aur faisla nahi kar sakta. agar aap log (shart ke mutabiq iske intizam se) aajiz hain to wo jaaidaad mujhey wapas kar dein main khud uska intizam karunga."
4034,"Malik bin Aus ne ye riwayat tum se sahi bayan ki hai. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak biwi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon ne Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bheja aur unse darkhaast ki ke Allah Taala ne jo faiy apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di thi usmein se unke hissey diye jaaein, lekin maine unhein rokaa aur unse kaha tum Allah se nahi dartii ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud nahi farmaya tha ke hamara tarka taqseem nahi hotaa? ham jo kuchh chhod jayen wo sadqa hota hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ishara us irshad mein khud apni zaat ki taraf tha. albatta aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us jaaidaad mein se poori zindagi (unki zarooriyaat ke liye) milta rahega. jab maine paak beeviyon ko ye hadis sunai to unhon-ne bhi apna khayal badal diya. Urwa ne kaha ke yahi wo sadqa hai jiska intizam pahley Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath mein tha. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko iske intizam mein Sharik nahi kya tha balke khud iska intizam kartey they (aur jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey kharch kya tha, isi tarah unhiin raston mein wo bhi kharch kartey they) iske baad wo sadqa Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke intizam mein aa gaya tha. phir Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke intizam mein raha. phir janab Ali-bin Husain aur Hasan-bin-Hasan ke intizam mein aa gaya tha aur ye haq hai ke ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sadqa tha."
4035,"Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zameen jo fidak mein thi aur jo khaibar mein aapko hissey mila tha, usmein se apni meeraas ka mutalba kya."
4036,"maine khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke hamara tarka taqseem nahi hota. jo kuchh ham chhod jayen wo sadqa hai. albatta aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us jaaidaad mein se kharch zaroor milta rahega aur Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qaraabat daaron ke sath umda mamla karna mujhey khud apne qaraabat daaron ke sath husne-muaamlat se zyada azeez hai."
4037,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Kab-bin-Ashraf ka kaam kon tamam karega? wo Allah aur uske rasool ko bahut sataa raha hai.'' is par Muhammad-bin-Muslima Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya aap ijazat dengey ke main usey qatl kar aaoon ? aap ne farmaya '' haan mujh ko ye pasand hai.'' unhon-ne arz kya, phir aap mujhey ijazat inayat farmaein ke main us se kuchh baatein kahun aap ne unhein ijazat de di. ab Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) Kab-bin-Ashraf ke paas aaey aur us se kaha, ye shakhs ( ishara Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf tha) ham se sadqa mangta rehta hai aur us ne hamein thakaa maara hai. isliye main tum se qarz leney aaya hun. is par Kab ne kaha, abhi aagey dekhnaa , khuda ki qasam ! bilkul uktaa jaogey. Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, chunkey ham ne bhi ab unki ittaba (pairvi) kar li hai. isliye jab tak ye na khul jaey ke unka anjam kya hota hai, unhein chhodnaa bhi munasib nahi. tum se aik wasq ya ( rawi ne bayan kya ke) 2 wasq ghalla qarz leney aaya hun aur ham se Amr-bin-Dinar ne ye hadis kai baar bayan ki lekin aik wasq ya 2 wasq ghalley ka koi zikr nahi kya. maine unse kaha ke hadis mein aik ya 2 wasq ka zikr hai? unhon-ne kaha ke mera bhi khayal hai ke hadis mein aik ya 2 wasq ka zikr aaya hai. Kab-bin-Ashraf ne kaha, haan, mere paas kuchh girwii rakh do. unhon-ne poochha, girwii main tum kya chahtey ho? us ne kaha, apni aurton ko rakh do. unhon-ne kaha ke tum Arab ke bahut khoobsurat mard ho. ham tumharey paas apni auratein kis tarah girwii rakh saktey hain. usney kaha, phir apne bachchon ko girwii rakh do. unhon-ne kaha, ham bachchon ko kis tarah girwii rakh saktey hain. kal unhein isi par gaaliyaan di jaeyngi ke aik ya 2 wasq ghalley par usey rahan rakh diya gaya tha, ye to badi be ghairti hogi. albatta ham tumharey paas apne ( اللأمة ( girwii rakh saktey hain. Sufiyan ne kaha ke murad us se hathiyar they Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se dobara milney ka wada kya aur raat ke waqt uske yahan aaey. unke sath abu-Naeyla bhi maujood they wo Kab-bin-Ashraf ke dudh-sharik bhai they. phir iske qil'e ke paas ja kar unhon-ne awaz di. wo bahar aaney laga to uski biwi ne kaha ke us waqt ( itni raat gaey ( kahan bahar ja rahe ho? us ne kaha, wo to Muhammad-bin-Muslima aur mera bhai abu-Naeyla hai. Amr ke siwa (doosrey rawi ( ne bayan kya ke uski biwi ne us se kaha tha ke mujhey to ye awaz aisi lagti hai jaisey us se khoon tapak raha ho. Kab ne jawab diya ke mere bhai Muhammad-bin-Muslima aur mere dudh-sharik bhai abu-Naeyla hain. sharif ko agar raat mein bhi neza bazi ke liye bulaya jaey to wo nikal padta hai. rawi ne bayan kya ke jab Muhammad-bin-Muslima andar gaey to unke sath 2 aadmi aur they. Sufiyan se puchha gaya ke kya Amr-bin-Dinar ne unke naam bhi liye they? unhon-ne bataya ke kuchh ka naam liya tha. Amr ne bayan kya ke wo aaey to unke sath 2 aadmi aur they aur Amr-bin-Dinar ke siwa ( rawi ne) abu-Abas bin jabr, Haaris-bin-Aos aur Ibaad-bin-Bishr naam bataatey they. Amr ne bayan kya ke wo apne sath 2 aadmiyon ko laey they aur unhein ye hidayat ki thi ke jab Kab aaey to main iske ( sar ke) baal hath mein ley loonga aur usey soonghney lagoonga. jab tumhen andaza ho jaey ke maine uska sar poori tarah apne qabze mein ley liya hai to phir tum taiyaar ho jana aur usey qatl kar daalnaa . Amr ne aik martaba bayan kya ke phir main uska sar soonghoonga. aakhir Kab chadar lapetey huey bahar aaya. uske jism se khushbu phooti padti thi Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, aaj se zyada umda khushbu maine kabhi nahi soonghii thi. Amr ke siwa (doosrey raawii) ne bayan kya ke Kab is par bola, mere paas Arab ki wo aurat hai jo har waqt atr mein basii rehti hai aur husno-jamaal mein bhi uski koi misal nahi. Amr ne bayan kya ke Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha, kya tumharey sar ko soonghney ki mujhey ijazat hai? us ne kaha, soongh saktey ho. rawi ne bayan kya ke Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne uska sar soonghaa aur unke baad unke sathiyon ne bhi soonghaa. phir unhon-ne kaha, kya dobara soonghney ki ijazat hai? us ne is martaba bhi ijazat de di. phir jab Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey poori tarah apne qaabu mein kar liya to apne sathiyon ko ishara kya ke taiyaar ho jao. chunanche unhon-ne usey qatl kar diya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar uski itlaa di."
4038,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand aadmiyon ko abu-Raafe ke paas bheja (minjumla unke) Abdullaah-bin-Ateek raat ko us ghar mein ghusey, wo so raha tha. usey qatl kya."
4039,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Raafe Yahudi (ke qatl) ke liye chand Ansari sahaba ko bheja aur Abdullaah-bin-Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) ko unka ameer banaya. ye abu-Raafe Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko takleef diya karta tha aur aap ke dushmanon ki madad kya karta tha. hijaaz mein iska aik qil'a tha aur wahin wo raha karta tha. jab uske qile' ke qareeb ye pahunchey to suraj ghurub ho chuka tha aur log apne maweshii lekar (apne gharon ko) wapas ho chukey they. Abdullaah-bin-Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne sathiyon se kaha ke tum log yahin thahrey raho main (is qil'a par) ja raha hun aur darbaan par koi tadbeer karunga. taake main andar janey mein kaamyaab ho jaun. chunanche wo (qile ke paas) aaey aur darwazey ke qareeb pahunch kar unhon-ne khud ko apne kapdon mein is tarah chipa liya jaisey koi qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) kar raha ho. qile ke tamam aadmi andar dakhil ho chukey they. darbaan ne awaz di, aey Allah ke bandey ! agar andar aana hai to jald aa jaa, main ab darwaza band kar doonga. (Abdullaah-bin-Ateek (rz) ne kaha ( chunanche main bhi andar chala gaya aur chhup kar uski kaarrwaaii dekhney laga. jab sab log andar aagey to usne darwaza band kya aur kunjiyon ka guchchaa aik khoontii par latkaa diya. unhon-ne bayan kya ke ab main un kunjiyon ki taraf badha aur maine unhein ley liya, phir maine qile ka darwaza khol liya. abu-Raafe ke paas raat ke waqt daastanein bayan ki ja rahi thin aur wo apne khas baalaa-khaaney mein tha. jab daastaan bhale hi uske yahan se uth kar chaley gaey to main us kamrey ki taraf chadhney laga. us arse mein, main jitney darwazey us tak pahunchne ke liye kholtaa tha unhein andar se band karta jata tha. mera matlab ye tha ke agar qile walon ko mere mutaalliq ilm bhi ho jaey to us waqt tak ye log mere paas na pahunch sakein jab tak main usey qatl na kar loon. aakhir mein uske qareeb pahunch gaya. us waqt wo aik andherey kamrey main apne baal bachchon ke sath ( so raha ( tha mujhey kuchh andaza nahi ho saka ke wo kahan hai. isliye maine awaz di, ya abaa Raafe ? wo bola kon hai? ab maine awaz ki taraf badh kar talwaar ki aik zarb lagaaii. us waqt mera dil dhak-dhak kar raha tha. yahi wjah hui ke main uska kaam tamam nahi kar saka. wo cheekhaa to main kamrey se bahar nikal aaya aur thodi der tak bahar hi thehra raha. phir dobara andar gaya aur maine awaz badal kar poochha, abu-Raafea'! ye awaz kaisi thi? wo bola teri maan ghaarat ho. abhi abhii mujh par kisi ne talwaar se hamla kya hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir (aawaaz ki taraf badh kar) maine talwaar ki aik zarb aur lagaaii. unhon-ne bayan kya ke agarche main usey zakhmi to bahut kar chuka tha lekin wo abhi maraa nahi tha. isliye maine talwaar ki nauk uske pet par rakh kar dabaai jo uski peeth tak pahunch gaee. mujhey ab yaqin ho gaya ke main usey qatl kar chuka hun. chunanche maine darwazey eik-eik karke kholney shuru kiye. aakhir mein aik zeeney par pahuncha. main ye samjha ke zameen tak main pahunch chuka hun (lekin abhi main pahuncha na tha) isliye maine is par paon rakh diya aur nichey gir padaa. chaandnii raat thi. is tarah gir padney se meri pindlii toot gaee. maine usey apne amaame se baandh liya aur aa kar darwazey par baith gaya. maine ye irada kar liya tha ke yahan se us waqt tak nahi jaaunga jab tak ye na malum kar loon ke aaya mein usey qatl kar chuka hun ya nahi? jab murgh ne awaz di to usi waqt qile ki faseel par aik pukarney waley ne khadey ho kar pukara ke main ahale-hijaaz ke taajir abu-Raafe ki maut ka elaan karta hun. main apne sathiyon ke paas aaya aur unse kaha ke chalney ki jaldi karo. Allah Taala ne abu-Raafe ko qatl kara diya. chunanche main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aapko uski itlaa di. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apna paon phailaao maine paon phailaayaa to aap ne is par apna hath phera aur paon utnaa achchha ho gaya jaisey kabhi usmein mujh ko koi takleef hui hi na thi."
4040,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdullaah-bin-Ateek aur Abdullah-bin Utba (Raziallahu anhu) ko chand sahaba ke sath abu-Raafe (ke qatl (ke liye bhejaa. ye log rawaana huey jab uske qile ke nazdeek pahunchey to Abdullaah-bin-Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne sathiyon se kaha ke tum log yahin thahar jao pahley main jata hun, dekhun soorate-haal kya hai. Abdullaah-bin-Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke (qile ke qareeb pahunch kar) main andar janey ke liye tadbeerein karne laga. ittifaq se qile ka aik gadhaa gum tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke us gadhey ko talash karne ke liye qile waley roshni lekar bahar nikley. bayan kya ke main dara ke kahin mujhey koi pehchan na ley. isliye maine apna sar dhak liya jaisey koi qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) kar raha hai. iske baad darbaan ne awaz di ke us se pahley ke main darwaza band kar loon jisey qile ke andar dakhil hona hai wo jaldi aa jaey. main (ne mauqa ghaneemat samjha aur) andar dakhil ho gaya aur qile ke darwazey ke paas hi jahan gadhey baandhey jatey they wahin chhup gaya. qile walon ne abu-Raafe ke sath khana khaya aur phir usey qissey sunatey rahe. aakhir kuchh raat gaey wo sab qile ke andar hi apne apney gharon mein wapas aa gaey. ab sannaataa chhaa chuka tha aur kahin koi harkat nahi hoti thi. isliye main us taweela se bahar niklaa. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine pahley hi dekh liya tha ke darbaan ne chaabii aik taaq mein rakhi hai. maine pahley chaabii apne qabze mein ley li aur phir sabse pahley qile ka darwaza khola . bayan kya ke maine ye sochaa tha ke agar qile walon ko mera ilm ho gaya to main badi aasani ke sath bhag sakoonga. iske baad maine unke kamron ke darwazey kholney shuru kiye aur unhein andar se band karta jata tha. ab main zeenon se abu-Raafe ke baalaakhaanon tak pahunch chuka tha. uske kamre mein andhera tha. uska charagh bujhaa diya gaya tha. main ye nahi andaza kar paya tha ke abu-Raafe kahan hai. isliye maine awaz di. aey abu-Raafe ! is par wo bola ke kon hai? unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir awaz ki taraf main badha aur maine talwaar se is par hamla kya. wo chillaaney laga lekin ye waar ochhaa padaa tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir dobara main uske qareeb pahuncha, maano main uski madad ko aaya hun. maine awaz badal kar poochha. abu-Raafe kya baat pesh aai hai? usne kaha teri maan ghaarat ho, abhi koi shakhs mere kamrey mein aa gaya aur us ne talwaar se mujh par hamla kya hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke is martaba phir maine uski awaz ki taraf badh kar dobara hamla kya. is hamle mein bhi wo qatl, na ho saka. phir wo chillaaney laga aur uski biwi bhi uth gaee (aur chillaaney lagii). unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir main bazahir madadgaar bin kar pahuncha aur maine apni awaz badal li. us waqt wo chit leta hua tha. maine apni talwaar uske pet par rakh kar zor se usey dabaayaa. aakhir jab maine haddi tootney ki awaz sun li to main wahan se nikla, bahut ghabraayaa hua. ab zeene par aa chuka tha. main utarnaa chahta tha ke nichey gir padaa. jis se mera paon toot gaya. maine is par patti baandhii aur langdaatey huey apne sathiyon ke paas pahuncha. maine unse kaha ke tum log jao aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khushkhabri sunao. main to yahan se us waqt tak nahi hatoonga jab tak ke uski maut ka elaan na sun loon. chunanche subah ke waqt maut ka elaan karne wala (qile ki faseel par) chadhaa aur us ne elaan kya ke abu-Raafe ki maut waaqe ho gaee hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir main chalney ke liye uthaa, mujhey (kaamyaabii ki khushkhabri mein) koi takleef malum nahi hoti thi. is se pahley ke mere sathi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchein, maine apne sathiyon ko pa liya to maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khushkhabri sunai."
4041,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par farmaya ''ye Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) hain, hathiyar band, apne ghodey ki lagaam thaamey huey.''"
4042,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aath (8) saal baad yani aathwein baras mein Uhud ki jang ke shohdaa par namaaze-janaaza ada ki. jaisey aap zindon aur mardon sabse rukhsat ho rahe hun. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif laey aur farmaya ''main tum se aagey-aagey hun, main tum par gawah rahunga aur mujh se (qiyamat ke din) tumhari mulaqat hauz ( kausar ( par hogi. us waqt bhi main apni is jagah se hauz (kausar) ko dekh raha hun. tumharey barey mein mujhey iska koi khatrah nahi hai ke tum shirk karogey, haan main tumharey barey mein duniya se darta hun ke tum kahin duniya ke liye aapas mein muqaabla na karne lago.'' Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mere liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye aakhiri deedaar tha jo mujh ko naseeb hua."
4043,"jange-Uhud ke mauqe par jab mushrekeen se muqable ke liye ham pahunchey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teerandaazon ka aik dasta Abdullaah-bin-Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) ki ma-tehti main ( pahaadii par) muqarrar farmaya tha aur unhein ye hukm diya tha ke tum apni jagah se na hatna , us waqt bhi jab tum log dekh lo ke ham un par ghalib aagey hain phir bhi yahan se na hatna aur us waqt bhi jab dekh lo ke wo ham par ghalib aa gaey, tum log hamari madad ke liye na aana . phir jab hamari mudbhed kuffaar se hui to unmein bhagdad mach gaee. maine dekha ke unki auratein pahaadiyon par badi tezi ke sath bhaagii ja rahi thin, pindliyon se uper kapdey uthaey huey, jis se unke paazeb dikhai de rahe they. Abdullaah-bin-Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke) teerandaaz ( sathi kehney lagey ke ghaneemat ghaneemat . is par Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne takeed ki thi ke apni jagah se na hatna (is liye tum log maale-ghanimat lootney na jaao) lekin unke sathiyon ne unka hukm manney se inkar kar diya. unki us hukm ki nafarmani ke nateejey mein musalmanon ko haar hui aur 70 musalman Shahid ho gaey. iske baad Abu-Sufiyan ne pahaadii par se awaz di, kya tumharey sath Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maujood hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi jawab na de, phir unhon-ne poochha, kya tumharey sath ibn-abii-Qahaafa maujood hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske jawab ki bhi manaahii farma di. unhon-ne poochha, kya tumharey sath ibne-khattaab maujood hain? iske baad wo kehney lagey ke ye sab qatl kar diye gaey. agar zinda hotey to jawab detey. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) be qaabu ho gaey aur farmaya : Allah ke dushman to jhoota hai. Allah ne abhi unhein tumhen zaleel karne liye baqi rakha hai. Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha, hubal (eik but ( buland rahe. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iska jawab do. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke ham kya jawab dein ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kaho , Allah sabse buland aur buzurg w bartar hai. Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha, hamarey paas uzzaa (but) hai aur tumharey paas koi uzzaa nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iska jawab do. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, kya jawab dein ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kaho , Allah hamara haami aur madadgaar hai aur tumhara koi haami nahi. Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha, aaj ka din badr ke din ka badla hai aur ladai ki misal dol ki hoti hai. ( kabhi hamarey hath main aur kabhi tumharey hath mein) tum apne maqtooleen mein kuchh laashon ka musla kya hua paogey, maine iska hukm nahi diya tha lekin mujhey bura nahi malum hua."
4044,kuchh sahaba ne Uhud ki jang ki subah ko sharab pi (jo abhi haram nahi hui thi) aur phir shahadat ki maut naseeb hui.
4045,"(unke waalid) Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas khana laya gaya aur wo rozey se they, to unhon-ne kaha, Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu)) ahad ki jang mein) Shahid kar diye gaey, wo mujh se afzal aur behtar they lekin unhein jis chadar ka kafan diya gaya (wo itni chhoti thi ke) agar us se unka sar chhipaayaa jata to paon khul jatey aur paon chhipaaey jatey to sar khul jata tha. mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne kaha aur Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) bhi (usi jang mein) Shahid kiye gaey, wo mujh se behtar aur afzal they. phir jaisa ke tum dekh rahe ho, hamarey liye duniya mein kushadgi di gaee ya unhon-ne ye kaha ke phir jaisa ke tum dekhtey ho, hamein duniya di gaee. hamein to uska dar hai ke kahin yahi hamari nekiyon ka badla na ho jo isi duniya mein hamein diya ja raha hai. iske baad aap roey ke khana na kha sakey."
4046,aik sahabi ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par puchha : ya Rasulullah ! agar main qatl kar diya gaya to main kahan jaaunga ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jannat mein. unhon-ne khajoor phenk di jo unke hath mein thi aur ladney lagey yahan tak ke Shahid ho gaey.
4047,"ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hijrat ki thi. hamara maqsad sirf Allah ki raza thi. iska sawab Allah ke zimmey tha. phir ham mein se kuchh log to wo they jo guzar gaey aur koi ajr unhon-ne is duniya mein nahi dekha, unhein main se Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. Uhud ki ladai mein unhon-ne shahadat paai thi. aik dhaarii daar chadar ke siwa aur koi cheez unke paas nahi thi (aur wahi unka kafan bani ( jab ham us se unka sar chhipaatey to paon khul jatey aur paon chhipaatey to sar khul jata. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sar chadar se chipa 2 aur paon par izkhir ghaas daal do. ya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye alfaz farmaai they ke (ألقوا على رجله من الإذخر) bajaaey (اجعلوا على رجله الإذخر) ke aur ham kuchh wo they jinhein unke us amal ka badla (usi duniya mein) mil raha hai aur wo us se fayda utha rahe hain."
4048,"unke chacha ( Anas-bin-Nazar ( badr ki ladai mein Sharik na ho sakey they, phir unhon-ne kaha ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath pehli hi ladai mein ghair hazir raha. agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Allah Taala ne mujhey kisi aur ladai mein shirkat ka mauqa diya to Allah dekhega ke main kitni be-jigrii se ladtaa hun. phir Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par jab musalmanon ki jamat mein afraa-tafree paida ho gaee to unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ! musalmanon ne aaj jo kuchh kya main terey huzoor mein uske liye ma'zirat chaata hun aur mushrekeen ne jo kuchh kya main terey huzoor mein us se apni bezaarii zahir karta hun. phir wo apni talwaar lekar aagey badhey . rastey mein Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat hui to unhon-ne unse kaha, Sad ! kahan ja rahe ho? main to Uhud pahaadii ke daman mein jannat ki khushbu soongh raha hun. iske baad wo aagey badhey aur Shahid kar diye gaey. unki laash pahchaanii nahi ja rahi thi. aakhir unki behan ne aik til ya unki ungliyon ke por se unki laash ko pehchaana . unko assii ( 80 ( se zyada zakhm bhaale aur talwaar aur teeron ke lagey they."
4049,jab ham Quran Majeed ko likhney lagey to mujhey sura Ahzaab ki aik aayat ( likhi hui ( nahi mili . maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski tilawat kartey bahut baar suna tha. phir jab ham ne uski talash ki to wo aayat Khuzaima bin Sabit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas hamein mili ( aayat ye thii) من المؤمنين رجال صدقوا ما عاهدوا الله عليه فمنهم من قضى نحبه ومنهم من ينتظرphir ham ne us aayat ko uski sura mein Quran Majeed mein mila diya.
4050,"unhon-ne bayan kya, jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Uhud ki jang ke liye nikley to kuchh log jo aap ke sath they (munaafeqeen, bahana bana kar) wapas lot gaey. phir sahaba ki un wapas hone-waale munaafeqeen ke barey mein 2 raayein ho gain thin. aik jamat to kehti thi hamein pahley unse jang karni chahiye aur dusri jamat kehti thi ke unse hamein jang na karni chahiye is par aayat nazil huii ( فما لكم في المنافقين فئتين والله أركسهم بما كسبوا‏ ) ''pas tumhen kya ho gaya hai ke munaafeqeen ke barey mein tumhari 2 jamatein ho gain hain, halanke Allah Taala ne unki bad-aamaali ki wjah se unhein kufr ki taraf lota diya hai.'' aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Madina ''tayiba'' hai, sarkashon ko ye is tarah apne se door kar deta hai jaisey aag ki bhattii chandi ke mail kuchail ko door kar deti hai."
4051,"ye aayat hamarey barey mein nazil hui thi ( إذ همت طائفتان منكم أن تفشلا‏ ( ) Aale-Imran : 122 ( yani bani Harisa aur bani Salma ke barey mein. meri khahish nahi hai ke ye aayat nazil na hoti, jabke Allah aagey farma raha hai) والله وليهما‏ ( ''aur Allah un donon jamaton ka madadgaar tha.''"
4052,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se malum farmaya ''Jaabir ! kya nikah kar liya ?'' maine arz kya, ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' kunwari se ya bewa se ?'' maine arz kya ke bewa se. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi kunwari ladki se kyon na kiya? jo tumharey sath khelaa karti.'' maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mere walid Uhud ki ladai mein Shahid ho gaey. nau (9) ladkiyan chhodein. to meri nau (9) bahnein maujood hain. isi liye maine munasib nahi khayal kya ke unhiin jaisi naa tajribe kaar ladki unke paas la kar bitha dun, balke aik aisi aurat laaun jo unki dekh bhaal kar sakey aur unki safaaii-suthraaii ka khayal rakhey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ne achchha kya."
4053,"unke walid ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) Uhud ki ladai mein Shahid ho gaey they aur qarz chhod gaey they aur chh ladkiyan bhii. jab darakhton se khajoor utaarey janey ka waqt qareeb aaya to unhon-ne bayan kya ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke jaisa ke aap ke ilm mein hai, mere walid sahib Uhud ki ladai mein Shahid ho gaey aur qarz chhod gaey hain, main chahta tha ke qarz-khaah aapko dekh lein (aur kuchh narmii bartein (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jao aur har qism ki khajoor ka alag alag dher laga lo. maine hukm ke mutabiq amal kya aur phir aapko bulaney gaya. jab qarz-khaahon ne aapko dekha to jaisey us waqt mujh par aur zyada bhadak uthey. (kyonke wo Yahudi they) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab unka ye tarze-amal dekha to aap pahley sabse badey dher ke charon taraf teen martaba ghoomey . iske baad is par baith gaey aur farmaya apne qarz-khaahon ko bula laao. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) barabar unhein naap kar detey rahe yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne mere walid ki taraf se unki saari amanat ada kar di. main is par khush tha ke Allah Taala mere walid ki amanat ada kara de aur main apni bahnon ke liye aik khajoor bhi na ley jaun lekin Allah Taala ne tamam doosrey dher bacha diye balke us dher ko bhi jab dekha jis par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey huey they ke jaisey usmein se aik khajoor ka daana bhi kam nahi hua."
4054,Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aur aap ke sath 2 aur ashaab (yani Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aur Mikaail (Alaihissalam) insani sura mein) aaey huey they. wo aapko apni hifazat mein lekar kuffaar se badi sakhti se lad rahe they. unke jism par safaid kapdey they. maine unhein na us se pahley kabhi dekha tha aur na uske baad kabhi dekha.
4055,"maine Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne tarkash ke teer mujhey nikal kar diye aur farmaya ke khub teer barsaey jaa. mere maan-baap tum par fidaa hon."
4056,Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( meri himmat afzaai ke liye) apne walid aur walida donon ko jama farmaya ke mere maan-baap tum par fidaa hon.
4057,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par) meri himmat badhaney ke liye) apne walid aur walida donon ko jama farmaya, unki murad aap ke us irshad se thi jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt farmaya tha jab wo jang kar rahe they ke mere maan-baap tum par fidaa hon."
4058,Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nahi suna ke aap uske liye dua mein maan-baap donon ko is tarah jama kar rahe hon.
4059,"Sad bin Malik ke siwa maine aur kisi ke liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne waalidain ka aik sath zikr kartey nahi suna, maine khud suna ke Uhud ke din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke Sad ! khub teer barsaao. mere maan-baap tum par qurbaan hon."
4060,un jangon mein se jin main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuffaar se qitaal kya. kuchh jange-Uhud mein aik mauqe par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Talha aur Sad ke siwa aur koi baqi nahi reh gaya tha. abu-Usman ne ye baat Talha aur Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki thi.
4061,un jangon mein se jin main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuffaar se qitaal kya. kuchh jange-Uhud mein aik mauqe par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Talha aur Sad ke siwa aur koi baqi nahi reh gaya tha. abu-Usman ne ye baat Talha aur Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki thii.
4062,"main, Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf , Talha bin Ubaidullah , Miqdaad-bin-Aswad aur Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ki sohbat mein raha hun lekin maine un hazraat mein se kisi ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se koi hadis bayan kartey nahi suna. sirf Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se Uhud ki jang ke mutaalliq hadis suni thi."
4063,maine Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka wo hath dekha jo shal ho chuka tha. us hath se unhon-ne Uhud ki jang ke din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hifazat ki thi.
4064,"Uhud ki jang mein jab musalman Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se muntashir ho kar paspaa ho gaey to Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki apne chamdey ki dhaal se hifazat kar rahe they. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) badey teerandaaz they aur kamaan khub kheench kar teer chillaayaa kartey they. us din unhon-ne 2 ya teen kamaanein tod di thin. musalmanon mein se koi agar teer ka tarkash liye guzarta to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unse farmatey ye teer abu-Talha ke liye yahin rakhtey jao . Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mushrekeen ko dekhney ke liye sar utha kar jhaanktey to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) arz kartey : mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hon, sar Mubarak uper na uthaaiye kahin aisa na ho ke idhar se koi teer aapko lag jaey. meri gardan aap se pahley hai aur maine dekha ke jang main Aaisha binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) aur) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida ( Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) apne kapdey uthaey huey hain ke unki pindliyaan nazar aa rahi thin aur mishkeezey apni peethon par liye daud rahi hain aur uska pani zakhmi musalmanon ko pilaa rahi hain phir (jab iska pani khatm ho jata hai) to wapas aati hain aur mashk bhar kar phir ley jati hain aur musalmanon ko pilaatii hain. us din abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath se 2 ya teen martaba talwaar gir gaee thi."
4065,"shuru jange-Uhud mein pahley mushrekeen shikast kha gaey they lekin iblees , Allah ki is par laanat ho, dhokaa dene ke liye pukarney laga. aey ibaadullaah! ( musalmaanon ! ( apne peechhey walon se khabardaar ho jao. is par aagey jo musalman they wo lot padey aur apne peechhey walon se bhid gaey. Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo dekha to unke walid Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) unhiin mein hain ( jinhein musalman apna dushman mushrik samajh kar mar rahe they). wo kehney lagey musalmaanon ! ye to mere walid hain, mere walid . Urwa ne kaha, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, to Allah ki qism unhon-ne unko us waqt tak nahi chhoda jab tak qatl na kar liya. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne sirf itna kaha ke Allah musalmanon ki ghalati maaf kare. Urwa ne bayan kya ke iske baad Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) barabar maghfirat ki dua kartey rahe yahan tak ke wo Allah se ja miley. ( بصرت ( yani main dil ki aankhon se kaam ko samajhta hun aur) أبصرت ( aankhon se dekhney ke liye istemal hota hai. ye bhi kaha gaya hai ke) بصرت (aur ( أبصرت (ke aik hi mana hain. ( بصرت ( dil ki aankhon se dekhnaa aur) أبصرت ( zahir ki aankhon se dekhnaa murad hai."
4066,"aik sahib Baitullah ke Haj ke liye aaey they. dekha ke kuchh log baithey huey hain. puchha ke ye baithey huey kon log hain? logon ne bataya ke ye Quraish hain. puchha ke unmein Shekh kon hain? bataya ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) . wo sahib ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur unse kaha ke main aap se aik baat poochhta hun. aap mujh se waaqiaat ( sahi ( bayan kar dijiye. is ghar ki hurmat ki qism de kar main aap se poochhta hun. kya aapko malum hai ke Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par raahe-faraar ikhtiyar ki thi? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, sahi hai. unhon-ne puchha aapko ye bhi malum hai Usman (Raziallahu anhu) badr ki ladai mein Sharik nahi they? kaha ke haan, ye bhi hua tha. unhon-ne puchha aur aapko ye bhi malum hai ke wo (baite-rizwan (Suleh Hudaibiya ( mein bhi peechhey reh gaey they aur hazir na ho sakey they? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, ye bhi sahi hai. is par un sahib ne ( maarey khushi ke) Allahu-akbar kaha lekin ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, yahan aao main tumhen bataaoonga aur jo sawalat tum ne kiye hain unki main tumharey samney tafseel bayan kar doonga . Uhud ki ladai mein faraar se mutaalliq jo tum ne kaha to main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala ne unki ghalati maaf kar di hai. badr ki ladai mein unke na honey ke mutaalliq jo tum ne kaha to uski wjah ye thi. ke unke nikah mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi (Ruqaiya (Raziallahu anhu)) thin aur wo bimar thin. aap ne farmaya tha ke tumhen us shakhs ke barabar sawab milega jo badr ki ladai mein Sharik hoga aur usi ke barabar maale-ghanimat se hissey bhi milega. (baite-rizwan mein unke Sharik na honey ka jahan tak sawal hai to Makka ki wadi mein Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se zyada koi shakhs har dil azeez hota to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke bajaey usi ko bhejtey . isliye Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko wahan bhejna padaa aur (baite-rizwan us waqt hui jab wo Makka mein they. ( bait letey huey) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne daain hath ko utha kar farmaya ke ye Usman ka hath hai aur usey apne ( baain ( hath par mar kar farmaya ke ye bait Usman ki taraf se hai. ab ja saktey ho. albatta meri baton ko yad rakhna."
4067,Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( teerandaazon ke) paidal daste ka ameer Abdullaah-bin-Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya tha lekin wo log shikast khurda ho kar aaey. ( aayat ( يدعوهم الرسول في أخراهم‏) un hi ke barey mein nazil hui thi) aur ye paspaaii us waqt pesh aai jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unko peechhey se pukar rahe they.
4068,"main un logon mein tha jinhein Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par oongh ne aa gheraa tha aur usi haalat mein meri talwaar kai martaba (haath se chhoot kar be ikhtiyaar) gir padi thi. main usey utha letaa, phir gir jati aur main usey phir utha letaa."
4069,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki aakhiri rakaat ke rukoo se sar Mubarak uthatey to ye dua kartey ''aey Allaah! fulaan, falan aur falan ( Safwan bin Umayya , Suhail-bin-Amr aur Haris-bin-Hisham ( ko apni rehmat se door kar de. ''ye dua aap ( سمع الله لمن حمده ربنا ولك الحمد (ke baad kartey they. is par Allah Taala ne aayat ( ليس لك من الأمر شىء‏ ( se ( فإنهم ظالمون‏ ( ) Aale-Imran : 128 ( tak nazil ki."
4070,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Safwan bin Umayya , Suhail-bin-Amr aur Haris-bin-Hisham ke liye baddua kartey they is par ye aayat ( ليس لك من الأمر شىء‏ ( se ( فإنهم ظالمون‏ ( tak nazil hui."
4071,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Madina ki khawaateen mein chaadrein taqseem karwaaiin. aik umda qism ki chadar baqi bach gaee to aik sahib ne jo wahin maujood they, arz kya : ya ameerul-momineen! ye chadar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nawaasi ko de dijiye jo aap ke nikah mein hain. unka ishara umme-kulsoom binte- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf tha. lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke umme-saleet (Raziallahu anhu) unse zyada mustahiq hain. umme-saleet (Raziallahu anhu) ka talluq qabila Ansar se tha aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Uhud ki jang mein wo hamarey liye pani ki mashk bhar-bhar kar laatii thin."
4072,"mein Ubaidullah bin Adii-bin khiyaar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath rawaana hua. jab teiswin pahunchey to mujh se Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, aapko wahshii ( ibne- Harab habshi jisne Uhud ki jang mein Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ko qatl kya aur hinda bevi Abu-Sufiyan ne unki laash ka musla kya tha) se Taaruf : hai. ham chal ke unse Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ke barey mein malum kartey hain. maine kaha ke theek hai zaroor chalo. wahshii teiswin mein maujood they. chunanche ham ne logon se unke barey mein malum kya to hamein bataya gaya ke wo apne makan ke saaey mein baithey huey hain, jaisey koi bada sa kuppaa ho. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir ham unke paas aaey aur thodi der unke paas khadey rahe. phir salam kya to unhon-ne salam ka jawab diya. bayan kya ke Ubaidullah ne apne amama ko jism par is tarah lapet rakha tha ke wahshii sirf unki aankhen aur paon dekh saktey they. Ubaidullah ne puchha : aey wahshii ! kya tum ne mujhey pehchaana ? rawi ne bayan kya ke phir us ne Ubaidullah ko dekha aur kaha ke nahi, Allah ki qism ! albatta main itna janta hun ke Adii-bin khiyaar ne aik aurat se nikah kya tha. usey Umme- qitaal binte- abii-al-ais kaha jata tha phir Makka mein uske yahan aik bachcha paida hua aur main uske liye kisi daaya ki talash ke liye gaya tha. phir main us bachchey ko uski (razaaii) maa ke paas ley gaya aur uski walida bhi sath thi. ghaaliban maine tumharey paon dekhey they. bayan kya ke is par Ubaidullah bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne chehrey se kapda hata liya aur kaha, hamein tum Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ke waaqiaat bata saktey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, baat ye hui ke badr ki ladai mein Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ne Tueima-bin-Adii-bin-khiyaar ko qatl kya tha. mere aaqa Jubair-bin-Mut'im ne mujh se kaha ke agar tum ne Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ko mere chacha (Tueima) ke badley mein qatl kar diya to tum aazad ho jaogey. unhon-ne bataya ke phir jab Quraish ainain ki jang ke liye nikley. ainain Uhud ki aik pahaadii hai aur uske aur Uhud ke darmyan aik wadi haail hai. to main bhi unke sath jang ke irade se ho liya. jab ( donon faujein aamney samney ( ladney ke liye saf aaraa ho gain to ( Quraish ki saf mein se) Sibaa'-bin-abdul-Uzzaa nikla aur us ne awaz di, hai koi ladney waalaa? bayan kya ke) uski us dawat mubaazirat par) ameer Hamza bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) nikal kar aaey aur farmaya, aey Sibaa'! aey umme-Anmaar ke betey ! jo aurton ke khatney kya karti thi, to Allah aur uske rasool se ladney aaya hai? bayan kya ke phir Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par hamla kya (aur usey qatl kar diyaa) ab wo waqia guzrey huey din ki tarah ho chuka tha. wahshii ne bayan kya ke idhar main aik chattaan ke nichey Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki taak mein tha aur joon hi wo mujh se qareeb huey, maine un par apna chhota neza phenk kar maaraa, neza unki naaf ke nichey ja kar laga aur unki peeth ke paar ho gaya. bayan kya ke yahi unki shahadat ka sabab banaa, phir jab Quraish wapas huey to main bhi unke sath wapas aa gaya aur Makka mein muqeem raha. lekin jab Makka bhi Islami saltanat ke tehet aa gaya to main Taaif chala gaya. Taaif walon ne bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik qaasid bheja to mujh se wahan ke logon ne kaha ke anbiya kisi par zyadti nahi kartey (is liye tum musalman ho jao . Islam qabool karne ke baad tumhari pichhli tamam ghaltiyaan maaf ho jaaeingii) chunanche main bhi unke sath rawaana hua. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha aur aap ne mujhey dekha to malum farmaya, kya tumhara hi naam wahshii hai? maine arz kya ke ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum hi ne Hamza ko qatl kya tha? maine arz kya, jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us mamley mein malum hai wahi sahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya : kya tum aisa kar saktey ho ke apni sura mujhey kabhi na dikhaao? unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir main wahan se nikal gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jab wafat hui to Musailma kazzaab ne khurooj kya. ab maine sochaa ke mujhey Musailma kazzaab ke khilaf jang mein zaroor shirkat karni chahiye mumkin hai main usey qatl kar dun aur is tarah Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ke qatl ka badal ho sakey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir main bhi uske khilaf jang ke liye musalmanon ke sath niklaa. us se jang ke waaqiaat sab ko malum hain. bayan kya ke (maidaane-jang mein) maine dekha ke aik shakhs (musailma) aik diwar ki daraaz se laga khada hai. jaisey gehunwey rang ka koi oont ho. sar ke baal muntashir they. bayan kya ke maine is par bhi apna chhota neza phenk kar maara . neza uske seeney par laga aur shaanon ko paar kar gaya. bayan kya ke itney mein aik sahabi Ansari jhaptey aur talwaar se uski khopdi par maaraa. unhon (abdul-Azeez bin-abdullaah) ne kaha, unse Abdullah-bin Fazal ne bayan kya ke phir mujhey Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ne khabar di aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kar rahe they ke) Musailma ke qatl ke baad) aik ladki ne chhat par khadi ho kar elaan kya ke ameerul-momineen ko aik kaley ghulam (yani wahshii ( ne qatl kar diya."
4073,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ka ghazab us qaum par intihai sakht hua jisne iske Nabi ke sath ye kya.'' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ishara aagey ke dandaane-mubaarak (ke toot jaaney) ki taraf tha. Allah Taala ka ghazab us shakhs (ubii-bin-khalaf) par intihai sakht hua. jisey iske Nabi ne Allah ke rastey mein qatl kya.
4074,Allah Taala ka us shakhs par intihai ghazab nazil hua jisey Allah ke Nabi ne qatl kya tha. Allah Taala ka intihai ghazab us qaum par nazil hua jinhoney Allah ke Nabi ke chehra Mubarak ko (Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par) khoon aalud kar diya tha.
4075,Allah ki qism ! mujhey achi tarah yad hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zakhmon ko kis ne dhoya tha aur kon un par pani daal raha tha aur jis dawaa se aap ka ilaaj kya gaya. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi khoon ko dho rahi thin. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) dhaal se pani daal rahe they. jab Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne dekha ke pani dalney se khoon aur zyada nikal raha hai to unhon-ne chatai ka aik tukda lekar jalaayaa aur phir usey zakhm par chupkaa diya jis se khoon ka aana band ho gaya. isi din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aagey ke daant Shahid huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak bhi zakhmi ho gaya tha aur khaud sar par toot gaee thi.
4076,Allah Taala ka intihai ghazab us shakhs par nazil hua jisey Allah ke Nabi ne qatl kya tha. Allah Taala ka intihai ghazab us shakhs par nazil hua jisne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak ko khoon aalud kya tha.
4077,"( aayat ) الذين استجابوا لله والرسول من بعد ما أصابهم القرح للذين أحسنوا منهم واتقوا أجر عظيم‏ ''wo log jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool ki awaz par labbaik kahaa'' unhon-ne Urwa se is aayat ke mutaalliq kaha, mere bhaanjey! tumharey walid Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) aur (naa-naa) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unhiin mein se they. Uhud ki ladai main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jo kuchh takleef pahunchi thi jab wo pahunchi aur mushrekeen wapas janey lagey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko iska khatrah hua ke kahin wo phir lot kar hamla na karein. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unka peechhaa karne kaun-kaun jaengey. usi waqt 70 sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) taiyaar ho gaey. rawi ne bayan kya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unhiin mein se they."
4078,Arab ke tamam qabaayel mein koi qabila Ansar ke muqaabley mein us izzat ko hasil nahi kar saka ke uske sabse zyada aadmi Shahid huey aur wo qabila qiyamat ke din sabse zyada izzat ke sath uthega. Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne ham se bayan kya ke Uhud ki jang mein qabila Ansar ke 70 aadmi Shahid huey aur Maoona kunwey ke haadise mein uske 70 aadmi Shahid huey aur yamaama ki ladai mein uske 70 aadmi Shahid huey. rawi ne bayan kya ke Maoona kunwey ka waqia Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke waqt mein pesh aaya tha aur yamaama ki jang Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke daure-khilaafat mein hui thi jo Musailma kazzaab se hui thi.
4079,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud ke shohdaa ko aik hi kapdey mein 2-2 ko kafan diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) malum farmatey ke unmein Quran ka aalim sabse zyada kon hai? jab kisi aik ki taraf ishara karke aapko bataya jata to lahad mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhi ko aagey farmatey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat ke din main un sab par gawah rahoonga. phir aap ne tamam shohdaa ko khoon samet dafn karne ka hukm farma diya aur unki namaaze-janaaza nahi padhi aur na unhein ghusl diya gaya.
4080,mere walid Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) Shahid kar diye gaey to main roney laga aur baar-baar unke chehrey se kapda hataataa . sahaba mujhey roktey they lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi rokaa. ( Fatima binte- umr (Raziallahu anhu) Abdullah ki behan bhi roney lagiin (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke ro'o mat. Farishtey barabar unki laash par apne paron ka saaya kiye huey they. yahan tak ke unko utha liya gaya.
4081,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' maine khuwab mein dekha ke maine talwaar ko hilaayaa aur us se uski dhaar toot gaee. uski tabeer musalmanon ke us nuqsan ki shakl mein zahir hui jo Uhud ki jang mein unhein uthana padaa tha. phir maine dobara us talwaar ko hilaayaa, to phir wo us se bhi zyada umda ho gaee jaisi pahley thi. uski tabeer Allah Taala ne fateh aur musalmanon ke phir naye sire se ijtimaa ki sura mein zahir ki. maine usi khuwab mein aik gaaey dekhi thi (jo zabah ho rahi thi) aur Allah Taala ke tamam kaam khair w barkat liye hotey hain. uski tabeer wo musalman they (jo ( Uhud ki ladai main (shaheed huey) ."
4082,ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hijrat ki aur hamara maqsad us se sirf Allah Taala ki razaamandii hasil karna tha. zaroori tha ke Allah Taala hamein is par sawab deta. ham mein se kuchh log to wo they jo Allah se ja miley aur) duniya mein) unhon-ne apna koi sawab nahi dekha. Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unhiin mein se they. Uhud ki jang mein unhon-ne shahadat paai aur aik chadar ke siwa aur koi cheez unhon-ne nahi chhodii. us chadar se ( kafan detey waqt) jab ham unka sar chhipaatey to paon khul jatey aur paon chhipaatey to sar khul jata tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaayaa غطوا بها رأسه ، Mina واجعلوا على رجليه الإذخرchaadar se sar chipa do aur paon par izkhir ghaas rakh do.'' ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun farmaayaa ألقوا على رجليه من الإذخرyaanii unke pairon par izkhir ghaas daal do.'' (donon jumlon ka matlab aik hi hai) aur ham mein kuchh wo hain jinhein unke us amal ka phal (isii duniya mein) de diya gaya aur wo us se khub fayda utha rahe hain.
4083,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Uhud pahaad ham se mohabbat rakhta hai aur ham us se mohabbat rakhtey hain.''
4084,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) khaibar se wapas hotey huey) Uhud pahaad dikhai diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ye pahaad ham se mohabbat rakhta hai aur ham us se mohabbat rakhtey hain. aey Allah ! Ibrahim ne Makka ko hurmat wala Shahar qarar diya tha aur main un 2 pathreeley maidaanon ke darmyan waley ilaaqey (Madina Munawra ( ko hurmat wala Shahar qarar deta hoon.''
4085,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din bahar tashrif laey aur shohdaa ahad par namaaze-janaaza ada ki, jaisey mardon par ada ki jati hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif laey aur farmaya ke main tumharey aagey jaunga, main tumharey haq mein gawah rahoonga. main ab bhi apne hauz (hauze-kausar) ko dekh raha hun. mujhey duniya ke khazaanon ki chaabii ata farmai gaee hai ya (aap hauze-kausar ne yun farmaayaa) ( مفاتيح الأرض ) yaanii zameen ki kunjiyaan di gaee hain. (donon jumlon ka matlab aik hi hai). Allah ki qism ! main tumharey barey mein is se nahi darta ke tum mere baad shirk karne lagogey balke mujhey iska dar hai ke tum duniya ke liye hirs karne lagogey."
4086,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jaasoosii ke liye aik jamat (Makka, Quraish ki khabar laney ke liye) bheji aur iska ameer Aasim-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya, jo Aasim bin umr bin-Khattab ke naana hain. ye jamat rawaana hui aur jab Asfan aur Makka ke darmyan pahunchi to qabila huzail ke aik qabeeley ko jisey banu-Lahyaan kaha jata tha, unka ilm ho gaya aur qabeele ke taqriban so teerandaazon ne unka peechhaa kya aur unke nishaanaate-qadam ko talash kartey huey chaley. aakhir aik aisi jagah pahunchne mein kaamyaab ho gaey jahan sahaba ki us jamat ne padao kya tha. wahan un khajooron ki guthliyaan milein jo sahaba Madina se laey they. qabila walon ne kaha ke ye to yasrib ki khajoor (ki guthlii) hai ab unhon-ne phir talash shuru ki aur sahaba ko pa liya. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke sathiyon ne jab ye soorate-haal dekhi to sahaba ki us jamat ne aik teeley par chadh kar panah li. qabila walon ne wahan pahunch kar teele ko apne gherey mein ley liya aur sahaba se kaha ke ham tumhen yaqin dilaatey hain aur ahad kartey hain ke agar tum ne hathiyar daal diye to ham tum mein se kisi ko bhi qatl nahi karengey. is par Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke main to kisi kaafir ki hifazat w amn mein khud ko kisi sura mein bhi nahi de sakta. aey Allah ! hamarey sath pesh aaney waley halaat ki khabar apne Nabi ko pahuncha de. chunanche un sahaba ne unse qitaal kya aur Aasim apne saat (7) sathiyon ke sath unke teeron se Shahid ho gaey. Khubaib , Zaid aur aik aur sahabi unke hamlon se abhi mehfooz they. qabila walon ne phir hifazat w aman ka yaqin dilaya . ye hazraat unki yaqin dahaanii par utar aaey. phir jab qabila walon ne unhein poori tarah apne qabzey mein ley liya to unki kamaan ki taant utaar kar un sahaba ko unhiin se baandh diya. teesrey sahaba jo Khubaib aur Zaid ke sath they, unhon-ne kaha ke ye tumhari pehli ghaddaar hai. unhon-ne unke sath janey se inkar kar diya. pahley to qabeele walon ne unhein ghaseetaa aur apne sath ley janey ke liye zor lagaatey rahe lekin jab wo kisi tarah taiyaar na huey to unhein wahin qatl kar diya aur Khubaib aur Zaid ko sath lekar rawaana huey. phir unhein Makka mein la kar bech diya. Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ko to Haris bin Aamir bin Nofal ke beton ne khareed liya kyonke Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne badr ki jang mein Haris ko qatl kya tha. wo unke yahan kuchh dinon tak qaidi ki haisiyat se rahe. jis waqt un sab ka Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ke qatl par ittifaq ho chuka to ittifaq se unhiin dinon Haris ki aik ladki ( Zenab ( se unhon-ne muey naaf ke nichey ke saaf karne ke liye ustra maanga aur unhon-ne unko ustra bhi de diya tha. unka bayan tha ke mera ladka meri ghafalat mein Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas chala gaya. unhon-ne usey apni raan par bitha liya. maine jo usey us haalat mein dekha to bahut ghabraaii . unhon-ne meri ghabraahat ko jaan liya, ustra unke hath mein tha. unhon-ne mujh se kaha, kya tumhen iska khatrah hai ke main is bachchey ko qatl kar doonga? inshaAllah main hargiz aisa nahi kar sakta. unka bayan tha ke Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) se behtar qaidi maine kabhi nahi dekha tha. maine unhein angoor ka khosha khaatey huey dekha halanke us waqt Makka mein kisi tarah ka phal maujood nahi tha jabke wo zanjeeron mein jakdey huey bhi they, to wo Allah ki bheji hui rozii thi. phir Haris ke betey qatl karne ke liye unhein lekar haram ke hudood se bahar gaey. Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse farmaya ke mujhey 2 rakaat Namaz padhney ki ijazat 2 ( unhon-ne ijazat de di aur). jab wo Namaz se farigh huey to unse farmaya ke agar tum ye khayal na karne lagtey ke main maut se ghabraa gaya hon to aur zyada Namaz padhtaa. Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) hi pahley wo shakhs hain jin se qatl se pahley 2 rakaat Namaz ka tariqa chala hai. iske baad unhon-ne unke liye baddua ki, aey Allaah! unhein eik-eik karke halaak kar de aur ye ashaar padhey ''jab ke main musalman honey ki haalat mein qatl kya ja raha hun to mujhey iski koi parwah nahi ke kis pahlu par Allah ki raah mein mujhey qatl kya jaeyga ye sab kuchh Allah ki raah mein hai aur agar wo chaahega to jism ke eik-eik katey huey tukdey mein barkat dega. '' phir Aqba bin-Haaris ne khadey ho kar unhein Shahid kar diya aur Quraish ne Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ki laash ke liye aadmi bhejey taake unke jism ka koi bhi hissey laaein jis se unhein pehchaana ja sakey. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne Quraish ke aik bahut badey , sardaar ko badr ki ladai mein qatl kya tha lekin Allah Taala ne bhidon ki aik fauj ko badal ki tarah unke uper bheja aur un bhidon ne unki laash ko Quraish ke aadmiyon se mehfooz rakha aur Quraish ke bhejey huey ye log (unke paas na phatak sakey ( kuchh na kar sakey."
4087,Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ko Abu-sarooaa ( Aqba-bin-Aamir ( ne qatl kya tha.
4088,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 70 sahaba ki aik jamat tableeghe-Islaam ke liye bheji thi. unhein qaari kaha jata tha. rastey mein banu-Sulaim ke 2 qabeeley Ra'l aur Zakwan ne aik kuwein ke qareeb unke sath takraaw hua. ye kunwaan Maoona kunwey ke naam se mashhoor tha. sahaba ne unse kaha ke Allah ki qism ! ham tumharey khilaaf, yahan ladney nahi aaey balke hamein to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se aik zarurat par maamoor kya gaya hai. lekin kuffaar ke un qabeelon ne tamam sahaba ko Shahid kar diya. is waaqie ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz mein unke liye aik mahina tak baddua kartey rahe. isi din se duaae-qunoot ki shuruaat hui, warna us se pahley ham duaae-qunoot nahi padha kartey they aur abdul-Azeez-bin-Suhaib ne bayan kya ke aik sahib (Aasim ahwal) ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se duaae-qunoot ke barey mein puchha ke ye dua rukoo ke baad padhi jaeygi ya qir'ate-qur'aan se farigh honey ke ba'd? ( rukoo se pahley) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke nahi balke qirat Quran se farigh honey ke baad) rukoo se pahley) ."
4089,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo ke baad aik mahina tak qunoot padhi jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Arab ke chand qabaayel ( Ra'l w Zakwan wghaira) ke liye baddua kartey they.
4090,"Ra-al, Zakwaan, usba aur banu-Lahyaan ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apne dushmanon ke muqabil madad chaahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 70 Ansari sahaba ko unki kumak ke liye rawaana kya. ham un hazraat ko qaari kaha kartey they. apni zindagi mein rozi-roti ke liye din mein lakdiyan jama kartey they aur raat mein Namaz padha kartey they. jab ye hazraat Maoona kunwey par pahunchey to un qabeeley walon ne unhein dhokaa diya aur unhein Shahid kar diya. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski khabar hui to aap ne subah ki Namaz mein aik mahiney tak baddua ki. Arab ke inhiin chand qabaayel Ra-al, Zakwaan, usba aur banu-Lahyaan ke liye. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke un sahaba ke barey mein Quran main (aayat nazil hui aur) ham uski tilawat kartey they. phir wo aayat mansukh ho gaee ( aayat ka tarjama ( '' hamari taraf se hamari qaum ( musalmanon ( ko khabar pahuncha 2 ke ham apne rab ke paas aagey hain. hamara rab ham se razi hai aur hamein bhi (apni ne'maton se) us ne khush rakha hai.'' aur Qatada se riwayat hai unse Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mahiney tak subah ki Namaz mein, Arab ke chand qabaayel yani Ra-al, Zakwaan, usba aur banu- Lahyaan ke liye baddua ki thi. khaleefa-bin-khayyaat (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke shekh) ne ye izafa kya ke ham se Yazeed bin Zaree ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Saeed-bin-abii Aruba ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne ke ham se Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ye 70 sahaba qabila Ansar se they aur unhein Maoona kunwey ke paas Shahid kar diya gaya tha."
4091,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke maamun , Umme-Sulaim ( Anas ki walida (ke bhai ko bhi un 70 sawaaron ke sath bheja tha. iski wjah ye hui thi ke mushrikon ke sardaar Aamir-bin-Tufail ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ( sharaarat aur takabbur se) teen sooratein rakhi thin. usne kaha ke ya to ye kijiye ke dehati aabadi par aap ki hukumat ho aur shehri aabadi par meri ho. ya phir mujhey aap ka jaa-nashiin muqarrar kya jaey warna phir main hazaaron Ghatfaaniyon ko lekar aap par chadhai kar doonga. (is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske liye baddua ki) aur Umme- falan ke ghar mein wo marz taaoon mein giraftaar hua. kehney laga ke us falan ki aurat ke ghar ke jawan oont ki tarah mujhey bhi ghudood nikal aaya hai. mera ghoda laao. chunanche wo apne ghodey ki pusht par hi mar gaya. bahar-haal Umme-Sulaim ke bhai Haraam-bin-Milhaan aik aur sahabi jo ek hi taang se chal patey they aur teesrey sahabi jinka talluq bani falan se tha, aagey badhey. haram ne (apne donon sathiyon se banu-Aamir tak pahunch kar pahley hi) keh diya ke tum donon mere qareeb hi kahin rehna. main unke paas pahley jata hun agar unhon-ne mujhey amn de diya to tum log qareeb hi ho aur agar unhon-ne qatl kar diya to aap hazraat apne sathiyon ke paas chaley jaanaa. chunanche qabeele mein pahunch kar unhon-ne unse kaha, kya tum mujhey aman detey ho ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka paigham tumhen pahuncha dun? phir wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka paigham unhein pahunchaney lagey to qabila walon ne aik shakhs ko ishara kya aur us ne peechhey se aa kar un par neze se waar kya. Hammam ne bayan kya, mera khayal hai ke neza aar paar ho gaya tha. haram ki zaban se us waqt nikla ''Allaahu-akbar, Kaba ke rab ki qism ! maine to apni murad hasil kar lii.'' iske baad unmein se aik sahabi ko bhi mushrekeen ne pakad liya (jo haram (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they aur unhein bhi Shahid kar diyaa) phir us muhim ke tamam sahaba ko Shahid kar diya. sirf ek hi taang se chal patey sahabi bach nikalney mein kaamyaab ho gaey wo pahaad ki choti par chadh gaey they. un shohdaa ki shaan mein Allah Taala ne aayat nazil farmai, baad mein wo aayat mansukh ho gaee (aayat ye thii) (إنا قد لقينا ربنا فرضي عنا وأرضانا)nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un qabaayel Ra-al, Zakwaan, banu- Lahyaan aur usba ke liye jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki thi tees din tak subah ki Namaz mein baddua ki."
4092,jab Haraam-bin-Milhaan ko jo unke maamun they Maoona kunwey ke mauqe par zakhmi kya gaya to zakhm par se khoon ko hath mein lekar unhon-ne apne chehre aur sar par laga liya aur kaha Kaba ke rab ki qism ! meri murad hasil ho gaee.
4093,"jab Makka mein mushrik log Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ko sakht takleef dene lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi ijazat chaahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke abhi yahin thahrey raho. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! kya aap bhi) Allah Taala se) apne liye hijrat ki ijazat ke ummeedwaar hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan mujhey uski ummeed hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) intizar karne lagey. aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din Zohar ke waqt (hamaarey ghar) tashrif laey aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko pukara aur farmaya ke tanha ho jao. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke sirf meri donon ladkiyan yahan maujood hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ko malum hai mujhey bhi hijrat ki ijazat de di gaee hai. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya mujhey bhi sath chalney ki khush-naseebi hasil hogi ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, tum bhi mere sath chalogey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mere paas 2 oontniyan hain aur maine unhein hijrat hi ki niyat se taiyaar kar rakha hai. chunanche unhon-ne aik ontni jiska naam '' الجدعا '' tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko de di. donon buzurg Sawar ho kar rawaana huey aur ye ghaare-saur pahaadii ka tha usmein ja kar donon posheeda ho gaey. Aamir-bin-Fuhaira jo Abdullah-bin Tufail bin sanjra , Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke walida ki taraf se bhai they, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik doodh dene wali ontni thi to Aamir-bin-Fuhaira subah w Sham (aam maweshiyon ke saath) usey charaney ley jatey aur raat ke aakhiri hisse main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aatey they. (ghaare-saur mein un hazraat ki khuraak usi ka doodh thi) aur phir usey charaney ke liye lekar rawaana ho jatey. is tarah koi charwaha is par aagah na ho saka. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ghaar se nikal kar rawaana huey to peechhey peechhey Aamir-bin-Fuhaira bhi pahunchey they. aakhir donon hazraat Madina pahunch gaey. Maoona kunwey ke haadise mein Aamir-bin-Fuhaira (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Shahid ho gaey they. abu-Usama se riwayat hai, unse Hisham-bin-Urwa ne bayan kya, unhein unke walid ne khabar di, unhon-ne bayan kya ke jab Maoona kunwey ke haadise mein qaari sahaba Shahid kiye gaey aur Amr bin Umayya Zamri (Raziallahu anhu) qaid kiye gaey to Aamir-bin-Tufail ne unse puchha ke ye kon hai? unhon-ne aik laash ki taraf ishara kya. Amr bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke ye Aamir-bin-Fuhaira (Raziallahu anhu) hain. is par Aamir-bin-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine dekha ke Shahid ho janey ke baad unki laash aasman ki taraf uthai gaee. maine uper nazar uthai to laash aasman w zameen ke darmyan latak rahi thi. phir wo zameen par rakh di gaee. un shohdaa ke mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne khuda ki marzi se bata diya tha. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki shahadat ki khabar sahaba ko di aur farmaya ke tumharey sathi Shahid kar diye gaey hain aur shahadat ke baad unhon-ne apne rab ke huzoor mein arz kya ke aey hamarey rab! hamarey ( musalman ( bhaiyon ko uski itlaa dedey ke ham terey paas pahunch kar kis tarah khush hain aur to bhi ham se razi hai. chunanche Allah Taala ne ( Quran Majeed ke zariey ( musalmanon ko uski itlaa de di. usi haadise mein Urwa bin Asma bin Salat (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Shahid huey they ( phir Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey jab paida huey) to unka naam Urwa, inhiin Urwa ibne- Asma (Raziallahu anha) ke naam par rakha gaya. munzir bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) us haadise mein Shahid huey they. (aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke doosrey sahib zadey ka naam ( munzir unhein ke naam par rakha gaya tha."
4094,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mahiney tak rukoo ke baad duaaey qunoot padhi. us duaaey qunoot mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ra'l aur Zakwan naam ke qabaayel ke liye baddua ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke qabila usba ne Allah aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki.
4095,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un logon ke liye jinhoney aap ke muazzaz ashaab ( qaariyon ( ko Maoona kunwey mein Shahid kar diya tha. tees din tak subah ki Namaz mein baddua ki thi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabaayel Ra-al, banu- Lahyaan aur usba ke liye un namazon mein baddua kartey they, jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nafarmani ki thi. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Allah Taala ne apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par unhi ashaab ke barey mein jo Maoona kunwey mein Shahid kar diye gaey they, Quran Majeed ki aayat nazil ki. ham us aayat ki tilawat kya kartey they lekin baad mein wo aayat mansukh ho gaee (is aayat ka tarjama ye hai) ''hamaarii qaum ko khabar pahuncha 2 ke ham apne rab se aa miley hain. hamara rab ham se razi hai aur ham bhi us se razi hain.''"
4096,"maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se Namaz mein qunoot ke barey mein puchha ke qunoot rukoo se pahley hai ya rukoo ke ba'd? unhon-ne kaha ke rukoo se pahley . maine arz kya ke falan sahib ne aap hi ka naam lekar mujhey bataya ke qunoot rukoo ke baad . Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke unhon-ne ghalat kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo ke baad sirf aik mahiney tak qunoot padhi. aap ne sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik jamat ko jo qaariyon ke naam se mashhoor thi jo 70 ki tadaad mein they, mushrekeen ke kuchh qabaayel ke yahan bheja tha. mushrekeen ke un qabaayel ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko un sahaba ke barey mein pahley hifz w aman ka yaqin dilaya tha lekin baad mein ye log sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ki us jamat par ghalib aagey (aur ghaddaari ki aur unhein Shahid kar diyaa) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi mauqe par rukoo ke baad aik mahiney tak qunoot padhi thi aur is mein un mushrekeen ke liye baddua ki thi."
4097,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney apne aapko unhon-ne Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par pesh kya (taake ladney walon mein unhein bhi bhartii kar liya jaey) us waqt wo chaudah saal ke they, to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ijazat nahi di. lekin Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par jab unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney apne ko pesh kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko manzoor farma liya. us waqt wo pandarah saal ki umr ke they."
4098,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khandaq mein they. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) khandaq khod rahe they aur mitti ham apne kandhon par utha utha kar nikal rahe they. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki اللهم لا عيش إلا عيش الآخره ، Mina padhi. فاغفر للمهاجرين والأنصار ''aey Allah ! aakhirat ki zindagi hi bas aaraam ki zindagi hai. to to Ansar aur muhajireen ki maghfirat farmaa. ''
4099,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khandaq ki taraf tashrif ley gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke muhajireen aur Ansar sardi mein subah sawerey hi khandaq khod rahe hain. unke paas ghulam nahi they ke unke bajaey wo us kaam ko anjam detey. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki us mashaqqat aur bhook ko dekha to dua ki ( اللهم إن العيش عيش الآخرة . فاغفر للأنصار والمهاجره )''aey Allaah! zindagi to bas aakhirat hi ki zindagi hai. to Ansar aur muhajireen ki maghfirat farmaa.'' sahaaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske jawab mein kahaa نحن الذين بايعوا محمدا * * * على الجهاد ما بقينا أبداham hi hain jinhoney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jihad karne ke liye bait ki hai. jab tak hamari jaan mein jaan hai.
4100,Madina ke gird muhajireen w Ansar khandaq khodney mein masroof ho gaey aur mitti apni peeth par uthaney lagey. us waqt wo ye sher padh rahe they نحن الذين بايعوا محمدا * * * على الأسلام ما بقينا أبدا ham ne hi Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Islam par bait ki hai jab tak hamari jaan mein jaan hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki اللهم إنه لا خير إلا خير الآخرة . فبارك في الأنصار والمهاجره''aey Allaah! khair to sirf aakhirat hi ki khair hai. to Ansar aur muhajireen ko to barkat ata farmaa.'' Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke aik muththii jau aata aur un sahaba ke liye aisey raughan mein jiska maza bhi bigad chuka hota mila kar pakka diya jata. yahi khana un sahaba ke samney rakh diya jata. sahaba bhookey hotey . ye unke halaq mein chipkaktaa aur is mein badboo hoti. maano us waqt unki khuraak ka bhi ye haal tha.
4101,"main Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to unhon-ne bayan kya ke ham Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par khandaq khod rahe they ke aik bahut sakht qism ki chattaan nikli (jis par kudaal aur phaawdey ka koi asar nahi hota tha isliye khandaq ki khudaaii mein rukawat paida ho gai) sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se arz kya ke khandaq mein aik chattaan zahir ho gaee hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main andar utartaa hun. chunanche aap khadey huey aur us waqt (bhook ki shiddat ki wjah se) aap ka pet patthar se bandhaa hua tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kudaal apne hath mein li aur chattaan par us se maaraa. chattaan (eik hi zarb mein) baalu ke dher ki tarah bah gaee. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mujhey ghar janey ki ijazat dijiye. (ghar aa kar) maine apni biwi se kaha ke aaj maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko (faaqon ki wjah se) us haalat mein dekha ke sabr na ho saka. kya tumharey paas ( khaney ki) koi cheez hai? unhon-ne bataya ke haan kuchh jau hain aur aik bakri ka bachcha. maine bakri ke bachche ko zabah kya aur meri biwi ne jau peesey. phir gosht ko ham ne choolhey par handi mein rakha aur main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. aata goondhaa ja chuka tha aur gosht choolhey par pakney ke qareeb tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine arz kya ghar khaney ke liye mukhtasar khana taiyaar hai. ya Rasulullah ! aap apne sath 1-2 aadmiyon ko lekar tashrif ley chalein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kitna hai? maine aapko sab kuchh bata diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to bahut hai aur bahut hi zyada umda w paak hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apni biwi se keh do ke choolhey se handi na utaarein aur na tannoor se roti nikaalein main abhi aa raha hun. phir sahaba se farmaya ke sab log chalein. chunanche tamam Ansar w muhajireen taiyaar ho gaey. jab Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ghar pahunchey to apni biwi se unhon-ne kaha ab kya hoga? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to tamam muhajireen w Ansar ko sath lekar tashrif la rahe hain. unhon-ne poochha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aap se kuchh puchha bhi tha? Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba se farmaya ke andar dakhil ho jao lekin bheed na honey paaey. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) roti ka chooraa karne lagey aur gosht is par dalney lagey. handi aur tannoor donon dhakey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey liya aur sahaba ke qareeb kar diya. phir aap ne gosht aur roti nikaalii. is tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) barabar roti chooraa kartey jatey aur gosht usmein daltey jatey. yahan tak ke tamam sahaba pet bhar gaya aur khana bach bhi gaya. aakhir mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi se) farmaya ke ab ye khana tum khud khaao aur logon ke yahan hadiye mein bhejo kyonke log aaj-kal faaqe mein mubtala hain."
4102,jab khandaq khodi ja rahi thi to maine malum kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) intihai bhook mein mubtala hain. main fauran apni biwi ke paas aaya aur kaha kya tumharey paas koi khaney ki cheez hai? mera khayal hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) intihai bhookey hain. meri biwi aik thailaa nikal kar laaiin jis mein aik saa jau they. ghar mein hamara aik bakri ka bachcha bhi bandhaa hua tha. maine bakri ke bachchey ko zabah kya aur meri biwi ne jau ko chakkii mein peesaa. jab main zabah se farigh hua to wo bhi jau pees chuki thin. maine gosht ki botiyaan karke handi mein rakh diya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. meri biwi ne pahley hi tanbeeh kar di thi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaba ke samney mujhey sharminda na karna. chunanche maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar aap ke kaan mein ye arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! ham ne aik chhota sa bachcha zabah kar liya hai aur aik saa jau pees liye hain jo hamarey paas they. isliye aap 2-1 sahaba ko sath lekar tashrif ley chalein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bahut buland awaz se farmaya ke aey ahale-khandaq! Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne tumharey liye khana taiyaar karwaya hai. bas ab Sara kaam chhod do aur jaldi chaley chalo. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tak main aa na jaun handi choolhey par se na utaarna aur tab aatey ki roti pakaanii shuru karna. main apne ghar aaya. udhar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi sahaba ko sath lekar rawaana huey. main apni biwi ke paas aaya to wo mujhey bura-bhala kehney lagiin. maine kaha ke tum ne jo kuchh mujh se kaha tha maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney arz kar diya tha. aakhir meri biwi ne gundhaa hua aata nikala aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein apne munh ka luaab laga diya aur barkat ki dua ki. handi mein bhi aap ne luaab milaya aur barkat ki dua ki. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab roti pakaaney wali ko bulaao. wo mere samney roti pakaaey aur gosht handi se nikaley lekin choolhey se handi na utaarnaa. sahaba ki tadaad hazaar ke qareeb thi. main Allah Taala ki qism khata hun ke itney hi khaney ko sab ne (pet bhar kar) khaya aur khana bach bhi gaya. jab tamam log wapas ho gaey to hamari handi isi tarah ubal rahi thi jis tarah shuru mein thi aur aatey ki rotiyaan barabar pakaaii ja rahi thin.
4103,( aayat ) ( إذا جاؤوكم من فوقكم ومن أسفل منكم وإذ زاغت الأبصار وبلغت القلوب الحناجر ) ''jab mushrekeen tumharey oopri ilaqe se aur tumharey nichey ke ilaqa se tum par chadh aaey they aur jab maarey dar ke aankhen chakaa-chaundh ho gaee thin aur dil halaq tak aagey they.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke ye aayat Khandaq ki jang ke mutaalliq nazil hui thi.
4104,Khandaq ki jang main (khandaq ki khudaaii ke waqt) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mitti utha utha kar la rahe they. yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka pet ghubaar se at gaya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban par ye kalimaat jari they ''Allah ki qasam! agar Allah na hota to hamein seedha rasta na miltaa. na ham sadqa kartey na Namaz padhtey to to hamarey dilon par sakeenat w itmeenaan nazil farma aur agar hamari kuffaar se mudbhed ho jaey to hamein Sabit qadmii inayat farmaa. jo log hamarey khilaf chadh aaey hain jab ye koi fitna chahtey hain to ham unki nahi maantey. ( أبينا أبينا ( (ham unki nahi maantey. ham unki nahi maantey) par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki awaz buland ho jaatii.''
4105,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''parwaa hawa ke zariey meri madad ki gaee aur qaume-aad pachhwaa hawa se halaak kar di gaee thii.''
4106,jange-Ehzaab ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maine dekha ke khandaq khodtey huey uske andar se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mitti utha utha kar la rahe hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pet ki khaal mitti se at gaee thi. aap ke (seeney se pet tak) ghaney baalon (ki aik lakeer) thi. maine khud suna ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ibne-rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ke rajziya ashaar mitti uthatey huey padh rahe they. ''aey Allaah! agar to na hota to hamein seedha rasta na milta na ham sadqa kartey na Namaz padhtey to ham par to apni taraf se sakeenat nazil farma aur agar hamara aamnaa-saamnaa ho jaey to hamein Sabit qadmii ata farmaa. ye log hamarey uper zulm se chadh aaey hain. jab ye ham se koi fitna chahtey hain to ham unki nahi suntey.'' rawi ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aakhiri kalimaat ko kheench kar padhtey they.
4107,sabse pehli jang jis mein maine shirkat ki wo Khandaq ki jang hai.
4108,"mujhey Abdullah-bin Taaus ne khabar di, unse Ikrima bin Khalid ne aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan gaya to unke sar ke baalon se pani ki boondein tapak rahi thin. maine unse kaha ke tum dekhti ho logon ne kya kya aur mujhey to kuchh bhi hukumat nahi milii. Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke musalmanon ke majme' mein jao, log tumhara intizar kar rahe hain. kahin aisa na ho ke tumhara mauqe par na pahunchnaa mazeed phoot ka sabab bin jaey. aakhir Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke israar par Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) gaey. phir jab log wahan se chaley gaey to Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne khutba diya aur kaha ke khilafat ke mas'ale par jisey guftgu karni ho wo zara apna sar to uthaaey. yaqinan ham us se zyada khilafat ke haqdaar hain aur uske bap se bhi zyada. Habeeb-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se is par kaha ke aap ne wahin iska jawab kyon nahi diya ? Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine usi waqt apni lungii kholii (jawaab dene ko taiyaar hua) aur irada kar chuka tha ke unse kahun ke tum se zyada khilafat ka haqdaar wo hai jisne tum se aur tumharey bap se Islam ke liye jang ki thi. lekin phir main dara ke kahin meri is baat se musalmanon mein ikhtilaf badh na jaey aur khoonrezii na ho jaey aur meri baat ka matlab meri mansha ke khilaf na liya janey lagey. iske bajaey mujhey jannat ki wo ne'matein yad aa gain jo Allah Taala ne (sabr karne walon ke liye) jannat mein taiyaar kar rakhi hain. Habib ibne-abi Muslim ne kaha ke achchha hua aap mehfooz rahe aur bacha liye gaey, aafat mein nahi padey. Mehmood ne Abdur-Razzaq se ( نسواتها‏ .) ke bajaey lafz ( ) ونوساتها‏ .) bayan kya ( jiske mana choti ke hain jo auratein sar par baal goondhtey waqt nikaaltii hain)."
4109,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-Ehzaab ke mauqe par (jab kuffaar ka lashkar naakaam wapas ho gaya) farmaya ke ab ham unse ladengey. aainda wo ham par chadh kar kabhi na aa sakengey.
4110,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, jab Arab ke qabaayel (jo Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par Madina chadh kar aaey they) naakaam wapas ho gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab ham unse jang karengey, wo ham par chadh kar na aa sakengey balke ham hi un par fauj kashii kya karengey."
4111,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par farmaya ke jis tarah un kuffaar ne hamein salaatul-Wustaa (namaaze-asr) nahi padhney di aur suraj ghurub ho gaya, Allah Taala bhi unki qabron aur gharon ko aag se bhar de."
4112,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par suraj ghurub honey ke baad) lad kar) wapas huey. wo kuffaare-Quraish ko bura bhala keh rahe they. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! suraj ghurub honey ko hai aur main Asr ki Namaz ab tak nahi padh saka. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki qism ! Namaz to main bhi na padh saka. aakhir ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath wadi Bathaan mein utrey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz ke liye wuzu kya. ham ne bhi wuzu kya, phir Asr ki Namaz suraj ghurub honey ke baad padhi aur uske baad maghrib ki Namaz padhi."
4113,jange-Ehzaab ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kuffaar ke lashkar ki khabrein kon laaeyga? Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke main taiyaar hun. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kuffaar ke lashkar ki khabrein kon laaeyga? is martaba bhi Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri martaba puchha ke kuffaar ke lashkar ki khabrein kon laaeyga? Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne us martaba bhi apne aapko pesh kya. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har Nabi ke hawaarii hotey hain aur mere hawaarii Zuber hain.
4114,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they ''Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, wo akelaa hai jisne apne lashkar ko fateh di. apne bandey ki madad ki (yani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki) aur ehzaab (yani kuffaar ki faujon) ko tanha bhagaa diya to iske baad koi cheez iske madde-muqaabil nahi ho saktii.''"
4115,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehzaab (kuffaar ki faujon) ke liye (Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par) baddua ki ''aey Allaah! kitab ke nazil karne waale! jaldi hisab leney waley ! kuffaar ke lashkar ko shikast de. aey Allah ! unhein shikast de. ya Allah ! unki taqat ko hilaa de. ''
4116,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab jang, Haj ya Umerey se wapas aatey to sabse pahley teen martaba Allahu-akbar kehtey. phir yun farmatey ''Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, badhshahat usi ke liye hai, hamd usi ke liye hai aur wo har cheez par qaadir hai. (ya Allah ! ( ham wapas ho rahe hain tauba kartey huey, ibadat kartey huey apne rab ke huzoor sajda kartey huey aur apne rab ki hamd kartey huey. Allah ne apna wada sach kar dikhaya . apne bandey ki madad ki aur kuffaar ki faujon ko us ne akeley shikast de dii.''"
4117,joon hi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jange-khandaq se Madina wapas huey aur hathiyar utaar kar ghusl kya to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aap ke paas aaey aur kaha : aap ne abhi hathiyar utaar diye ? Allah ki qism ! ham ne to abhi hathiyar nahi utaarey . chaliye un par hamla kijiye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kin par? Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke un par aur unhon-ne ( yahood ke qabila ( banu-Quraiza ki taraf ishara kya. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Quraiza par chadhai ki.
4118,jaisey ab bhi wo gardo-ghubaar mein dekh raha hun jo Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ke sath sawar farishton ki wjah se qabila banu-ghanam ki gali mein utha tha jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) banu-Quraiza ke khilaf chadh kar gaey they.
4119,jange-Ehzaab ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tamam musalman Asr ki Namaz banu-Quraiza tak pahunchne ke baad hi ada karein. kuchh hazraat ki Asr ki Namaz ka waqt rastey hi mein ho gaya. unmein se kuchh sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne to kaha ke ham rastey mein Namaz nahi padhengey . (kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Quraiza mein namaze-Asr padhney ke liye farmaya hai) aur kuchh sahaba ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke irshad ka mansha ye nahi tha. (balke jaldi jana maqsad tha) baad mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney iska tazkira hua to aap ne kisi par narazgi nahi farmai.
4120,"bataur hadiya sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) apne baagh mein se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye chand khajoor ke darakht muqarrar kar diye they yahan tak ke banu-Quraiza aur banu- nazeer ke qabaayel fateh ho gaey (to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un hadiyon ko wapas kar diyaa) mere ghar walon ne bhi mujhey us khajoor ko , tamam ki tamam ya iska kuchh hissey leney ke liye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhejaa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo khajoor Umme- aiman (Raziallahu anhu) ko de di thi. itney mein wo bhi aa gain aur kapda meri gardan mein daal kar kehney lagiin, hargiz nahi. us zaat ki qasam! jiske siwa koi maabood nahi ye phal tumhen nahi milengey. ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey inayat farma chukey hain. ya isi tarah ke alfaz unhon-ne bayan kiye. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke tum mujh se iske badley mein itney ley lo. (aur unka maal unhein wapas kar do) lekin wo ab bhi yahi kahey ja rahi thin ke hargiz nahi, khuda ki qasam! yahan tak ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein, mera khayal hai ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke iska das guna dene ka wada farmaya (phir unhon-ne mujhey chhodaa) ya isi tarah ke alfaz Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiye."
4121,banu-Quraiza ne Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko saalis maan kar hathiyar daal diye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bulaney ke liye aadmi bhejaa. wo gadhey par Sawar ho kar aaey. jab us jagah ke qareeb aaey jisey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhney ke liye muntakhab kar rakha tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar se farmaya ke apne sardaar ke leney ke liye khadey ho jao . ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun farmaya ( apne se behtar shakhs ke liye khadey ho jao . iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke banu-Quraiza ne tum ko saalis maan kar hathiyar daal diye hain. chunanche Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye faisla kya ke jitney log unmein jang ke qaabil hain unhein qatl kar diya jaey aur unke bachchon aur aurton ko qaidi bana liya jaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke tum ne Allah ke faisle ke mutabiq faisla kya ya ye farmaya ke jaisey badshah (yani Allah (ka hukm tha.
4122,"Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par Sad (Raziallahu anhu) zakhmi ho gaey they. Quraish ke aik kaafir shakhs, Hassan bin Arfa naam ke ne un par teer chalaayaa tha aur wo unke bazu ki rag mein aa ke laga tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye masjid mein aik khema laga diya tha taake qareeb se unki iyaadat kartey rahen. phir jab aap Khandaq ki jang se wapas huey aur hathiyar rakh kar ghusl kya to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aap ke paas aaey. wo apne sar se ghubaar jhaad rahe they. unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha aap ne hathiyar rakh diye. Allah ki qism ! abhi maine hathiyar nahi utaarey hain. aapko un par fauj kashii karni hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kin par? to unhon-ne banu-Quraiza ki taraf ishara kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) banu-Quraiza tak pahunchey (aur unhon-ne Islami lashkar ke pandarah din ke sakht muhaasre ke baad) Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko saalis maan kar hathiyar daal diye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ko faisle ka ikhtiyar diya. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main unke barey mein faisla karta hun ke jitney log unke jang karne ke qaabil hain wo qatl kar diye jaaein, unki auratein aur bachchey qaid kar liye jayen aur unka maal taqseem kar liya jaey. Hisham ne bayan kya ke phir mujhey mere walid ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di ke Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye dua ki thi ''aey Allah ! to khub janta hai ke is se zyada mujhey koi cheez azeez nahi ke main terey rastey mein us qaum se jihad karun jisne terey rasool ko jhutlaayaa aur unhein unke watan se nikala lekin ab aisa malum hota hai ke tu ney hamari aur unki ladai ab khatm kar di hai. lekin agar Quraish se hamari ladai ka koi bhi silsila abhi baqi ho to mujhey uske liye zinda rakhna. yahan tak ke main terey rastey mein unse jihad karun aur agar ladai ke silsiley ko to ney khatm hi kar diya hai to mere zakhmon ko phir se haraa kar de aur usi mein meri maut waaqe kar de. is dua ke baad seeney par unka zakhm phir se taaza ho gaya. masjid mein qabila banu-ghifaar ke kuchh sahaba ka bhi aik khema tha. khoon unki taraf bah kar aaya to wo ghabraaey aur unhon-ne kaha : aey kheme waalo! tumhari taraf se ye khoon hamari taraf bah kar aa raha hai? dekha to Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke zakhm se khoon bah raha tha, unki wafat usi mein hui."
4123,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke mushrekeen ki hijo (mazammat) kar ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske bajaey) ( هاجهم ( farmaya Jibraeel tumharey sath hain.
4124,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jang banu-Quraiza ke mauqe par Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya tha ke mushrekeen ki hijo (mazammat) karo Jibraeel tumhari madad par hain.
4125,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ashaab ke sath Namaz khof saatween jang mein padhi thi. yani jang zaatur-Riqaa' mein. Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaaze-khauf zu-qard mein padhi thi.
4126,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jang Maharib aur bani so'lba main apne sathiyon ko namaaze-khauf padhai thi.
4127,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jange-zaatur-Riqaa' ke liye maqam nakhl se rawaana huey they. wahan aap ka qabila Ghatfan ki aik jamat se saamnaa hua lekin koi jang nahi hui aur chunkey musalmanon par kuffaar ke (achaanak hamley ka ( khatrah tha. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakaat namaaze-khauf padhai aur Yazeed ne Salma bin Akwa' (Raziallahu anhu) ke waastey se bayan kya ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang zu-qard mein Sharik tha.
4128,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jang ke liye nikley. ham chh sathi they aur ham sab ke liye sirf aik oont tha, jis par baari-baari ham sawar hotey they. (paidal lamba aur pur-mashaqqat safar ki wjah se) hamarey paon phat gaey aur mere bhi paon phat gaey they. naakhun bhi jhad gaey they. chunanche ham qadmon par kapdey ki patti baandh-baandh kar chal rahe they. isi liye iska naam jange-zaatur-Riqaa' padaa, kyonke ham ne qadmon ko pattiyon se baandh rakha tha. abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye hadis to bayan kar di, lekin phir unko uska izhar achchha nahi malum hua. farmaney lagey ke mujhey ye hadis bayan na karni chahiye thi. unko apna nek amal zahir karna bura malum hua."
4129,"jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang zaatur-Riqaa' mein Sharik they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaaze-khauf padhi thi. uski sura ye hui thi ke pahley aik jamat ne aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhi. us waqt dusri jamat (musalmanon ki) dushman ke muqaabley par khadi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us jamat ko jo aap ke peechhey saf mein khadi thi, aik rakaat Namaz khof padhai aur uske baad aap khadey rahe. us jamat ne us arse main apni Namaz poori kar li aur wapas aa kar dushman ke muqaabley mein khadi ho gaee. iske baad dusri jamat aai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Namaz ki dusri rakaat padhai jo baqi reh gaee thi aur (rukoo' w sajde ke baad) aap Qada mein baithey rahe. phir un logon ne jab apni Namaz (jo baqi reh gaee thi) poori kar li to aap ne unke sath salam pheraa."
4130,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maqam nakhl mein they. phir unhon-ne Namaz khof ka zikr kya. Imam Malik ne bayan kya ke Namaz khof ke silsiley mein jitni riwayat maine suni hain ye riwayat un sab mein zyada behtar hai. Muaz bin Hisham ke sath is hadis ko Lais-bin-Sad ne bhi Hisham bin Sad madni se, unhon-ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se riwayat kya aur unse Qasim-bin-Muhammad ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jang banu-Anmaar mein (namaaze-khauf) padhi thi."
4131,(namaaze-khauf mein) imam qibla rukh ho kar khada hoga aur musalmanon ki aik jamat uske sath Namaz mein Sharik hogi. us doran mein musalmanon ki dusri jamat dushman ke muqable par khadi hogi. unhiin ki taraf munh kiye huey. imam apne sath wali jamat ko pahley aik rakaat Namaz padhaaeyga (eik rakaat padhney ke baad phir) ye jamat khadi ho jaeygi aur khud (Imam ke baghair) usi jagah aik rukoo aur 2 sajdey karke dushman ke muqaabla par ja kar khadi ho jaeygi. jahan dusri jamat pahley se maujood thi. iske baad imam dusri jamat ko aik rakaat Namaz padhaaeyga. is tarah imam ki 2 rakatein poori ho jaeyngi aur ye dusri jamat aik rukoo aur 2 sajdey khud karegii.
4132,main Najad ki taraf Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang ke liye gaya tha. wahan ham dushman ke aamney samney huey aur unke muqaabley mein saf bandi ki.
4133,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik jamat ke sath Namaz (namaaze-khauf ( padhi aur dusri jamat us arsa mein dushman ke muqaabley par khadi thi. phir ye jamat jab apne doosrey sathiyon ki jagah (namaz padh kar) chali gaee to dusri jamat aai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bhi aik rakaat Namaz padhai. iske baad aap ne us jamat ke sath salam pheraa. aakhir us jamat ne khadey ho kar apni aik rakaat poori ki aur pehli jamat ne bhi khadey ho kar apni aik rakaat poori ki.
4134,wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aas-paas Najad mein ladai ke liye gaey they.
4135,"wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aas-paas Najad mein jang ke liye gaey they. phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas huey to wo bhi wapas huey. qailula ka waqt aik wadi mein aaya, jahan babool ke darakht bahut they. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahin utar gaey aur sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) darakhton ke saaey ke liye poori wadi mein phail gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi aik babool ke darakht ke nichey qiyam farmaya aur apni talwaar us darakht par latkaa di. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke abhi thodi der hamein soey huey hui thi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein pukara . ham jab khidmat mein hazir huey to aap ke paas aik badwi betha hua tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is shakhs ne meri talwaar ( mujh hi par) kheench li thi, main us waqt soyaa hua tha, meri aankh khuli to meri nangii talwaar uske hath mein thi. us ne mujh se kaha, tumhen mere hath se aaj kon bachaaeyga? maine kaha ke Allaah! ab dekho ye betha hua hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey phir koi saza nahi di."
4136,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath zaatur-Riqaa' mein they. ke ham aik ghaney saaya daar darakht ke paas aaey. wo darakht ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye makhsoos kar diya ke aap wahan aaraam farmaein . baad mein mushrekeen mein se aik shakhs aaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki talwaar darakht se latak rahi thi. us ne wo talwaar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par kheench li aur poochha, tum mujh se dartey ho? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. is par us ne puchha aaj mere hath se tumhen kon bachaaeyga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ! phir sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey daantaa dhamkaayaa aur Namaz ki takbeer kahi gaee. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahley aik jamat ko 2 rakaat Namaz khof padhai jab wo jamat (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey se) hat gaee to aap ne dusri jamat ko bhi 2 rakaat Namaz padhai. is tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki char rakaat Namaz hui. lekin muqtadiyon ki sirf 2-2 rakaat aur Musaddad ne bayan kya, unse abu-Awana ne, unse Abu-Basar ne ke us shakhs ka naam ( jisne aap par talwaar khinchi thi) Ghauras-bin-Haaris tha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us jang mein qabila Maharib khasfaa se jang ki thi."
4137,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maqam nakhl mein they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz khof padhai aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath namaaze-khauf jang Najad mein padhi thi. ye yad rahe ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (sab se pahley) Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par hazir huey they."
4138,main masjid mein dakhil hua to Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) andar maujood they. main unke paas baith gaya aur maine azl ke mutaalliq unse sawal kya. unhon-ne bayan kya ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-banii-mustaliq ke liye nikley. us jang mein hamein kuchh Arab ke qaidi miley (jin mein auratein bhi thiin) phir us safar mein hamein aurton ki khahish hui aur be aurat rehna ham par mushkil ho gaya. dusri taraf ham azl karna chahtey they (is khof se ke bachcha na paida ho) hamara irada yahi tha ke azl kar lein lekin phir ham ne sochaa ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maujood hain. aap se poochhey baghair azl karna munasib na hoga. chunanche ham ne aap se iske mutaalliq puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum azl na karo phir bhi koi harj nahi kyonke qiyamat tak jo jaan paida honey wali hai wo zaroor paida ho kar rahegii.
4139,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Najad ki taraf jang ke liye gaey. do-pahar ka waqt hua to aap aik jangal mein pahunchey jahan babool ke darakht bahut they. aap ne ghaney darakht ke nichey saaye ke liye qiyam kya aur darakht se apni talwaar tikaa di. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) bhi darakhton ke nichey saaya hasil karne ke liye phail gaey. abhi ham usi kaifiyat mein they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein pukara . ham hazir huey to aik badwi aap ke samney betha hua tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye shakhs mere paas aaya to main so raha tha. itney mein is ne meri talwaar kheench li aur main bhi bedaar ho gaya. ye meri nangii talwaar kheenchey huey mere sar par khada tha. mujh se kehney laga aaj mujh se tumhen kon bachaaeyga? maine kaha ke Allah ! (wo shakhs sirf aik lafz se itna maroob hua ke) talwaar ko niyaam mein rakh kar baith gaya aur dekh lo. ye betha hua hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey koi saza nahi di.
4140,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jange-Anmaar mein dekha ke nafl Namaz aap apni sawari par mashriq ki taraf munh kiye huey padh rahe they.
4141,"jab ahal ifk (yani tohmat lagaaney waalon) ne unke mutaalliq wo sab kuchh kaha jo unhein kehna tha (ibne-Shahaab ne bayan kya ke) tamam hazraat ne (jin char hazraat ke naam unhon-ne riwayat ke silsiley mein liye hain) mujh se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki hadis ka eik-eik tukda bayan kya. ye bhi tha ke unmein se kuchh ko ye qissa zyada behtar tareeqe par yad tha aur umdagii se ye qissa bayan karta tha aur maine unmein se har aik ki riwayat yad rakhi jo usney Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se yad rakhi thi. agarche kuchh logon ko doosrey logon ke muqaabley mein riwayat zyada behtar tariqa par yad thi. phir bhi unmein aapasii aik ki riwayat doosrey ki riwayat ki tasdeeq karti hai. un logon ne bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab safar ka irada kartey to paak beeviyon (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmyan Qura daala kartey they aur jiska naam aata to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein apne sath safar mein ley jatey. Mina Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke aik jang ke mauqe par jab aap ne Qura daala to mera naam nikla aur main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar mein rawaana hui. ye waqia parde ke hukm ke nazil honey ke baad ka hai. chunanche mujhey hodaj samet utha kar sawar kar diya jata aur usi ke sath utara jata. is tarah ham rawaana huey. phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne us jang se farigh ho gaey to wapas huey. waapsii mein ab ham Madina ke qareeb they (aur aik maqam par padao tha) jahan se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kooch ka raat ke waqt elaan kya. kooch ka elaan ho chuka tha to main khadi hui aur thodi door chal kar lashkar ke hudood se aagey nikal gaee. phir qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) se farigh ho kar main apni sawari ke paas pahunchi . wahan pahunch kar jo maine apna Sina tatola to zifaar (Yaman ka aik shahar) ki mohr ka bana hua mera haar ghayab tha. ab main phir wapas hui aur apna haar talash karne lagi us talash mein der ho gaee. unhon-ne bayan kya ke jo log mujhey sawar kya kartey they wo aaey aur mere hodaj ko utha kar unhon-ne mere oont par rakh diya. Mina jis par main sawar hua karti thi. unhon-ne samjha ke main hodaj ke andar hi maujood hun. un dinon auratein bahut halkii-phulkii hoti thin. unke jism mein zyada gosht nahi hota tha kyonke bahut maamooli khuraak unhein miltii thi. isliye uthaney walon ne jab uthaya to hodaj ke halkepan mein unhein koi farq malum nahi hua. yun bhi us waqt main aik kam-Umr ladki thi. gharaz oont ko utha kar wo bhi rawaana ho gaey. jab lashkar guzar gaya to mujhey bhi apna haar mil gaya. main derey par aai to wahan koi bhi na tha. na pukarney wala na jawab dene wala. isliye main wahan aai jahan mera asl dera tha. mujhey yaqin tha ke jald hi mere na honey ka unhein ilm ho jaeyga aur mujhey leney ke liye wo wapas lot aaeingey. Mina apni jagah par baithey baithey meri aankh lag gaee aur main so gaee. Safwan bin muattal Salma zakwaanii (Raziallahu anhu) lashkar ke peechhey peechhey aa rahe they. (taake lashkar ki koi cheez gum ho gaee ho to wo utha lein) unhon-ne aik soey insan ka saaya dekha aur jab ( qareeb aa kar) mujhey dekha to pehchan gaey parde se pahley wo mujhey dekh chukey they. mujhey jab wo pehchan gaey to inna-lillaah padhna shuru kya aur unki awaz se main jaag uthi aur fauran apni chadar se maine apna chehra chipa liya. Allah ki qasam! maine unse aik lafz bhi nahi kaha aur na siwa inna-lillaah ke maine unki zaban se koi lafz suna. wo sawari se utar gaey aur usey unhon-ne bitha kar uski agli taang ko mod diya (taake baghair kisi madad ke Ummul-Momenin is par Sawar ho sakein ( main uthi aur is par Sawar ho gaee. Mina ab wo sawari ko aagey se pakdey huey lekar chaley. jab ham lashkar ke qareeb pahunchey to theek do-pahar ka waqt tha. lashkar padao kiye huey tha. Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir jisey halaak hona tha wo halaak hua. asl mein tohmat ka beda Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool ( munafiq ( ne utha rakha tha. Urwa ne bayan kya ke mujhey malum hua ke wo us tohmat ka charcha karta aur uski majlison mein iska tazkira hua karta. wo uski tasdeeq karta, khub ghaur aur tawajjoh se sunta aur phailaaney ke liye khub khod kured karta. Urwa ne pehli sanad ke hawale se ye bhi kaha ke Hassan bin saabit, mistah bin asaasa aur hamna binte-Jahash ke siwa tohmat lagaaney mein Sharik kisi ka bhi naam nahi liya ke mujhey unka ilm hota. agarche usmein Sharik hone-waale bahut se they. Mina jaisa ke Allah Taala ne irshad farmaya (ke jin logon ne tohmat lagai hai wo bahut se hain) lekin is maamle mein sabse badh chadh kar hissey leney wala Abdullaah-bin-Ubaii-ibne-salool tha. Urwa ne bayan kya ke Aaisha is par badi narazgi ka izhar karti thin. agar unke samney Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ko bura bhala kaha jata, aap farmaatiin ke ye sher Hassan hi ne kaha hai ke '' mere walid aur mere walid ke walid aur meri izzat , Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki izzat ki hifazat ke liye tumharey samney dhaal bani rahengii.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir ham Madina pahunch gaey aur wahan pahunchtey hi main bimar ho gaee to aik mahiney tak bimar hi rahi. is arse mein logon mein tohmat lagaaney walon ki afwaahon ka bada charcha raha lekin main aik baat bhi nahi samajh rahi thi albatta apne marz ke doran aik cheez se mujhey bada shuba hota ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wo mohabbat w inayat main nahi mehsus karti thi jis ko pahley jab bhi bimar hoti main dekh chuki thi. Mina aap mere paas tashrif latey , salam kartey aur malum farmatey kaisi tabeeat hai? sirf itna poochh kar wapas tashrif ley jatey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke is tarze-amal se mujhey shuba hota tha. lekin shar (jo phail chuka tha) iska mujhey koi ehsas nahi tha. marz se jab fayda hua to main umme-mistah ke sath manaasea' ki taraf gaee. manaasea' (Madina ki aabadi se baahar) hamarey rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ki jagah thi. ham yahan sirf raat ke waqt jatey they. ye us se pahley ki baat hai. jab baitul-khala hamarey gharon ke qareeb ban gaey they. Ummul-Momenin ne bayan kya ke abhi ham Arab qadeem ke tareeqey par amal kartey aur maidan mein rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ke liye jaya kartey they aur hamein us se takleef hoti thi ke baitul-khala hamarey gharon ke qareeb banaey jaaein. Mina unhon-ne bayan kya ke gharaz ye ke main aur Umme- mistah ( rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ke liye) gaey. Umme- mistah abi raham bin abdul-Muttalib bin abd munaaf ki beti hain. unki walida Sakhr-bin-Aamir ki beti hain aur wo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khala thin. unhi ke betey mistah bin Asaasa-bin-Ibaad-bin-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) hain. phir main aur Umme- mistah haajat se farigh ho kar apne ghar ki taraf wapas aa rahe they ke Umme- mistah apni chadar mein ulajh gain aur unki zaban se nikla ke mistah zaleel ho. maine kaha, aap ne buri baat zaban se nikaalii , aik aisey shakhs ko aap bura keh rahi hain jo badr ki ladai mein Sharik ho chuka hai. unhon-ne is par kaha kyon mistah ki baatein tum ne nahi suniin? Ummul-Momenin ne bayan kya ke maine puchha ke unhon-ne kya kaha hai? bayan kya, phir unhon-ne tohmat lagaaney walon ki baatein sunaiin. bayan kya ke un baton ko sun kar mera marz aur badh gaya. Mina jab main apne ghar wapas aai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey aur salam ke baad malum farmaya ke kaisi tabeeat hai? maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke kya aap mujhey apne waalidain ke ghar janey ki ijazat dengey? Ummul-Momenin ne bayan kya ke mera irada ye tha ke unse is khabar ki tasdeeq karoongii. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ijazat de di. maine apni walida se ( ghar ja kar) puchha ke aakhir logon mein kis tarah ki afwahen hain? unhon-ne farmaya ke beti ! fikr na kar, Allah ki qism ! aisa shayad hi kahin hua ho ke aik khoobsurat aurat kisi aisey shauhar ke sath ho jo us se mohabbat bhi rakhta ho aur uski saukanein bhi hon aur phir is par tohmatein na lagai gaee hun. uske andar aib na nikaley gaey hon. Ummul-Momenin ne bayan kya ke maine is par kaha ke Subhan-Allah ( meri sokanon se iska kya talluq ( iska to aam logon mein charcha hai. Mina unhon-ne bayan kya ke idhar phir jo maine ronaa shuru kya to raat bhar roti rahi isi tarah subah ho gaee aur mere aansu kisi tarah na thamtey they aur na neend hi aati thi. bayan kya ke idhar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) aur Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko apni biwi ko alehda karne ke mutaalliq mashwara karne ke liye bulaya kyonke is silsiley mein ab tak aap par wahi nazil nahi hui thi. bayan kya ke Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko usi ke mutabiq mashwara diya jo wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki biwi (muraad khud apni zaat se hai) ki pakeezgi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki unse mohabbat ke mutaalliq jantey they. chunanche unhon-ne kaha ke aap ki biwi mein mujhey khair w bhalai ke siwa aur kuchh malum nahi hai lekin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala ne aap par koi tangi nahi rakhi hai aur auratein bhi unke ilawa bahut hain. Mina aap unki baandi ( Barira (Raziallahu anhu)) se bhi malum farma lein wo haqeeqate-haal bayan kar degi. bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur unse malum farmaya ke kya tum ne koi aisi baat dekhi hai jis se tumhen ( Aaisha par) shuba hua ho. Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is zaat ki qism ! jisne aapko haq ke sath maboos kya. maine unke andar koi aisi cheez nahi dekhi jo buri ho. itni baat zaroor hai ke wo aik nau-umr ladki hain, aata goondh kar so jati hain aur bakri aa kar usey kha jati hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke us din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko khitab kya aur member par khadey ho kar Abdullah-bin-Ubai ( munafiq (ka mamla rakha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey musalmaanon ke garoh! us shakhs ke barey mein meri kon madad karega jiski takleefein ab meri biwi ke mamley tak pahunch gaee hain. Mina Allah ki qism ke maine apni biwi main khair ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi dekhi aur naam bhi un logon ne aik aisey shakhs ( Safwan bin muattal (Raziallahu anhu) jo Ummul-Momenin ko apne oont par laey they) ka liya hai jiske barey mein bhi main khair ke siwa aur kuchh nahi janta. wo jab bhi mere ghar aaey to mere sath hi aaey. Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke is par Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) qabila banu- as'hal ke ham-rishta khadey huey aur arz kya mein, ya Rasulullah ! aap ki madad karunga . agar wo shakhs qabila Aus ka hua to main uski gardan mar doonga aur agar wo hamarey qabila ka hua aap ka iske mutaalliq bhi jo hukm hoga ham bajaa laaengey . Ummul-Momenin ne bayan kya ke is par qabila khazraj ke aik sahabi khadey huey. Hassan ki walida unki chacha zaad behan thin yani Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) wo qabila khazraj ke sardaar they aur us se pahley badey Saleh aur mukhlis logon mein they lekin aaj qabeele ki hamiiyat un par ghalib aa gaee. unhon-ne Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ko mukhaatab karke kaha : Allah ki qasam! tum jhootey ho, tum usey qatl nahi kar saktey , aur na tumharey andar itni taqat hai. Mina agar wo tumharey qabila ka hota to tum iske qatl ka naam na letey. iske baad Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) jo Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ke chacherey bhai they khadey huey aur Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ko mukhaatab karke kaha : Allah ki qism ! tum jhootey ho, ham usey zaroor qatl karengey. ab ismein shuba nahi raha ke tum bhi munafiq ho, tum munaafiqon ki taraf se bachaw kartey ho. itney mein Aus w Khazraj ke donon qabeeley bhadak uthey aur aisa malum hota tha ke aapas hi mein lad padengey . us waqt tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par hi tashrif farma they. Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sab ko khamosh karaaney lagey. sab hazraat chup ho gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi khamosh ho gaey. Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke main us roz pura din roti rahi. na mera aansu thamtaa tha aur na aankh lagti thi. bayan kya ke subah ke waqt mere waalidain mere paas aaey. 2 raatein aur aik din mera rotey huey guzar gaya tha. is poorey arse mein na mera aansu ruka aur na neend aai. aisa malum hota tha ke rotey-rotey mera kalejaa phat jaeyga abhi mere waalidain mere paas hi baithey huey they aur main roey ja rahi thi ke qabila Ansar ki aik khatun ne andar aaney ki ijazat chaahi. maine unhein ijazat de di aur wo bhi mere sath baith kar roney lagiin. bayan kya ke ham abhi usi haalat mein they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey. Mina aap ne salam kya aur baith gaey. bayan kya ke jab se mujh par tohmat lagai gaee thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas nahi baithey they. aik mahina guzar gaya tha aur mere barey mein aapko wahi ke zariey koi itlaa nahi di gaee thi. bayan kya ke baithney ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kalima shahadat padha phir farmaya ''ammaa ba'd!'' aey Aaisha! mujhey tumharey barey mein is-is tarah ki khabrein mili hain, agar tum waqei is maamle mein paak w saaf ho to Allah tumhari paakii khud bayan kar dega lekin agar tum ne kisi gunah ka irada kya tha to Allah ki maghfirat chaho aur uske huzoor mein tauba karo kyonke banda jab (apne gunahon ka ( aetraaf kar leta hai aur phir Allah ki bargah mein tauba karta hai to Allah Taala uski tauba qabool kar leta hai. Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna kalam pura kar chukey to mere aansu is tarah khushk ho gaey ke aik qatra bhi mehsus nahi hota tha. maine pahley apne walid se kaha ke meri taraf se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unke kalam ka jawab dein. walid ne farmaya : Allah ki qasam! mein kuchh nahi janta ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mujhey kya kehna chahiye Mina phir maine apni walida se kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo kuchh farmaya hai wo uska jawab dein. walida ne bhi yahi kaha, Allah ki qism ! mujhey kuchh nahi malum ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mujhey kya kehna chahiye isliye maine khud hi arz kya. halanke main bahut kam Umr ladki thi aur Quran Majeed bhi maine zyada nahi padha tha ke Allah ki qism ! mujhey bhi malum hua hai ke aap logon ne is tarah ki afwaahon par kaan dharaa aur baat aap logon ke dilon mein utar gaee aur aap logon ne uski tasdeeq ki. ab agar main ye kahun ke main is tohmat se barii hun to aap log meri tasdeeq nahi karengey aur agar us gunah ka iqrar kar loon aur Allah Taala khub janta hai ke main us se barii hun to aap log uski tasdeeq karne lag jaengey. to Allah ki qasam! meri aur logon ki misal Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke walid jaisi hai. jab unhon-ne kaha thaa (فصبر جميل والله المستعان على ما تصفون) ( Yusuf : 18 ( ''to sabre-jameel behtar hai aur Allah hi ki madad darkaar hai us barey mein jo kuchh tum keh rahe ho'' phir maine apna rukh dusri taraf kar liya aur apne bistar par let gaee. Mina Allah khub janta tha ke main us maamle mein hargiz barii thi aur wo khud meri Bara't (Tauba) zahir karega. kyonke main waqei barii thi lekin Allah ki qasam! mujhey iska koi waham w guman bhi na tha ke Allah Taala wahi ke zariey Quran Majeed mein mere mamley ki safaaii utaarega kyonke main apne ko us se bahut kamtar samajhtii thi ke Allah Taala mere maamle mein khud koi kalam farmaaey, mujhey to sirf itni ummeed thi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) koi khuwab dekhengey jiske zariey Allah Taala meri Bara't (Tauba) kar dega lekin Allah ki qasam! abhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) majlis se uthey bhi nahi they aur na aur koi ghar ka aadmi wahan se utha tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil honii shuru hui aur aap par wo kaifiyat taarii hui jo wahi ki shiddat mein taarii hoti thi. motiyon ki tarah pasiney ke qatrey aap ke chehrey se girney lagey. halanke sardi ka mausam tha. ye us wahi ki wjah se tha jo aap par nazil ho rahi thi. Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir aap ki wo kaifiyat khatm hui to aap muskuraa rahe they. sabse pahlaa kalima jo aap ki zaban Mubarak se nikla wo ye tha. Mina Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Aaisha ! Allah ne tumhari Bara't (Tauba) nazil kar di hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke is par meri walida ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney khadi ho jao. maine kaha, nahi Allah ki qasam! main aap ke samney nahi khadi hongi . main izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke siwa aur kisi ki hamd w sana nahi karoongii (ke usi ne meri Bara't (Tauba) nazil ki hai) bayan kya ke Allah Taala ne nazil farmaya ( إن الذين جاءوا بالإفك‏ ( ''jo log tohmat tarashi mein Sharik huey hain ''das aayatein is silsile mein nazil farmaaein. jab Allah Taala ne (sura Noor mein) ye aayatein meri Bara't (Tauba) ke liye nazil farmain to Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) (jo Mistah bin Asaasa ke kharchey, unse qaraabat aur unki mohtaajii ki wjah se khud uthatey they) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! Mistah ne jab Aaisha ke mutaalliq is tarah ki tohmat tarashi mein hissey liya to main is par ab kabhi kuchh kharch nahi karunga. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) wla يأتل أولو al-Fazal منكم‏ ( yani '' ahal Fazal aur ahal himmat qism na khaaein'' se ( ghafoor رحيم‏ ( tak. (kyonke mistah (Raziallahu anhu) ya doosrey momineen ki usmein shirkat mahz ghalat-fahmii ki bina par thi). Mina chunanche Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qasam! meri tamanna hai ke Allah Taala mujhey us kehney par maaf kar de aur mistah ko jo kuchh diya kartey they, usey phir dene lagey aur kaha ke Allah ki qasam! ab us wazeefe ko main kabhi band nahi karunga. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke mere mamley mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ummul-Momenin Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) se bhi mashwara kya tha. aap ne unse puchha ke Aaisha ke mutaalliq kya maaloomaat hain tumhen ya unmein tum ne kya cheez dekhi hai? unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main apni aankhon aur kanon ko mehfooz rakhti hun (ke unki taraf khilaf waqia nisbat karun ( Allah ki qism ! main unke barey mein khair ke siwa aur kuchh nahi janti . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Zenab hi tamam paak beeviyon mein mere muqabil ki thin lekin Allah Taala ne unke taqwa aur paakbaazii ki wjah se unhein mehfooz rakha. Mina bayan kya ke albatta unki behan hamna ne ghalat rasta ikhtiyar kya aur halaak honey walon ke sath wo bhi halaak hui thin. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke yahi thi wo tafseel us hadis ki jo un badey logon ki taraf se mujh tak pahunchi thi. phir Urwa ne bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Allah ki qism ! jin sahabi ke sath ye tohmat lagai gaee thi wo (apne par us tohmat ko sun kar) kehtey, Subhan-Allah , us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, maine aaj tak kisi aurat ka parda nahi kholaa. Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir us waaqie ke baad wo Allah ke rastey mein Shahid ho gaey they."
4142,"mujh se khaleefa Waleed bin Abdul-Malik ne poochha, kya tum ko malum hai ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) par tohmat lagaaney walon mein they? maine kaha ke nahi, albatta tumhari qaum ( Quraish (ke 2 aadmiyon abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haris ne mujhey khabar di ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unse kaha ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) unke mamley mein khamosh they. phir logon ne Hisham bin-Yoosuf (ya Zohri ( se dobara poochha. unhon-ne yahi kaha ( muslimaa ( usmein shak na kya ( مسيئا (ka lafz nahi kaha aur) عليه (ka lafz ziyawah kya (yani Zohri ne Waleed ko aur kuchh jawab nahi diya aur puraaney nuskha main ( muslimaa (ka lafz tha) ."
4143,"mujh se umme-Roomaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, wo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki walida hain. unhon-ne bayan kya ke main aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) baithi hui thin ke aik Ansari khatun aaein aur kehney lagein ke Allah falan , falan ko tabah kare. umme-Roomaan ne puchha ke kya baat hai? unhon-ne kaha ke mera ladka bhi un logon ke sath Sharik ho gaya hai. jinhoney is tarah ki baat ki hai. umme-Roomaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha ke aakhir baat kya hai? is par unhon-ne tohmat lagaaney walon ki baatein naql kar din. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi ye baatein suniin hain? unhon-ne bayan kya ke haan. unhon-ne puchha aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi ? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, unhon-ne bhii. ye suntey hi wo ghash kha kar gir padiin aur jab hosh aaya to jaadey ke sath bukhar chadhaa hua tha. maine un par unke kapdey daal diye aur achi tarah dhak diya. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur malum farmaya ke unhein kya hua hai? maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! jaadey ke sath bukhar chadh gaya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghaaliban us ne us toofaan ki baat sun li hai. umme-Roomaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ji haan. phir Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne baith kar kaha ke Allah ki qism ! agar main qism khaaun ke main be-gunaah hun to aap log meri tasdeeq nahi karengey aur agar kuchh kahun tab bhi mera uzr nahi sunengey. meri aur aap logon ki Yaqoob (Alaihissalam) aur unke beton jaisi misal hai ke unhon-ne kaha thaa والله المستعان على ما تصفون yaanii ''Allah un baton par jo tum banatey ho madad karne wala hai.'' umme-Roomaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki ye taqreer sun kar lot gaey, kuchh jawab nahi diya. chunanche Allah Taala ne khud unki talaafii nazil ki. wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kehney lagiin bas main Allah hi ka shukr ada karti hun na aap ka na kisi aur kaa."
4144,Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( sura Noor ki aayat mein) qirat ( إذ تلقونه بألسنتكم‏ ( karti thin aur) uski tafseer mein) farmati thin ke) الولق ( jhoot ke mana mein hai. ibne-abi-Mulaika ne bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) un aayatein ko dusron se zyada janti thin kyonke wo khas un hi ke baab mein utri thin.
4145,"main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke samney Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ko bura kehney laga to unhon-ne kaha ke unhein bura na kaho, kyonke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se kuffaar ko jawab detey they aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushrekeen Quraish ki hijo (mazammat) kehney ki ijazat chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir mere nasb ka kya hoga? Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main aapko unse is tarah alag kar loonga jaisey baal gundhey huey aatey se kheench liya jata hai. aur Muhammad-bin-Aqba (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke shekh) ne bayan kya, ham se Usman bin Farqad ne bayan kya, kaha maine Hisham se suna, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ko bura bhala kaha kyonke unhon-ne bhi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) par tohmat lagaaney mein bahut hissey liya tha."
4146,"ham Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unke yahan Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) maujood they aur Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne ashaar suna rahe they. aik sher tha jiska tarjama ye hai. wo sanjeeda aur paak daman hain jis par kabhi tohmat nahi lagai gaee, wo har subah bhookii ho kar naadaan bahnon ka gosht nahi khaatii. is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha lekin tum to aisey nahi Sabit huey. Masruq ne bayan kya ke phir maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se arz kya, aap unhein apne yahan aaney ki ijazat kyon deti hain. jabke Allah Taala unke mutaalliq farma chuka hai  والذي تولى كبره منهم له عذاب عظيم ''aur unmein wo shakhs jo tohmat lagaaney mein sabse zyada zimme daar hai uske liye bada azab hoga.'' is par Ummul-Momenin ne farmaya ke naa-beenaa ho janey se sakht azab aur kya hoga (Hassaan (Raziallahu anhu) ki aankhon ki roshnii aakhir umr mein chali gaee thi) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unse kaha ke Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki himaayat kya kartey they."
4147,"Hudaibiya ke saal ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley to aik din , raat ko barish hui. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne subah ki Namaz padhaaney ke baad ham se khitab kya aur malum farmaya ke malum hai tumharey rab ne kya kaha ? ham ne arz kya ke Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala farmata hai ke subah hui to mere kuchh bandon ne us haalat mein subah ki ke unka eman mujh par tha aur kuchh ne us haalat mein subah ki ke wo mera inkar kiye huey they. to jisne kaha ke ham par ye barish Allah ke rizq , Allah ki rehmat aur Allah ke Fazal se hui hai to wo mujh par eman laney wala hai aur sitaarey ka inkar karne wala hai aur jo shakhs ye kehta hai ke barish falan sitaarey ki taaseer se hui hai to wo sitaron par eman laney wala aur mere sath kufr karne wala hai."
4148,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char Umerey kiye aur siwa us Umerey ke jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj ke sath kya, tamam Umerey Zi-Qaada (ke mahiney ( mein kiye. Hudaibiya ka Umra bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zi-Qada (ke mahiney ( mein karne tashrif le gaey phir doosrey saal ( uski qaza mein) aap ne Zi-Qada mein Umra kya aur aik Umra Jaarana se aap ne kya tha, jahan jange-Hunain ki ghaneemat aap ne taqseem ki thi. ye bhi Zi-Qada mein kya tha aur aik Umra Haj ke sath kya (jo Zil-Hijja mein kya tha) ."
4149,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath suleh Hudaibiya ke saal rawaana huey, tamam sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne ehram baandh liya tha lekin maine abhi ehram nahi baandha tha."
4150,"tum log ( sura انا فتحنا mein) fateh se murad Makka ki fateh letey ho. fateh Makka to bahar-haal fateh hi thi lekin ham jang Hudaibiya ki (baite-rizwan ko haqiqi fateh samajhtey hain. us din ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chaudah so aadmi they. Hudaibiya naam ke aik kunwaan wahan par tha, ham ne usmein se itna pani kheenchaa ke iske andar aik qatra bhi pani baqi na raha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab ye khabar hui (ke pani khatm ho gaya hai) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuwein par tashrif laey aur uske kinarey par baith kar kisi aik bartan mein pani talab farmaya, us se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur kulli ki aur dua farmai . phir Sara pani us kuwein mein daal diya. thodi der ke liye ham ne kuwein ko yun hi rehney diya aur uske baad jitna ham ne chaha usmein se pani piyaa aur apni sawaariyon ko pilaya ."
4151,hamein Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke wo log Hudaibiya ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik hazaar char so ki tadaad mein they ya us se bhi zyada . aik kuwein par padao hua lashkar ne iska ( Sara (pani kheench liya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuwein ke paas tashrif laey aur uski mundeer par baith gaey. phir farmaya ke aik dol mein usi kuwein ka pani laao. pani laya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein kulli ki aur dua farmai . phir farmaya ke kuwein ko yun hi thodi der ke liye rehney do. iske baad Sara lashkar khud bhi sairaab hota raha aur apni sawaariyon ko bhi khub pilaataa raha. yahan tak ke wahan se unhon-ne kooch kya.
4152,"jang Hudaibiya ke mauqe par Sara hi lashkar piyaasaa ho chuka tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik chhaagal tha, iske pani se aap ne wuzu kya. phir sahaba aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya baat hai? sahaba boley ke ya Rasulullah! hamarey paas ab pani nahi raha, na wuzu karne ke liye aur na peeney ke liye. siwa us pani ke jo aap ke bartan mein maujood hai. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath us bartan mein rakha aur pani aap ki ungliyon ke darmyan se chashmey ki tarah phoot phoot kar ubalney laga. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir ham ne pani piyaa bhi aur wuzu bhi kya. (Saalim kehtey hain ke) maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke aap log kitni tadaad mein they? unhon-ne batlaya ke agar ham aik laakh bhi hotey to bhi wo pani kafi ho jata. waisey us waqt hamari tadaad pandarah so thi."
4153,"(Hudaibiya ki suleh ke mauqe par) sahaba ki tadaad chaudah so thi. is par Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bayan kya ke mujh se Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye kaha tha us mauqe par pandarah so sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) maujood they. jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Hudaibiya mein bait ki thi. Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ne bayan kya, ham se Qurrat-bin-Khalid ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne aur Muhammad-bin-Bashaar ne bhi Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ke sath usko riwayat kya hai."
4154,"ham se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jang Hudaibiya ke mauqe par farmaya tha ke tum log tamam zameen walon mein sabse behtar ho. hamari tadaad us mauqe par chaudah so thi. agar aaj meri aankhon mein beenaaii hoti to main tumhen us darakht ka maqam dikhaataa. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Aamash ne ki, unse Salim ne suna aur unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke chaudah so sahaba Hudaibiya mein they."
4155,"darakht walon (baite-rizwan karne waalon) ki tadaad 13 so thi. qabila Aslam muhajireen ka aathwaan hissey they. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Muhammad-bin-Bashaar ne ki, unse Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ne bayan kya aur unse Shoba ne."
4156,pahley saaleheen qabz kiye jaengey. jo zyada Saleh hoga uski Rooh sabse pahley aur jo iske baad ke darjey ka hoga uski iske baad phir raddi aur be-kaar khajoor aur jau ki tarah be-kaar log baqi reh jaeinge jinki Allah ke nazdeek koi qadr nahi hogi.
4157,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par taqriban aik hazaar sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar rawaana huey. jab aap zul-Hulaifa pahunchey to aap ne qurbani ke janwar ko haar pahnaayaa aur un par nishan lagaya aur Umre ka ehram baandhaa. main nahi shumaar kar sakta ke maine ye hadis Sufiyan bin Yasar se kitni baar suni aur aik martaba ye bhi suna ke wo bayan kar rahe they ke mujhey Zohri se nishan lagaaney aur haar pahnaaney ke mutaalliq yad nahi raha. isliye main nahi janta, us se unki murad sirf nishan lagaaney aur haar pahnaaney se thi ya poori hadis se thi."
4158,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par taqriban aik hazaar sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar rawaana huey. jab aap zul-Hulaifa pahunchey to aap ne qurbani ke janwar ko haar pahnaayaa aur un par nishan lagaya aur Umre ka ehram baandhaa. main nahi shumaar kar sakta ke maine ye hadis Sufiyan bin Yasar se kitni baar suni aur aik martaba ye bhi suna ke wo bayan kar rahe they ke mujhey Zohri se nishan lagaaney aur haar pahnaaney ke mutaalliq yad nahi raha. isliye main nahi janta, us se unki murad sirf nishan lagaaney aur haar pahnaaney se thi ya poori hadis se thi."
4159,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dekha ke juein unke chehrey par gir rahi hain to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya us se tumhen takleef hoti hai? wo boley ke ji haan, is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein sar mundwaaney ka hukm diya. aap us waqt Hudaibiya mein they ( Umra ke liye ehram baandhey huey) aur unko ye malum nahi hua tha ke wo Umra se rokey jaengey. Hudaibiya hi mein unko ehram khol dena padega. balke unki to ye aarzoo thi ke Makka mein kisi tarah dakhil hua jaey. phir Allah Taala ne fidye ka hukm nazil farmaya (yani ehram ki haalat mein) sar mundwaaney wghaira par, us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kab ko hukm diya ke aik farq anaaj chh miskinon ko khilaa dein ya aik bakri ki qurbani karein ya teen din rozey rakhein."
4160,"main umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bazar gaya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) se aik naujawaan aurat ne mulaqat ki aur arz kya ke ameerul-momineen ! mere shauhar ki wafat ho gaee hai aur chand chhoti chhotii bachchiyaan chhod gaey hain. Allah ki qasm ke ab na unke paas bakri ke paaey hain ke unko pakka lein, na kheti hai, na doodh ke janwar hain. mujhey dar hai ke wo faqr w faaqa se halaak na ho jaaein. main Khufaaf bin Iimaa Ghifari (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti hun. mere walid Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang Hudaibiya mein Sharik they. ye sun kar umr (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas thodi der ke liye khadey ho gaey, aagey nahi badhey. phir farmaya, marhabaa, tumhara khaandaanii talluq to bahut qaribi hai. phir aap aik bahut qawii oont ki taraf mudey jo ghar mein bandhaa hua tha aur is par 2 borey ghalley se bharey huey rakh diye. un donon boron ke darmyan rupya aur dusri zarurat ki cheezein aur kapdey rakh diye aur uski nakel unke hath mein thamaa kar farmaya ke isey ley jaa, ye khatm na hoga us se pahley hi Allah Taala tujhey is se behtar dega. aik sahib ne is par kaha, aey ameerul-momineen ! aap ne usey bahut de diya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, teri maan tujhey roey, Allah ki qasam! us aurat ke walid aur uske bhai jaisey ab bhi meri nazron ke samney hain ke aik muddat tak aik qile ke muhaasrey mein wo Sharik rahe, aakhir usey fateh kar liya. phir ham subah ko un donon ka hissa maale-ghanimat se wsool kar rahe they."
4161,"main umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bazar gaya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) se aik naujawaan aurat ne mulaqat ki aur arz kya ke ameerul-momineen ! mere shauhar ki wafat ho gaee hai aur chand chhoti chhotii bachchiyaan chhod gaey hain. Allah ki qasm ke ab na unke paas bakri ke paaey hain ke unko pakka lein, na kheti hai, na doodh ke janwar hain. mujhey dar hai ke wo faqr w faaqa se halaak na ho jaaein. main Khufaaf bin Iimaa Ghifari (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti hun. mere walid Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang Hudaibiya mein Sharik they. ye sun kar umr (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas thodi der ke liye khadey ho gaey, aagey nahi badhey. phir farmaya, marhabaa, tumhara khaandaanii talluq to bahut qaribi hai. phir aap aik bahut qawii oont ki taraf mudey jo ghar mein bandhaa hua tha aur is par 2 borey ghalley se bharey huey rakh diye. un donon boron ke darmyan rupya aur dusri zarurat ki cheezein aur kapdey rakh diye aur uski nakel unke hath mein thamaa kar farmaya ke isey ley jaa, ye khatm na hoga us se pahley hi Allah Taala tujhey is se behtar dega. aik sahib ne is par kaha, aey ameerul-momineen ! aap ne usey bahut de diya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, teri maan tujhey roey, Allah ki qasam! us aurat ke walid aur uske bhai jaisey ab bhi meri nazron ke samney hain ke aik muddat tak aik qile ke muhaasrey mein wo Sharik rahe, aakhir usey fateh kar liya. phir ham subah ko un donon ka hissa maale-ghanimat se wsool kar rahe they."
4162,maine wo darakht dekha tha lekin phir baad mein jab aaya to main usey nahi pehchan saka. Mehmood ne bayan kya ke phir baad mein wo darakht mujhey yad nahi raha tha.
4163,"Haj ke iraadey se jatey huey main kuchh aisey logon ke paas se guzra jo Namaz padh rahe they. maine puchha ke ye kon si masjid hai? unhon-ne bataya ke ye wahi darakht hai jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (baite-rizwan li thi. phir main Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ke paas aaya aur maine unhein uski khabar di, unhon-ne kaha mujh se mere walid Musaiyab bin huzn ne bayan kya, wo un logon mein they jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us darakht ke taley bait ki thi. kehtey they jab main doosrey saal wahan gaya to us darakht ki jagah ko bhool gaya. Saeed ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab to us darakht ko pehchan na sakey. tum logon ne kaisey pehchan liya (iske taley masjid bana li ( tum unse zyada ilm waley thahrey ."
4164,unhon-ne bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us darakht ke taley bait ki thi. kehtey they ke jab ham doosrey saal udhar gaey to hamein pata nahi chala ke wo kon sa darakht tha.
4165,Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ki majlis main ( الشجرة (ka zikr hua to wo hansey aur kaha ke mere walid ne mujhey bataya ke wo bhi us darakht ke taley bait mein Sharik they.
4166,"maine Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo (baite-rizwan mein Sharik they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein jab koi sadqa lekar hazir hota to aap dua kartey ke aey Allaah! is par apni rehmat nazil farmaa. chunanche mere walid bhi apna sadqa lekar hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki ke aey Allaah! aale-abii-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) par apni rehmat nazil farmaa."
4167,Harra ki ladai mein log Abdullaah-bin-Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath par bait kar rahe they. Abdullah-bin-Zaid ne puchha ke ibne-Hanzala se kis baat par bait ki ja rahi hai? to logon ne bataya ke maut par. ibne-zaid ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad ab main kisi se bhi maut par bait nahi karunga. wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Hudaibiya mein Sharik they.
4168,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Juma ki Namaz padh kar wapas huey to diiwaaron ka saaya abhi itna nahi hua tha ke ham usmein aaraam kar sakein.
4169,maine Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par aap logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kis cheez par bait ki thi? unhon-ne batlaya ke maut par.
4170,"main Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya, Mubarak ho ! aapko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat naseeb hui aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap ne ped ke nichey bait ki. unhon-ne kaha betey ! tumhen malum nahi ke ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad kya kya kaam kiye hain."
4171,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darakht ke nichey bait ki thi.
4172,"( aayat ( ) إنا فتحنا لك فتحا مبينا‏ ( '' beshak ham ne tumhen khuli hui fateh di. ''ye fateh suleh Hudaibiya thi. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye to marhala aasan hai (ke aap ki tamam agli aur pichhli khataein maaf ho chuki hain) lekin hamara kya hoga? is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaaii ( ليدخل المؤمنين والمؤمنات ) '' isliye ke momin mard aur momin auratein jannat mein dakhil ki jaeyngi jiske nichey nehrein jari hongi .'' Shoba ne bayan kya ke phir main Kufa aaya aur main Qatada se pura waqia bayan kya, phir main dobara Qatada ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unke samney iska zikr kya to unhon-ne kaha ke) إنا فتحنا لك‏ ( '' beshak ham ne tumhen khuli fateh di hai.'' ki tafseer to Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai lekin iske baad) هنيئا مريئا ( (yani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye to har marhala aasan hai) ye tafseer Ikrima se manqul hai."
4173,wo (baite-rizwan mein Sharik they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke main handi mein gadhey ka gosht ubaal raha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik manaadii ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se elaan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumhen gadhey ke gosht ke khaney se mana farmatey hain.
4174,"aur majza'at ne apne hi qabeele ke aik sahabi ke mutaalliq jo (baite-rizwan mein Sharik they aur jinka naam Ahbaan-bin-Aos (Raziallahu anhu) tha, naql kya ke unke aik ghutney mein takleef thi, isliye jab wo sajda kartey to us ghutney ke nichey koi narm takiya rakh letey they."
4175,maano ab bhi wo manzar meri aankhon ke samney hai jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney sattu laya gaya. jisey un hazraat ne piyaa. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Muaz ne Shoba se ki hai.
4176,unhon-ne Aaiz bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi they aur (baite-rizwan mein Sharik they ke kya witr ki Namaz (eik rakaat aur padh kar) todii ja sakti hai? unhon-ne kaha ke agar shuru raat main tu ney witr padh liya ho to aakhir raat mein na padho .
4177,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi safar yani (safare-Hudaibiya ( mein they, raat ka waqt tha aur umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke saath-saath they. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se kuchh puchha lekin (us waqt aap wahi mein mashghool they, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko khabar na thi) aap ne koi jawab nahi diya. unhon-ne phir poochha, aap ne phir koi jawab nahi diya. unhon-ne phir poochha, aap ne is martaba bhi koi jawab nahi diya. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apne dil mein) kaha : umr ! teri maan tujh par roey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se tum ne teen martaba sawal kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen aik martaba bhi jawab nahi diya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir maine apne oont ko eid lagai aur musalmanon se aagey nikal gaya. mujhey dar tha ke kahin mere barey mein koi wahi na nazil ho jaey. abhi thodi der hui thi ke maine suna, aik shakhs mujhey awaz de raha tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine sochaa ke main to pahley hi dar raha tha ke mere barey mein kahin koi wahi nazil na ho jaey. phir main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aapko salam kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke raat mujh par aik sura nazil hui hai aur wo mujhey us tamam kaaynaat se zyada azeez hai jis par suraj tuloo hota hai. phir aap ne sura ( إنا فتحنا لك فتحا مبينا‏ ( '' beshak ham ne aapko khuli hui fateh di hai.'' ki tilawat farmai ."
4178,"jab Zohri ne ye hadis bayan ki (jo aagey mazkoor hui hai) to usmein se kuchh maine yad rakhi aur Mamar ne usko achi tarah yad dilaya . unse Urwa-bin-Zubair ne, unse Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) aur Marwaan-bin-Hakam ne bayan kya, unmein se har aik doosrey se kuchh badhata hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par taqriban aik hazaar sahaba ko sath lekar rawaana huey. phir jab aap zul-Hulaifa pahunchey to aap ne qurbani ke janwar ko haar pahnaayaa aur is par nishan lagaya aur wahin se Umre ka ehram baandhaa. phir aap ne qabila khuza'aa ke aik sahabi ko jaasoosii ke liye bheja aur khud bhi safar jari rakha. jab aap Ghadeerul-ashtaat par pahunchey to aap ke jaasus bhi khabrein lekar aa gaey. jinhoney bataya ke Quraish ne aap ke muqaabley ke liye bahut bada lashkar taiyaar kar rakha hai aur bahut se qabaayel ko bulaya hai. wo aap se jang karne par tuley huey hain aur aapko Baitullah se rokengey. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba se farmaya ke mujhey mashwara do kya tumharey khayal mein ye munasib hoga ke main un kuffaar ki aurton aur bachchon par hamla kar dun jo hamarey Baitullah tak pahunchne mein rukawat bannaa chahtey hain? agar unhon-ne hamara muqaabla kya to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne mushrekeen se hamarey jaasus ko mehfooz rakha hai aur agar wo hamarey muqaabley par nahi aatey to ham unhein aik haarii hui qaum jaan kar chhod dengey. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! aap to sirf Baitullah ke Umra ke liye nikley hain na aap ka irada kisi ko qatl karne ka hai aur na kisi se ladai kaa. isliye aap Baitullah tashrif ley chalein . agar hamein phir bhi koi Baitullah tak janey se rokega to ham us se jang karengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir Allah ka naam lekar safar jari rakho."
4179,"jab Zohri ne ye hadis bayan ki (jo aagey mazkoor hui hai) to usmein se kuchh maine yad rakhi aur Mamar ne usko achi tarah yad dilaya . unse Urwa-bin-Zubair ne, unse Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) aur Marwaan-bin-Hakam ne bayan kya, unmein se har aik doosrey se kuchh badhata hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par taqriban aik hazaar sahaba ko sath lekar rawaana huey. phir jab aap zul-Hulaifa pahunchey to aap ne qurbani ke janwar ko haar pahnaayaa aur is par nishan lagaya aur wahin se Umre ka ehram baandhaa. phir aap ne qabila khuza'aa ke aik sahabi ko jaasoosii ke liye bheja aur khud bhi safar jari rakha. jab aap Ghadeerul-ashtaat par pahunchey to aap ke jaasus bhi khabrein lekar aa gaey. jinhoney bataya ke Quraish ne aap ke muqaabley ke liye bahut bada lashkar taiyaar kar rakha hai aur bahut se qabaayel ko bulaya hai. wo aap se jang karne par tuley huey hain aur aapko Baitullah se rokengey. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba se farmaya ke mujhey mashwara do kya tumharey khayal mein ye munasib hoga ke main un kuffaar ki aurton aur bachchon par hamla kar dun jo hamarey Baitullah tak pahunchne mein rukawat bannaa chahtey hain? agar unhon-ne hamara muqaabla kya to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne mushrekeen se hamarey jaasus ko mehfooz rakha hai aur agar wo hamarey muqaabley par nahi aatey to ham unhein aik haarii hui qaum jaan kar chhod dengey. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! aap to sirf Baitullah ke Umra ke liye nikley hain na aap ka irada kisi ko qatl karne ka hai aur na kisi se ladai kaa. isliye aap Baitullah tashrif ley chalein . agar hamein phir bhi koi Baitullah tak janey se rokega to ham us se jang karengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir Allah ka naam lekar safar jari rakho."
4180,"mujh ko Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di aur unhon-ne Marwaan-bin-Hakam aur Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, donon rawiyon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Umra Hudaibiya ke barey mein bayan kya to Urwa ne mujhey usmein jo kuchh khabar di thi, usmein ye bhi tha ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur (Quraish ka numaainda ( Suhail-bin-Amr Hudaibiya mein aik muqarrara muddat tak ke liye suleh ki dastaawez likh rahe they aur is mein Suhel ne ye shart bhi rakhi thi ke hamara agar koi aadmi aap ke yahan panah ley chahe wo aap ke Deen par hi kyon na ho jaey to aapko usey hamarey hawale karna hi hoga taake ham iske sath jo chaahein karein. Suhel us shart par ad gaya aur kehney laga ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us shart ko qabool kar lein aur musalman us shart par kisi tarah razi na they. majbooran unhon-ne is par guftgu ki (kaha ye kaise ho sakta hai ke musalman ko kaafir ke sipurd kar dein) Suhel ne kaha ke ye nahi ho sakta to suleh bhi nahi ho saktii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye shart bhi taslim kar li aur abu-jandal bin Suhel (Raziallahu anhu) ko unke walid Suhail-bin-Amr ke sipurd kar diya (jo usi waqt Makka se faraar ho kar bedii ko ghaseet'tey huey musalmanon ke paas pahunchey they) ( shart ke mutabiq suleh ki muddat main Makka se faraar ho kar) jo bhi aata Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey wapas kar detey, chahe wo musalman hi kyon na hota. us muddat mein kuchh momin auratein bhi hijrat karke Makka se aaein. umme-kulsoom binte- Aqba-ibn-abii-Mueet bhi unmein se hain jo us muddat main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aai thin, wo us waqt naujawaan thin, unke ghar waley Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se mutalba kya ke unhein wapas kar dein. is par Allah Taala ne momin aurton ke barey mein wo aayat nazil ki jo shart ke munasib thi."
4181,"mujh ko Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di aur unhon-ne Marwaan-bin-Hakam aur Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, donon rawiyon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Umra Hudaibiya ke barey mein bayan kya to Urwa ne mujhey usmein jo kuchh khabar di thi, usmein ye bhi tha ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur (Quraish ka numaainda ( Suhail-bin-Amr Hudaibiya mein aik muqarrara muddat tak ke liye suleh ki dastaawez likh rahe they aur is mein Suhel ne ye shart bhi rakhi thi ke hamara agar koi aadmi aap ke yahan panah ley chahe wo aap ke Deen par hi kyon na ho jaey to aapko usey hamarey hawale karna hi hoga taake ham iske sath jo chaahein karein. Suhel us shart par ad gaya aur kehney laga ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us shart ko qabool kar lein aur musalman us shart par kisi tarah razi na they. majbooran unhon-ne is par guftgu ki (kaha ye kaise ho sakta hai ke musalman ko kaafir ke sipurd kar dein) Suhel ne kaha ke ye nahi ho sakta to suleh bhi nahi ho saktii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye shart bhi taslim kar li aur abu-jandal bin Suhel (Raziallahu anhu) ko unke walid Suhail-bin-Amr ke sipurd kar diya (jo usi waqt Makka se faraar ho kar bedii ko ghaseet'tey huey musalmanon ke paas pahunchey they) ( shart ke mutabiq suleh ki muddat main Makka se faraar ho kar) jo bhi aata Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey wapas kar detey, chahe wo musalman hi kyon na hota. us muddat mein kuchh momin auratein bhi hijrat karke Makka se aaein. umme-kulsoom binte- Aqba-ibn-abii-Mueet bhi unmein se hain jo us muddat main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aai thin, wo us waqt naujawaan thin, unke ghar waley Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se mutalba kya ke unhein wapas kar dein. is par Allah Taala ne momin aurton ke barey mein wo aayat nazil ki jo shart ke munasib thii."
4182,"aayat (ya أيها النبي إذا جاءك المؤمنات‏ (ke nazil honey ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hijrat karke aaney wali aurton ko pahley aazmaatey they aur unke chacha se riwayat hai ke hamein wo hadis bhi malum hai jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya tha ke jo musalman auratein hijrat karke chali aati hain unke shauharon ko wo sab kuchh wapas kar diya jaey jo apni un beeviyon ko wo de chukey hain aur hamein ye bhi malum hua hai ke Abu-Baseer, phir unhon-ne tafseel ke sath hadis bayan ki."
4183,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) fitna ke zamane mein Umra ke irade se nikley. phir unhon-ne kaha ke agar Baitullah janey se mujhey rok diya gaya to main wahi kaam karunga jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha. chunanche aap ne sirf Umre ka ehram baandha kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par sirf Umra hi ka ehram baandha tha.
4184,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ehram baandha aur kaha ke agar mujhey Baitullah janey se rokaa gaya to main bhi wahi kaam karunga jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha. jab aapko kuffaare-Quraish ne Baitullah janey se rokaa to is aayat ki tilawat ki ke لقد كان لكم في رسول الله أسوة حسنة''yaqeenan tum logon ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi behtreen namoona hai.''
4185,"un donon ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se guftgu ki (doosri sanad) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha aur ham se Musa bin Ismail ne bayan kya, unse Juweriya ne bayan kya aur unse Naafe ne ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke kisi ladkey ne unse kaha, agar us saal aap ( Umra karne) na jatey to behtar tha kyonke mujhey dar hai ke aap Baitullah tak nahi pahunch sakengey . is par unhon-ne kaha ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley they, to kuffaare-Quraish ne Baitullah pahunchne se rok diya tha. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni qurbani ke janwar wahin ( Hudaibiya mein) zabah kar diye aur sar ke baal mundwaa diye. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi baal chhotey karwaa liye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske baad farmaya ke main tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine apne uper aik Umra wajib kar liya hai (aur isi tarah tamam sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) par bhi wo wajib ho gaya) agar aaj mujhey Baitullah tak janey diya gaya to main tawaaf kar loonga aur agar mujhey rok diya gaya to main bhi wahi karunga jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha. phir thodi door chaley aur kaha ke main tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine apne uper Umra ke sath Haj ko bhi zaroori qarar de liya hai aur kaha meri nazar main to Haj aur Umra donon aik hi jaisey hain, phir unhon-ne aik tawaaf kya aur aik saee ki (jis din Makka pahunchey) aur donon hi ko pura kya."
4186,"Abdullah, umr (Raziallahu anhu) se pahley Islam mein dakhil huey they, halanke ye ghalat hai. albatta umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko apna aik ghoda laney ke liye bheja tha, jo aik Ansari sahabi ke paas tha taake usi par Sawar ho kar jang mein Sharik hun. usi doran Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) darakht ke nichey baith kar bait ley rahe they. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko abhi uski itlaa nahi hui thi. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne pahley bait ki phir ghoda leney gaey. jis waqt wo usey lekar umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey to wo jang ke liye apni zirah pahan rahe they. unhon-ne us waqt umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bataya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) darakht ke nichey bait ley rahe hain. bayan kya ke phir aap apne ladkey ko sath le gaey aur bait ki. itni si baat thi jis par log ab kehtey hain ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) se pahley ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Islam laey they."
4187,"suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, mukhtalif darakhton ke saaey mein phail gaey they. phir achcha bahut se sahaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke charon taraf jama ho gaey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : betaa Abdullaah! dekho to sahii log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jama kyon ho gaey hain? unhon-ne dekha to sahaba bait kar rahe they. chunanche pahley unhon-ne khud bait kar li. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko aa kar khabar di phir wo bhi gaey aur unhon-ne bhi bait ki."
4188,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umra ( qaza ( kya to ham bhi aap ke sath they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tawaaf kya to ham ne bhi aap ke sath tawaaf kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi to ham ne bhi aap ke sath Namaz padhi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safa w Marwa ki saee bhi ki. ham aap ki ahal Makka se hifazat kartey they taake koi takleef ki baat aapko pesh na aa jaey.
4189,"Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) jab jang safain (jo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) mein hui thi) se wapas aaey to ham unki khidmat mein halaat malum karne ke liye hazir huey. unhon-ne kaha ke us jang ke barey main tum log apni raey aur fikr par fakhr mat karo. main yaume-abu-jandal (Suleh Hudaibiya ( mein bhi maujood tha. agar mere liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm ko manney se inkar mumkin hota to main us din zaroor hukm ki nafarmani karta. Allah aur uska rasool khub jantey hain ke jab ham ne kisi mushkil kaam ke liye apni talwaaron ko apne kandhon par rakha to soorate-haal aasan ho gaee aur hamne mushkil hal kar li. lekin us jang ka kuchh ajeeb haal hai, usmein ham (fitney ke) aik koney ko band kartey hain to doosra kona khul jata hai. ham nahi jantey ke ham ko kya tadbeer karni chahiye"
4190,"wo Umra Hudaibiya ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to juein unke chehrey par gir rahi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke ye juein jo tumharey sar se gir rahi hain, takleef de rahi hain? unhon-ne arz kya : ji haan! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir sar mundwaa lo aur teen din roza rakh lo ya chh miskinon ka khana khilaa do ya phir koi qurbani kar daalo. ( sar mundwaaney ka fidya hoga) Ayub sakhtiyan ne bayan kya ke mujhey malum nahi ke un teenon umur (baton) mein se pahley Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kon si baat irshad farmai thi."
4191,suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they aur ehram baandhey huey they. idhar mushrekeen hamein Baitullah tak janey nahi dena chahtey they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke mere sar par baal badey badey they jin se juein mere chehrey par girney lagiin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey dekh kar malum farmaya ke kya ye juein takleef de rahi hain? maine kaha : ji haan. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir ye aayat nazil huii فمن كان منكم مريضا أو به أذى من رأسه ففدية من صيام أو صدقة أو نسك ''to agar tum mein koi mareez ho ya uske sar mein koi takleef dene wali cheez ho to usey ( baal mundwaa leney chaahiein aur) teen din ke rozey ya sadqa ya qurbani ka fidya dena chaahiye.''
4192,"qabaayel ukul w Uraina ke kuchh log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Madina aaey aur Islam mein dakhil ho gaey. phir unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! ham log maweshii rakhtey they, khet wghaira hamarey paas nahi they, (is liye ham sirf doodh par Basar oqaat kya kartey they) aur unhein Madina ki aab w hua na-muwaafiq aai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh oont aur charwaha unke sath kar diya aur farmaya ke inhiin oonton ka doodh aur peshab piyo (to tumhen sihat hasil ho jaeygi) wo log ( charaagaah ki taraf ( gaey. lekin maqam Harra ke kinarey pahunchtey hi wo Islam se phir gaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke charwaahey ko qatl kar diya aur oonton ko lekar bhaagney lagey. uski khabar jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mili to aap ne chand sahaba ko unke peechhey daudaayaa. (wo pakad kar Madina laey gaey.) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se unki aankhon mein garm salaaiyaan pher di gain aur unke hath aur pair kaat diye gaey (kyonke unhon-ne bhi aisa hi kya tha) aur unhein Harra ke kinarey chhod diya gaya. aakhir wo usi haalat mein mar gaey. Qatada ne bayan kya ke hamein ye riwayat pahunchi hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske baad sahaba ko sadqe ka hukm diya aur musla (maqtool ki laash bigaadnaa ya eiizaa de kar usey qatl karnaa) se mana farmaya aur Shoba, Aban aur Hammad ne Qatada se bayan kya ke (ye log) Uraina ke qabeeley ke they (ukul ka naam nahi liyaa) aur Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir aur Ayub ne bayan kya, unse abu-Qilaba ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke qabila ukul ke kuchh log aaey."
4193,"khaleefa Umar-bin-abdul-Azeez ne aik din logon se mashwara kya ke us ''qasaama'' ke barey mein tumhari kya raey hai? logon ne kaha ke ye haq hai. iska faisla Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur phir Khulafae-Rashedeen aap se pahley kartey rahe hain. abu-Rijaa ne bayan kya ke us waqt abu-Qilaba , Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke takht ke peechhey they. itney mein anbasaa bin Saeed ne kaha ke phir qabila Uraina ke logon ke barey mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis kahan gaii? is par abu-Qilaba ne kaha ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khud mujh se ye bayan kya. Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb ne (apni riwayat mein) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se sirf Uraina ka naam liya aur abu-Qilaba ne apni riwayat mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se sirf ukul ka naam liya phir yahi qissa bayan kya."
4194,"mein fajr ki azan se pahley (Madina se bahar Ghaaba ki taraf niklaa) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki doodh dene wali oontniyan zaatul-qard mein charaa karti thin. unhon-ne bayan kya ke rastey mein mujhey Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghulam miley aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki oontniyan pakad li gain hain. maine puchha ke kis ne pakda hai? unhon-ne bataya ke qabila Ghatfan walon ne. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir maine teen martaba badi zor-zor se pukaaraa, ya sabaahaa! unhon-ne bayan kya ke apni awaz maine Madina ke donon kinaron tak pahuncha di aur uske baad mein seedha tezi ke sath daudta hua aagey badha aur aakhir unhein ja liya. us waqt wo janwaron ko pani pilaaney ke liye utrey they. maine un par teer barsaney shuru kar diye. main teerandaazii mein maahir tha aur ye sher kehta jata tha ''main ibne-Akwa hun, aaj daleelon ki barbadi ka din hai ''main yahi rajz padhta raha aur aakhir oontniyan unse chhudaa lein balke tees chaadrein unki mere qabzey mein aa gaiin. Salma ne bayan kya ke iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar aa gaey. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! maine teer maar-maar kar unko pani nahi diya aur wo abhi piyaasey hain. aap fauran unke ta'aqub ke liye fauj bhej dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey ibne-Akwa! jab to kisi par qaabu pa ley to narmii ikhtiyar kar. Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, phir ham wapas aagey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey apni ontni par peechhey bitha kar laey yahan tak ke ham Madina wapas aa gaey."
4195,"Khaibar ki jang ke liye wo bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley they. (bayaan kya) jab ham maqaame-sahbaa mein pahunchey jo khaibar ke nasheb mein waaqe hai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr ki Namaz padhi phir aap ne khane-pine ka saamaane-safar mangwaayaa. sattu ke siwa aur koi cheez aap ki khidmat mein nahi laai gaee. wo sattu aap ke hukm se bhigoya gaya aur wahi aap ne bhi khaya aur ham ne bhi khaayaa. iske baad maghrib ki Namaz ke liye aap khadey huey (choonke wuzu pahley se maujood tha) isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi sirf kulli ki aur ham ne bhi, phir Namaz padhi aur us Namaz ke liye naey sirey se wuzu nahi kya."
4196,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaibar ki taraf nikley. raat ke waqt hamara safar jari tha ke aik sahib (Usaid-bin-Huzair) ne Aamir se kaha : aamir! apne kuchh sher sunaao, Aamir shaair they. us farmaaish par wo sawari se utar kar hadii padhney lagey. kahaa ''aey Allaah! agar to na hota to hamein seedha rasta na miltaa, na ham sadqa kar saktey aur na ham Namaz padh saktey. to hamari jaldi maghfirat kar, jab tak ham zinda hain hamari jaanein terey rastey mein fidaa hain aur agar hamari mudbhed ho jaey to hamein Sabit rakh ham par sakeenat nazil farma, hamein jab ( baatil ki taraf ( bulaya jata hai to ham inkar kar detey hain, aaj chilla chillaa kar wo hamarey khilaf maidan mein aaey hain.'' nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kon sher keh raha hai? logon ne bataya ke Aamir bin Akwaa hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah is par apni rehmat nazil farmaai . sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne to unhein shahadat ka mustahiq qarar de diya, kash! abhi aur hamein unse fayda uthaney detey. phir ham khaibar aaey aur qile ka muhaasra kya, us doran hamein sakht takaaleef aur faaqon se guzarna padaa. aakhir Allah Taala ne hamein fateh ata farmai. jis din qila fateh hona tha, uski raat jab hui to lashkar mein jagah-jagah aag jal rahi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ye aag kaisi hai, kis cheez ke liye usey jagah-jagah jalaa rakha hai? sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke gosht pakaaney ke liye, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kis janwar ka gosht hai? sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke paaltu gadhon ka, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tamam gosht phenk do aur haandiyon ko tod do. aik sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aisa na kar lein ke gosht to phenk dein aur haandiyon ko dho lein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yun hi kar lo phir ( din mein jab sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne jang ke liye) saf bandi ki to chunkey Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ki talwaar chhoti thi, isliye unhon-ne jab aik Yahudi ki pindlii par) jhuk kar) waar karna chaha to khud unhiin ki talwaar ki dhaar se unke ghutney ka uper ka hissa zakhmi ho gaya aur unki shahadat usi mein ho gaee. bayan kya ke phir jab lashkar wapas ho raha tha to Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke mujhey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha aur mera hath pakad kar farmaya, kya baat hai? maine arz kya, mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon, kuchh logon ka khayal hai ke Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sara amal akaarat ho gaya (kyonke khud apni hi talwaar se unki wafat huii). Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jhoota hai wo shakhs jo is tarah ki baatein karta hai, unhein to dohra ajr milega phir aap ne apni donon ungliyon ko aik sath milaayaa, unhon-ne takleef aur mashaqqat bhi uthai aur Allah ke rastey mein jihad bhi kya, shayad hi koi arabii ho, jisne un jaisi misal qaaim ki ho. ham se Quteba ne bayan kya."
4197,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaibar raat ke waqt pahunchey. aap ka qaaeyda tha ke jab kisi qaum par hamla karne ke liye raat ke waqt mauqe par pahunchtey to fauran hi hamla nahi kartey balke subah ho jati jab kartey. chunanche subah ke waqt Yahudi apne kulhaadey aur tokrey lekar bahar nikley lekin jab unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha to shor karne lagey ke Muhammad , Allah ki qism ! Muhammad lashkar lekar aa gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khaibar barbad hua, ham jab kisi qaum ke maidan mein utar jatey hain to daraaye huey logon ki subah buri ho jati hai."
4198,"ham khaibar subah ke waqt pahunchey, Yahudi apne phaawdey waghaira lekar bahar aaey lekin jab unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha to chalaney lagey Muhammad ! Allah ki qism Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) lashkar lekar aa gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki zaat sabse buland w bartar hai. yaqinan jab ham kisi qaum ke maidan mein utar jayen to phir daraaey huey logon ki subah buri ho jati hai. phir hamein wahan gadhey ka gosht mila lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se elaan karne waley ne elaan kya ke Allah aur uske rasool tumhen gadhey ka gosht khaney se mana kartey hain ke ye napak hai."
4199,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik aaney waley ne hazir ho kar arz kya ke gadhey ka gosht khaya ja raha hai. is par aap ne khamoshi ikhtiyar ki phir dobara wo hazir huey aur arz kya ke gadhey ka gosht khaya ja raha hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is martaba bhi khamosh rahe, phir wo teesri martaba aaey aur arz kya ke gadhey khatm ho gaey. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik manaadii se elaan karaya ke Allah aur uske rasool tumhen paaltu gadhon ke gosht ke khaney se mana kartey hain. chunanche tamam haandiyaan ulat di gain halanke wo gosht ke sath josh mar rahi thin."
4200,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne subah ki Namaz khaibar ke qareeb pahunch kar ada ki, abhi andhera tha phir farmaya, Allah ki zaat sabse buland w bartar hai. khaibar barbad hua, yaqinan jab ham kisi qaum ke maidan mein utar jatey hain to daraaey logon ki subah buri ho jati hai. phir Yahudi galiyon mein dartey huey nikley. aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke jang karne waley logon ko qatl kara diya aur aurton aur bachchon ko qaid kar liya. qaidiyon mein Ummul-Momenin Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) bhi thin jo Dahiya Kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) ke hisse mein aai thin. phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aa gain . chunanche aap ne unse nikah kar liya aur mehar mein unhein aazad kar diya. Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb ne Sabit se puchha : abu-Muhammad ! kya tum ne ye puchha tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko mehar kya diya tha? Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne asbaat mein sar hilaayaa ."
4201,Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qaidiyon mein thin lekin aap ne unhein aazad karke unse nikah kar liya tha. Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein mehar kya diya tha? unhon-ne kaha ke khud unhein ko unke mehar mein diya tha yani unhein aazad kar diya tha.
4202,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apne lashkar ke saath) mushrekeen (yani ( khaibar ke yahudiyon ka muqaabla kya. donon taraf se logon ne jang ki, phir jab aap apne khemey ki taraf wapas huey aur Yahudi bhi apne khemon mein wapas chaley gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik sahabi ke mutaalliq kisi ne zikr kya ke yahudiyon ka koi bhi aadmi agar unhein mil jaey to wo iska peechhaa karke usey qatl kiye baghair nahi rehtey. kaha gaya ke aaj falan shakhs hamari taraf se jitni bahaadurii aur himmat se lada hai shayad itni bahaadurii se koi bhi nahi lada hoga lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke mutaalliq farmaya ke wo ahale-dozakh mein se hai. aik sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke phir main unke saath-saath rahoonga, bayan kya ke phir wo unke peechhey ho liye jahan wo thahartey ye bhi thahar jatey aur jahan wo daud kar chaltey ye bhi daudney lagtey. bayan kya ke phir wo sahib zakhmi ho gaey, intihai shadeed taur par aur chaha ke jaldi maut aa jaey. isliye unhon-ne apni talwaar zameen mein gaad di aur uski nauk seene ke muqabil karke is par gir padey aur is tarah khudkushii kar li. ab doosrey sahabi (jo unki justju mein lagey huey they) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya main gawahi deta hun ke aap Allah ke rasool hain. puchha kya baat hai? un sahabi ne arz kya ke jinke mutaalliq abhi aap ne farmaya tha ke wo ahale-dozakh mein se hain to logon par aap ka ye farmana bada sakht guzra tha. maine unse kaha ke main tumharey liye unke peechhey peechhey jata hun. chunanche main unke saath-saath raha. aik mauqe par jab wo shadeed zakhmi ho gaey to is khahish mein ke maut jaldi aa jaey apni talwaar unhon-ne zameen mein gaad di aur uski nauk ko apne seene ke samney karke is par gir padey aur is tarah unhon-ne khud apni jaan ko halaak kar diya. usi mauqe par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke insan zindagi bhar jannat walon ke amal karta hai halanke wo ahale-dozakh mein se hota hai. isi tarah doosra shakhs zindagi bhar ahale-dozakh ke amal karta hai halanke wo jannati hota hai."
4203,ham khaibar ki jang mein Sharik they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sahib ke mutaalliq jo aap ke sath they aur khud ko musalman kehtey they farmaya ke ye shakhs ahale-dozakh mein se hai. phir jab ladai shuru hui to wo sahib badi madaangii se ladey aur bahut zyada zakhmi ho gaey. mumkin tha ke kuchh log shube mein pad jatey lekin un sahib ke liye zakhmon ki takleef naaqaabile-bardaasht thi. chunanche unhon-ne apne tarkash mein se teer nikala aur apne seene mein chubho diya. ye manzar dekh kar musalman daudtey huey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! Allah Taala ne aap ka farman sach kar dikhaayaa. us shakhs ne khud apne seeney mein teer chubho kar khudkushii kar li hai. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey falan ! ja aur elaan kar de ke jannat mein sirf momin hi dakhil hongey. yun Allah Taala apne Deen ki madad faajir shakhs se bhi ley leta hai. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Mamar ne Zohri se ki.
4204,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Khaibar ki jang mein maujood they aur ibne-Mubarak ne bayan kya, unse Yunus ne, unse Zohri ne, unse Saeed-bin-Musaiyab (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Saleh ne Zohri se ki aur Zubaidi ne bayan kya, unhein Zohri ne khabar di, unhein Abdur-Rehman bin Kab ne khabar di aur unhein Ubaidullah bin Kab ne khabar di ke mujhey un sahabi ne khabar di jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Khaibar ki jang mein maujood they. Zohri ne bayan kya aur mujhey Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah aur Saeed-bin-Musaiyab (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
4205,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar par lashkar kashii ki ya yun bayan kya ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( khaibar ki taraf ( rawaana huey to ( rastey mein) log aik wadi mein pahunchey aur buland awaz ke sath takbeer kehney lagey Allahu-akbar , Allahu-akbar , la ilaaha-illallaah ''Allah sabse buland w bartar hai, Allah sabse buland w bartar hai, Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi. '' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apni jaanon par raham karo, tum kisi behrey ko ya aisey shakhs ko nahi pukar rahe ho, jo tum se door ho, jisey tum pukar rahe ho wo sabse zyada sunney wala aur tumharey bahut nazdeek hai balke wo tumharey sath hai. main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari ke peechhey tha. maine jab (لا حول wla قوة إلا بالله) kahaa to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sun liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Abdullah-bin-Qais ! maine kaha labbaik ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya main tumhen aik kalima na bata dun jo jannat ke khazaanon mein se aik khazaana hai? maine arz kya zaroor bataaiye, ya Rasulullah! mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo kalima yahi hai (لا حول wla قوة إلا بالله) yaanii gunahon se bachna aur neki karna ye usi waqt mumkin hai jab Allah ki madad shamil ho."
4206,"maine Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ki pindlii mein aik zakhm ka nishan dekh kar unse puchha : aey abu-Muslim ! ye zakhm ka nishan kaisa hai? unhon-ne bataya ke Khaibar ki jang mein mujhey ye zakhm laga tha, log kehney lagey ke Salma zakhmi ho gaya. chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen martaba is par dam kya, uski barkat se aaj tak mujhey us zakhm se koi takleef nahi hui."
4207,"aik jang ( khaibar ( main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur mushrekeen ka muqaabla hua aur khub jam kar jang hui aakhir donon lashkar apne apney khemon ki taraf wapas huey aur musalmanon mein aik aadmi tha jinhein mushrekeen ki taraf ka koi shakhs kahin mil jata to uska peechhaa karke qatl kiye baghair wo na rehtey. kaha gaya ke ya Rasulullah ! jitni bahaadurii se aaj falan shakhs lada hai, itni bahaadurii se to koi na lada hoga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo ahale-dozakh mein se hai. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, agar ye bhi dozakhi hai to phir ham jaisey log kis tarah jannat waley ho saktey hain? is par aik sahabi boley ke main unke peechhey peechhey rahunga . chunanche jab wo daudtey ya aahista chaltey to main unke saath-saath hota. aakhir wo zakhmi huey aur chaha ke maut jald aa jaey. isliye wo talwaar ka qabza zameen mein gaad kar uski nauk seeney ke muqabil karke is par gir padey. is tarah se us ne khudkushii kar li. ab wo sahabi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke aap Allah ke rasool hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kya baat hai? unhon-ne tafseel batai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik shakhs bazahir jannatiyon jaisey amal karta rehta hai halanke wo ahale-dozakh mein se hota hai. isi tarah aik doosra shakhs bazahir dozkhiyon ke se amal karta rehta hai halanke wo jannati hota hai."
4208,Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( Basra ki masjid mein) Juma ke din logon ko dekha ke (unke saron par) chaadrein hain jin par phool kudhey huey hain. unhon-ne kaha ke ye log us waqt khaibar ke yahudiyon ki tarah malum hotey hain.
4209,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Khaibar ki jang main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath na ja sakey they kyonke wo aashoob chashm (aankhon ki takleef) mein mubtala they. (jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ja chukey) to unhon-ne kaha, main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang se peechhey rahoon (aisaa nahi ho saktaa) ? chunanche wo bhi aa gaey. jis din khaibar fateh hona tha, jab uski raat aai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kal main (Islaamii) jhanda us shakhs ko doonga ya farmaya ke jhanda wo shakhs lega jisey Allah aur uska rasool azeez rakhtey hain aur jiske hath par fateh hasil hogi. ham sab hi us khush-naseebi ke ummeedwaar they lekin kaha gaya ke ye hain Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhiin ko jhanda diya aur unhiin ke hath par khaibar fateh hua."
4210,"Khaibar ki jang main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke kal mein jhanda aik aisey shakhs ko doonga jiske hathon par Allah Taala fateh ata farmaeyga aur jo Allah aur uske rasool se mohabbat rakhta hai aur Allah aur uske rasool bhi usey azeez rakhtey hain. rawi ne bayan kya ke wo raat sab ki is fikr mein guzar gaee ke dekhein, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jhanda kisey ata farmatey hain. subah hui to sab khidmate-nabawii mein hazir huey aur is ummeed ke sath ke jhanda unhiin ko miley lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke Ali-bin abi-Talib kahan hain? arz kya gaya ke ya Rasulullah ! wo to aankhon ki takleef mein mubtala hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein bula laao. jab wo laey gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna thook unki aankhon mein lagaya aur unke liye dua ki. us dua ki barkat se unki aankhen itni achi ho gain jaisey pahley koi bimari hi nahi thi. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne jhanda sanbhaal kar arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main unse us waqt tak jang karunga jab tak wo hamarey hi jaisey na ho jaaein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yun hi chaltey raho, unke maidan mein utar kar pahley unhein Islam ki dawat do aur bataao ke Allah ka un par kya haq hai. Allah ki qism ! agar tumharey zariey aik shakhs ko bhi hidayat mil jaey to ye tumharey liye surkh oonton se behtar hai."
4211,"ham khaibar aaey phir jab Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khaibar ki fateh inayat farmai to aap ke samney Safiya-binte-Huyi bin akhtab (Raziallahu anhu) ki khoobsoortii ka kisi ne zikr kya, unke shauhar qatl ho gaey they aur unki shadi abhi nai hui thi. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein apne liye ley liya aur unhein sath lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rawaana huey. aakhir jab ham maqaame-saddassahbaa mein pahunchey to Ummul-Momenin Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) haiz se paak huin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke sath khilwat farmai phir aap ne hees banaya. (jo khajoor ke sath ghi aur paneer wghaira mila kar banaya jata hai) aur usey chhotey se aik dastar-khuwaan par rakh kar mujh ko hukm farmaya ke jo log tumharey qareeb hain unhein bula lo. Ummul-Momenin Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se yahi walima tha. phir ham Madina ke liye rawaana huey to maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye abaa oont ki kohan mein baandh di taake peechhey se wo usey pakdey rahen aur apne oont ke paas baith kar apna ghutna is par rakha aur Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) apna paon Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghutney par rakh kar sawar huin."
4212,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye khaibar ke raaste mein teen din tak qiyam farmaya aur aakhiri din unse khilwat farmai aur wo bhi ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) mein shamil ho gaiin.
4213,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina aur khaibar ke darmyan (maqaame-Saddassehbaa mein) teen din tak qiyam farmaya aur wahin Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) se khilwat ki thi phir maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se musalmanon ko walima ki dawat di. aap ke walima mein na roti thi, na gosht tha sirf itna hua ke aap ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko dastar-khuwaan bichhaaney ka hukm diya aur wo bichhaa diya gaya. phir is par khajoor , paneer aur ghi (ka maleeda) rakh diya. musalmanon ne kaha ke Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) mein se hain ya baandi hain? kuchh logon ne kaha ke agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein pardey mein rakha to wo ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) mein se hongi aur agar aap ne unhein pardey mein nahi rakha to phir ye iski alamat hogi ke wo baandi hain. aakhir jab kooch ka waqt hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye apni sawari par peechhey baithney ki jagah banai aur unke liye parda kya."
4214,"ham khaibar ka muhaasra kiye huey they ke kisi shakhs ne chamdey ki aik kuppii phenkii jis mein charbi thi, main usey uthaney ke liye douda lekin maine jo mud kar dekha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maujood they. main sharm se pani paanii ho gaya."
4215,Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne lehsun aur paaltu gadhon ke khaney se mana farmaya tha. lehsun khaney ki manaahii ka zikr sirf Naafe se bayan hui hai aur paaltu gadhon ke khaney ki manaahii sirf Salim se bayan hui hai.
4216,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par aurton se mutaa ki manaahii ki thi aur paaltu gadhon ke khaney ki bhii.
4217,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par paaltu gadhey ka gosht khaney ki manaahii ki thi.
4218,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne paaltu gadhon ke gosht ki manaahii ki thi.
4219,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par gadhey ke gosht khaney ki manaahii ki thi aur ghodon ke gosht khaney ki ijazat di thi.
4220,"Khaibar ki jang mein aik mauqe par ham bahut bhookey they, idhar haandiyon mein ubaal aa raha tha ( gadhey ka gosht pakaya ja raha tha) aur kuchh paak bhi gain thin ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke manaadii ne elaan kya ke gadhey ke gosht ka aik zarra bhi na khaao aur usey phenk do. ibne-abii-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir kuchh logon ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski manaahii isliye ki hai ke abhi usmein se khums nahi nikala gaya tha aur kuchh logon ka khayal tha ke aap ne uski waqei manaahii ( hamesha ke liye) kar di hai, kyonke ye gandagi khata hai."
4221,"wo log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, phir unhein gadhey miley to unhon-ne unka gosht pakaya lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke manaadii ne elaan kya ke haandiyaan undel do."
4222,"wo log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, phir unhein gadhey miley to unhon-ne unka gosht pakaya lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke manaadii ne elaan kya ke haandiyaan undel do."
4223,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par farmaya tha ke haandiyon ka gosht phenk do, us waqt haandiyaan choolhey par rakhi ja chuki thin."
4224,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par farmaya tha ke haandiyon ka gosht phenk do, us waqt haandiyaan choolhey par rakhi ja chuki thin."
4225,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang mein Sharik they phir pehli hadis ki tarah riwayat naql ki.
4226,"Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke paaltu gadhon ka gosht ham phenk dein, kachchaa bhi aur pakka hua bhi, phir hamein iske khaney ka kabhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm nahi diya."
4227,mujhey malum nahi ke aaya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne gadhey ka gosht khaney se isliye mana kya tha ke us se bojh dhoney waley ka kaam liya jata hai aur aap ne pasand nahi farmaya ke bojh dhoney waley janwar khatm ho jayen ya aap ne sirf Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par paaltu gadhon ke gosht ki manaahii ki thi.
4228,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khaibar ki jang mein (maal ghaneemat se) sawaaron ko 2 hissey diye they aur paidal faujiyon ko aik hissey , uski tafseer Naafe ne is tarah ki hai agar kisi shakhs ke sath ghoda hota to usey teen hissey miltey they aur agar ghoda na hota to sirf aik hissey milta tha."
4229,main aur Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. ham ne arz kya ke aap ne banu-muttalib ko to khaibar ke khums mein se inayat farmaya hai aur hamein nazar-andaaz kar diya hai halanke aap se qaraabat mein ham aur wo barabar they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya yaqinan banu-Haashim aur banu-muttalib aik hain. Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu- Abd Shams aur banu- Nofal ko) khums mein se) kuchh nahi diya tha.
4230,"jab hamein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hijrat ke mutaalliq khabar mili to ham Yaman mein they. isliye ham bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hijrat ki niyat se nikal padey . main aur mere 2 bhaaii, main donon se chhota tha. mere aik bhai ka naam abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) tha aur doosrey ka abu-Raham. unhon-ne kaha ke kuchh uper pachaas ya unhon-ne yun bayan kya ke tirpan ( 53 (ya baawan ( 52 ( meri qaum ke log sath they. ham kashtii par Sawar huey lekin hamari kashtii ne hamein Najashi ke mulk Habsha mein la dala. wahan hamari mulaqat Jafar bin abii-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu) se ho gaee, jo pahley hi Makka se hijrat karke wahan pahunch chukey they. ham ne wahan unhein ke sath qiyam kya, phir ham sab Madina sath rawaana huey. yahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein us waqt pahunchey jab aap khaibar fateh kar chukey they. kuchh log ham kashtii walon se kehney lagey ke ham ne tum se pahley hijrat ki hai aur Asma binte- Umais (Raziallahu anhu) jo hamarey sath Madina aai thin, Ummul-Momenin Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huin, unse mulaqat ke liye wo bhi Najashi ke mulk mein hijrat karne walon ke sath hijrat karke chali gaee thin. umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar pahunchey. us waqt Asmaa-bint-amees (Raziallahu anhu) wahin thin. jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein dekha to malum farmaya ke ye kon hain? Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke Asma binte- amees. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha achchha wahi jo Habsha se bahrii safar karke aai hain? Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke ji haan. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke ham tum logon se hijrat mein aagey hain isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ham tumharey muqable mein zyada qareeb hain. Asma (Raziallahu anha) is par bahut ghussa ho gain aur kaha hargiz nahi : Allah ki qasam! tum log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rahe ho, tum mein jo bhookey hotey they usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khana khilaatey they aur jo na-waqif hotey usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) waaz aur nasihat kya kartey they. lekin ham bahut door Habsha mein ghairon aur dushmanon ke mulk mein rahtey they, ye sab kuchh ham ne Allah aur uske rasool ke rastey hi main to kya aur Allah ki qasam! mein us waqt tak na khana khaaungii na pani piyungii jab tak tumhari baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se na keh loon. hamein azeeyat di jati thi, dhamkaayaa-daraayaa jata tha. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr karoongii aur aap se iske mutaalliq poochhoongii. Allah ki qism na main jhoot boloongii, na kaj rawii ikhtiyar karun gii aur na kisi ( khilaf waqia baat ka ( izafa karun gii."
4231,chunanche jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to unhon-ne arz kya : ya Nabi Allaah! umr (Raziallahu anhu) is tarah ki baatein kartey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke phir tum ne unhein kya jawab diya? unhon-ne arz kya ke maine unhein ye jawab diya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke wo tum se zyada mujh se qareeb nahi hain. unhein aur unke sathiyon ko sirf aik hijrat hasil hui aur tum kashtii walon ne 2 hijraton ka sharf hasil kya. unhon-ne bayan kya ke us waaqie ke baad abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) aur tamam kashtii waley mere paas giroh dar giroh aaney lagey aur mujh se us hadis ke mutaalliq poochhney lagey. unke liye duniya main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke unke mutaalliq us irshad se zyada khush kun aur baaise-fakhr aur koi cheez nahi thi.
4232,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab mere Ash-ari Ahbaab raat mein aatey hain to main unki Quran ki tilawat ki awaz pehchan jata hun. bhale hi din mein, maine unki iqamat gaahon ko na dekha ho lekin jab raat mein wo Quran padhtey hain to unki awaz se main unki iqamat gaahon ko pehchan leta hun. mere unhi Ash-ari bhaiyon mein aik mard daanaa bhi hai ke jab kahin uski sawaaron se mudbhed ho jati hai ya aap ne farmaya ke dushman se, to unse kehta hai ke mere doston ne kaha hai ke tum thodi der ke liye unka intizar kar lo."
4233,khaibar ki fateh ke baad ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (maale-ghaneemat mein) hamara bhi hissey lagaya. aap ne hamarey siwa kisi bhi aisey shakhs ka hissa maale-ghanimat mein nahi lagaya jo fateh ke waqt (Islaamii lashkar ke saath) maujood na raha ho.
4234,"jab khaibar fateh hua to maale-ghanimat mein sona aur chandi nahi mila tha balke gaaey, oont, saman aur baghaat miley they phir ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath waadii-ul-Quraa ki taraf lautey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik mud'am naam ke ghulam tha jo bani Zubaab ke aik sahabi ne aapko hadiye mein diya tha. wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka kajaawa utaar raha tha ke kisi naa-maaloom samt se aik teer aa kar unke laga. logon ne kaha Mubarak ho : shahaadat! lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hargiz nahi, us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai jo chadar us ne khaibar mein taqseem se pahley maale-ghanimat mein se churaaii thi wo is par aag ka sho'la bin kar bhadak rahi hai. ye sun kar aik doosrey sahabi aik ya do tasmey lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke ye maine utha liye they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye bhi jahannam ka tasma bantaa."
4235,"unhon-ne kaha haan us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai agar iska khatrah na hota ke baad ki naslein be-jaaidaad reh jaeyngi aur unke paas kuchh na hoga to jo bhi basti mere zamaanae-khilaafat mein fateh hoti, main usey isi tarah taqseem kar deta jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ki taqseem ki thi. main un fateh ki hui zameenon ko baad mein aaney waley musalmanon ke liye mehfooz chhodey ja raha hun taake wo usey taqseem kartey rahen."
4236,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha agar baad mein aaney waley musalmanon ka khayal na hota to jo basti bhi mere daur mein fateh hoti, mein usey isi tarah taqseem kar deta jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ki taqseem kar di thi."
4237,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se (khaibar ki ghaneemat mein se) hissey maangaa. Saeed bin Aas ke aik ladkey ( Aban bin Saeed (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! unhein na dijiye. is par Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye shakhs to ibne-Qoqal ka qaatil hai. Aban (Raziallahu anhu) is par boley hairat hai is (Wabr) ( billi se chhota aik janwar ( par jo qudoom as-Sanaan pahaadii se utar aaya hai.
4238,"Aban (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi sariya (raat ko nikalney wali jangjuon ki chhoti tukdii) par Madina se Najad ki taraf bheja tha. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Aban (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke sathi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, khaibar fateh ho chuka tha. un logon ke ghodey tang chhaal hi ke they, (yani unhon-ne muhim mein koi kamiyabi hasil nahi ki thi). Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ghaneemat mein unka hissey na lagaaiye. is par Aban (Raziallahu anhu) boley aey Wabr! teri haisiyat to sirf ye ke qudoom-as-Sanaan ki choti se utar aaya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Aban ! baith ja ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un logon ka hissa nahi lagaya ."
4239,wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur salam kya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke ya Rasulullah ! ye to ibne-Qoqal ka qaatil hai aur Aban (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha hairat hai us (Wabr) par jo qudoom-as-Sanaan se abhi utra hai aur mujh par aib lagata hai aik aisey shakhs par ke jiske hath se Allah Taala ne unhein (ibne-Qoqal (Raziallahu anhu) ko) izzat di aur aisa na honey diya ke unke hath se mujhey zaleel karta.
4240,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas kisi ko bheja aur unse apni meeraas ka mutalba kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us maal se jo aapko Allah Taala ne Madina aur fidak mein inayat farmaya tha aur khaibar ka jo panchwan hissey reh gaya tha. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye jawab diya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud hi irshad farmaya tha ke ham paighambaron ka koi waaris nahi hota, ham jo kuchh chhod jayen wo sab sadqa hota hai, albatta aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usi maal se khaatii rahegi aur main, Allah ki qism ! jo sadqa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chhod gaey hain usmein kisi qism ka badlaaw nahi karunga. jis haal mein wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein tha ab bhi isi tarah rahega aur us main (uskii taqseem wghaira) mein main bhi wahi tarze-amal ikhtiyar karunga jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka apni zindagi mein tha. gharaz Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko kuchh bhi dena manzoor na kya. is par Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se khafa ho gain aur unse tarake-mulaaqaat kar liya aur uske baad wafat tak unse koi guftgu nahi ki. Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad chh mahiney tak zinda rahiin. jab unki wafat hui to unke shauhar Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein raat mein dafn kar diya aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko uski khabar nahi di aur khud unki namaaze-janaaza padh li. Fatima (Raziallahu anha) jab tak zinda rahiin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) par log bahut tawajjoh rakhtey rahe lekin unki wafat ke baad unhon-ne dekha ke ab logon ke munh unki taraf se phirey huey hain. us waqt unhon-ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se suleh kar lena aur unse bait kar lena chaha. us se pahley chh maah tak unhon-ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se bait nahi ki thi phir unhon-ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula bheja aur kelha bheja ke aap sirf tanha aaein aur kisi ko apne sath na laaein unko ye manzoor na tha ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) unke sath aaein . umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Allah ki qism ! aap tanha unke paas na jaaein. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha kyon wo mere sath kya karengey main to Allah ki qism ! zaroor unke paas jaaunga. aakhir aap Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah ko gawah kya, uske baad farmaya hamein aap ke Fazal w kamaal aur jo kuchh Allah Taala ne aapko bakhshaa hai, sab ka hamein iqrar hai jo khair w imtiyaz aapko Allah Taala ne diya tha ham ne usmein koi kami bhi nahi ki lekin aap ne hamarey sath zyadti ki (ke khilafat ke maamle mein ham se koi mashwara nahi liyaa) ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath apni qaraabat ki wjah se apna haq samajhtey they (ke aap ham se mashwara kartey) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) par un baton se giryaa (ronaa) taarii ho gaee aur jab baat karne ke qaabil huey to farmaya us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qaraabat ke sath sila-rehmii mujhey apni qaraabat se sila rehmii se zyada azeez hai. lekin mere aur logon ke darmyan un amwaal ke silsiley mein jo ikhtilaf hua hai to main usmein haq aur khair se nahi hata hun aur is silsile mein jo rasta maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka dekha khud maine bhi usi ko ikhtiyar kya. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke do-pahar ke baad mein aap se bait karunga. chunanche Zohar ki Namaz se farigh ho kar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) member par aaey aur khutbe ke baad Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke mamley ka aur unke ab tak bait na karne ka zikr kya aur wo uzr bhi bayan kya jo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne pesh kya tha. phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne istighfar aur shahadat ke baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka haq aur unki buzurgi bayan ki aur farmaya ke jo kuchh unhon-ne kya hai iski wjah Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se hasad nahi tha aur na unke Fazal w kamaal ka inkar maqsud tha jo Allah Taala ne unhein inayat farmaya ye baat zaroor thi ke ham is muaamlae-khilaafat mein apna haq samajhtey they (ke ham se mashwara liya jaataa) hamarey sath yahi zyadti hui thi jis se hamein ranj pahuncha. musalman us waaqie par bahut khush huey aur kaha ke aap ne durust farmaya, jab Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne us maamle mein ye munasib rasta ikhtiyar kar liya to musalman unse khush ho gaey aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se aur zyada mohabbat karne lagey jab dekha ke unhon-ne achi baat ikhtiyar kar li hai."
4241,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas kisi ko bheja aur unse apni meeraas ka mutalba kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us maal se jo aapko Allah Taala ne Madina aur fidak mein inayat farmaya tha aur khaibar ka jo panchwan hissey reh gaya tha. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye jawab diya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud hi irshad farmaya tha ke ham paighambaron ka koi waaris nahi hota, ham jo kuchh chhod jayen wo sab sadqa hota hai, albatta aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usi maal se khaatii rahegi aur main, Allah ki qism ! jo sadqa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chhod gaey hain usmein kisi qism ka badlaaw nahi karunga. jis haal mein wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein tha ab bhi isi tarah rahega aur us main (uskii taqseem wghaira) mein main bhi wahi tarze-amal ikhtiyar karunga jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka apni zindagi mein tha. gharaz Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko kuchh bhi dena manzoor na kya. is par Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se khafa ho gain aur unse tarake-mulaaqaat kar liya aur uske baad wafat tak unse koi guftgu nahi ki. Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad chh mahiney tak zinda rahiin. jab unki wafat hui to unke shauhar Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein raat mein dafn kar diya aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko uski khabar nahi di aur khud unki namaaze-janaaza padh li. Fatima (Raziallahu anha) jab tak zinda rahiin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) par log bahut tawajjoh rakhtey rahe lekin unki wafat ke baad unhon-ne dekha ke ab logon ke munh unki taraf se phirey huey hain. us waqt unhon-ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se suleh kar lena aur unse bait kar lena chaha. us se pahley chh maah tak unhon-ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se bait nahi ki thi phir unhon-ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula bheja aur kelha bheja ke aap sirf tanha aaein aur kisi ko apne sath na laaein unko ye manzoor na tha ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) unke sath aaein . umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Allah ki qism ! aap tanha unke paas na jaaein. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha kyon wo mere sath kya karengey main to Allah ki qism ! zaroor unke paas jaaunga. aakhir aap Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah ko gawah kya, uske baad farmaya hamein aap ke Fazal w kamaal aur jo kuchh Allah Taala ne aapko bakhshaa hai, sab ka hamein iqrar hai jo khair w imtiyaz aapko Allah Taala ne diya tha ham ne usmein koi kami bhi nahi ki lekin aap ne hamarey sath zyadti ki (ke khilafat ke maamle mein ham se koi mashwara nahi liyaa) ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath apni qaraabat ki wjah se apna haq samajhtey they (ke aap ham se mashwara kartey) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) par un baton se giryaa (ronaa) taarii ho gaee aur jab baat karne ke qaabil huey to farmaya us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qaraabat ke sath sila-rehmii mujhey apni qaraabat se sila rehmii se zyada azeez hai. lekin mere aur logon ke darmyan un amwaal ke silsiley mein jo ikhtilaf hua hai to main usmein haq aur khair se nahi hata hun aur is silsile mein jo rasta maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka dekha khud maine bhi usi ko ikhtiyar kya. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke do-pahar ke baad mein aap se bait karunga. chunanche Zohar ki Namaz se farigh ho kar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) member par aaey aur khutbe ke baad Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke mamley ka aur unke ab tak bait na karne ka zikr kya aur wo uzr bhi bayan kya jo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne pesh kya tha. phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne istighfar aur shahadat ke baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka haq aur unki buzurgi bayan ki aur farmaya ke jo kuchh unhon-ne kya hai iski wjah Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se hasad nahi tha aur na unke Fazal w kamaal ka inkar maqsud tha jo Allah Taala ne unhein inayat farmaya ye baat zaroor thi ke ham is muaamlae-khilaafat mein apna haq samajhtey they (ke ham se mashwara liya jaataa) hamarey sath yahi zyadti hui thi jis se hamein ranj pahuncha. musalman us waaqie par bahut khush huey aur kaha ke aap ne durust farmaya, jab Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne us maamle mein ye munasib rasta ikhtiyar kar liya to musalman unse khush ho gaey aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se aur zyada mohabbat karne lagey jab dekha ke unhon-ne achi baat ikhtiyar kar li hai."
4242,jab khaibar fateh hua to ham ne kaha ab khajooron se hamara ji bhar jaeyga
4243,jab tak khaibar fateh nahi hua tha ham tangi mein they.
4244,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sahabi (Suwaad-bin-Ghaziya (Raziallahu anhu)) ko khaibar ka aamil muqarrar kya. wo wahan se umda qism ki khajoorein laey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ke kya khaibar ki tamam khajoorein aisi hi hain? unhon-ne arz kya ke nahi, Allah ki qism ya Rasulullah ! ham is tarah ki aik saa khajoor (is se kharaab ( 2 ya teen saa khajoor ke badley mein unse ley letey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is tarah na kya karo, balke (agar achi khajoor laanii ho to) raddi khajoor pahley dirham ke badley beech daala karo, phir un daraahim se achi khajoor khareed liya karo."
4245,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sahabi (Suwaad-bin-Ghaziya (Raziallahu anhu)) ko khaibar ka aamil muqarrar kya. wo wahan se umda qism ki khajoorein laey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ke kya khaibar ki tamam khajoorein aisi hi hain? unhon-ne arz kya ke nahi, Allah ki qism ya Rasulullah ! ham is tarah ki aik saa khajoor (is se kharaab ( 2 ya teen saa khajoor ke badley mein unse ley letey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is tarah na kya karo, balke (agar achi khajoor laanii ho to) raddi khajoor pahley dirham ke badley beech daala karo, phir un daraahim se achi khajoor khareed liya karo."
4246,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke khandan bani Adi ke bhai ko khaibar bheja aur unhein wahan ka aamil muqarrar kya aur Abdul-Majeed se riwayat hai ke unse Abu-Saleh samaan ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi tarah naql kya hai.
4247,nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke khandan bani Adi ke bhai ko khaibar bheja aur unhein wahan ka aamil muqarrar kya aur Abdul-Majeed se riwayat hai ke unse Abu-Saleh samaan ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi tarah naql kya hai.
4248,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar (ki zameen w baghaat wahan ke) yahudiyon ke paas hi rehney diye they ke wo unmein kaam karein aur boein jotein aur unhein unki paidawar ka aadha hissey milega.
4249,khaibar ki fateh ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko (eik Yahudi aurat ki taraf se) bakri ke gosht ka hadiya pesh kya gaya jis mein zahar mila hua tha.
4250,aik jamat ka ameer Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya. unki amaarat par kuchh logon ko aetraz hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aaj tum ko uski amaarat par aetraz hai tum hi kuchh din pahley iske bap ki amaarat par aetraz kar chukey ho. halanke Allah ki qism wo amaarat ke mustahiq w ahal they. iske ilawa wo mujhey sabse zyada azeez they jis tarah ye Usama (Raziallahu anhu) unke baad mujhey sabse zyada azeez hai.
4251,"Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zi-Qada mein Umre ka ehram baandhaa. Makka waley aap ke Makka mein dakhil honey se rukawat baney. aakhir muaahida is par hua ke) aainda saal ( Makka mein teen din aap qiyam kar saktey hain. muaahida yun likha janey laga ''ye wo muaahida hai jo Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya. kuffaare-Quraish kehney lagey ke ham ye taslim nahi kartey. agar ham aapko Allah ka rasool mantey to roktey hi kyon, aap to bas Muhammad-bin-Abdullah hain. aap ne farmaya ke main Allah ka rasool bhi hun aur Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bhi hun. phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke (rasoolullaah ka lafz mitaa do) unhon-ne kaha ke hargiz nahi, Allah ki qasam! main ye lafz kabhi nahi mitaa sakta. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo tahreer apne hath mein ley li. aap likhnaa nahi jantey they lekin aap ne uske alfaz is tarah kar diye ''ye muaahida hai jo Muhammad-bin-Abdullah ne kya ke wo hathiyar lekar Makka mein nahi aaeingey. albatta aisi talwaar jo niyaam mein ho sath la saktey hain aur ye agar Makka walon mein se koi unke sath jana chaahega to usey apne sath nahi ley jaengey. lekin agar unke sathiyon mein koi Makka mein rehna chaahega usey na rokengey. phir jab (aainda saal) aap us muaahide ke mutabiq Makka mein dakhil huey (aur teen din ki) muddat poori ho gaee to Makka waley Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha ke apne sathi se kaho ke ab yahan se chaley jaaein, kyonke muddat poori ho gaee hai. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka se nikley to aap ke peechhey Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti chacha chachaa kehti hui aaein . Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein ley liya aur hath pakad kar Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke paas laey aur kaha ke apne chacha ki beti ko ley lo main usey leta aaya hun. Ali , Zaid , Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ka ikhtilaf hua. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye mere chacha ki ladki hai aur Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye mere chacha ki ladki hai uski khala mere nikah mein hain. Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ye mere bhai ki ladki hai lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki khala ke haq mein faisla farmaya (jo Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein thiin) aur farmaya khala maa ke darjey mein hoti hai aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke tum mujh se ho aur main tum se hun. Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke tum sura w shakl aur aadat w akhlaq donon mein mujh se mushabeh (similar) ho aur Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke tum hamarey bhai aur hamarey Maula ho. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki sahibzadi ko aap apne nikah mein ley lein lekin aap ne farmaya ke wo mere dudh-sharik bhai ki ladki hai."
4252,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Umre ke iraadey se nikley, lekin Quraish ke kaafiron ne Baitullah pahunchney se aapko rokaa. chunaanchey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna qurbani ka janwar Hudaibiya mein hi zabah kar diya aur wahin sar bhi mundwaaya aur unsey muaahida kiya ke aap aainda saal umra kar saktey hain, lekin (niyaam mein talwaaron ke siwa aur) koi hathiyar sath nahi la saktey aur jitney dinon Makka waaley chaahengey, ussey zyada aap wahan thahar nahi sakenge. is liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne agley saal umra kiya aur muaahidey ke mutabiq Makka mein dakhil huey. teen din wahan thehrey rahey. phir Quraish ne aap se janey ke liye kaha aur aap Makka se chaley aaey."
4253,main aur Urwa-bin-Zubair donon masjide-Nabawi mein dakhil huey to ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujrey ke nazdeek baithey huey they. Urwa ne sawal kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kal kitney Umerey kiye they? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke char aur aik unmein se rajab mein kya tha.
4254,"phir ham ne Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke (apne ghar mein) miswak karne ki awaz suni to Urwa ne unse puchha : aey eman walon ki maan! aap ne suna hai ya nahi, abu-Abdur-Rehman (Abdullaah-bin-Umar (rz)) kehtey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char Umerey kiye they jis mein se aik rajab mein kya tha. Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab bhi Umra kya to Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sath they lekin aap ne rajab mein koi Umra nahi kya."
4255,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umra kya to ham aap par aad kiye huey mushrekeen ke ladkon aur mushrekeen se aap ki hifazat kartey rahtey they taake wo aapko koi takleef na de sakein.
4256,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath (Umra ke liye Makka) tashrif laey to mushrekeen ne kaha ke tumharey yahan wo log aa rahe hain jinhein yasrib (Madeena) ke bukhar ne kamzor kar diya hai. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke tawaaf ke pahley teen chakkaron mein akad kar chala jaey aur rukne-Yamaanii aur hajre-Aswad ke darmyan mamool (routine) ke mutabiq chalein. tamam chakkaron mein akad kar chalney ka hukm aap ne isliye nahi diya ke kahin ye (ummat par) dushwar na ho jaey. aur Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Ayub se is hadis ko riwayat karke ye izafa kya hai. unse Saeed-bin-Jubair ne aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us saal Umra karne aaey jis mein mushrekeen ne aapko amn diya tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke akad kar chalo taake mushrekeen tumhari quwwat ko dekhein. mushrekeen Jabal Qaiiqa'an ki taraf khadey dekh rahe they.
4257,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ke tawaaf mein ramal aur Safa w Marwa ke darmyan daud, mushrekeen ke samney apni taqat dikhaaney ke liye ki thi."
4258,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya to aap ehram ki haalat mein they aur jab unse khilwat ki to aap ehram khol chukey they. Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ka intiqal bhi usi maqam sarf mein hua.
4259,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se Umra qaza mein nikah kya tha.
4260,is Mautaa ki jang mein Jafar tayyar (Raziallahu anhu) ki laash par khadey ho kar maine shumaar kya to nezon aur talwaaron ke pachaas zakhm unke jism par they lekin peechhey yani peeth par aik zakhm bhi nahi tha.
4261,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Mautaa ki jang ke lashkar ka ameer Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farma diya tha ke agar Zaid Shahid ho jayen to Jafar ameer hon aur agar Jafar bhi Shahid ho jayen to Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha ameer hon. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke is jang mein, main bhi Sharik tha. baad mein jab ham ne Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ko talash kya to unki laash hamein shohdaa mein mili aur unke jism par kuchh uper nawwey zakhm nezon aur teeron ke they."
4262,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zaid, Jafar aur Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ki khabar us waqt sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko de di thi jab abhi unke mutaalliq koi khabar nahi aai thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ja rahe they ke ab Zaid jhanda uthaey huey hain, ab wo Shahid kar diye gaey, ab Jafar ne jhanda utha liya, wo bhi Shahid kar diye gaey. ab ibne- Rawaha ne jhanda utha liya, wo bhi Shahid kar diye gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon se aansu jari they. aakhir Allah ki talwaaron mein se aik talwaar Khalid-bin Waleed ne jhanda apne hath mein ley liya aur Allah ne unke hath par fateh inayat farmai."
4263,"maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya Zaid-bin-Haarisa , Jafar bin abii-Taalib aur Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ki khabar aai thi, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey huey they aur aap ke chehrey se gham zahir ho raha tha. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke main darwazey ki daraaz se jhank rahi thi. itney mein aik aadmi ne aa kar arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ki auratein chilla kar ro rahi hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke unhein rok do. bayan kya ke wo sahib gaey aur phir wapas aa kar kaha ke maine unhein rokaa aur ye bhi keh diya ke unhon-ne uski baat nahi maana . phir us ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir mana karne ke liye farmaya, wo sahib phir ja kar wapas aaey aur kaha : qism Allah ki ! wo to ham par ghalib aa gaee hain. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti thin ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke phir unke munh mein mitti jhonk do. Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, maine kaha : Allah teri naak ghubaar aalud karey na to to aurton ko rok saka na to ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko takleef dena hi chhodaa."
4264,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab Jafar bin abii-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey ke liye salam bhejtey to Assalaamualaikum ya ibne-zil-Janaahain kehtey.
4265,"maine Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Mautaa ki jang mein mere hath nau (9) talwaarein tootii thin. sirf aik Yaman ka bana hua chaudey phal ka tegha baqi reh gaya tha."
4266,"Mautaa ki jang mein mere hath se nau (9) talwaarein tootii thin, sirf aik yamnii tegha mere hath mein baqi reh gaya tha."
4267,"Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) par (eik martaba kisi marz mein) be-hoshi taarii hui to unki behan Umra walida Noman-bin-Bashir ye samajh karke koi haadisa aa gaya, Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye pukar kar roney lagiin. haaye mere bhaaii, haaye mere aisey aur waisey. unki khubiyan is tarah eik-eik karke ginaaney lagiin lekin jab Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko hosh aaya to unhon-ne kaha ke tum jab meri kisi khoobi ka bayan karti thin to mujh se puchha jata tha ke kya tum waqei aisey hi they."
4268,"Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ko be-hoshii ho gaee thi, phir uper ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya. chunanche jab (Mautaa ki jang) mein wo Shahid huey to unki behan un par nahi roiin."
4269,"hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila hirqa ki taraf bhejaa. ham ne subah ke waqt un par hamla kya aur unhein shikast de di, phir main aur aik aur Ansari sahabi us qabeele ke aik shakhs (Mirdaas-bin-Umar naamii) se bhid gaey. jab ham ne is par ghalba pa liya to wo la ilaaha-illallaah kehney laga. Ansari to fauran hi ruk gaya lekin maine usey apne barchhey se qatl kar diya. jab ham lautey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bhi uski khabar hui. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke Usama kya iske la ilaaha-illallaah kehney ke bawajud tum ne usey qatl kar diya? maine arz kya ke wo qatl se bachna chahta tha (us ne ye kalima dil se nahi padha thaa). is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baar-baar yahi farmatey rahe (kya tum ne iske la ilaaha-illallaah kehney par bhi usey qatl kar diyaa) ke mere dil mein ye aarzoo paida hui ke kash! mein aaj se pahley Islam na laataa."
4270,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath saat (7) jangon mein Sharik raha hun aur nau (9) aisey lashkaron mein Sharik hua hun jo aap ne rawaana kiye they. (magar aap khud unmein nahi gaey) kabhi ham par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ameer huey aur kisi fauj ke ameer Usama (Raziallahu anhu) huey.
4271,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath saat (7) jangon mein Sharik raha hun aur nau (9) aisey lashkaron mein Sharik hua hun jo aap ne rawaana kiye they. (magar aap khud unmein nahi gaey) kabhi ham par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ameer huey aur kisi fauj ke ameer Usama (Raziallahu anhu) huey.
4272,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath saat (7) jangon mein Sharik raha hun aur maine ibne- Harisa (yani Usama (Raziallahu anhu)) ke sath bhi jang kya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ham par ameer banaya tha.
4273,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath saat (7) jangein kin. is silsile mein unhon-ne Khaibar ki jang, jange-Hudaibiya, jange-Hunain aur jange-zaatul-qard ka zikr kya. Yazeed ne kaha ke baqi jangon ke naam main bhool gaya."
4274,"maine Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke mujhey, Zuber aur Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rawaana kya aur hidayat ki ke (Makka ke rastey par) chaley jana jab tum maqam rauza khaakh par pahuncho to wahan tumhen hodaj mein aik aurat milegii. wo aik khat liye huey hai, tum us se wo ley lenaa. unhon-ne kaha ke ham rawaana huey. hamarey ghodey hamein tezi ke sath liye ja rahe they. jab ham rauza khaakh par pahunchey to waqei wahan hamein aik aurat hodaj mein sawar mili (jiska naam Sara ya kanaad hai) ham ne us se kaha ke khat nikal . wo kehney lagi ke mere paas to koi khat nahi hai lekin jab ham ne us se ye kaha ke agar tu ney khud se khat nikal kar hamein nahi diya to ham tera kapda utaar kar talashi lengey, tab us ne apni choti mein se wo khat nikala . ham wo khat lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein wapas huey. usmein ye likha tha ke Haatib bin abi Balta' ki taraf se chand mushrekeen Makka ke naam ( Safwan bin Umayya aur Suhail-bin-Amr aur Ikrima bin abu-Jahal ( phir unhon-ne usmein mushrekeen ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh bhedon ki khabar bhi di thi. (aap fauj lekar aana chahtey hain) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke aey Haatib ! to ne ye kya kya? unhon-ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! mere barey mein faisla karne mein aap jaldi na farmaaein, main iski wjah arz karta hun. baat ye hai ke main doosrey muhajireen ki tarah Quraish ke khandan se nahi hun, sirf unka haleef bin kar unse jud gaya hun aur doosrey muhajireen ke wahan rishtedar hain jo unke ghar baar maal w asbaab ki nigrani kartey hain. maine chaha ke jab main khandan ki taraf se unka Sharik nahi hun to kuchh ehsan hi un par aisa kar dun jiske khayal se wo mere kunbe walon ko na sataaein. maine ye kaam apne Deen se phir kar nahi kya aur na Islam laney ke baad mere dil mein kufr ki himaayat ka jazba hai. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke waqei unhon-ne tumharey samney sachchii baat keh di hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ijazat ho to main is munafiq ki gardan uda dun lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye jange-badr mein Sharik rahe hain aur tumhen kya malum Allah Taala jo jange-badr mein Sharik honey walon ke kaam se waaqif hai sura Mumtahina mein us ne unke mutaalliq khud farma diya hai ke ''jo chaho karo maine tumharey gunah maaf kar diye'' is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تتخذوا عدوي وعدوكم أولياء تلقون إليهم بالمودة''aey wo logo jo eman la chukey ho ! mere aur apne dushmanon ko dost na banao ke unse tum apni mohabbat ka izhar kartey raho. aayat ( فقد ضل سواء السبيل ( tak."
4275,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-fatah Makka Ramazan mein ki thi. Zohri ne ibne- Sad se bayan kya ke maine Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se suna ke wo bhi isi tarah bayan kartey they. Zohri ne Ubaidullah se riwayat kya, unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke (jange-fatah ke safar mein jatey huey) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se they lekin jab aap maqam kudaid pahunchey, jo Kudaid aur Asfan ke darmyan aik chashma hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne roza tod diya. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne roza nahi rakha yahan tak ke Ramazan ka mahina khatm ho gaya."
4276,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (fatah ke liye) Madina se rawaana huey. aap ke sath (das ya baara hazaar ka ( lashkar tha. us waqt aapko Madina mein tashrif laey saadhey aath (8) saal poorey hone-waale they. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sath jo musalman they Makka ke liye rawaana huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi rozey se they aur tamam musalman bhi, lekin jab aap maqam kudaid par pahunchey jo Kudaid aur Asfan ke darmyan aik chashma hai to aap ne roza tod diya aur aap ke sath musalmanon ne bhi roza tod diya. Zohri ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sabse aakhiri amal par hi amal kya jaeyga"
4277,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan mein Hunain ki taraf tashrif ley gaey. musalmanon mein kuchh hazraat to rozey se they aur kuchh ne roza nahi rakha tha lekin jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par poori tarah baith gaey to aap ne bartan mein doodh ya pani talab farmaya aur usey apni ontni par ya apni hatheli par rakha (aur phir pi liya ( phir aap ne logon ko dekha to jin logon ne pahley se roza nahi rakha tha, unhon-ne roza daaron se kaha ke ab roza tod lo."
4278,"aur Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha ham ko Mamar ne khabar di, unhein Ayub ne, unhein Ikrima ne aur unhein Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kya aur Hammad ne Ayub se riwayat kya, unhon-ne Ikrima se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kya."
4279,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan mein (fatah Makka ka ( safar shuru kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se they lekin jab maqam Asfan par pahunchey to pani talab farmaya, din ka waqt tha aur aap ne wo pani piyaa taake logon ko dikhla sakein phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne roza nahi rakha aur Makka mein dakhil huey. bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne safar main ( kabhi-kabhi ( roza bhi rakha tha aur kabhi-kabhi roza nahi bhi rakha. isliye (safar mein) jiska ji chahey roza rakhey aur jiska ji chahey na rakhey . musaafir ke liye roza na rakhney ki ijazat hai. (riwaayat mein fateh Makka ke liye safar karne ka zikr hai. yahi baab se mutaabiqat hai)."
4280,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka ke liye rawaana huey to Quraish ko uski khabar mil gaee thi. chunanche Abu-Sufiyan bin Harab , Hakeem-bin-Hizaam aur Budail-bin-Warqaa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein maaloomaan ke liye Makka se nikley. ye log chaltey chaltey maqam Marruz-Zohraan par jab pahunchey to unhein jagah jagah aag jaltii hui dikhai di. aisa malum hota tha ke maqam Arafaat ki aag hai. Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha ye aag kaisi hai? ye Arafaat ki aag ki tarah dikhai deti hai. is par Budail-bin-Warqaa ne kaha ke ye bani Amr (yani Quba ke qabeeley ( ki aag hai. Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha ke bani Amr ki tadaad us se bahut kam hai. itney main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke muhaafiz dastey ne unhein dekh liya aur unko pakad kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laaey, phir Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne Islam qabool kya. iske baad jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey (Makka ki taraf) badhey to Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke Abu-Sufiyan ko aisi jagah par rokey rakho jahan ghodon ka jatey waqt hujoom ho taake wo musalmanon ki fauji quwwat ko dekh lein. chunanche Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) unhein aisey hi maqam par rok kar khadey ho gaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath qabaayel ke dastey eik-eik karke Abu-Sufiyan ke samney se guzarney lagey. aik dasta guzra to unhon-ne puchha : Abbas ! ye kon hain? unhon-ne bataya ke ye qabila ghifaar hai. Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha ke mujhey ghifaar se kya sarokaar , phir qabila juhaina guzra to unke mutaalliq bhi unhon-ne yahi kaha, qabila Sulaim guzra to unke mutaalliq bhi yahi kaha, aakhir aik dasta samney aaya. us jaisa fauji dasta nahi dekha gaya hoga. Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha ye kon log hain? Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye Ansar ka dasta hai. Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) iske ameer hain aur unhiin ke hath main ( Ansar ka jhanda hai) Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Abu-Sufiyan ! aaj ka din qatl aam ka din hai. aaj Kaba mein bhi ladna durust kar diya gaya hai. Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) is par boley : aey Abbas ! ( Quraish ki halaakat w barbadi ka din achchha aa laga hai. phir aik aur dasta aaya ye sabse chhota dasta tha. usmein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka jhanda Zubair-bin-Awaam (Raziallahu anhu) uthaey huey they. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Sufiyan ke qareeb se guzrey to unhon-ne kaha aapko malum nahi, Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) kya keh gaey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke unhon-ne kya kaha hai? to Abu-Sufiyan ne bataya ke ye ye keh gaey hain ke aap Quraish ka kaam tamam kar dengey. (sab ko qatl kar daalengey). Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Sad ne ghalat kaha hai balke aaj ka din wo hai jis mein Allah Kaba ki azmat aur zyada kar dega. aaj Kaba ko ghilaaf pahnaayaa jaeyga Urwa ne bayan kya phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke aap ka jhanda maqam Jahoon mein gaad diya jaey. Urwa ne bayan kya aur mujhey Naafe bin Juber bin Mut-im ne khabar di, kaha ke maine Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne Zubair-bin-Awaam (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha (fatah Makka ke baad) ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko yahin jhanda gaadney ke liye hukm farmaya tha. rawi ne bayan kya ke us din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya tha ke Makka ke oopri ilaqe kadaa ki taraf se dakhil hun aur khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kadaa (nashebii ilaaqe) ki taraf se dakhil huey. us din Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ke daste ke 2 sahaabii, Habish bin ash'ar aur Kurz-bin-Jaabir fahrii Shahid huey they."
4281,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka ke mauqe par apne oont par Sawar hain aur behtreen awaz ke sath sura fateh ki tilawat farma rahe hain. Muaawiya-bin-Qurra (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar iska khatrah na hota ke log mujhey gher lengey to main bhi isi tarah tilawat karke dikhaataa jaisey Abdullah-bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ne padh kar sunaya tha.
4282,fateh Makka ke safar mein unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : ya Rasulullah! kal (Makka mein) aap kahan qiyam farmaaengey ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hamarey liye Aqeel ne koi ghar hi kahan chhoda hai.
4283,"phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke momin, kaafir ka waaris nahi ho sakta aur na kaafir momin ka waaris ho sakta hai. Zohri se puchha gaya ke phir abu-Taalib ki wiraasat kisey mili thi? unhon-ne bataya ke unke waaris Aqeel aur taalib huey they. Mamar ne Zohri se ( Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ka sawal yun naql kya hai ke) aap apne Haj ke doran kahan qiyam farmaaengey ? aur Yunus ne (apni riwayat mein) na Haj ka zikr kya hai aur na fateh Makka kaa."
4284,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' inshaAllah hamari qiyam gaah agar Allah Taala ne fateh inayat farmai to khaif bani kinaana mein hogi. jahan Quraish ne kufr ki himaayat ke liye qism khaaii thi. ''
4285,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab Hunain ka irada kya to farmaya ''insha'allah kal hamara qiyam khaif bani kinaana mein hoga jahan Quraish ne kufr ke liye qism khaaii thii.''
4286,"fateh Makka ke mauqe par jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huey to sar Mubarak par khaud thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey utara hi tha ke aik sahabi ne aa kar arz kya ke ibne- khatal Kaba ke parde se chimtaa hua hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey ( wahin ( qatl kar do. Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha jaisa ke ham samajhtey hain aagey Allah janey , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us din ehram baandhey huey nahi they."
4287,"fateh Makka ke din jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huey to Baitullah ke charon taraf teen so sath but they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik chhadi se jo hath mein thi, maartey jatey they aur is aayat ki tilawat kartey jaatey (جاء الحق وزهق الباطل ‏‏‏‏ Mina جاء الحق ‏‏‏‏ Mina وما يبدئ الباطل وما يعيد ) ke ''haq qaaim ho gaya aur baatil maghloob ho gaya, haq qaaim ho gaya aur baatil se na shuru mein kuchh ho saka hai na aainda kuchh ho sakta hai.''"
4288,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Makka aaey to Baitullah mein us waqt tak dakhil nahi huey jab tak usmein but maujood rahe balke aap ne hukm diya to buton ko bahar nikal diya gaya. unhiin mein aik tasweer Ibrahim aur Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki bhi thi aur unke hathon main ( paanse ke) teer they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah in mushrekeen ka naas karey, inhein khub malum tha ke in buzurgon ne kabhi paansa nahi phainkaa . phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Baitullah mein dakhil huey aur andar charon taraf takbeer kahi phir bahar tashrif laey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne andar Namaz nahi padhi thi. Abdus-Samad ke sath is hadis ko Mamar ne bhi Ayub se riwayat kya aur Wuhaib bin Khalid ne yun kaha, ham se Ayub ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Ikrima se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
4289,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par fateh Makka ke din Makka ke oopri ilaqe ki taraf se Shahar mein dakhil huey. Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki sawari par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey baithey huey they. aap ke sath Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aur Kaba ke haajib Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. aakhir apne oont ko aap ne masjid (ke qareeb bahar ( bithaya aur Baitullah ki chaabii laney ka hukm diya phir aap Baitullah ke andar tashrif ley gaey. aap ke sath Usama-bin-Zaid , Bilal aur Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. aap andar kafi der tak thahrey , jab bahar tashrif laey to log jaldi se aagey badhey . Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sabse pahley andar janey walon mein they. unhon-ne Baitullah ke darwazey ke peechhey Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko khadey huey dekha aur unse puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kahan Namaz padhi thi. unhon-ne wo jagah batlaaii jahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi thi. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main ye poochhna bhool gaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz mein kitni rakatein padhi thin."
4290,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka ke din Makka ke oopri ilaqe kadaa se Shahar mein dakhil huey they. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) abu-Usama aur Wuhaib ne kadaa ke zikr ke sath ki hai.
4291,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka ke din Makka ke oopri ilaqe kadaa ki taraf se dakhil huey they.
4292,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chasht ki Namaz padhi, unhi ne kaha ke jab Makka fateh hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke ghar ghusl kya aur aath (8) rakaat Namaz padhi. unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maine itni halki Namaz padhtey kabhi nahi dekha tha. phir bhi usmein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukoo aur sajda poori tarah kartey they."
4293,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne rukoo aur sajde mein ye padhtey they  سبحانك اللهم ، Mina ربنا وبحمدك ، Mina اللهم اغفر لي
4294,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) mujhey apni majlis mein us waqt bhi bula letey jab wahan badr ki jang mein Sharik hone-waale buzurg sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) baithey hotey . is par kuchh log kehney lagey is jawan ko aap hamari majlis mein kyon bulatey hain? iske jaisey to hamarey bachchey bhi hain. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha wo to un logon mein se hai jinka ilm w Fazal tum jantey ho. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir un buzurg sahaabiyon ko aik din umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bulaya aur mujhey bhi bulaya. bayan kya ke main samajhta tha ke mujhey us din aap ne isliye bulaya tha taake aap mera ilm bata sakein . phir aap ne malum kya ( إذا جاء نصر الله والفتح * ورأيت Naas يدخلون‏ ( , khatm sura tak, ke mutaalliq tum logon ka kya khayal hai? kisi ne kaha ke hamein is aayat mein hukm diya gaya hai ke ham Allah ki hamd bayan karein aur us se istighfar karein ke usne hamari madad ki aur hamein fateh inayat farmai. kuchh ne kaha ke hamein iske mutaalliq kuchh malum nahi hai aur kuchh ne koi jawab nahi diya phir unhon-ne mujh se malum kya : Ibne-Abbas ! kya tumhara bhi yahi khayal hai? maine jawab diya ke nahi, poochha, phir tum kya kehtey ho? maine kaha ke ismein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ki taraf ishara hai ke jab Allah Taala ki madad aur fateh hasil ho gaee. yani fateh Makka to ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ki nishani hai. isliye aap apne rab ki hamd aur tasbeeh aur uski maghfirat talab karein ke wo tauba qabool karne wala hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jo kuchh tum ne kaha wahi mein bhi samajhta hun."
4295,"abu-Shuraih Adwi (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Madina ke ameer ( Amr bin Saeed se kaha jabke Amr bin Saeed ( Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke khilaf ( Makka ki taraf lashkar bhej rahe they ke aey ameer ! mujhey ijazat dijiye ke main aap se aik hadis bayan karun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke doosrey din irshad farmai thi. is hadis ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) irshad farma rahe they, to main apni aankhon se aapko dekh raha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahley Allah ki hamd w sana bayan ki aur phir farmaya, bila shubah Makka ko Allah Taala ne hurmat wala Shahar qarar diya hai kisi insan ne usey apni taraf se hurmat wala qarar nahi diya. isliye kisi shakhs ke liye bhi jo Allah aur yaume- aakhirat par eman rakhta ho, jaaiz nahi ke usmein kisi ka khoon bahaaey aur koi is sar zameen ka koi darakht kaatey aur agar koi shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke (fatah Makka ke mauqe par) jang se apne liye bhi rukhsat nikaley to tum us se keh dena ke Allah Taala ne sirf apne rasool ko) thodi der ke liye) iski ijazat di thi. hamarey liye bilkul ijazat nahi hai aur mujhey bhi uski ijazat din ke thodey se hissey ke liye mili thi aur aaj phir uski hurmat isi tarah lot aai hai jis tarah kal ye Shahar hurmat wala tha. to jo log yahan maujood hain wo ( unko mera kalam ( pahuncha dein jo maujood nahi. abu-Shuraih se puchha gaya ke Amr bin Saeed ne aapko phir jawab kya diya tha? to unhon-ne bataya ke usne kaha ke main ye masayel tum se zyada janta hun, haram kisi gunahgaar ko panah nahi detaa, na kisi ka khoon karke bhaagney waley ko panah deta hai, fasaadii ko bhi panah nahi deta."
4296,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap ne fateh Makka ke mauqe par Makka Mukarrama mein farmaya tha ke Allah aur uske rasool ne sharab ki khareed-farokht haram qarar de di hai.
4297,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (Makka mein) das din thahrey they aur us muddat mein ham Namaz qasr kartey they.
4298,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Makka mein unnees din qiyam farmaya tha aur us muddat mein Namaz 2 rakatein ( qasr ( padhtey they.
4299,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar mein (fatah Makka ke baad) unnees din tak to Namaz qasr padhtey they, lekin jab us se zyada muddat guzar jati to phir poori Namaz padhtey they."
4300,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka ke din unke chehrey par (shafqat ke taur par) hath phera tha.
4301,jab ham se Abu-Jameela (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki to ham Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ke sath they bayan kya ke Abu-Jameela (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat paai aur wo aap ke sath jange-fatah Makka ke liye nikley they.
4302,"mujh se abu-Qilaba ne kaha, Amr bin Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar ye qissa kyon nahi poochhtey? abu-Qilaba ne kaha ke phir main unki khidmat mein gaya aur unse sawal kya, unhon-ne kaha ke jahiliyat mein hamara qiyam aik chashme par tha jahan aam rasta tha. sawar hamarey qareeb se guzartey to ham unse poochhtey, logon ka kya khayal hai, us shakhs ka kya mamla hai? (ye ishara Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf hota tha) log bataatey ke wo kehtey hain ke Allah ne unhein apna rasool bana kar bheja hai aur Allah un par wahi nazil karta hai, ya Allah ne un par wahi nazil ki hai (wo Quran ki koi aayat sunatey ( mein wo fauran yad kar leta , unki baatein mere dil ko lagti thin. idhar sarey Arab waley fateh Makka par apne Islam ko thahraaey huey they. unka kehna ye tha ke us Nabi ko aur uski qaum ( Quraish ( ko nimatney do, agar wo un par ghalib aagey to phir waqei wo sachey Nabi hain. chunanche jab Makka fateh ho gaya to har qaum ne Islam laney mein pahal ki aur mere walid ne bhi meri qaum ke Islam mein jaldi ki. phir jab (Madina ( se wapas aaey to kaha ke main Allah ki qism aik sachey Nabi ke paas se aa raha hun. unhon-ne farmaya hai ke falan Namaz is tarah falan waqt padha karo aur jab Namaz ka waqt ho jaey to tum mein se koi aik shakhs azan de aur imamat wo karey jisey Quran sabse zyada yad ho. logon ne andaza kya ke kisey Quran sabse zyada yad hai to koi shakhs unke qabeeley mein mujh se zyada Quran yad karne wala unhein nahi mila. kyonke main aaney janey waley sawaaron se sun kar Quran Majeed yad kar liya karta tha. isliye mujhey logon ne imam banaya. halanke us waqt meri umr chh ya saat (7) saal ki thi aur mere paas aik hi chadar thi. jab main ( usey lapet kar) sajda karta to uper ho jati (aur peechhey ki jagah ( khul jati. us qabeele ki aik aurat ne kaha, tum apne qaari ka koolhaa to pahley chipa do. aakhir unhon-ne kapda khareedaa aur mere liye aik qamees banaaii, main jitna khush us qamees se hua itna kisi aur cheez se nahi hua tha."
4303,"Utba-bin-abii-Waqaas ne (martey waqt zamana jahiliyat mein) apney bhai (Sa’d-bin-abii-Waqaas (Raziallahu anhu)) ko wasiiyat ki thi ke wo Zam-aa bin Lesi ki baandi se paida honey waaley bachchey ko apney qabze mein ley lein. Utba ne kaha tha ke wo mera ladka hoga. chunanche jab fateh Makka ke mauqe par rasoolullullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huey too Sa’d bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) is bachchey ko lekar huzoor akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unke sath Abd-bin Zam-aa bhii aaey. Sa’d-bin-abii-Waqaas (Raziallahu anhu) ne to ye kaha ke ye mere bhai ka ladka hai. bhai ne wasiiyat ki thi ke usi ka ladka hai. lekin Abd-bin-Zam'a ne kaha : ya rasoollullah ! ye mera bhai hai (mere waalid) Zam-aa ka betaa hai kyonke unhein ke bistar par paida hua hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zam-aa ki baandi ke ladkey ko dekha too wo waqei (Sa’d ke bhai ( Utba-bin-abii-Waqaas ki shakl par tha lekin huzoor (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (shariiat ke mutaabiq) faisla ye kya ke aey abd bin Zam-aa ! tumhii is bachchey ko rakho, ye tumhara bhai hai, kyonke ye tumharey walid ke bistar par (uskii baandi ke pet se paida hua hai. lekin dusri taraf ummulmomeneen Sauda (Raziallahu anha) se jo Zam-aa ki beti thin farmaya Sauda ! is ladkey se pardaa kya karna kyonke aapney is ladkey mein Utba-bin-abii-Waqaas (Raziallahu anhu) ki shabaahat paai thi. ibne-Shahab ne kaha un se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke rasool Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha, ladka uska hota hai jiski joru ya londi ke pet se paida hua ho aur zina karney waaley ke hissey mein sang hi hain. ibne- Shahab ne bayan kya ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) is hadis ko pukaar-pukaar kar bayan kya kartey they."
4304,"jange-fatah (Makka) ke mauqe par aik aurat ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein chori kar li thi. us aurat ki qaum ghabraaii hui Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aai taake wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uski sifarish kar dein (ke uska hath chori ke jurm mein na kaataa jaey) . Urwa ne bayan kya ke jab Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne uske barey mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se guftgu ki to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey ka rang badal gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ! tum mujh se Allah ki qaaim ki hui aik had ke barey mein sifarish karne aaey ho. Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : mere liye dua maghfirat kijiye , ya Rasulullah ! phir do-pahar baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko khitab kya, Allah Taala ki uske shaan ke mutabiq tareef karne ke baad farmaya : ammaa ba'd! tum mein se pahley log isliye halaak ho gaey ke agar unmein se koi muazzaz shakhs chori karta to usey chhod detey lekin agar koi kamzor chori kar leta to is par had qaaim kartey aur us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai agar Fatima binte- Muhammad bhi chori kar ley to main uska hath kaatoonga. uske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aurat ke liye hukm diya aur unka hath kaat diya gaya. phir us aurat ne sachey dil se tauba kar li aur shadi bhi kar li. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke baad mein wo mere yahan aati thin. unko aur koi zarurat hoti to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney pesh kar deti."
4305,"fateh Makka ke baad main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne bhai ( majaalid ( ko lekar hazir hua aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! main isey isliye lekar hazir hua hun taake aap hijrat par is se bait ley lein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hijrat karne waley uski fazeelat w sawab ko hasil kar chukey (yani ab hijrat karne ka zamana to guzar chukaa). maine arz kya : phir aap is se kis cheez par bait lengey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke eman , Islam aur jihad par. abi Usman nehdi ne kaha ke phir main (majaashea' ke bhai ( abu-Ma'bad majaalid se mila wo donon bhaiyon se badey they, maine unse bhi us hadis ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke majaashea' ne hadis theek tarah bayan ki hai."
4306,"fatah Makka ke baad main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne bhai ( majaalid ( ko lekar hazir hua aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! main isey isliye lekar hazir hua hun taake aap hijrat par is se bait ley lein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hijrat karne waley uski fazeelat w sawab ko hasil kar chukey (yani ab hijrat karne ka zamana to guzar chukaa). maine arz kya : phir aap is se kis cheez par bait lengey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke eman , Islam aur jihad par. abi Usman nehdi ne kaha ke phir main (majaashea' ke bhai ( abu-Ma'bad majaalid se mila wo donon bhaiyon se badey they, maine unse bhi us hadis ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke majaashea' ne hadis theek tarah bayan ki hai."
4307,"main apne bhai ( abu-Ma'bad (Raziallahu anhu)) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aap se hijrat par bait karaaney ke liye ley gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hijrat ka sawab to hijrat karne walon ke sath khatm ho chukaa. albatta main is se Islam aur jihad par bait leta hun. abu-Usman ne kaha ke phir maine abu-Ma'bad (Raziallahu anhu) se mil kar unse iske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke majaashea' (Raziallahu anhu) ne theek bayan kya aur Khalid Hazaa ne bhi abu-Usman se bayan kya, unse majaashea' (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke wo apne bhai majaalid (Raziallahu anhu) ko lekar aaey they, (phir hadis ko aakhir tak bayan kya, isko Ismail ne wasl kya hai)."
4308,"main apne bhai ( abu-Ma'bad (Raziallahu anhu)) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aap se hijrat par bait karaaney ke liye ley gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hijrat ka sawab to hijrat karne walon ke sath khatm ho chukaa. albatta main is se Islam aur jihad par bait leta hun. abu-Usman ne kaha ke phir maine abu-Ma'bad (Raziallahu anhu) se mil kar unse iske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke majaashea' (Raziallahu anhu) ne theek bayan kya aur Khalid Hazaa ne bhi abu-Usman se bayan kya, unse majaashea' (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke wo apne bhai majaalid (Raziallahu anhu) ko lekar aaey they, (phir hadis ko aakhir tak bayan kya, isko Ismail ne wasl kya hai)."
4309,"maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se arz kya ke mera irada hai ke main mulk Sham ko hijrat kar jaun, farmaya : ab hijrat baqi nahi rahii, jihad hi baqi reh gaya hai. isliye jao aur khud ko pesh karo. agar tum ne kuchh pa liya to behtar warna wapas aa jaanaa."
4310,jab maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se arz kya to unhon-ne kaha ke ab hijrat baqi nahi rahi ya ( farmaya ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad phir hijrat kahan rahi.
4311,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke fateh Makka ke baad hijrat baqi nahi rahi.
4312,"mein Ubaid-bin-Umair ke sath Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Ubaid ne unse hijrat ka masla puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke ab hijrat baqi nahi rahi. pahley musalman apna Deen bachaney ke liye Allah aur uske rasool ki taraf panah leney ke liye aatey they, us khof se ke kahin Deen ki wjah se fitne mein na pad jaaein. isliye ab jabke Allah Taala ne Islam ko ghalib kar diya to musalman jahan bhi chahey apne rab ki ibadat kar sakta hai. ab to sirf jihad aur jihad ki niyat ka sawab baqi hai."
4313,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka ke din khutba sunaney khadey huey aur farmaya ''jis din Allah Taala ne aasman w zameen ko paida kya tha, isi din us ne Makka ko hurmat wala Shahar qarar de diya tha. to ye Shahar Allah ke hukm ke mutabiq qiyamat tak ke liye hurmat wala rahega. jo mujh se pahley kabhi kisi ke liye halal nahi hua aur na mere baad kisi ke liye halal hoga aur mere liye bhi sirf aik ghadi ke liye halal hua tha. yahan hudoode-haram mein shikar ke qaabil janwar na chhedey jaaein. yahan ke kaantey daar darakht na kaatey jayen na yahan ki ghaas ukhaadii jaey aur yahan par girii-padii cheez us shakhs ke siwa jo elaan karne ka irada rakhta ho aur kisi ke liye uthaanii jaaiz nahi.'' is par Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! izkhir (ghaas) ki ijazat de dijiye kyonke sunaaron ke liye aur makanon (ki tameer wghaira) ke liye ye zaroori hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey phir farmaya'' izkhir us hukm se alag hai iska (kaatnaa) halal hai.'' dusri riwayat ibne-Juraij se (usi sanad se) aisi hi hai unhon-ne Abdul-Karim bin Malik se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas se aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aisey hi riwayat ki hai."
4314,"maine Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath mein zakhm ka nishan dekha phir unhon-ne batlaya ke ye zakhm us waqt aaya tha jab main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-Hunain mein Sharik tha. maine kaha, aap Hunain mein Sharik they? unhon-ne kaha ke us se pahley bhi main kai jangon mein Sharik ho chuka hun."
4315,"maine Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unke yahan aik shakhs aaya aur kehney laga ke aey abu ammaara! kya tum ne Hunain ki ladai mein peeth pher li thi? unhon-ne kaha, mein iski gawahi deta hun ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni jagah se nahi hatey they. albatta jo log qaum mein jald baaz they, unhon-ne apni jald bazi ka suboot diya tha, to qabila Hawazin walon ne un par teer barsaey. Abu-Sufiyan bin-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke safaid khachchar ki lagaam thaamey huey they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they أنا النبي لا كذب ، Mina أنا ابن عبد المطلب ''main Nabi hun ismein bilkul jhoot nahi, main abdul-Muttalib ki aulad hoon.''"
4316,"Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya aur main sun raha tha ke tum logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-Hunain mein peeth pher li thi? unhon-ne kaha jahan tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka talluq hai to aap ne peeth nahi pherii thi. hua ye tha ke Hawazin waley badey teerandaaz they, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us mauqe par farmaya thaa أنا النبي لا كذب ، Mina أنا ابن عبد المطلب ''main Nabi hon usmein jhoot nahi, mein abdul-Muttalib ki aulad hoon.''"
4317,"unse qabila Qais ke aik aadmi ne puchha ke kya tum log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jange-Hunain mein chhod kar bhag nikley they? unhon-ne kaha : lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni jagah se nahi hatey they. qabila Hawazin ke log teerandaaz they, jab un par ham ne hamla kya to wo paspaa ho gaey phir ham log maale-ghanimat mein lag gaey. aakhir hamein unke teeron ka saamnaa karna padaa . maine khud dekha tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne safaid khachchar par Sawar they aur Abu-Sufiyan bin-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) uski lagaam thaamey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they أنا النبي لا كذب '' main Nabi hun, usmein jhoot nahi. '' Israel aur Zuhair ne bayan kya ke baad mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne khachchar se utar gaey."
4318,"jab qabila Hawazin ka wafad musalman ho kar hazir hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukhsat dene khadey huey, unhon-ne aap se ye darkhaast ki ke unka maal aur unke (qabeeley ke qaidi) unhein wapas de diye jaaein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jaisa ke tum log dekh rahe ho, mere sath kitney aur log bhi hain aur dekho sachchii baat mujhey sabse zyada pasand hai. isliye tum log aik hi cheez pasand kar lo ya to apne qaidi ley lo ya maal ley lo. maine tum hi logon ke khayal se (qaidiyon ki taqseem mein) taakheer ki thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Taaif se wapas ho kar taqriban das din unka intizar kya tha. aakhir jab un par waazeh ho gaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein sirf aik hi cheez wapas karengey to unhon-ne kaha ke phir ham apne ( qabeeley ke) qaidiyon ki waapsii chahtey hain. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon ko khitab kya, Allah Taala ki uski shaan ke mutabiq sana karne ke baad farmaya : ammaa ba'd! tumharey bhai (qabeela Hawazin ke log) tauba karke hamarey paas aaey hain, musalman ho kar aur meri raey ye hai ke unke qaidi unhein wapas kar diye jaaein. isliye jo shakhs (bila kisi duniyawi sile ke) unhein apni khushi se wapas karna chahey wo wapas kar de ye behtar hai aur jo log apna hissey na chhodnaa chahtey hun, unka haq qaaim rahega. wo yun kar lein ke iske baad jo sabse pahley ghaneemat Allah Taala hamein inayat farmaeyga usmein se ham unhein iske badle de dengey to wo unke qaidi wapas kar dein. tamam sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! ham khushi se (bila kisi badle ke) wapas karna chahtey hain lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is tarah hamein iska ilm nahi hoga ke kis ne apni khushi se wapas kya hai aur kis ne nahi, isliye sab log jayen aur tumharey chaudhry log tumhara faisla hamarey paas laaein . chunanche sab wapas aagey aur unke chaudhariyon ne unse guftgu ki phir wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke sab ne khushi aur khuley dil ke sath ijazat de di hai. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha yahi hai wo hadis jo mujhey qabila Hawazin ke qaidiyon ke mutaalliq pahunchi hai."
4319,"jab qabila Hawazin ka wafad musalman ho kar hazir hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukhsat dene khadey huey, unhon-ne aap se ye darkhaast ki ke unka maal aur unke (qabeeley ke qaidi) unhein wapas de diye jaaein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jaisa ke tum log dekh rahe ho, mere sath kitney aur log bhi hain aur dekho sachchii baat mujhey sabse zyada pasand hai. isliye tum log aik hi cheez pasand kar lo ya to apne qaidi ley lo ya maal ley lo. maine tum hi logon ke khayal se (qaidiyon ki taqseem mein) taakheer ki thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Taaif se wapas ho kar taqriban das din unka intizar kya tha. aakhir jab un par waazeh ho gaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein sirf aik hi cheez wapas karengey to unhon-ne kaha ke phir ham apne ( qabeeley ke) qaidiyon ki waapsii chahtey hain. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon ko khitab kya, Allah Taala ki uski shaan ke mutabiq sana karne ke baad farmaya : ammaa ba'd! tumharey bhai (qabeela Hawazin ke log) tauba karke hamarey paas aaey hain, musalman ho kar aur meri raey ye hai ke unke qaidi unhein wapas kar diye jaaein. isliye jo shakhs (bila kisi duniyawi sile ke) unhein apni khushi se wapas karna chahey wo wapas kar de ye behtar hai aur jo log apna hissey na chhodnaa chahtey hun, unka haq qaaim rahega. wo yun kar lein ke iske baad jo sabse pahley ghaneemat Allah Taala hamein inayat farmaeyga usmein se ham unhein iske badle de dengey to wo unke qaidi wapas kar dein. tamam sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! ham khushi se (bila kisi badle ke) wapas karna chahtey hain lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is tarah hamein iska ilm nahi hoga ke kis ne apni khushi se wapas kya hai aur kis ne nahi, isliye sab log jayen aur tumharey chaudhry log tumhara faisla hamarey paas laaein . chunanche sab wapas aagey aur unke chaudhariyon ne unse guftgu ki phir wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke sab ne khushi aur khuley dil ke sath ijazat de di hai. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha yahi hai wo hadis jo mujhey qabila Hawazin ke qaidiyon ke mutaalliq pahunchi hai."
4320,"jab ham jange-Hunain se wapas ho rahe they, to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apni aik nazar ke mutaalliq puchha jo unhon-ne zamana jahiliyat mein aetikaf ki maana thi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein usey poori karne ka hukm diya aur kuchh ( Ahmad-bin-Abda zabi ( ne Hammad se bayan kya, unse Ayub ne, unse Naafe ne aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur is riwayat ko Jareer-bin-Haazim aur Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Ayub se bayan kya, unse Naafe ne, unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
4321,"jange-Hunain ke liye ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley. jab jang hui to musalman zara dagmagaa gaey (yani aagey peechhey ho gaey ( . maine dekha ke aik mushrik aik musalman ke uper ghalib ho raha hai, maine peechhey se uski gardan par talwaar maari aur uski zirah kaat dali . ab wo mujh par palat padaa aur mujhey itni zor se bheencha ke maut ki tasweer meri aankhon mein phir gaee, aakhir wo mar gaya aur mujhey chhod diya. phir meri mulaqat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se hui. maine puchha logon ko kya ho gaya hai? unhon-ne farmaya, yahi izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ka hukm hai. phir musalman paltey aur (jang khatm honey ke baad) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif farma huey aur farmaya ke jisne kisi ko qatl kya ho aur uske liye koi gawah bhi rakhta ho to uska tamam saman w hathiyar usey hi milega. maine apne dil mein kaha ke mere liye kon gawahi dega? phir main baith gaya. bayan kya ke phir aap ne dobara yahi farmaya, is martaba phir maine dil mein kaha ke mere liye kon gawahi dega? aur phir baith gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir apna farman dohraya to main is martaba khada ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is martaba farmaya kya baat hai, aey abu-Qatada ! maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataya to aik sahib ( Aswad bin Khuzai Aslami ( ne kaha ke ye sach kehtey hain aur unke maqtool ka saman mere paas hai. aap mere haq mein unhein razi kar dein (ke saman mujh se na lein) is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : nahi, Allah ki qism ! Allah ke sheron mein se aik sher , jo Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se ladtaa hai phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iska haq tumhen hargiz nahi de saktey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhon-ne sach kaha, tum saman abu-Qatada ko de do. unhon-ne saman mujhey de diya. maine us saman se qabila Salma ke mahalle mein aik baagh khareedaa Islam ke baad ye mera pahlaa maal tha, jisey maine hasil kya tha."
4322,"jange-Hunain ke din maine aik musalman ko dekha ke aik mushrik se lad raha tha aur aik doosra mushrik peechhey se musalman ko qatl karne ki ghaat mein tha, pahley to main usi ki taraf badhaa, us ne apna hath mujhey maarney ke liye uthaya to maine uske hath par waar karke kaat diya. iske baad wo mujh se chimat gaya aur itni zor se mujhey bheencha ke main dar gaya. aakhir usne mujhey chhod diya aur dhila pad gaya. maine usey dhakka de kar qatl kar diya aur musalman bhag nikley aur main bhi unke sath bhag padaa . logon mein umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) nazar aaey to maine unse poochha, ke log bhag kyon rahe hain? unhon-ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ka yahi hukm hai, phir log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aa kar jama ho gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs is par gawah qaaim kar dega ke kisi maqtool ko usi ne qatl kya hai to uska Sara saman usey milega. main apne maqtool par gawah ke liye utha lekin mujhey koi gawah dikhai nahi diya. aakhir mein baith gaya phir mere samney aik sura aai. maine apne mamley ki itlaa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baithey huey aik sahib ( Aswad bin Khuzai Aslami (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha ke unke maqtool ka hathiyar mere paas hai, aap mere haq mein unhein razi kar dein. is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha hargiz nahi, Allah ke sheron mein se aik sher ko chhod kar jo Allah aur uske rasool ke liye jang karta hai, iska haq Quraish ke aik buzdil ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nahi de saktey. abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur mujhey wo saman ata farmaya, maine us se aik baagh khareedaa aur ye sabse pahlaa maal tha jisey maine Islam laney ke baad hasil kya tha."
4323,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jange-Hunain se farigh ho gaey to aap ne aik dastey ke sath abu-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ko wadi Autas ki taraf bhejaa. us ladaai mein Duraid-ibn-Samma se muqaabla hua. Duraid qatl kar diya gaya aur Allah Taala ne uske lashkar ko shikast de di. abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke abu-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bhi bheja tha. abu-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghutney mein teer aa kar laga. bani Jaasham ke aik shakhs ne un par teer maara tha aur unke ghutney mein utaar diya tha. main unke paas pahuncha aur kaha : chacha ! ye teer aap par kis ne phainkaa ? unhon-ne abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko ishaarey se bataya ke wo Ja'shamii mera qaatil hai jisne mujhey nishana banaya hai. main uski taraf lapkaa aur uske qareeb pahunch gaya lekin jab usne mujhey dekha to wo bhag padaa maine iska peechhaa kya aur main ye kehta jata tha, tujhey sharm nahi aatii, tujh se muqaabla nahi kya jata. aakhir wo ruk gaya aur ham ne eik-doosrey par talwaar se waar kya. maine usey qatl kar diya aur abu-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se ja kar kaha ke Allah ne aap ke qaatil ko qatl karwaa diya. unhon-ne farmaya ke mere ( ghutney mein se) teer nikal ley, maine nikal diya to us se pani jari ho gaya phir unhon-ne farmaya : bhatijey ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mera salam pahunchaanaa aur arz karna ke mere liye maghfirat ki dua farmaaein. abu-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon par mujhey apna naaib bana diya. iske baad wo thodi der aur zinda rahe aur shahadat paaii. main wapas hua aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha. aap apne ghar mein baanon ki aik charpai par tashrif farma they. is par koi bistar bichhaa hua nahi tha aur baanon ke nishanat aap ki peeth aur pahlu par pad gaey they. maine aap se apne aur abu-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke waaqiaat bayan kiye aur ye ke unhon-ne dua'ae-maghfirat ke liye darkhaast ki hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani talab farmaya aur wuzu kya, phir hath utha kar dua ki, aey Allaah! Ubaid abu-Aamir ki maghfirat farmaa. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baghl mein safedi (jab aap dua kar rahe they) dekhi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki, aey Allaah! qiyamat ke din abu-Aamir ko apni bahut si makhlooq se buland tar darja ata farmaaiyo. maine arz kya aur mere liye bhi Allah se maghfirat ki dua farma dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki aey Allah ! Abdullah-bin-Qais abu-Musa ke gunahon ko bhi maaf farma aur qiyamat ke din achchha maqam ata farmaaiyo . abu-Barda ne bayan kya ke aik dua abu-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye thi aur dusri abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye."
4324,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey to mere paas aik mukhannas betha hua tha phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suna ke wo Abdullah-bin Umayya se keh raha tha ke aey Abdullaah! dekho agar kal Allah Taala ne Taaif ki fateh tumhen ata farmai to Ghelaan bin Salma ki beti (baadiya naamii) ko ley lena wo jab samney aati hai to pet par char bal aur peeth mod kar jati hai to aath (8) bal dikhai detey hain (yani bahut motii taaza aurat hai) to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye log ab tumharey ghar mein na aaya karein. ibne-Uena ne bayan kya ke ibne-Juraij ne kaha, us mukhannas ka naam haiyat tha. ham se Mehmood ne bayan kya, unse abu-Usama ne bayan kya, unse Hisham ne isi tarah bayan kya aur ye izafa kya hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt Taaif ka muhaasra kiye huey they."
4325,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Taaif ka muhaasra kya to dushman ka kuchh bhi nuqsan nahi kya. aakhir aap ne farmaya ke ab inshaAllah ham wapas ho jaengey. musalmanon ke liye naakaam lautnaa bada sakht guzraa. unhon-ne kaha ke waah baghair fateh ke ham wapas chaley jayen (raawii ne) aik martaba ( نذهب (ke bajaey ( نقفل (ka lafz istemal kya yani ham. lot jayen aur Taaif ko fateh na karein (ye kyonkar ho sakta hai) is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir subah sawerey maidan mein jang ke liye aa jao. to wo sahaba sawerey hi aagey lekin unki badi tadaad zakhmi ho gaee. ab phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke inshaAllah ham kal wapas chalengey. sahaba ne usey bahut pasand kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par hans padey aur Sufiyan ne aik martaba bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraa diye. Humaidii ne kaha ke ham se Sufiyan ne ye poori khabar bayan ki.
4326,"maine Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, jinhoney sabse pahley Allah ke rastey mein teer chillaayaa tha aur Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se jo Taaif ke qil'ey par chand musalmanon ke sath chadhey they aur is tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey they. un donon sahaabiyon ne bayan kya ke ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they ke jo shakhs jantey huey apne bap ke siwa kisi doosrey ki taraf apne aapko mansub karey to is par jannat haram hai. aur Hisham ne bayan kya aur unhein Mamar ne khabar di, unhein Aasim ne, unhein abul-Aaliyaa ya abu-Usman nehdi ne, kaha ke maine Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Aasim ne bayan kya ke maine (abul-Aaliyaa ya abu-Usman nehdi (rz)) se kaha aap se ye riwayat aisey 2 ashaab (Sa'd aur Abu-Bakra (rz)) ne bayan ki hai ke yaqin ke liye unke naam kafi hain. unhon-ne kaha yaqinan unmein se aik (Sa'd-bin-abii-Waqaas (rz)) to wo hain jinhoney Allah ke rastey mein sabse pahley teer chillaayaa tha aur doosrey (abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu)) wo hain jo teeswein aadmi they un logon mein jo Taaif ke qil'a se utar kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey they."
4327,"maine Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, jinhoney sabse pahley Allah ke rastey mein teer chillaayaa tha aur Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se jo Taaif ke qil'ey par chand musalmanon ke sath chadhey they aur is tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey they. un donon sahaabiyon ne bayan kya ke ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they ke jo shakhs jantey huey apne bap ke siwa kisi doosrey ki taraf apne aapko mansub karey to is par jannat haram hai. aur Hisham ne bayan kya aur unhein Mamar ne khabar di, unhein Aasim ne, unhein abul-Aaliyaa ya abu-Usman nehdi ne, kaha ke maine Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Aasim ne bayan kya ke maine (abul-Aaliyaa ya abu-Usman nehdi (rz)) se kaha aap se ye riwayat aisey 2 ashaab (Sa'd aur Abu-Bakra (rz)) ne bayan ki hai ke yaqin ke liye unke naam kafi hain. unhon-ne kaha yaqinan unmein se aik (Sa'd-bin-abii-Waqaas (rz)) to wo hain jinhoney Allah ke rastey mein sabse pahley teer chillaayaa tha aur doosrey (abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu)) wo hain jo teeswein aadmi they un logon mein jo Taaif ke qil'a se utar kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey they."
4328,"ham se Muhammad-bin Alaa ne bayan kya, kaha ham se abu-Usama ne bayan kya, unse bareed bin-Abdullah ne, unse abu-Barda ne aur unse abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb hi tha jab aap Jaarana sey, jo Makka aur Madina ke darmyan mein aik maqam hai, utar rahey they. aap ke sath Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) they. usi arse mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik badwi aaya aur kehney laga ke aapney jo mujh se wada kya hai usey pura kyon nahi kartey? huzoor (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen bashaarat ho. is par wo badwi bola bashaarat to aap mujhey bahut dey chukey phir huzoor (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chehra Mubarak abu-Musa aur Bilal ki taraf phera kya phir aap bahut ghussey mein malum ho rahey they. aapney farmaya is ne bashaarat wapas kar di tum donon usey qabool kar lo. Un donon hazraat ne arz kya ham ne qabool kya. phir aapney pani ka aik piyala talab farmaya aur apney donon hathon aur chehrey ko is mein dhoya aur usi mein kulli ki aur (abu-Moosa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) donon sey) farmaya ke is ka pani pi lo aur apney chehron aur seenon par usey daal lo aur bashaarat hasil karo . un donon ne piyala ley liya aur hidayat ke mutabiq amal kyaa. parde ke peechhey se Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bhii kaha ke apni maan ke liye bhii kuchh chhod dena. chunanche un donon ne unke liye aik hissey chhod diyaa."
4329,"Yala ne kaha kash! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us waqt dekh sakta jab aap par wahi nazil hoti hai. bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jaarana mein thahrey huey they. aap ke liye aik kapdey se saaya kar diya gaya tha aur us main chand sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath maujood they. itney mein aik dehati aaey wo aik jubba pahney huey they, khushbu mein basaa hua. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aik aisey shakhs ke barey mein aap ka kya hukm hai jo apne jubbe mein khushbu lagaaney ke baad ehram baandhey ? fauran hi umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Yala (Raziallahu anhu) ko aaney ke liye hath se ishara kya. Yala (Raziallahu anhu) hazir ho gaey aur apna sar (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhney ke liye) andar kya ( nuzool wahi ki kaifiyat se) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak surkh ho raha tha aur zor-zor se saans chal rahi thi. thodi der tak yahi kaifiyat rahi phir khatm ho gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke abhi Umra ke mutaalliq jisne sawal kya tha wo kahan hai? unhein talash karke laya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo khushbu tum ne laga rakhi hai usey teen martaba dho lo aur jubba utaar do aur phir Umra mein wahi kaam karo jo Haj mein kartey ho."
4330,"jange-Hunain ke mauqe par Allah Taala ne apne rasool ko jo ghaneemat di thi aap ne uski taqseem kamzor eman ke logon mein (jo fateh Makka ke baad eman laey they) kar di aur Ansar ko usmein se kuchh nahi diya. iska unhein kuchh malaal hua ke wo maal jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dusron ko diya unhein kyon nahi diya. aap ne iske baad unhein khitab kya aur farmaya : aey ansaariyo! kya maine tumhen gumrah nahi paya tha phir tum ko mere zariey Allah Taala ne hidayat naseeb ki aur tum mein aapas mein dushmanii aur naa-ittifaaqii thi to Allah Taala ne mere zariey tum mein aapasii ulfat paida ki aur tum mohtaaj they Allah Taala ne mere zariey ghanii kya. aap ke eik-eik jumley par Ansar kehtey jatey they ke Allah aur uske rasool ke ham sabse zyada ehsan mand hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri baton ka jawab deney se tumhen kya cheez rukawat rahii? bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke har ishara par Ansar arz kartey jatey ke Allah aur uske rasool ke ham sabse zyada ehsaan-mand hain phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum chahtey to mujh se is tarah bhi keh saktey they (ke aap aaey to log aapko jhutlaa rahe they, lekin ham ne aap ki tasdeeq ki wghaira) kya tum is par khush nahi ho ke jab log oont aur bakriyan ley ja rahe hon to tum apne gharon ki taraf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sath ley jaao? agar hijrat ki fazeelat na hoti to main bhi Ansar ka aik aadmi hota. log chahe kisi ghaati ya wadi mein rahengey main to Ansar ki ghaati aur wadi mein rahoonga. Ansar aster ki tarah hain jo jism se hamesha laga rehta hai aur doosrey log uper ke kapdey yani abrah ki tarah hain. tum log ( Ansar ( dekhogey ke mere baad tum par dusron ko tarjeeh di jaeygi. tum aisey waqt mein sabr karna yahan tak ke mujh se hauz par aa milo."
4331,"jab qabila Hawazin ke maal mein se Allah Taala ne apne rasool ko jo dena tha wo diya to Ansar ke kuchh logon ko ranj hua kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh logon ko so so oont de diye they. kuchh logon ne kaha ke Allah apne rasool ki maghfirat karey, Quraish ko to aap inayat farma rahe hain aur ham ko aap ne chhod diya hai halanke hamari talwaaron se unka khoon tapak raha hai. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Ansar ki ye baat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kanon mein aai to aap ne unhein bula bheja aur chamdey ke aik khemey mein unhein jama kya, unke sath unke ilawa kisi ko bhi aap ne nahi bulaya tha. jab sab log jama ho gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur aap ne farmaya tumhari jo baat mujhey malum hui hai kya wo sahi hai? Ansar ke jo samajhdaar log they unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! jo log hamarey muazzaz aur sardaar hain, unhon-ne aisi koi baat nahi kahi . albatta hamarey kuchh log jo abhi nau-umr hain, unhon-ne kaha hai ke Allah , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maghfirat karey, Quraish ko aap de rahe hain aur hamein aap ne chhod diya hai halanke hamari talwaaron se unka khoon tapak raha hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke main aisey logon ko deta hun jo abhi naey naey Islam mein dakhil huey hain, is tarah mein unki diljoii karta hun. kya tum is par razi nahi ho ke doosrey log to maal w daulat ley jayen aur tum Nabi ko apne sath apne ghar ley jao. Allah ki qism ! jo cheez tum apne sath ley jaogey wo us se behtar hai jo wo ley ja rahe hain. Ansar ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! ham is par razi hain. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere baad tum dekhogey ke tum par dusron ko tarjeeh di jaeygi. us waqt sabr karnaa, yahan tak ke Allah aur uske rasool se aa milo. mein hauz kausar par miloonga. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha lekin Ansar ne sabr nahi kya."
4332,fateh Makka ke zamaney main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Quraish main (Hunain ki) ghaneemat ki taqseem kar di. Ansar (Raziallahu anhu) us se ranjeeda huey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum is par razi nahi ho ke doosrey log duniya apne sath ley jayen aur tum apne sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ley jao . Ansar ne arz kya ke ham is par khush hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke log doosrey kisi wadi ya ghaati mein rahen to main Ansar ki wadi ya ghaati mein rahoonga.
4333,"jange-Hunain mein jab qabila Hawazin se jang shuru hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath das hazaar fauj thi. Quraish ke wo log bhi sath they jinhein fateh Makka ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhod diya tha phir sab ne peeth pher li. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pukara : aey ansaariyo! unhon-ne jawab diya ke ham hazir hain, ya Rasulullah ! aap ke har hukm ki ta'meel ke liye ham hazir hain. ham aap ke samney hain. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari se utar gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main Allah ka banda aur uska rasool hon phir mushrekeen ki haar ho gaee. jin logon ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke baad chhod diya tha aur muhajireen ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne diya lekin Ansar ko kuchh nahi diya. is par Ansar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne gham ka izhar kya to aap ne unhein bulaya aur aik kheme mein jama kya phir farmaya ke tum is par razi nahi ho ke doosrey log bakri aur oont apne sath ley jayen aur tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne sath ley jao . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar log kisi wadi ya ghaati mein rahen aur Ansar dusri ghaati mein rahen to main Ansar ki ghaati ko ikhtiyar karunga ."
4334,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke kuchh logon ko jama kya aur farmaya ke Quraish ke kufr ka aur unki barbaadiyon ka zamana qareeb hai. mera maqsad sirf unki diljoii aur dilon ko parchaanaa tha. kya tum is par razi aur khush nahi ho ke log duniya apne sath lekar jayen aur tum Allah ke rasool ko apne ghar ley jao ? sab Ansari boley, kyon nahi ( ham isi par razi hain) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar doosrey log kisi wadi mein chalein aur Ansar kisi aur ghaati mein chalein to main Ansar ki wadi ya ghaati mein chaloonga."
4335,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hunain ke maale-ghanimat ki taqseem kar rahe they, to Ansar ke aik shakhs ne (jo munafiq tha) kaha ke is taqseem mein Allah ki khushnoodii ka koi khayal nahi rakha gaya. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us badgo ki itlaa di to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak ka rang badal gaya phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala Musa (Alaihissalam) par raham farmaaey, unhein is se bhi zyada dukh pahunchaya gaya to unhon-ne sabr kya."
4336,"jange-Hunain ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand logon ko bahut-bahut janwar diye. chunanche Aqra-bin-Habis ko jinka dil parchaanaa manzoor tha, so oont diye. Uena bin Hisn fazari ko bhi itney hi diye aur isi tarah doosrey ashraafe-arab ko diya. is par aik shakhs ne kaha ke is taqseem mein Allah ki raza ka koi khayal nahi kya gaya. (ibn-Mas'ood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) maine kaha ke main uski khabar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko karunga. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye kalima suna to farmaya ke Allah Musa (Alaihissalam) par raham farmaai ke unhein us se bhi zyada dukh diya gaya tha lekin unhon-ne sabr kya."
4337,"jab Hunain ka din hua to qabila Hawazin aur Ghatfan apne maweshii aur baal bachchon ko sath lekar jang ke liye nikley. us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath das hazaar ka lashkar tha. unmein kuchh log wo bhi they, jinhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke baad ehsan rakh kar chhod diya tha, phir un sab ne peeth pher li aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tanha reh gaey. us din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 martaba pukara donon pukar aik doosrey se alag alag thin, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne daain taraf mutwajjeh ho kar pukara : aey ansaariyo ! unhon-ne jawab diya ham hazir hain : ya Rasulullah ! aapko bashaarat ho, ham aap ke sath hain, ladney ko taiyaar hain. phir aap baain taraf mutwajjeh huey aur awaz di, aey ansaariyo ! unhon-ne idhar se jawab diya ke ham hazir hain, ya Rasulullah ! bashaarat ho, ham aap ke sath hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt aik safaid khachchar par Sawar they phir aap utar gaey aur farmaya ke main Allah ka banda aur uska rasool hun. anjaame-kaar kaafiron ko haar hui aur us ladai mein bahut zyada ghaneemat hasil hui. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey muhajireen main aur Quraishiyon mein taqseem kar diya (jinhein fateh Makka ke mauqe par ehsan rakh kar chhod diya tha) Ansar ko unmein se kuchh nahi ata farmaya, Ansar (ke kuchh naujawaanon) ne kaha ke jab sakht waqt aata hai to hamein bulaya jata hai aur ghaneemat dusron ko taqseem kar di jati hai. ye baat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchi to aap ne Ansar ko aik kheme mein jama kya aur farmaya aey ansaariyo! kya wo baat sahi hai jo tumharey barey mein mujhey malum hui hai? is par wo khamosh ho gaey phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey ansaariyo ! kya tum is par khush nahi ho ke log duniya apne sath ley jayen aur tum Rasulullah ko apne ghar ley jao. ansaariyon ne arz kya ham isi par khush hain. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar log kisi wadi mein chalein aur Ansar kisi ghaati mein chalein to main Ansar hi ki ghaati mein chalnaa pasand karunga . is par Hisham ne puchha : aey abu-Hamza ! kya aap wahan maujood they? unhon-ne kaha ke main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ghayab hi Kab hota tha."
4338,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najad ki taraf aik lashkar rawaana kya tha, main bhi usmein Sharik tha. usmein hamara hissey (maal ghaneemat mein) baara baara oont padey aur eik-eik oont hamein aur faaltu diya gaya. is tarah ham 13-13 oont sath lekar wapas aaey."
4339,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko bani Jazeema ki taraf bhejaa. Khaalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein Islam ki dawat di lekin unhein ( أسلمنا‏ ( ''ham Islam laey '' kehna nahi aata tha, iske bajaey wo ( صبأنا‏ . صبأنا‏ .) ''ham be-deen ho gaey, yani apne aabaaii Deen se hat gaey '' kehney lagey. Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein qatl karna aur qaid karna shuru kar diya aur phir ham mein se har shakhs ko uska qaidi uski hifazat ke liye de diya phir jab aik din Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne ham sab ko hukm diya ke ham apne qaidiyon ko qatl kar dein. maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! main apne qaidi ko qatl nahi karunga aur na mere sathiyon mein koi apne qaidi ko qatl karega aakhir jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se soorate-haal bayan ki to aap ne hath utha kar dua ki. aey Allaah! main is kaam se bezaarii ka elaan karta hun, jo Khalid ne kya. 2 martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi farmaayaa."
4340,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mukhtasar lashkar rawaana kya aur uska ameer aik Ansari sahabi ( Abdullah-bin Huzafa Sehmi (Raziallahu anhu)) ko banaya aur lashkariyon ko hukm diya ke sab apne ameer ki itaat karein phir ameer kisi wjah se ghussa ho gaey aur apne faujiyon se puchha ke kya tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri itaat karne ka hukm nahi farmaya hai? sab ne kaha ke haan, farmaya hai. unhon-ne kaha phir tum sab lakdiyan jama karo. unhon-ne lakdiyan jama kiin to ameer ne hukm diya ke usmein aag lagaao aur unhon-ne aag laga di. ab unhon-ne hukm diya ke sab usmein kood jao. fauji kood jana hi chahtey they ke unhiin mein se kuchh ne kuchh ko rokaa aur kaha ke ham to is aag hi ke khof se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf aaey hain! in baton mein waqt guzar gaya aur aag bhi bujh gaee. uske baad ameer ka ghussa thanda ho gaya. jab uski khabar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar ye log usmein kood jatey to phir qiyamat tak usmein se na nikaltey . itaat ka hukm sirf nek kaamon ke liye hai."
4341,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Musa Ash-ari aur Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman ka Hakim bana kar bhejaa. rawi ne bayan kya ke donon sahaabiyon ko iske eik-eik soobey mein bhejaa. rawi ne bayan kya ke Yaman ke 2 soobey they. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke dekho logon ke liye aasaaniyaan paida karnaa, dushwaariyaan na paida karnaa, unhein khush karne ki koshish karnaa, Deen se nafrat na dilaanaa . ye donon buzurg apne apney kaamon par rawaana ho gaey. donon mein se jab koi apne ilaaqey ka daurah kartey kartey apne doosrey sathi ke paas pahunch jata to unse taazii ( mulaqat (ke liye aata aur salam karta. aik martaba Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) apne ilaqe mein apne sahib abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke qareeb pahunch gaey aur apne khachchar par unse mulaqat ke liye chaley. jab unke qareeb pahunchey to dekha ke wo baithey huey hain aur unke paas kuchh log jama hain aur aik shakhs unke samney hai jiski mashkein kasi hui hain. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse puchha : aey Abdullah-bin-Qais ! ye kya waqia hai? abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke ye shakhs Islam laney ke baad murtad ho gaya hai. unhon-ne kaha ke phir jab tak usey qatl na kar diya jaey main apni sawari se nahi utroonga. Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke qatl karne hi ke liye usey yahan laya gaya hai. aap utar jayen lekin unhon-ne ab bhi yahi kaha ke jab tak usey qatl na kya jaeyga main na utroonga. aakhir Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne hukm diya aur usey qatl kar diya gaya. tab wo apni sawari se utrey aur poochha, Abdullah ! aap Quran kis tarah padhtey hain? unhon-ne kaha, main to thoda thodaa har waqt padhta rehta hun phir unhon-ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Muaz ! aap Quran Majeed kis tarah padhtey hain? Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main to raat ke shuru mein sota hun phir apni neend ka aik hissey pura karke mein uth baithtaa hun aur jo kuchh Allah Taala ne mere liye muqaddar kar rakha hai is mein Quran Majeed padhta hun. is tarah bedaarii mein jis sawab ki ummeed Allah Taala se rakhta hun soney ki haalat ke sawab ka bhi us se isi tarah ummeedwaar rehta hun."
4342,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Musa Ash-ari aur Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman ka Hakim bana kar bhejaa. rawi ne bayan kya ke donon sahaabiyon ko iske eik-eik soobey mein bhejaa. rawi ne bayan kya ke Yaman ke 2 soobey they. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke dekho logon ke liye aasaaniyaan paida karnaa, dushwaariyaan na paida karnaa, unhein khush karne ki koshish karnaa, Deen se nafrat na dilaanaa . ye donon buzurg apne apney kaamon par rawaana ho gaey. donon mein se jab koi apne ilaaqey ka daurah kartey kartey apne doosrey sathi ke paas pahunch jata to unse taazii ( mulaqat (ke liye aata aur salam karta. aik martaba Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) apne ilaqe mein apne sahib abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke qareeb pahunch gaey aur apne khachchar par unse mulaqat ke liye chaley. jab unke qareeb pahunchey to dekha ke wo baithey huey hain aur unke paas kuchh log jama hain aur aik shakhs unke samney hai jiski mashkein kasi hui hain. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse puchha : aey Abdullah-bin-Qais ! ye kya waqia hai? abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke ye shakhs Islam laney ke baad murtad ho gaya hai. unhon-ne kaha ke phir jab tak usey qatl na kar diya jaey main apni sawari se nahi utroonga. Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke qatl karne hi ke liye usey yahan laya gaya hai. aap utar jayen lekin unhon-ne ab bhi yahi kaha ke jab tak usey qatl na kya jaeyga main na utroonga. aakhir Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne hukm diya aur usey qatl kar diya gaya. tab wo apni sawari se utrey aur poochha, Abdullah ! aap Quran kis tarah padhtey hain? unhon-ne kaha, main to thoda thodaa har waqt padhta rehta hun phir unhon-ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Muaz ! aap Quran Majeed kis tarah padhtey hain? Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main to raat ke shuru mein sota hun phir apni neend ka aik hissey pura karke mein uth baithtaa hun aur jo kuchh Allah Taala ne mere liye muqaddar kar rakha hai is mein Quran Majeed padhta hun. is tarah bedaarii mein jis sawab ki ummeed Allah Taala se rakhta hun soney ki haalat ke sawab ka bhi us se isi tarah ummeedwaar rehta hoon."
4343,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Yaman bhejaa. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un sharbaton ka masla puchha jo Yaman mein banaey jatey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke wo kya hain? abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke '' bitaa' ''aur '' Muzar '' ( Saeed bin abi burda ne kaha ke) maine abu-Barda (apne walid ( se puchha '' bitaa' ''kya cheez hai? unhon-ne bataya ke shehad se taiyaarii ki hui sharab aur '' Muzar '' jau se taiyaar ki hui sharab . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab mein farmaya ke har nasha aawar cheez peenaa haram hai. uski riwayat Jarir aur abdul-Wahid ne Shebani se ki hai aur unhon-ne abu-Barda se ki hai.
4344,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke dada abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) aur Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman ka Hakim bana kar bheja aur farmaya ke logon ke liye aasani paida karnaa, unko dushwaariyon mein na daalnaa . logon ko khush khabriyaan dena Deen se nafrat na dilaanaa aur tum donon aapas mein muwafiqat rakhna. is par abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : aey Allah ke Nabi ! hamarey mulk mein jau se aik sharab taiyaar hoti hai jiska naam '' Muzar '' hai aur shehad se aik sharab taiyaar hoti hai jo '' bitaa' '' kahlaatii hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har nasha laney wali cheez haram hai. phir donon buzurg rawaana huey. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha aap Quran kis tarah padhtey hain? unhon-ne bataya ke khadey ho kar bhi, baith kar bhi aur apni sawari par bhi aur main thodey thodey arsa baad padhta hi rehta hun. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha lekin mera mamool (routine) ye hai ke shuru raat mein, main so jata hun aur phir bedaar ho jata hun. is tarah main apni neend par bhi sawab ka ummeedwaar hun jis tarah bedaar ho kar) ibadat karne par) sawab ki mujhey ummeed hai aur unhon-ne aik khema laga liya aur aik doosrey se mulaqat barabar hoti rehti . aik martaba Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se milney ke liye aaey, dekha aik shakhs bandhaa hua hai. puchha ye kya baat hai? abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke ye aik Yahudi hai, pahley khud Islam laya ab ye murtad ho gaya hai. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main usey qatl kiye baghair hargiz na rahunga . Muslim-bin Ibrahim ke sath is hadis ko Abdul-Malik bin-Amr aqadii aur Wahab bin Jarir ne Shoba se riwayat kya hai aur Wakee , nazar aur Abu-Dawud ne isko Shoba se, unhon-ne Saeed se, unhon apne bap burda se, unhon-ne Saeed ke dada abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya aur Jarir bin abdul-Hameed ne usko Shebani se riwayat kya, unhon-ne abu-Barda se."
4345,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke dada abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) aur Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman ka Hakim bana kar bheja aur farmaya ke logon ke liye aasani paida karnaa, unko dushwaariyon mein na daalnaa . logon ko khush khabriyaan dena Deen se nafrat na dilaanaa aur tum donon aapas mein muwafiqat rakhna. is par abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : aey Allah ke Nabi ! hamarey mulk mein jau se aik sharab taiyaar hoti hai jiska naam '' Muzar '' hai aur shehad se aik sharab taiyaar hoti hai jo '' bitaa' '' kahlaatii hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har nasha laney wali cheez haram hai. phir donon buzurg rawaana huey. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha aap Quran kis tarah padhtey hain? unhon-ne bataya ke khadey ho kar bhi, baith kar bhi aur apni sawari par bhi aur main thodey thodey arsa baad padhta hi rehta hun. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha lekin mera mamool (routine) ye hai ke shuru raat mein, main so jata hun aur phir bedaar ho jata hun. is tarah main apni neend par bhi sawab ka ummeedwaar hun jis tarah bedaar ho kar) ibadat karne par) sawab ki mujhey ummeed hai aur unhon-ne aik khema laga liya aur aik doosrey se mulaqat barabar hoti rehti . aik martaba Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se milney ke liye aaey, dekha aik shakhs bandhaa hua hai. puchha ye kya baat hai? abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke ye aik Yahudi hai, pahley khud Islam laya ab ye murtad ho gaya hai. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main usey qatl kiye baghair hargiz na rahunga . Muslim-bin Ibrahim ke sath is hadis ko Abdul-Malik bin-Amr aqadii aur Wahab bin Jarir ne Shoba se riwayat kya hai aur Wakee , nazar aur Abu-Dawud ne isko Shoba se, unhon-ne Saeed se, unhon apne bap burda se, unhon-ne Saeed ke dada abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya aur Jarir bin abdul-Hameed ne usko Shebani se riwayat kya, unhon-ne abu-Barda se."
4346,"mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri qaum ke watan ( Yaman ( mein bhejaa. phir main aaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka ki) wadi Abtah mein padao kiye huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya : Abdullah-bin-Qais ! tum ne Haj ka ehram baandh liya ? maine arz kya : ji haan ya Rasulullah ! aap ne malum farmaya ke kalimaat ehram kis tarah kahey ? bayan kya ke maine arz kya (ke yun kalimaat ada kiye hain) ''aey Allah main hazir hun, aur jis tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram baandha hai, maine bhi isi tarah baandha hai.'' farmaya tum apne sath qurbani ka janwar bhi laey ho? maine kaha ke koi janwar to main apne sath nahi laya. farmaya tum phir pahley Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee kar lo. un ruknon ki adaaeygi ke baad halal ho jaanaa. maine isi tarah kya aur banu- Qais ki khatun ne mere sar mein kangha kya aur usi qaayde par ham us waqt tak chaltey rahe jab tak umr (Raziallahu anhu) khaleefa huey (usi ko hajje-tamatto kehtey hain aur ye bhi sunnat hai)."
4347,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman ka (haakim bana kar bhejtey waqt unhein) hidayat farmai thi ke tum aik aisi qaum ki taraf ja rahe ho jo ahle-kitab Yahudi aur nasrani wghaira mein se hain. isliye jab tum wahan pahuncho to pahley unhein uski dawat do ke wo gawahi dein ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke rasool hain. agar usmein wo tumhari baat maan lein to phir unhein bataao ke Allah Taala ne rozaana un par panch waqt ki namazein farz ki hain, jab ye bhi maan lein to unhein bataao ke Allah Taala ne un par zakat ko bhi farz kya hai, jo unke maaldaar logon se li jaeygi aur unhein ke ghareebon mein taqseem kar di jaeygi. jab ye bhi maan jayen to ( phir zakat wsool kartey waqt) unka sabse umda maal leney se parhez karna aur mazloom ki aah se har waqt dartey rehna ke iske aur Allah ke darmyan koi rukawat nahi hoti hai. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke sura Mayeda mein jo ( طوعت‏ (ka lafz aaya hai iska wahi mana hai jo ( taa'at (aur ( أطاعت (ka hai jaisey kehtey hain ( طعت وطعت وأطعت‏) sab ka mana aik hi hai."
4348,"jab wo Yaman pahunchey to Yaman walon ko subah ki Namaz padhai aur Namaz mein aayat ( واتخذ الله إبراهيم خليلا‏ ( ki qirat ki to unmein se aik sahib (namaz hi mein) boley ke Ibrahim ki walida ki aankh thandii ho gaee hogi. Muaaz-bin-Muaaz Baghwii ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Habib se, unhon-ne Saeed se, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Memoon se us hadis mein sirf itna badhaya hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz ko Yaman bheja wahan unhon-ne subah ki Namaz mein sura Nisa padhi jab is aayat par pahunchey ( واتخذ الله إبراهيم خليلا‏ ( to aik sahib jo unke peechhey khadey huey they kaha ke Ibrahim ki walida ki aankh thandii ho gaee hogi."
4349,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Yaman bhejaa, bayan kya ke phir iske baad unki jagah Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja aur aap ne unhein hidayat ki ke Khalid ke sathiyon se kaho ke jo unmein se tumharey sath Yaman mein rehna chahey wo tumharey sath phir Yaman ko lot jaey aur jo wahan se wapas aana chahey wo chala aaey. Bara (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main un logon mein se tha jo Yaman ko lot gaey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke mujhey ghaneemat mein kai auqiya chandi ke miley they."
4350,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ki jagah Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko) Yaman ( bheja taake ghaneemat ke khums (maale-ghaneemat mein se paanchwein hisse) ko unse ley aaein. mujhey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se bahut bughz tha aur maine unhein ghusl kartey dekha tha. maine Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha tum dekhtey ho Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kya kya (aur aik londi se sohbat ki) phir jab ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to maine aap se bhi iska zikr kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya (Bareeda) kya tumhen Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se bughz hai? maine arz kya ke ji haan, farmaya Ali se dushmanii na rakhna kyonke khums (ghaneemat ke paanchwein hissey) mein us se bhi zyada haq hai."
4351,"Yaman se Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas berii ke patton se dabaaghat diye huey chamdey ke aik thailey mein soney ke chand daley bhejey. unse (kaan ki) mitti bhi abhi saaf nahi ki gaee thi. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo sona char aadmiyon mein taqseem kar diya. Uena-bin-Badr, Aqraa'-bin-Haabis, Zaid-bin-Khail aur chauthey Alqama (Raziallahu anhu) they ya Aamir-bin-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) they. aap ke ashaab mein se aik sahib ne is par kaha ke un logon se zyada ham us soney ke mustahiq they. rawi ne bayan kya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko malum hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mujh par eitibaar nahi kartey halanke us Allah ne mujh par eitibaar kya hai jo aasman par hai aur uski jo aasman par hai wahi mere paas subah w Sham aati hai. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir aik shakhs jiski aankhen dhansii hui thin, donon rukhsar phooley huey they, peshani bhi ubhrii hui thi, ghanii dadhi aur sar mundaa hua, tehband uthaey huey tha, khada hua aur kehney laga : ya Rasulullah! Allah se dariye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke afsos tujh par, kya main is poori zameen par Allah se darney ka sabse zyada mustahiq nahi hoon? rawi ne bayan kya phir wo shakhs chala gaya. Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main kyon na is shakhs ki gardan mar dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi shayad wo Namaz padhta ho, is par Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke bahut se Namaz padhney waley aisey hain jo zaban se Islam ka dawa kartey hain aur unke dil mein wo nahi hota. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iska hukm nahi hua hai ke logon ke dilon ki khoj lagaaun aur na iska hukm hua ke unke pet chaak karun. rawi ne kaha phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us ( munafiq ( ki taraf dekha to wo peeth pher kar ja raha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iski nasl se aik aisi qaum niklegii jo kitabullah ki tilawat badi achchi awaz ke sath karegi lekin wo unke halaq se nichey nahi utrega. Deen se wo log is tarah nikal chukey hongey jaisey teer janwar ke paar nikal jata hai aur mera khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya ke agar main unke daur mein hua to Samood ki qaum ki tarah unko bilkul qatl kar daalunga."
4352,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se (jab wo Yaman se Makka aaey) farmaya tha ke wo apne ehram par baqi rahen Muhammad-bin-bakr ne ibne-Juraij se itna badhaya ke unse Ata ne bayan kya ke Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Ali (Raziallahu anhu) apni wilaayat ( Yaman ( se aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ke Ali ! tum ne ehram kis tarah baandha hai? arz kya ke jis tarah ehram aap ne baandha ho. farmaya phir qurbani ka janwar bhej 2 aur jis tarah ehram baandha hai, usi ke mutabiq amal karo. bayan kya ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye qurbani ke janwar laey they."
4353,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umra aur Haj donon ka ehram baandha tha aur ham ne bhi aap ke sath Haj hi ka ehram baandha tha. phir ham jab Makka aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiske sath qurbani ka janwar na ho wo apne Haj ke ehram ko Umre ka ehram kar ley (aur tawaaf aur saee karke ehram khol de) aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath qurbani ka janwar tha. phir Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) Yaman se lot kar Haj ka ehram baandh kar aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ke tum ne kis tarah ehram baandha hai? hamarey sath tumhari bevi Fatima bhi hain. unhon-ne arz kya ke maine isi tarah ka ehram baandha hai jis tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baandha ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir apne ehram par qaaim raho, kyonke hamarey sath qurbani ka janwar hai."
4354,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umra aur Haj donon ka ehram baandha tha aur ham ne bhi aap ke sath Haj hi ka ehram baandha tha. phir ham jab Makka aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiske sath qurbani ka janwar na ho wo apne Haj ke ehram ko Umre ka ehram kar ley (aur tawaaf aur saee karke ehram khol de) aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath qurbani ka janwar tha. phir Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) Yaman se lot kar Haj ka ehram baandh kar aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ke tum ne kis tarah ehram baandha hai? hamarey sath tumhari bevi Fatima bhi hain. unhon-ne arz kya ke maine isi tarah ka ehram baandha hai jis tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baandha ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir apne ehram par qaaim raho, kyonke hamarey sath qurbani ka janwar hai."
4355,"mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke zul-khalasa se mujhey kyon nahi be-fikrii dilaatey ! maine arz kya main hukm ki ta'meel karunga. chunanche qabila Ahmas ke dedh so sawaaron ko sath lekar mein rawaana hua. ye sab achchhey sawar they, lekin main sawari achi tarah nahi kar paata tha. maine iske mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath mere seeney par maara jiska asar maine apne seene mein dekha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai."
4356,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke tum mujhey zul-khalasa se kyon nahi be-fikr kartey? ye qabila Khasam ka aik but khaana tha. usey Kaba yamaaniya bhi kehtey they. chunanche main dedh so qabila Ahmas ke sawaaron ko lekar rawaana hua. ye sab achchhey shahsawaar they. magar main ghodey ki sawari achi tarah nahi kar sakta tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere seeney par hath maara yahan tak ke maine aap ki ungliyon ka asar apne seeney mein paya. phir aap ne dua ki ke aey Allah ! usey ghodey ka achchha sawar bana de aur usey rasta bataaney wala aur khud rasta paya hua bana de. phir wo us but-khaaney ki taraf rawaana huey aur usey dhaa kar usmein aag laga di. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein itlaa bhejii. Jarir ke eilchii ne aa kar arz kya is zaat ki qism ! jisne aapko haq ke sath maboos kya, main us waqt tak aap ki khidmat mein hazir honey ke liye nahi chala jab tak wo khaarish zada oont ki tarah jal kar) siyah ( nahi ho gaya. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila Ahmas ke ghodon aur logon ke liye panch martaba barkat ki dua farmai ."
4357,"mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke zul-khalasa se mujhey kyon nahi be-fikrii dilaatey ! maine arz kya main hukm ki ta'meel karunga . chunanche qabila Ahmas ke dedh so sawaaron ko sath lekar mein rawaana hua. ye sab achchhey sawar they, lekin main sawari achi tarah nahi kar paata tha. maine iske mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zikr kya to aap ne apna hath mere seeney par maara jiska asar maine apne Sina mein dekha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai ''aey Allah ! isey achchha sawar bana de aur isey hidayat karne wala aur khud hidayat paya hua bana de.'' rawi ne bayan kya ke phir iske baad mein kabhi kisi ghodey se nahi gira . rawi ne bayan kya ke zul-khalasa aik ( but khaana ( tha, Yaman mein qabila Khasam aur bajeela ka, usmein but they jinki puja ki jati thi aur usey Kaba bhi kehtey they. bayan kya ke phir Jarir wahan pahunchey aur usey aag laga di aur dhaa diya. bayan kya ke jab Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) Yaman pahunchey to wahan aik shakhs tha jo teeron se faal nikala karta tha. us se kisi ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke eilchii yahan aagey hain. agar unhon-ne tumhen pa liya to tumhari gardan mar dengey. bayan kya ke abhi wo faal nikal hi rahe they ke Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) wahan pahunch gaey. aap ne us se farmaya ke ye faal ke teer tod kar kalima la Ilaah illallaah padh ley warna main teri gardan mar doonga. rawi ne bayan kya us shakhs ne teer wghaira tod daley aur kalima eman ki gawahi di. iske baad Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ne qabila Ahmas ke aik sahabi abu-artaat (Raziallahu anhu) naam ke ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja jab wo khidmat mein hazir huey to unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath maboos kya hai. main aap ki khidmat mein hazir honey ke liye us waqt tak nahi chala jab tak us but kade ko khaarish zada oont ki tarah jalaa kar siyah nahi kar diya. bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila Ahmas ke ghodon aur sawaaron ke liye panch martaba barkat ki dua farmai."
4358,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ko jange-zaatus-salaasil ke liye ameere-lashkar bana kar bhejaa. Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke (jang se wapas aa kar) main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se puchha ke aapko sabse zyada azeez kon shakhs hai? farmaya ke Aaisha, maine puchha aur mardon mein? farmaya ke uske waalid, maine poochha, uske baad kaun? farmaya ke Umar. is tarah aap ne kai aadmiyon ke naam liye bas mein khamosh ho gaya ke kahin aap mujhey sabse baad mein na kar dein."
4359,"( Yaman se waapsii par Madina aaney ke liye) main dariya ke rastey se safar kar raha tha. us waqt Yaman ke 2 aadmiyon zoo-kulaa' aur zu-Amr se meri mulaqat hui mein unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baatein karne laga is par zu-Amr ne kaha : agar tumharey sahib (yani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) wahi hain jinka zikr tum kar rahe ho to unki wafat ko bhi teen din guzar chukey. ye donon mere sath hi (Madina ( ki taraf chal rahe they. rastey mein hamein Madina ki taraf se aatey huey kuchh sawar dikhai diye, ham ne unse puchha to unhon-ne uski tasdeeq ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wafat pa gaey hain. aap ke khaleefa Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) muntakhab huey hain aur log ab bhi sab khairiyat se hain. un donon ne mujh se kaha ke apne sahib (abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) se kehna ke ham aaey they aur inshaAllah phir Madina aaeingey ye keh kar donon Yaman ki taraf wapas chaley gaey. phir maine Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko unki baton ki itlaa di to aap ne farmaya ke phir unhein apne sath laey kyon nahi? bahut dinon baad khilaafate-Umar mein zu-Amr ne aik martaba mujh se kaha ke Jarir ! tumhara mujh par ehsan hai aur tumhen main aik baat bataaoonga ke tum ahale-arab us waqt tak khair w bhalai ke sath rahogey jab tak tumhara tarze-amal ye hoga ke jab tumhara koi ameer wafat pa jaeyga to tum apna koi doosra ameer muntakhab kar liya karogey. lekin jab (amaarat ke liye) talwaar tak baat pahunch jaey to tumharey ameer badshah bin jaengey. baadshaahon ki tarah ghussa hua karengey aur unhiin ki tarah khush hua karengey."
4360,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saahile-samandar ki taraf aik lashkar bheja aur uska ameer abu-Ubaida bin-Jarraah (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya. usmein teen so aadmi Sharik they. khair ham Madina se rawaana huey aur abhi rastey hi mein they ke raashan khatm ho gaya, jo kuchh bach raha tha wo abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) hamein rozaana thoda thodaa usi mein se khaney ko detey rahe. aakhir jab ye bhi khatm ke qareeb pahunch gaya to hamarey hissey mein sirf eik-eik khajoor aati thi. Wahab ne kaha maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke aik khajoor se kya hota raha hoga? Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha wo aik khajoor hi ghaneemat thi. jab wo bhi na rahi to ham ko uski qadr malum hui thi, aakhir ham samandar ke kinarey pahunch gaey. wahan kya dekhtey hain badey teeley ki tarah aik machhli nikal kar padi hai. us machhli ko Sara lashkar atthaara raaton tak khata raha. baad mein abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ke hukm se uski paslii ki do haddiyaan khadi ki gain wo itni unchi thin ke oont par kajaawa kasaa gaya wo unke taley se nikal gaya aur haddiyon ko bilkul nahi laga."
4361,"hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen so sawaaron ke sath bheja aur hamara ameer abu-Ubaida bin-Jarraah (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya. taake ham Quraish ke qaafilae-tijaarat ki talash mein rahiin. saahil samandar par ham pandarah din tak padao daley rahe. hamein (is safar mein) badi sakht bhook aur faaqey ka saamnaa karna padaa, yahan tak naubat pahunchi ke ham ne babool ke pattey kha kar waqt guzaaraa. isi liye us fauj ka laqab patton ki fauj ho gaya. phir ittifaq se samandar ne hamarey liye aik machhli jaisa janwar saahil par phenk diya, uska naam anbar tha, ham ne usko pandarah din tak khaya aur uski charbi ko tel ke taur par (apne jismon par) mila. us se hamarey badan ki taqat w quwwat phir lot aai. baad mein abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski aik paslii nikal kar khadi karwai aur jo lashkar mein sabse lambey aadmi they, unhein iske nichey se guzara . Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne aik martaba is tarah bayan kya ke aik paslii nikal kar khadi kar di aur aik shakhs ko oont par Sawar karaya wo iske nichey se nikal gaya. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke lashkar ke aik aadmi ne pahley teen oont zabah kiye phir teen oont zabah kiye aur jab teesri martaba teen oont zabah kiye to abu-Ubaida ne unhein rok diya kyonke agar sab oont zabah kar detey to safar kaisey hota aur Amr-bin-Dinar ne bayan kya ke ham ko Abu-Saleh Zakwan ne khabar di ke Qais-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( wapas aa kar) apne walid ( Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu)) se kaha ke main bhi lashkar mein tha jab logon ko bhook lagi to abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke oont zabah karo, Qais-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine zabah kar diya kaha ke phir bhookey huey to unhon-ne kaha ke oont zabah karo, maine zabah kya, bayan kya ke jab phir bhookey huey to kaha ke oont zabah karo, maine zabah kya, phir bhookey huey to kaha ke oont zabah karo, phir Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke us martaba mujhey ameere-lashkar ki taraf se mana kar diya gaya."
4362,"ham patton ki fauj mein Sharik they. abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey ameer they. phir hamein shiddat se bhook lagii, aakhir samandar ne aik aisi murda machhli bahar phenkii ke ham ne waisii machhli pahley kabhi nahi dekhi thi. usey anbar kehtey they. wo machhli ham ne pandarah din tak khaaii. phir abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski haddi khadi karwaa di to oont ka sawar iske nichey se guzar gaya. ( ibne- Jarir ne bayan kya ke) phir mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di aur unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha is machhli ko khaao phir jab ham Madina lot kar aaey to ham ne iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo rozii khaao jo Allah Taala ne tumharey liye bheji hai. agar tumharey paas usmein se kuchh bachi ho to mujhey bhi khilaao. chunanche aik aadmi ne iska gosht la kar aap ki khidmat mein pesh kya aur aap ne bhi usey khaayaa."
4363,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko Hijjatul-wada se pahley jis Haj ka ameer bana kar bheja tha, usmein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey kai aadmiyon ke sath qurbani ke din ( Mina ( mein elaan karne ke liye bheja tha ke is saal ke baad koi mushrik ( Baitullah (ka Haj karne na aaey aur na koi shakhs Baitullah ka tawaaf nangey ho kar kare."
4364,sabse aakhiri sura jo poori utri wo sura Bara't (Tauba) thi aur aakhiri aayat jo utri wo sura Nisa ki ye aayat hai) يستفتونك قل الله يفتيكم في الكلالة‏ ( .
4365,"banu-Tameem ke chand logon ka (eik wafad ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ''aey banu- Tameem ! bashaarat qabool karo. ''wo kehney lagey ke bashaarat to aap hamein de chukey, kuchh maal bhi dijiye. unke us jawab par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak par na-gawari ka asar dekha gaya, phir Yaman ke chand logon ka aik (wafad) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke banu-Tameem ne bashaarat nahi qabool ki, tum qabool kar lo. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! ham ko bashaarat qabool hai."
4366,mein us waqt se hamesha banu- Tameem se mohabbat rakhta hun jab se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zabani unki teen khubiyan maine suni hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke mutaalliq farmaya tha ke banu- Tameem dajjal ke haq mein meri ummat ke sabse zyada sakht log Sabit hongey aur banu- Tameem ki aik qaidi khatun Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey aazad kar do kyonke ye Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mein se hai aur unke yahan se zakat wsool ho kar aai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye aik qaum ki ya (ye farmaya ke) ye meri qaum ki zakat hai.
4367,banu- Tameem ke chand sawar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unhon-ne arz kya ke aap hamara koi ameer muntakhab kar dijiye Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Qaaqaa bin Mabad bin-Zaraara (Raziallahu anhu) ko ameer muntakhab kar dijiye. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! balke aap Aqra-bin-Habis (Raziallahu anhu) ko unka ameer muntakhab farma dijiye. is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke tumhara maqsad sirf mujh se ikhtilaf karna hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke nahi meri gharaz mukhalifat ki nahi hai. donon itna jhagdey ki awaz buland ho gaee. usi par sura al-hujuraat ki ye aayat nazil huiiيا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تقدموا‏ aakhir aayat tak.
4368,"mere paas aik ghadaa hai jis mein mere liye nabeez yani khajoor ka sharbat banaya jata hai. main wo methey rehney tak piyaa karta hun. kuchh waqt bahut pi leta hun aur logon ke paas der tak betha rehta hun to darta hun ke kahin fazeehat na ho. ( log kehney lagein ke ye nasha baaz hai) is par Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke qabila abdul-Qais ka wafad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchhey aaey na zaleel huey, na sharminda ( khushi se musalman ho gaey na hotey to zillat aur sharmindagi hasil hoti ( unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! hamarey aur aap ke darmyan mein mushrekeen ke qabaayel padtey hain. isliye ham aap ki khidmat mein sirf hurmat waley mahiney hi mein hazir ho saktey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein wo ehkaam w hidaayaat suna dein ke agar ham un par amal kartey rahen to jannat mein dakhil hon aur jo log hamarey sath nahi aa sakey hain unhein bhi wo hidaayaat pahuncha dein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhen char chizon ka hukm deta hun aur char chizon se roktaa hun. main tumhen hukm deta hun Allah par eman laney ka, tumhen malum hai Allah par eman lana kisey kehtey hain? uski gawahi dena ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, Namaz qaaim karne ka, zakat diye ka, Ramazan ke rozey rakhney aur maale-ghanimat mein se panchwan hissey ( baitul-maal ko) ada karne ka hukm deta hun aur main tumhen char chizon se roktaa hon yani kadu ke taunbey main aur kuredii hui lakdi ke bartan main aur sabz laakhii bartan main aur roghanii bartan mein nabeez bhigoney se mana karta hun."
4369,"jab qabila abdul-Qais ka wafad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to unhon-ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! ham qabila Rabee ki aik shaakh hain aur hamarey aur aap ke darmyan kuffaar Muzar ke qabaayel padtey hain. ham aap ki khidmat mein sirf hurmat waley mahinon mein hi hazir ho saktey hain. isliye aap chand aisi baatein batla dijiye ke ham bhi un par amal karein aur jo log hamarey sath nahi aa sakey hain, unhein bhi uski dawat dein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhen char chizon ka hukm deta hun aur char chizon se roktaa hon (main tumhen hukm deta hun ( Allah par eman laney ka yani uski gawahi dene ka ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apni ungli se) aik ishara kya, aur Namaz qaaim karne ka, zakat dene ka aur iska ke maale-ghanimat mein se panchwan hissey ( baitul-maal ko) ada kartey rehna aur main tumhen dabbaa, naqeer, muzaffat aur hantam ke bartanon ke istemal se roktaa hun."
4370,"Ummul-Momenin se ham sab ka salam kehna aur Asr ke baad 2 rakaton ke mutaalliq unse poochhna aur ye ke hamein malum hua hai ke aap unhein padhti hain aur hamein ye bhi malum hua hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein padhney se rokaa tha. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main un 2 rakaton ke padhney par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath (unke daure-khilaafat mein) logon ko maara karta tha. Kureb ne bayan kya ke phir main Ummul-Momenin ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unka paigham pahunchaya . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke iske mutaalliq Umme-Salma se poochho , maine un hazraat ko aa kar uski itlaa di to unhon-ne mujh ko Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein bheja , wo baatein poochhney ke liye jo Aaisha se unhon-ne puchhwaaii thin. Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke maine khud bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke aap Asr ke baad 2 rakaton se mana kartey they lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik martaba Asr ki Namaz padhi, phir mere yahan tashrif laaey, mere paas us waqt qabila banu- haram ki kuchh auratein baithi hui thin aur aap ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhi. ye dekh kar maine khaadima ko aap ki khidmat mein bheja aur usey hidayat kar di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pahlu mein khadi ho jana aur arz karna ke Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha hai : ya Rasulullah ! maine to aap se hi suna tha aur aap ne Asr ke baad un 2 rakaton ke padhney se mana kya tha lekin main aaj khud aapko 2 rakaat padhtey dekh rahi hun. agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hath se ishara karein to phir peechhey hat jaanaa. khaadima ne meri hidayat ke mutabiq kya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hath se ishara kya to wo peechhey hat gaee. phir jab aap farigh huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey abu-Umayya ki beti ! Asr ke baad ki 2 rakaton ke mutaalliq tum ne sawal kya hai, wjah ye hui thi ke qabila abdul-Qais ke kuchh log mere yahan apni qaum ka Islam lekar aaey they aur unki wjah se Zohar ke baad ki 2 rakatein mein nahi padh saka tha ye wahi 2 rakatein hain."
4371,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid yani masjide-Nabawi ke baad sabse pahlaa Juma Jawaasii ki masjid abdul-Qais mein qaaim hua. Jawaasii Bahrain ka aik gaaun tha.
4372,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najad ki taraf kuchh sawar bhejey wo qabila banu-Haneefa ke) sardaaron mein se) aik shakhs Samaama-bin-Assaal naam ke ko pakad kar laey aur masjide-Nabawi ke aik sutoon se baandh diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur puchha Samama to kya samajhta hai? (main terey sath kya karoonga?) unhon-ne kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mere paas khair hai (iske bawajud ( agar aap mujhey qatl kar dein to aap aik shakhs ko qatl karengey jo khoonii hai, us ne jang mein musalmanon ko maara aur agar aap mujh par ehsan karengey to aik aisey shakhs par ehsan karengey jo (ehsaan karne waley ka ( shukr ada karta hai lekin agar aapko maal matloob hai to jitna chaahein mujh se maal talab kar saktey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan se chaley aaey, doosrey din aap ne phir puchha : Samama ab to kya samajhta hai? unhon-ne kaha, wahi jo main pahley keh chuka hun, ke agar aap ne ehsan kya to aik aisey shakhs par ehsan karengey jo shukr ada karta hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) phir chaley gaey, teesrey din phir aap ne unse puchha : ab to kya samajhta hai samaama? unhon-ne kaha ke wahi jo main aap se pahley keh chuka hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke Samama ko chhod do (rassii khol di gai) to wo masjide-Nabawi se qareeb aik baagh mein gaey aur ghusl karke masjide-Nabawi mein hazir huey aur padhaa أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله ، Mina padhi. وأشهد أن محمدا رسول الله aur kaha aey Muhammad ! Allah ki qism poori zameen par koi chehra aap ke chehrey se zyada mere liye bura nahi tha lekin aaj aap ke chehrey se zyada koi chehra mere liye mahboob nahi hai. Allah ki qism koi Deen aap ke Deen se zyada mujhey bura nahi lagta tha lekin aaj aap ka Deen mujhey sabse zyada pasandida aur azeez hai. Allah ki qism ! koi Shahar aap ke Shahar se zyada bura mujhey nahi lagta tha lekin aaj aap ka Shahar mera sabse zyada mahboob Shahar hai. aap ke sawaaron ne mujhey pakda to main Umre ka irada kar chuka tha. ab aap ka kya hukm hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bashaarat di aur Umra ada karne ka hukm diya. jab wo Makka pahunchey to kisi ne kaha ke tum be-deen ho gaey ho. unhon-ne jawab diya ke nahi balke mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath eman ley aaya hun aur Allah ki qism ! ab tumharey yahan yamaama se gehun ka aik daana bhi us waqt tak nahi aayega jab tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ijazat na de dein."
4373,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein Musailma kazzaab aaya, is da'we ke sath ke agar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey apne baad) apna naaib w khaleefa ( bana dein to main unki ittaba (pairvi) kar loon. iske sath uski qaum (banu-Haneefa) ka bahut bada lashkar tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski taraf tableegh ke liye tashrif ley gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sabit bin Qais-bin Shamas (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. aap ke hath mein khajoor ki aik tahnii thi. jahan Musailma apni fauj ke sath padao kiye huey tha, aap wahin ja kar thahar gaey aur aap ne us se farmaya agar to mujh se ye tahnii maangega to main tujhey ye bhi nahi doonga aur to Allah ke us faisley se aagey nahi badh sakta jo terey barey mein pahley hi ho chuka hai. tu ney agar meri itaat se ru-gardani (munh pherna) ki to Allah Taala tujhey halaak kar dega. mera to khayal hai ke to wahi hai jo mujhey khuwab mein dikhaya gaya tha. ab teri baton ka jawab meri taraf se Saabit-bin-Qais dengey, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif laey."
4374,"phir maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us irshad ke mutaalliq puchha ke ''meraa khayal to ye hai ke to wahi hai jo mujhey khuwab mein dikhaya gaya tha.'' to Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main soyaa hua tha, maine apne hathon mein soney ke 2 kangan dekhey, mujhey unhein dekh kar bada dukh hua phir khuwab hi mein mujh par wahi ki gaee ke main unmein phoonk mar dun. chunanche maine unmein phoonkaa to wo ud gaey. maine uski tabeer 2 jhooton se li jo mere baad niklengey. aik Aswad ansaa tha aur doosra Musailma kazzaab, jin har 2 ko khuda ne phoonk ki tarah khatm kar diya."
4375,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' khuwab mein mere paas zameen ke khazaaney laey gaey aur mere hathon mein soney ke 2 kangan rakh diye gaey. ye mujh par bada sakht guzraa. uske baad mujhey wahi ki gaee ke main unmein phoonk maarun . maine phoonkaa to wo ud gaey. maine uski tabeer 2 jhooton se li jinke darmyan mein, main hun yani sahib san'aa ( Aswad ansaa (aur sahib yamaama ( Musailma kazzaab ( .''"
4376,ham pahley patthar ki puja kartey they aur agar koi patthar hamein us se achchha mil jata to usey phenk detey aur us doosrey ki puja shuru kar detey. agar hamein patthar na milta to mitti ka aik teela bana letey aur bakri la kar is par dohtey aur uske gird tawaaf kartey. jab rajab ka mahina aa jata to ham kehtey ke ye mahina nezon ko door rakhney ka hai. chunanche hamarey paas lohey se baney huey jitney bhi neze ya teer hotey ham rajab ke mahiney mein unhein apne se door rakhtey aur unhein kisi taraf phenk detey.
4377,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maboos huey to main abhi kam-Umr tha aur apne ghar ke oont charaaya karta tha phir jab ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki fateh (Makka ki khabar suni ( to ham aapko chhod kar dozakh mein chaley gaey, yani Musailma kazzaab ke perokar bin gaey."
4378,"hamein malum hai ke jab Musailma kazzaab Madina aaya to binte- Haris ke ghar us ne qiyam kya, kyonke binte- Haris bin kurez uski biwi thi. yahi Abdullah bin-abdullaah-bin-Aamir ki maan hai, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske yahan tashrif laey ( tableegh ke liye) aap ke sath Sabit bin Qais-bin Shamas (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) wahi hain jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khateeb ke naam se mashhoor they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein aik chhadi thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske paas aa kar thahar gaey aur us se guftgu ki aur usey Islam ki dawat di. Musailma ne kaha ke main is shart par musalman hota hun ke aap ke baad mujh ko hukumat miley. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum mujh se ye chhadi maangogey to main ye bhi nahi de sakta aur main to samajhta hun ke tum wahi ho jo mujhey khuwab mein dikhaaey gaey they. ye Saabit-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) hain aur meri taraf se tumhari baton ka yahi jawab dengey , phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif ley aaey."
4379,"mujhey malum hua hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke mujhey khuwab mein dikhaya gaya tha ke mere hathon par soney ke 2 kangan rakh diye gaey hain. main us se bahut ghabraayaa aur un kanganon se mujhey tashwish hui, phir mujhey hukm hua aur maine unhein phoonk diya to donon kangan ud gaey. maine uski tabeer 2 jhooton se li jo khurooj karne waley hain. Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke unmein se aik Aswad ansaa tha, jisey feeroz ne Yaman mein qatl kya aur doosra Musailma kazzaab tha."
4380,"Najran ke 2 sardaar aaqib aur saiyed , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mubaahala karne ke liye aaey they lekin aik ne apne doosrey sathi se kaha ke aisa na karo kyonke Allah ki qism ! agar ye Nabi huey aur phir bhi ham ne unse mubaahala kya to ham panap nahi saktey aur na hamarey baad hamari naslein reh sakengii. phir un donon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke jo kuchh aap maangein ham jiziya dene ke liye taiyaar hain. aap hamarey sath koi ameen bhej dijiye, jo bhi aadmi hamarey sath bhejein wo ameen hona zaroori hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumharey sath aik aisa aadmi bhejoonga jo amanat daar hoga balke pura pooraa amanat daar hoga. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke muntazir they, aap ne farmaya ke abu-Ubaida bin Jarraah! utho. jab wo khadey huey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye is ummat ke ameen hain."
4381,"ahal Najran Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke hamarey sath koi amanat daar aadmi bhejiye . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumharey sath aisa aadmi bhejoonga jo har haisiyat se amanat daar hoga. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) muntazir they, aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhejaa."
4382,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''har ummat mein ameen ( amaanatdaar ( hotey hain aur is ummat ke ameen abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah hain.''
4383,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya tha jab mere paas Bahrain se rupya aayega to main tumhen itna itnaa teen lap bhar kar rupya doonga , lekin Bahrain se jis waqt rupya aaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho chuki thi. isliye wo rupya Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur unhon-ne elaan karwaa diya ke agar kisi ka Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par qarz ya kisi se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka koi wada ho to wo mere paas aaey. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main unke yahan aa gaya aur unhein bataya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya tha ke agar Bahrain se mere paas rupya aaya to main tumhen itna itnaa teen lap bhar kar doonga . Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir maine unse mulaqat ki aur unse iske mutaalliq kaha lekin unhon-ne is martaba mujhey nahi diya. main phir unke yahan gaya is martaba bhi unhon-ne nahi diya. main teesri martaba gaya, is martaba bhi unhon-ne nahi diya. isliye maine unse kaha ke main aap ke yahan aik martaba aaya. aap ne nahi diya, phir aaya aur aap ne nahi diya. phir teesri martaba aaya hun aur aap is martaba bhi nahi de rahe hain. agar aapko mujhey dena hai to de dijiye warna saaf keh dijiye ke mera dil dene ko nahi chaahtaa, main kanjoos hun. is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya tum ne kaha hai ke mere maamle mein kanjoosii kar lo, bhala kanjoosii se badh kar aur kya aib ho sakta hai. teen martaba unhon-ne ye jumla dohraya aur kaha maine tumhen jab bhi taala to mera irada yahi tha ke bahar-haal tumhen dena hai. aur isi sanad se Amr-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai, unse Muhammad-bin Ali Baaqar ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke main hazir hua to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey aik lap bhar kar rupya diya aur kaha ke usey gin lo. maine ginaa to panch so tha. farmaya ke 2 martaba itna hi aur ley lo."
4384,main aur mere bhai Abu-Raham ya abu-Barda Yaman se aaey to ham ( shuruaat mein) bahut dinon tak ye samajhtey rahe ke ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) aur unki walida umme-abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) donon Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahale-bait mein se hain kyonke ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar mein raat din bahut aaya jaya kartey they aur har waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath raha kartey they.
4385,"jab abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) (koofa ke ameer bin kar Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke daure-khilaafat mein) aaey to us qabila jurm ki unhon-ne bahut izzat kii. Zahdam kehtey hain ham aap ki khidmat mein baithey huey they aur wo murgh ka naashta kar rahe they. haaziriin mein aik aur sahib bhi baithey huey they. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bhi khaney par bulaya to un sahib ne kaha ke jab se maine murghiyon ko kuchh ( gandii ( cheezein khaatey dekha hai, usi waqt se mujhey uske gosht se ghin aaney lagi hai. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aao bhai maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uska gosht khaatey dekha hai. un sahib ne kaha lekin maine uska gosht na khaney ki qism kha rakhi hai. unhon-ne kaha ke tum aa to jao main tumhen tumhari qism ke barey mein bhi ilaaj bataaoonga. ham qabila ash'ar ke chand log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se (jange-Tabook ke liye) janwar maangey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sawari nahi hai. ham ne phir aap se maanga to aap ne is martaba qism khaaii ke aap ham ko sawari nahi dengey lekin abhi kuchh zyada der nahi hui thi ke ghaneemat mein kuchh oont aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein se panch oont ham ko dilaaey. jab ham ne unhein ley liya to phir ham ne kaha ke ye to ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dhokaa diya. aapko ghafalat mein rakhaa, qism yad nahi dilaaii. aisi haalat mein hamari bhalai kabhi nahi hogi. aakhir mein aap ke paas aaya aur maine kaha : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne to qism kha li thi ke aap ham ko sawari nahi dengey phir aap ne sawari de di. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke theek hai lekin jab bhi main koi qism khata hun aur uske siwa dusri sura mujhey us se behtar nazar aati hai to main wahi karta hun jo behtar hota hai (aur qism ka kaffara de deta hoon)."
4386,"banu- Tameem Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey banu- Tameem ! bashaarat qabool karo. unhon-ne kaha ke jab aap ne hamein bashaarat di hai to kuchh rupye bhi inayat farmaiye . is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey ka rang badal gaya. phir Yaman ke kuchh Ash-ari log aaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke banu- Tameem ne bashaarat qabool nahi ki, Yaman waalo! tum qabool kar lo. wo boley ham ne qabool ki ya Rasulullah ."
4387,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke eman to idhar hai aur aap ne apne hath se Yaman ki taraf ishara kya aur be-rahmii aur sakht dillii oont ki dam ke peechhey peechhey chalaney walon mein hai, jidhar se shaitan ke donon seeng nikaltey hain (yani mashriq) qabila Rabee aur Muzar ke logon mein."
4388,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey yahan ahale-Yaman aagey hain, unke dil ke pardey baareek , dil narm hotey hain, eman Yaman walon ka hai aur hikmat bhi Yaman ki achi hai aur fakhr w takabbur oont walon mein hota hai aur itminan aur sahoolat bakri walon main aur ghandar ne bayan kya is hadis ko Shoba se, unse Sulaiman ne, unhon-ne Zakwan se suna, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
4389,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke eman Yaman ka hai aur fitna (deen ki kharaabii) idhar se hai aur idhar hi se shaitan ke sar ka kona namudaar hoga.
4390,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey yahan ahal Yaman aaey hain jo narm dil hain, Deen ki samajh Yaman walon mein hai aur hikmat bhi Yaman ki hai."
4391,"ham Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas baithey huey they. itney mein Khabbaab-bin-Arat (Raziallahu anhu) mashhoor sahabi tashrif laey aur kaha : abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya ye naujawaan log (jo tumharey shagird hain) isi tarah Quran padh saktey hain jaisey aap padhtey hain? ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar aap chaahein to main kisi se tilawat ke liye kahun ? unhon-ne farmaya ke zaroor . is par ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Alqama ! tum padho, Zaid-bin Hudair , Ziyad bin Hudair ke bhai , boley aap Alqama se tilawat Quran ke liye farmatey hain halanke wo ham sabse achchhey qaari nahi hain. ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha agar tum chaho to main tumhen wo hadis suna dun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhari qaum ke haq mein farmai thi. khair Alqama kehtey hain ke maine sura Maryam ki pachaas aayatein padh kar sunain . Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabbaab (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kaho kaisa padhta hai? khabbaab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha bahut khub padha . Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jo aayat bhi mein jis tarah padhta hun Alqama bhi isi tarah padhta hai, phir unhon-ne khabbaab (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, unke hath mein soney ki anguthi thi, to kaha : kya abhi waqt nahi aaya hai ke ye anguthi phenk di jaey. khabbaab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aaj ke baad aap ye anguthi mere hath mein nahi dekhengey . chunanche unhon-ne anguthi utaar di. usi hadis ko ghandar ne Shoba se riwayat kya hai."
4392,Tufail-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke qabila dos to tabah hua. us ne nafarmani aur inkar kya (Islam qabool nahi kya (aap Allah se unke liye dua kijiye . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Allah ! qabila dos ko hidayat de aur unhein mere yahan ley aa.'
4393,"jab main apne watan se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir honey ke liye chala to rastey mein, maine ye sher padha ( tarjama ( '' kaisi hai takleef ki lambi ye raat , khair us ne kufr se di hai najaat'' aur mera ghulam rastey mein bhag gaya tha, phir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se bait ki, abhi aap ke paas main betha hi hua tha ke wo ghulam dikhai diya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! ye hai tumhara ghulam ! maine kaha Allah ke liye maine usko ab aazad kar diya."
4394,"ham umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein (unki daure-khilaafat mein) aik wafad ki shakl mein aaey. wo eik-eik shakhs ko naam ley lekar bulatey jatey they) maine unse kaha kya aap mujhey pehchantey nahi ? aey ameerul-momineen ! farmaya kya tumhen bhi nahi pahchaanoonga, tum us waqt Islam laey jab ye sab kufr par qaaim they. tum ne us waqt tawajjoh ki jab ye sab munh mod rahe they. tum ne us waqt wafaa ki jab ye sab be-wafaaii kar rahe they aur us waqt pehchaana jab un sab ne inkar kya tha. Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha bas ab mujhey koi parwah nahi."
4395,"Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rawaana huey. ham ne Umre ka ehram baandha tha phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiske sath qurbani ka janwar ho wo Umra ke sath Haj ka bhi ehram baandh ley aur jab tak donon ke arkaan na ada kar ley ehram na kholey. phir main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jab Makka aai to mujh ko haiz aa gaya. isliye na Baitullah ka tawaaf kar saki aur na Safa aur Marwa ki saee kar sakii. maine uski shikayat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ki to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sar khol ley aur kangha kar ley. iske baad Haj ka ehram baandh lo aur Umra chhod do. maine aisa hi kya. phir jab ham Haj ada kar chukey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey (mere bhaaii) Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath taneem se (Umra ki) niyat karne ke liye bheja aur maine Umra kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye tumharey us chhootey huey Umra ki qaza hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke jin logon ne sirf Umre ka ehram baandha tha. unhon-ne Baitullah ke tawaaf aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee ke baad ehram khol diya. phir Mina se waapsii ke baad unhon-ne doosra tawaaf (Haj ka ( kya, lekin jin logon ne Haj aur Umra donon ka ehram aik sath baandha tha, unhon-ne aik hi tawaaf kya."
4396,( Umra karne wala ( sirf Baitullah ke tawaaf se halal ho sakta hai. (ibne-Juraij ne kaha ( maine Ata se puchha ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye masla kahan se nikaalaa? unhon-ne bataya ke Allah Taala ke irshad ( ثم محلها إلى البيت العتيق‏ ( (sura Haj) se aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us hukm ki wjah se jo aap ne apne ashaab ko Hijjatul-wada mein ehram khol dene ke liye diya tha maine kaha ke ye hukm to Arafaat mein thaharney ke baad ke liye hai. unhon-ne kaha lekin Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye mazhab tha ke Arafaat mein thaharney se pahley aur baad har haal mein jab tawaaf kar ley to ehram khol daalnaa durust hai.
4397,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wadi Batha (sangrezi zameen) mein qiyam kiye huey they. aap ne puchha tum ne Haj ka ehram baandh liyaa? maine arz kya ke ji haan. malum farmaya, ehram kis tarah baandha hai? arz kya (is tarah) ke main bhi isi tarah ehram baandhtaa hun jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baandha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke pahley (Umra karne ke liye) Baitullah ka tawaaf kar, phir Safa aur Marwa ki saee kar, phir halal ho jaa. chunanche main Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee karke qabila Qais ki aik aurat ke ghar aaya aur unhon-ne mere sar se juein nikaaliin."
4398,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein khabar di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par apni beeviyon ko hukm diya ke) Umra karne ke baad) halal ho jayen (yani ehram khol dein ( Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya (ya Rasulullah ! ( phir aap kyon nahi halal hotey ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine to apne baalon ko jama liya hai aur apni qurbani ko haar pehna diya hai, isliye main jab tak qurbani na kar loon us waqt tak ehram nahi khol sakta."
4399,"qabila Khasam ki aik aurat ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik masla poochha, Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ki sawari par aap ke peechhey baithey huey they. unhon-ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah! Allah ka jo fareeza uske bandon par hai (yani Haj) mere walid par bhi farz ho chuka hai lekin budhapey ki wjah se unki haalat ye hai ke wo sawari par nahi baith saktey. to kya main unki taraf se Haj ada kar sakti hon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan! kar sakti ho."
4400,"fateh Makka ke din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qaswaa ontni par peechhey Usama (Raziallahu anhu) baithey huey they aur aap ke sath Bilal aur Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they aap ne Kaba ke paas apni ontni bitha di aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke Kaba ki chaabii lao , wo chaabii laey aur darwaza khola . aap andar dakhil huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Usama , Bilal aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi andar gaey, phir darwaza andar se band kar liya aur der tak andar (namaz aur duaon mein mashghool ( rahe. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey to log andar janey ke liye aik doosrey se aagey badhney lagey aur main sabse aagey badh gaya. maine dekha ke Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) darwazey ke peechhey khadey huey hain. maine unse puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz kahan padhi thi? unhon-ne bataya ke khaana Kaba mein chh sutoon they. 2 qataaron main aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aagey ki qataar ke 2 sutunon ke darmyan Namaz padhi thi. Kaba ka darwaza Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki peeth ki taraf tha aur chehra Mubarak us taraf tha, jidhar darwazey se andar jatey huey chehra karna padta hai. aap ke aur diwar ke darmyan (teen hath ka fasla thaa). ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ye poochhna main bhool gaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kitni rakaat Namaz padhi thi. jis jagah aap ne Namaz padhi thi wahan surkh sang marmar bichhaa hua tha."
4401,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par haaiza ho gaee thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya abhi hamein unki wjah se rukna padega? maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! ye to Makka lot kar tawaafe-ziyaarat kar chuki hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir usey chalnaa chahiye (tawaaf wadaa' ki zarurat nahin).
4402,"ham (hijjatul-wadaa') kaha kartey they, jabke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maujood they aur ham nahi samajhtey they ke Hijjatul-wada ka mafhoom kya hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki hamd aur uski sana bayan ki phir Masih dajjal ka zikr tafseel ke sath kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jitney bhi anbiya Allah ne bhejey hain, sab ne dajjal se apni ummat ko daraayaa hai. Nuh (Alaihissalam) ne apni ummat ko us se daraayaa aur doosrey baad mein aaney waley anbiya ne bhi aur wo tum hi mein se niklega. to yad rakhna ke tum ko iske jhootey honey ki aur koi daleel na malum ho to yahi daleel kafi hai ke wo mardood kaana hoga aur tumhara rab kaana nahi hai uski aankh aisi malum hogi jaisey angoor ka daana ! ."
4403,"khub sun lo ke Allah Taala ne tum par tumharey aapas ke khoon aur amwaal isi tarah haram kiye hain jaisey is din ki hurmat is Shahar aur us mahiney mein hai. haan bolo! kya maine pahuncha diya? sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke aap ne pahuncha diya. farmaya : aey Allah ! to gawah rahiyo, teen martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye jumla dohraayaa. afsos! (aap ne ( ويلكم ( farmaya ya ( ويحكم ), rawi ko shak hai) dekho , mere baad kaafir na bin jana ke aik doosrey (muslmaan) ki gardan maarney lag jao ."
4404,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unnees jangein kiin aur hijrat ke baad sirf aik Haj kya. us Haj ke baad phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi Haj nahi kya. ye Haj , Hijjatul-wada tha. Abu-Ishaq ne bayan kya ke doosra Haj Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (hijrat se pahley) Makka mein kya tha."
4405,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya tha logon ko khamosh kar do, phir farmaya, mere baad kaafir na bin jana ke aik doosrey ki gardan maarney lago ."
4406,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke zamane apni asl haalat par ghoom kar aa gaya hai. us din ki tarah jab Allah ne zameen w aasman ko paida kya tha. dekho! saal ke baara mahiney hotey hain. char unmein se hurmat waley mahiney hain. teen lagaataar hain, zii-Qa'da, Zil-Hijja aur Mohrim (aur chauthaa) rajab Muzar jo jumaadal-oola aur Shoban ke beech mein padta hai. ( phir aap ne malum farmaya ( ye kon sa mahina hai? ham ne kaha ke Allah aur unke rasool ko behtar ilm hai. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey. ham ne samjha shayad aap mashhoor naam ke siwa uska koi aur naam rakhengey. lekin aap ne farmaya : kya ye Zil-Hijja nahi hai? ham boley ke kyon nahi. phir malum farmaya aur ye Shahar kon sa hai? ham boley ke Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada behtar ilm hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey. ham ne samjha shayad uska koi aur naam Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rakhengey, jo mashhoor naam ke ilawa hoga. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya ye Makka nahi hai? ham boley kyon nahi (ye Makka hi hai) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya aur ye din kon sa hai? ham boley ke Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada behtar ilm hai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey aur ham ne samjha shayad iska Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske mashhoor naam ke siwa koi aur naam rakhengey, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya ye yaumun-Nahar ( qurbani ka din) nahi hai? ham boley ke kyon nahi. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to tumhara khoon aur tumhara maal Muhammad ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai ke Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bhi kaha, aur tumhari izzat tum par isi tarah haram hai jis tarah ye din ka tumharey is Shahar aur tumharey is mahiney main aur tum bahut jald apne rab se milogey aur wo tum se tumharey aamaal ke barey mein sawal karega. haan, to mere baad tum gumrah na ho jana ke aik doosrey ki gardan maarney lago. haan aur jo yahan maujood hain wo un logon ko pahuncha dein jo maujood nahi hain, ho sakta hai ke jisey wo pahunchaaein unmein se koi aisa bhi ho jo yahan kuchh sunney walon se zyada is (hadees ( ko yad rakh sakta ho Muhammad-bin-Siiriin jab us hadis ka zikr kartey to farmatey ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sach farmaya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to kya maine pahuncha diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 martaba ye jumla farmaya,"
4407,"chand yahudiyon ne kaha ke agar ye aayat hamarey yahan nazil hui hoti to ham us din eid manaayaa kartey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, kon si aayat ? unhon-ne kahaa اليوم أكملت لكم دينكم وأتممت عليكم نعمتي‏ ''aaj maine tum par apne Deen ko mukammal kya aur apni nemat tum par poori kar di. '' is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke mujhey khub malum hai ke ye aayat kahan nazil hui thi. jab ye aayat nazil hui to rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maidan Arafaat mein khadey huey they (yani Hijjatul-wada mein) ."
4408,"ham jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (Haj ke liye) nikley to kuchh log ham mein se Umre ka ehram baandhey huey they, kuchh Haj ka aur kuchh Umra aur Haj donon kaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi Haj ka ehram baandha tha. jo log Haj ka ehram baandhey huey they ya jinhoney Haj aur Umra donon ka ehram baandha tha, wo qurbani ke din halal huey they. ham se Abdullah-bin Yusuf taneesii ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko Imam Malik ne khabar di, phir yahi hadis bayan ki. usmein yun hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Hijjatul-wada (ke liye ham nikley) ham se Ismaaeel-bin-abii ovais ne bayan kya, ham se Imam Malik ne bayan kya, isi tarah jo pahley mazkoor hua. ham se Abdullah-bin Yusuf taneesii ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko Imam Malik ne khabar di, phir yahi hadis bayan ki. usmein yun hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Hijjatul-wada (ke liye ham nikley) ham se Ismail bin abi ovais ne bayan kya, ham se Imam Malik ne bayan kya, isi tarah jo pahley mazkoor hua."
4409,"Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laey. bimari ne mujhey maut ke munh mein la daala tha. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! jaisa ke aap ne dekha hai, mera marz us had ko pahunch gaya hai aur mere paas maal hai, jiski waaris khali meri aik ladki hai, to kya main apna 2 tehai maal khairat kar dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. maine arz kya, aadha kar dun. farmaya ke nahi. maine farmaya kya phir tehai kar dun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tehai bhi bahut hai. tum apne waarison ko maaldaar chhod kar jao to ye us se behtar hai ke unhein mohtaaj chhodo aur wo logon ke samney hath phailaatey phirein aur tum jo kuchh bhi kharch karogey, agar us se Allah ki raza maqsud rahi to tumhen is par sawab milega. yahan tak ke us luqme par bhi tumhen sawab milega jo tum apni biwi ke munh mein rakhogey. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! (beemaarii ki wjah se) kya main apne sathiyon ke sath (Madeena) nahi ja sakoonga? farmaya agar tum nahi ja sakey tab bhi agar tum Allah ki raza hasil karney ke liye koi amal karogey to tumhara darja Allah ke yahan aur buland hoga aur ummeed hai ke tum abhi zinda rahogey aur tum se kuchh logon ( muslmaanon) ko nafa pahunchega aur kuchh logon (Islam ke dushmanon) ko nuqsan pahunchega. aey Allaah! mere sathiyon ki hijrat ko kaamil farma aur unhein peechhey na hata lekin nuqsan main to Sad bin Khaula rahe. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke Makka mein wafat pa janey ki wjah se zahir farmaayaa."
4410,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada mein apna sar mundwaayaa tha.
4411,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aap ke kuchh ashaab ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par sar mundwaayaa tha aur kuchh doosrey sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne sirf tarashwa liya tha.
4412,"wo aik gadhey par Sawar ho kar aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Mina mein khadey logon ko Namaz padha rahe they. ye Hijjatul-wada ka mauqa tha. unka gadhaa saf ke kuchh hissey se guzraa, phir wo utar kar logon ke sath saf mein khadey ho gaey."
4413,Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki (safar mein) raftaar ke mutaalliq puchha gaya to unhon-ne kaha ke beech ki chaal chaltey they aur jab kushaada jagah miltii to us se tez chaltey they.
4414,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par maghrib aur isha mila kar aik sath padhi thin.
4415,"mujhey mere sathiyon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja ke main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se unke liye sawari ke janwaron ki darkhaast karun. wo log aap ke sath jange-Tabook mein Sharik hona chahtey they. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mere sathiyon ne mujhey aap ki khidmat mein bheja hai taake aap unke liye sawari ke janwaron ka intizam kara dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main tum ko sawari ke janwar nahi de sakta. main jab aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua tha to aap ghusse mein they aur main usey malum na kar saka tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke inkar se main bahut ghamgeen wapas hua. ye khof bhi tha ke kahin aap sawari maangney ki wjah se khafa na ho gaey hon. main apne sathiyon ke paas aaya aur unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke irshad ki khabar di, lekin abhi kuchh zyada waqt nahi guzra tha ke maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki awaz suni, wo pukar rahe they, aey Abdullah-bin Qais! maine jawab diya to unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumhen bula rahe hain. main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye 2 jodey oont ke ley jao . aap ne chh oont inayat farmaaey. un oonton ko aap ne usi waqt Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se khareedaa tha aur farmaya ke unhein apne sathiyon ko de do aur unhein bataao ke Allah Taala ne ya aap ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhari sawari ke liye unhein diya hai, un par Sawar ho jao. main un oonton ko lekar apne sathiyon ke paas gaya aur unse maine kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhari sawari ke liye ye inayat farmaai hain lekin Allah ki qasam! ke ab tumhen un sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas chalnaa padega, jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka inkar farmana suna tha, kahin tum ye khayal na kar baitho ke maine tum se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke irshad ke mutaalliq ghalat baat keh di thi. unhon-ne kaha ke tumhari sachchai mein hamein koi shuba nahi hai lekin agar aap ka israar hai to ham aisa bhi kar lengey. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) unmein se chand logon ko lekar un sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka wo irshad suna tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahley to deney se inkar kya tha lekin phir inayat farmaya, un sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi isi tarah hadis bayan ki jis tarah abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse bayan ki thi."
4416,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jange-Tabook ke liye tashrif le gaey to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko Madina mein apna naaib banaya. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke aap mujhey bachchon aur aurton mein chhodey ja rahe hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum is par khush nahi ho ke mere liye tum aisey ho jaisey Musa ke liye Harun they. lekin farq ye hai ke mere baad koi Nabi nahi hoga aur Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ne us hadis ko yun bayan kya ke ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, unse hakam bin Utba ne aur unhon-ne kaha maine Musab se suna."
4417,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-Tabook mein Sharik tha. bayan kya ke Yala (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke mujhey apne tamam amalon mein isi par sabse zyada bharosa hai. Ata ne bayan kya, unse Safwan ne bayan kya ke Yala (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, maine aik mazdoor bhi apne sath ley liya tha. wo aik shakhs se lad padaa aur aik ne doosrey ka hath daant se kaataa. Ata ne bayan kya ke mujhey Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke un donon mein se kis ne apne muqabil ka hath kaataa tha, ye mujhey yad nahi hai. bahar-haal jiska hath kaataa gaya tha us ne apna hath kaatney waley ke munh se jo kheenchaa to kaatney waley ke aagey ka aik daant bhi sath chala aaya. wo donon Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne daant ke tootney par koi qisaas nahi dilwaayaa. Ata ne bayan kya mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne ye bhi bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir kya wo terey munh mein apna hath rehney deta taake to usey oont ki tarah chabaa jata."
4418,"(jab Kab (Raziallahu anhu) naa-beenaa ho gaey to unke ladkon mein wo hi Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ko rastey mein pakad kar chala kartey they) unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se unke jange-Tabook mein Sharik na ho sakney ka waqia suna. unhon-ne bataya ke jange-Tabook ke siwa aur kisi jang mein aisa nahi hua tha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sharik na hua hun. albatta jange-badr mein bhi Sharik nahi hua tha lekin jo log jange-badr mein Sharik nahi ho sakey they, unke mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi qism ki narazgi ka izhar nahi farmaya tha kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us mauqe par sirf Quraish ke qafley ki talash mein nikley they, lekin Allah Taala ke hukm se kisi pehli taiyaarii ke baghair , aap ki dushmanon se takkar ho gaee aur main lailatul-Aqba main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua tha. ye wahi raat hai jis mein ham ne (Makka mein) Islam ke liye ahad kya tha aur mujhey to ye jange-badr se bhi zyada azeez hai. haalaanki badr ka logon ki zabanon par charcha zyada hai. mera waqia ye hai ke main apni zindagi mein kabhi itna qawii aur itna sahib maal nahi hua tha jitna us mauqe par tha. jabke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Tabook ki jang mein Sharik nahi ho saka tha. Allah ki qism ! us se pahley kabhi mere paas 2 oont jama nahi huey they lekin us mauqe par mere paas 2 oont maujood they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kabhi kisi ghazwey ke liye tashrif ley jatey to aap uske liye mukhtalif-maanaa ke alfaz istemal kya kartey they lekin us jang ka jab mauqa aaya to garmi badi sakht thi, safar bhi bahut lamba tha, bayaabaanii rasta aur dushman ki fauj ki kasarate-ta'daad ! tamam Mina mushkilaat samney thin. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon se us jang ke mutaalliq bahut tafseel ke sath bata diya tha taake uske mutabiq poori tarah se taiyaarii kar lein. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us samt ki bhi nishaandehi kar di jidhar se aap ka janey ka irada tha. musalman bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bahut they. itney ke kisi rajister mein sab ke naamon ka likhnaa bhi mushkil tha. Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke koi bhi shakhs agar us ghazwey mein Sharik na hona chahta to wo ye khayal kar sakta tha ke uski ghair haziri ka kisi ko pata nahi chalega. siwa iske ke uske mutaalliq wahi nazil ho. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab us jang ke liye tashrif ley ja rahe they, to phal pakney ka zamana tha aur saaye mein baith kar log aaraam kartey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi taiyaariyon mein masroof they aur aap ke sath musalman bhii. lekin main rozaana sochaa karta tha ke kal se main bhi taiyaarii karunga aur is tarah har roz usey taalta raha. mujhey iska yaqin tha ke main taiyaarii kar loonga. mujhey aasaaniyaan muyassar hain, yun hi waqt guzarta raha aur aakhir logon ne apni taiyaariyaan mukammal bhi kar lin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) musalmanon ko sath lekar rawaana bhi ho gaey. us waqt tak maine taiyaarii nahi ki thi. us mauqe par bhi maine apne dil ko yahi keh kar samjha liya ke kal ya parson tak taiyaarii kar loonga aur phir lashkar se ja miloonga . kooch ke baad doosrey din maine taiyaarii ke liye sochaa lekin us din bhi koi taiyaarii nahi ki. phir teesrey din ke liye sochaa aur us din bhi koi taiyaarii nahi ki. yun hi waqt guzar gaya aur Islami lashkar bahut aagey badh gaya. jang mein shirkat mere liye bahut door ki baat ho gaee aur main yahi irada karta raha ke yahan se chal kar unhein pa loonga. Mina kash! ! maine aisa kar liya hota lekin ye mere naseeb mein nahi tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke tashrif ley janey ke baad jab main bahar nikalta to mujhey bada ranj hota kyonke ya to wo log nazar aatey jinke chehron se nifaq tapaktaa tha ya phir wo log jinhein Allah Taala ne ma'zoor aur zaeef qarar de diya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere barey mein kisi se kuchh nahi puchha tha lekin jab aap Tabook pahunch gaey to wahin aik majlis mein aap ne malum farmaya ke Kab ne kya kya? banu- Salma ke aik sahib ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! uske ghurur ne usey aaney nahi diya. (wo husno-jamaal ya libaas par itraa kar reh gaya) is par Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) boley tum ne buri baat kahi. ya Rasulullah ! Allah ki qism ! hamein unke mutaalliq khair ke siwa aur kuchh malum nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh nahi farmaya, Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab mujhey malum hua ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif la rahe hain to ab mujh par fikr sawar hua aur mera zahan koi aisa jhoota bahana talash karne laga jis se main kal Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki narazgi se bach sakoon. apne ghar ke har aqlmand aadmi se iske mutaalliq maine mashwara liya lekin jab mujhey malum hua ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina se bilkul qareeb aa chukey hain to ghalat khayalat mere zahan se nikal gaey aur mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke is maamle mein jhoot bol kar main apne ko kisi tarah mehfooz nahi kar sakta. chunanche maine sachchii baat kehney ka pukhta irada kar liya. subah ke waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey. jab aap kisi safar se wapas tashrif latey to ye aap ki aadat thi ke pahley masjid mein tashrif ley jatey aur 2 rakaat Namaz padhtey , phir logon ke sath majlis mein baithtey . Mina jab aap is amal se farigh ho chukey to aap ki khidmat mein log aaney lagey jo jang mein Sharik nahi ho sakey they aur qism kha kha kar apne uzr bayan karne lagey. aisey logon ki tadaad assii ke qareeb thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke zahir ko qabool farma liya, unse ahad liya. unke liye maghfirat ki dua farmai aur unke baatin ko Allah ke sipurd kya. iske baad main hazir hua. maine salam kya to aap muskuraaey. aapki muskuraahat mein narazgi thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aao, main chand qadam chal kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney baith gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se malum farmaya ke tum jang mein kyon Sharik nahi huey. kya tum ne koi sawari nahi kharidi thi? maine arz kya, mere paas sawari maujood thi. Allah ki qasam! agar main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke siwa kisi duniyaadaar shakhs ke samney aaj betha hota to koi na koi uzr ghad kar uski narazgi se bach sakta tha, mujhey khoobsoortii ke sath guftgu ka saleeqa malum hai. lekin Allah ki qism ! mujhey yaqin hai ke agar aaj main aap ke samney koi jhoota uzr bayan karke aapko razi kar loon to bahut jald Allah Taala aapko mujh se naraz kar dega. Mina iske bajaey agar main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sachchii baat bayan kar dun to yaqinan aapko meri taraf se narazgi hogi lekin Allah se mujhey maafi ki poori ummeed hai. nahi, Allah ki qism ! mujhey koi uzr nahi tha, Allah ki qism is waqt se pahley kabhi mein itna maaldaar nahi tha aur phir bhi mein aap ke sath Sharik nahi ho saka. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhon-ne sachchii baat bata di. achchha ab jao, yahan tak ke Allah Taala tumharey barey mein khud koi faisla kar de. main uth gaya aur mere peechhey banu-Salma ke kuchh log bhi daudey huey aaey aur mujh se kehney lagey ke Allah ki qasam! hamein tumharey mutaalliq ye malum nahi tha ke is se pahley tum ne koi gunah kya hai aur tum ne badi kotahi ki. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney waisaa hi koi uzr nahi bayan kya jaisa doosrey na-shareek honey walon ne bayan kar diya tha. tumharey gunah ke liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka istighfar hi kafi ho jata. Allah ki qism ! un logon ne mujhey is par itni malaamat ki ke mujhey khayal aaya ke wapas ja kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se koi jhoota uzr kar aaoon. phir maine unse puchha kya mere ilawa kisi aur ne bhi mujh jaisa uzr bayan kya hai? unhon-ne bataya ke yahan 2 hazraat ne isi tarah ma'zirat ki jis tarah tum ne ki hai aur unhein jawab bhi wahi mila hai jo tumhen mila. Mina maine puchha ke unke naam kya hain? unhon-ne bata kya ke muraara bin Rabe Umri aur Hilal bin Umayya waaqifii (Raziallahu anhu) . un 2 aisey sahaba ka naam unhon-ne ley diya tha jo Saleh they aur badr ki jang mein Sharik huey they. unka tarze-amal mere liye namoona bin gaya. chunanche unhon-ne jab un buzurgon ka naam liya to main apne ghar chala aaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko ham se baat-cheet karne ki manaahii kar di, bahut se log jo ghazwey mein Sharik nahi huey they, unmein se sirf ham teen they ! log ham se alag rehney lagey aur sab log badal gaey. aisa nazar aata tha ke ham se saari duniya badal gaee hai. hamara us se koi waasta hi nahi hai. pachaas din tak ham isi tarah rahe, mere 2 sathiyon ne to apne gharon se nikalnaa hi chhod diya, bas rotey rahtey they lekin mere andar himmat thi ke main bahar nikalta tha, musalmanon ke sath Namaz mein Sharik hota tha aur bazaron mein ghoomaa karta tha lekin mujh se boltaa koi na tha. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhi hazir hota tha, aapko salam karta, jab aap Namaz ke baad majlis mein baithtey, main is justju mein laga rehta tha ke dekhun salam ke jawab main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Mubarak hont hiley ya nahi, phir aap ke qareeb hi Namaz padhney lag jata aur aapko kankhiyon se dekhta rehta jab main apni Namaz mein mashghool ho jata to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri taraf dekhtey lekin junhii main aap ki taraf dekhta aap rukh Mubarak pher letey. aakhir jab is tarah logon ki be-rukhii badhtii hi gaee to main (eik din) abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ke baagh ki diwar par chadh gaya, wo mere chacha zaad bhai they aur mujhey unse bahut gehra talluq tha, maine unhein salam kya, lekin Allah ki qism ! unhon-ne bhi mere salam ka jawab nahi diya. maine kaha, abu-Qatada ! tumhen Allah ki qism ! kya tum nahi jantey ke Allah aur uske rasool se mujhey kitni mohabbat hai. unhon-ne koi jawab nahi diya. maine dobara unse yahi sawal kya Allah ki qism de kar lekin ab bhi wo khamosh they, phir maine Allah ka waasta de kar unse yahi sawal kya. is martaba unhon-ne sirf itna kaha ke Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai. is par mere aansu phoot padey. main wapas chala aaya aur diwar par chadh kar (neechey, bahar utar aayaa) unhon-ne bayan kya ke aik din mein Madina ke bazar mein ja raha tha ke Sham (Syria) ka aik kaashtkaar jo ghalla bechney Madina aaya tha, poochh raha tha ke Kab-bin-Malik kahan rahtey hain? logon ne meri taraf ishara kya to wo mere paas aaya aur ghassaan ke badshah ka aik khat mujhey diya, us khat mein ye tahreer thaa.''ammaa ba'd! mujhey malum hua hai ke tumharey sahib (yani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) tumharey sath zyadti karne lagey hain. Allah Taala ne tumhen koi zaleel nahi paida kya hai ke tumhara haq zaaye kya jaey, tum hamarey paas aa jao, ham tumharey sath behtar se behtar sulook karengey.'' jab maine ye khat padha to maine kaha ke ye aik aur imtihaan aa gaya. maine us khat ko tannoor mein jalaa diya. un pachaas dinon mein se jab chalis (40) din guzar chukey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke eilchii mere paas aaey aur kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen hukm diya hai ke apni biwi ke bhi qareeb na jao . maine puchha mein usey talaaq de dun ya phir mujhey kya karna chahiye ? unhon-ne bataya ke nahi sirf unse juda raho, unke qareeb na jao mere donon sathiyon ko (jinhon ne meri tarah ma'zirat ki thi) bhi yahi hukm aap ne bheja tha. maine apni biwi se kaha ke ab apne ghar chali jao aur us waqt tak wahin raho jab tak Allah Taala us maamle ka koi faisla na kar de. Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Hilaal-bin-Umayya (jinka muqaatiaa hua tha) ki biwi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : ya Rasulullah! Hilal bin Umayya bahut hi boodhey aur kamzor hain, unke paas koi khaadim bhi nahi hai, kya agar main unki khidmat kar diya karun to aap na-pasand farmaaengey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sirf wo tum se sohbat na karein. unhon-ne arz ki. Allah ki qism ! wo to kisi cheez ke liye harkat bhi nahi kar saktey. Mina jab se ye narazgi un par hui hai wo din hai aur aaj ka din hai unke aansu thamney mein nahi aatey . mere ghar ke kuchh logon ne kaha ke jis tarah Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ko unki khidmat kartey rehney ki ijazat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne de di hai, aap bhi isi tarah ki ijazat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ley lijiye . maine kaha nahi, Allah ki qism ! main uske liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat nahi loonga, main jawan hun, malum nahi jab se ijazat leney jaun to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya farmaaein. is tarah das din aur guzar gaey aur jab se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se baat cheet karne ki manaahii farmai thi iske pachaas din poorey ho gaey. pachaaswiin raat ki subah ko jab main fajr ki Namaz padh chuka aur apne ghar ki chhat par betha hua tha, is tarah jaisa ke Allah Taala ne zikr kya hai, mera dam ghutaa ja raha tha aur zameen apni tamam wusa'ton ke bawajud mere liye tang hoti ja rahi thi ke maine aik pukarney waley ki awaz suni, Jabal Sala par chadh kar koi buland awaz se keh raha tha, aey Kab bin Maalik! tumhen bashaarat ho. unhon-ne bayan kya ke ye suntey hi main sajdey mein gir padaa aur mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke ab faraakhii ho jaeygi. fajr ki Namaz ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki bargah mein hamari tauba ki qabooliyat ka elaan kar diya tha. log mere yahan bashaarat dene ke liye aaney lagey aur mere 2 sathiyon ko bhi ja kar bashaarat di. aik sahib (Zubair-bin-Awaam (rz)) apna ghoda daudaaey aa rahe they, idhar qabila Aslam ke aik sahabi ne pahaadii par chadh kar (aawaaz di) aur awaz ghodey se zyada tez thi. jin sahabi ne ( Sala pahaadii par se) awaz di thi, jab wo mere paas bashaarat diye aaey to apne donon kapdey utaar kar is bashaarat ki khushi mein, maine unhein de diye. Allah ki qism ke us waqt un 2 kapdon ke siwa (dene ke laaiq) aur mere paas koi cheez nahi thi. Mina phir maine (abu-Qataada (Raziallahu anhu) se) 2 kapdey maang kar pahney aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, jooq dar jooq log mujh se mulaqat kartey jatey they aur mujhey tauba ki qabooliyat par bashaarat detey jatey they, kehtey they Allah ki bargah mein tauba ki qabooliyat Mubarak ho. Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, aakhir main masjid mein dakhil hua Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif rakhtey they. charon taraf sahaba ka majma' tha. Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) daud kar meri taraf badhey aur mujh se musaafa kya aur mubaarkbaad di. Allah ki qism ! ( wahan maujood ( muhajireen mein se koi bhi unke siwaa, mere aaney par khada nahi hua. Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye ehsan main kabhi nahi bhoolonga. Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya to aap ne farmaya : (chehra Mubarak khushi aur musarrat damak utha tha) us Mubarak din ke liye tumhen bashaarat ho jo tumhari umr ka sabse Mubarak din hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ye bashaarat aap ki taraf se hai ya Allah Taala ki taraf se ? farmaya nahi, balke Allah ki taraf se hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi baat par khush hotey to chehra Mubarak roshan ho jata tha, aisa jaisey chaand ka tukda ho. aap ki musarrat ham to chehra Mubarak se samajh jatey they. phir jab main aap ke samney baith gaya to arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! apni tauba ki qabooliyat ki khushi mein, main apna maal Allah aur uske rasool ki raah mein sadqa kar dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya lekin kuchh maal apne paas bhi rakh lo, ye zyada behtar hai. maine arz kya phir main khaibar ka hissa apne paas rakh loonga. phir maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala ne mujhey sach bolney ki wjah se nijat di. Mina ab main apni tauba ki qabooliyat ki khushi mein ye ahad karta hun ke jab tak zinda rahunga sach ke siwa aur koi baat zaban par na laaunga. to Allah ki qasam! jab se maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ye ahad kya, main kisi aisey musalman ko nahi janta jisey Allah ne sach bolney ki wjah se itna nawaza ho, jitni nawaazishein uski mujh par sach bolney ki wjah se hain. jab se maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ye ahad kya, phir aaj tak kabhi jhoot ka irada bhi nahi kya aur mujhey ummeed hai ke Allah Taala baqi zindagi mein bhi mujhey us se mehfooz rakhega aur Allah Taala ne apne rasool par aayat ( hamarey barey mein) nazil ki thi. '' yaqinan Allah Taala ne Nabi , muhajireen aur Ansar ki tauba qabool ki '' iske irshad (وكونوا مع الصادقين) tak Allah ki qism ! Allah Taala ki taraf se Islam ke liye hidayat ke ba'd, meri nazar main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney us sach bolney se badh kar Allah ka mujh par aur koi inaam nahi hua ke maine jhoot nahi bola aur is tarah apne ko halaak nahi kya. jaisa ke jhoot bolney waley halaak ho gaey they. nuzoole-wahi ke zamane mein jhoot bolney walon par Allah Taala ne itni sakht dhamkii di jitni sakht dhamkii kisi doosrey ke liye nahi di hogi. Mina farmaya hai (سيحلفون بالله لكم إذا انقلبتم) irshaad (فإن الله لا يرضى an (an) القوم الفاسقين) tak. Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya. chunanche ham teen , un logon ke mamley se juda rahe jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney qism kha li thi aur aap ne unki baat maan bhi li thi, unse bait bhi li thi aur unke liye maghfirat bhi talab farmai thi. hamara mamla Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhod diya tha aur Allah Taala ne khud iska faisla farmaya tha. Allah Taala ke irshad ( وعلى الثلاثة الذين خلفوا‏ ( se yahi murad hai ke hamara muqaddima multawii rakha gaya aur ham dheel mein daal diye gaey. ye nahi murad hai ke jihad se peechhey reh gaey balke matlab ye hai ke un logon ke peechhey rahe jinhoney qasmein kha kar apne uzr bayan kiye aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke uzr qabool kar liye."
4419,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maqam hijr se guzrey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un logon ki bastiyon se jinhoney apni jaanon par zulm kya tha, jab guzarna ho to rotey huey hi guzro, aisa na ho ke tum par bhi wahi azab aa jaey jo un par aaya tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar Mubarak par chadar daal li aur badi tezi ke sath chalney lagey, yahan tak ke us wadi se nikal aaey."
4420,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ashaab hijr ke mutaalliq farmaya ke us (mua'zzab) qaum ki basti se jab tumhen guzarna hi hai to tum rotey huey guzro, kahin tum par bhi wo azab na aa jaey jawan par aaya tha."
4421,"ham se Yahya-bin-Bukair ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Lais-bin-Sad ne, unse Abdul-Azeez bin abi Salma ne, unse Sad bin Ibrahim ne, unse Naafe bin Juber ne, unse Urwa-bin-Mugheera ne aur unse unke walid Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye tashrif ley gaey they, phir (jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farigh ho kar wapas aaey too) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu ke liye main pani lekar hazir hua, jahan tak mujhey yaqin hai unhoney yahi bayan kya ke ye waqia jange-tabook ka hai, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chehra Mubarak dhoya aur jab kohniyon tuk dhoney ka irada kya to jubbe ki aasteen tang niklii. chunanche aapney hath jubbey ke nichey se nikal liye aur unhein dhoya, phir mozon par masah kyaa."
4422,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ham jange-Tabook se wapas aa rahe they. jab aap Madina ke qareeb pahunchey to (Madina ki taraf ishara karke ( farmaya ke ye ( طابة ( hai aur ye Uhud pahaad hai, ye ham se mohabbat rakhta hai aur ham us se mohabbat rakhtey hain."
4423,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jange-Tabook se wapas huey aur Madina ke qareeb pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Madina mein bahut se aisey log hain ke jahan bhi tum chaley aur jis wadi ko bhi tum ne qata' kya wo (apne dil se) tumharey saath-saath they. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! halaanki unka qiyam us waqt bhi Madina mein hi raha ho? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan, wo Madina mein rahtey huey bhi (apne dil se tumharey sath they) wo kisi uzr ki wjah se ruk gaey they."
4424,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (shaah faaras) Kisraa ke paas apna khat Abdullah-bin Huzafa Sehmi (Raziallahu anhu) ko de kar bheja aur unhein hukm diya ke ye khat Bahrain ke governer ko de dein (jo Kisraa ka aalim tha) Kisraa ne jab aap ka khat Mubarak padha to iske tukdey tukdey kar diye. mera khayal hai ke ibne-Musaiyab ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye baddua ki ke wo bhi tukdey tukdey ho jaaein.
4425,"jange-jamal ke mauqe par wo jumla mere kaam aa gaya jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha. main irada kar chuka tha ke ashaab jamal, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur aap ke lashkar ke sath Sharik ho kar (Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki) fauj se ladun. unhon-ne bayan kya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko malum hua ke ahal Faaris ne Kisraa ki ladki ko waarise-takht w taaj banaya hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo qaum kabhi falaah nahi pa sakti jisne apna hukmaraan kisi aurat ko banaya ho."
4426,mujhey yad hai jab main bachchon ke sath saniiyatul-wadaa' ki taraf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka istiqbaal karne gaya tha. Sufiyan ne aik martaba (مع الغلمان) ke bajaey) (مع الصبيان) bayan kya.
4427,"mujhey yad hai, jab main bachchon ke sath Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka istiqbaal karne gaya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jange-Tabook se wapas tashrif la rahe they."
4428,"aur Yunus ne bayan kya, unse Zohri ne, unse Urwa ne bayan kya aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne wafat k marz mein farmatey they ke khaibar main ( zahar aalud ( luqma jo maine apne munh mein rakh liya tha, uski takleef aaj bhi mein mehsus karta hun. aisa malum hota hai ke meri sheh-rag us zahar ki takleef se kat jaeygi."
4429,"maine suna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maghrib ki Namaz main (Mursalaat عرفا‏) ki qirat kar rahe they, iske baad phir aap ne hamein kabhi Namaz nahi padhai, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne aap ki Rooh qabz kar li."
4430,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) aapko (majaalis mein) apne qareeb bithatey they. is par Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne aetraz kya ke us jaisey to hamarey bachchey hain. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke maine ye tarze-amal jis wjah se ikhtiyar kya, wo aapko malum bhi hai? phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se us aayat (yani ) (إذا جاء نصر الله والفتح) ke mutaalliq poochha. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat thi, aapko Allah Taala ne (aayat mein) usi ki itlaa di hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke jo tum ne bataya wahi mein bhi us aayat ke mutaalliq janta hun."
4431,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne jumerat ke din ka zikr kya aur farmaya malum bhi hai jumerat ke din kya hua tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke marz mein tezi paida hui thi. us waqt aap ne farmaya ke laao, main tumharey liye wasiiyat naamaa likh dun ke tum is par chalo gey to iske baad phir tum kabhi sahi rastey ko na chhodo gey lekin ye sun kar wahan ikhtilaf paida ho gaya, halanke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney jhagda na hona chahiye kuchh logon ne kaha ke kya aap shiddate-marz ki wjah se be mana kalam farma rahe hain? (jo aap ki shaan ke khilaf hai) phir aap se baat samajhney ki koshish karo. to aap se sahaba poochhney lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jao (yahaan shor-ghul na karo) main jis kaam mein mashghool hun, wo us se behtar hai jiske liye tum keh rahe ho. iske baad aap ne sahaba ko teen chizon ki wasiiyat ki, farmaya ke mushrekeen ko jazeera Arab se nikal do. eilchii (jo qabaayel ke tumharey paas aaein) unki is tarah khaatir kya karna jis tarah mein karta aaya hun aur teesri baat Ibne-Abbas ne ya Saeed ne bayan nahi ki ya Saeed-bin-Jubair ne ya Sulaiman ne kaha, main teesri baat bhool gaya."
4432,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ka waqt qareeb hua to ghar mein bahut se sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) maujood they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya ke laao, main tumharey liye aik dastaawez likh dun, agar tum is par chaltey rahe to phir tum gumrah na ho sakogey. is par (Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par bimari ki sakhti ho rahi hai, tumharey paas Quran maujood hai. hamarey liye to Allah ki kitab bas kafi hai. phir ghar walon mein jhagdaa honey laga, kuchh ne to ye kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko koi cheez likhney ki de do ke is par aap hidayat likhwaa dein aur tum iske baad gumrah na ho sako. kuchh logon ne iske khilaf dusri raey par israar kya. jab shor-ghul aur jhagda zyada hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yahan se jao. Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke museebat sabse badi ye thi ke logon ne ikhtilaf aur shor karke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wo hidayat nahi likhney di."
4433,"marzul-maut main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko bulaya aur aahista se koi baat unse kahi jis par wo roney lagiin. phir dobara aahista se koi baat kahi jis par wo hansney lagiin. phir ham ne unse iske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya tha ke aap ki wafat usi marz mein ho jaeygi, main ye sun kar roney lagi dusri martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se jab sargoshi ki to ye farmaya ke aap ke ghar ke aadmiyon mein sabse pahley mein aap se ja miloongii to main hansi thi."
4434,"marzul-maut main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko bulaya aur aahista se koi baat unse kahi jis par wo roney lagiin. phir dobara aahista se koi baat kahi jis par wo hansney lagiin. phir ham ne unse iske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya tha ke aap ki wafat usi marz mein ho jaeygi, main ye sun kar roney lagi dusri martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se jab sargoshi ki to ye farmaya ke aap ke ghar ke aadmiyon mein sabse pahley mein aap se ja miloongii to main hansi thii."
4435,"mein suntii aai thi ke har Nabi ko wafat se pahley duniya aur aakhirat ke rehney mein ikhtiyar diya jata hai, phir maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhi suna, aap apne marzul-maut mein farma rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki awaz bhari ho chuki thi. aap aayat (مع الذين أنعم الله عليهم‏) ki tilawat farma rahe they (yani un logon ke sath jin par Allah ne inaam kya hai) mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke aapko bhi ikhtiyar de diya gaya hai."
4436,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne marzul-maut mein baar-baar farmatey they. '' ( اللهم ( ) الرفيق الأعلى (aey Allah ! mujhey mere sathiyon (anbiyaa aur siddeqeen) mein pahuncha de (jo aalaa Illeeyeen mein rahtey hain).''
4437,"tandurustii ke zamaney main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they ke jab bhi kisi Nabi ki Rooh qabz ki gaee to pahley jannat mein uski qiyam gaah usey zaroor dikhaa di gaee, phir usey ikhtiyar diya gaya ( rawi ko shak tha ke lafz ( يحيا ( hai ya ( يخير ( , donon ka mafhoom aik hi hai) phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar padey aur waqt qareeb aa gaya to sar Mubarak Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki raan par tha aur aap par ghashii taarii ho gaee thi, jab kuchh hosh hua to aap ki aankhen ghar ki chhat ki taraf uth gain aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ( اللهم في الرفيق الأعلى ( . main samajh gaee ke ab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein (yani duniyawi zindagi ko) pasand nahi farmaaengey. mujhey wo hadis yad aa gaee jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tandurustii ke zamaney mein farmai thi."
4438,"(unke bhaaii) Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere seeney se tek lagaey huey they. Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath mein aik taaza miswak istemal ke liye thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us miswak ki taraf dekhtey rahe. chunanche maine unse miswak ley li aur usey apne daanton se chabaa kar achi tarah jhadney aur saaf karne ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko de di. aap ne wo miswak istemal ki jitney umda tariqa se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt miswak kar rahe they, maine aapko itni achi tarah miswak kartey kabhi nahi dekha. miswak se farigh honey ke baad aap ne apna hath ya apni ungli uthai aur farmaya, ( في الرفيق الأعلى ( teen martaba, aur aap ka intiqal ho gaya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kaha karti thin ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to sar Mubarak meri hanslii aur thodii ke darmyan mein tha."
4439,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bimar padtey to apne uper muawwizatain ( sura Falaq aur sura Naas) padh kar dam kar liya kartey they aur apne jism par apne hath pher liya kartey they, phir jab wo marz aapko laahiq hua jis mein aap ki wafat hui to main muawwizatain padh kar aap par dam kya karti thi aur hath par dam karke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke jism par phera karti thi."
4440,"aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, wafat se kuchh pahley Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pusht se unka sahara liye huey they. aap ne kaan laga kar suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dua kar rahe hain ( اللهم اغفر لي وارحمني ‏‏‏‏ Mina وألحقني بالرفيق ) ''aey Allah ! meri maghfirat farma, mujh par raham kar aur mere rafeeqon se mujhey milaa.''"
4441,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne marzul-maut mein farmaya ke Allah Taala ne yahudiyon ko apni rehmat se door kar diya ke unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko sajda gaah bana liya tha. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke agar ye baat na hoti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qabr bhi khuli rakhi jati lekin aapko ye khatrah tha ke kahin aap ki qabr ko bhi sajda na kya janey lagey.
4442,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye uthna baithna dushwar ho gaya aur aap ke marz ne shiddat ikhtiyar kar li to tamam paak beeviyon (Raziallahu anhu) se aap ne mere ghar mein ayyaame-marz guzarney ke liye ijazat maangii. sab ne jab ijazat de di to aap Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar se nikley, aap 2 aadmiyon ka sahara liye huey they aur aap ke paon zameen se ghisat rahe they. jin 2 sahaba ka Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahara liye huey they, unmein aik Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) they aur aik aur sahib . Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke phir maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki is riwayat ki khabar Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko di to unhon-ne batlaya , malum hai wo doosrey sahib jinka naam Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne nahi liya, kon hain? bayan kya ke maine arz kya mujhey to nahi malum hai. unhon-ne batlaya ke wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti thin ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab mere ghar mein aagey aur takleef bahut badh gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke saat (7) mishkeezey pani ke bhar kar lao aur mujh par daal do, mumkin hai is tarah main logon ko kuchh nasihat karne ke qaabil ho jaun. chunanche ham ne aapko aap ki paak bevi Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke aik lagan mein bithaya aur unhein mishkezon se aap par pani dhaarney lagey. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath ke ishara se rokaa ke bas ho chukaa, bayan kya ke phir aap logon ke majme' mein gaey aur Namaz padhai aur logon ko khitab kya."
4443,"shiddate-marz ke dinon main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni chadar kheench kar baar-baar apne chehrey par daltey they, phir jab dam ghutney lagta to chehrey se hata detey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usi shiddat ke aalim mein farmatey they, yahood w nasara Allah ki rehmat se door huey kyonke unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko sajda gaah bana liya tha. is tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (apni ummat ko) unka amal ikhtiyar karne se bachtey rehney ki takeed farma rahe they."
4444,"shiddate-marz ke dinon main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni chadar kheench kar baar-baar apne chehrey par daltey they, phir jab dam ghutney lagta to chehrey se hata detey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usi shiddat ke aalim mein farmatey they, yahood w nasara Allah ki rehmat se door huey kyonke unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko sajda gaah bana liya tha. is tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (apni ummat ko) unka amal ikhtiyar karne se bachtey rehney ki takeed farma rahe they."
4445,"maine us maamle (yani dinon marz mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko imam banaaney) ke silsiley main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baar-baar poochha. main baar-baar aap se sirf isliye poochh rahi thi ke mujhey yaqin tha ke jo shakhs (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein) aap ki jagah par khada hoga, log us se kabhi mohabbat nahi rakh saktey balke mera khayal tha ke log us se bura shagoon lengey, isliye main chahti thi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko iska hukm na dein. iski riwayat ibne-Umar, abu-Musa aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ki hai."
4446,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to aap meri hanslii aur thodii ke darmyan (sar rakhey huey) they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki jaan nikalney ki shiddat) dekhney ke baad ab main kisi ke liye bhi jaan nikalney ki shiddat ko bura nahi samajhtii.
4447,"aur Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) un teen sahaba mein se aik they jinki (jange-Tabook mein shirkat na karne ki) tauba qabool hui thi. unhein Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se bahar aaey. ye us marz ka waqia hai jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wafat paai thi. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se puchha : abul-Hasan ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aaj mizaaj kya hai? subah unhon-ne bataya ke alhamdulillah ab aapko fayda hai. phir Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka hath pakad ke kaha ke tum, Allah ki qism teen din ke baad zindagi guzarney par tum majbur ho jaogey. Allah ki qasam, mujhey to aisey aasaar nazar aa rahe hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is marz se sihat nahi pa sakengey. maut ke waqt banu-abdul-Muttalib ke chehron ki mujhey khub shanaakht hai. ab hamein aap ke paas chalnaa chahiye aur aap se poochhna chahiye ke hamarey baad khilafat kisey milegii. agar ham iske mustahiq hain to hamein malum ho jaeyga aur agar koi doosra mustahiq hoga to wo bhi malum ho jaeyga aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey mutaalliq apne khaleefa ko mumkin hai kuchh wasiiyatein kar dein lekin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qasam! agar ham ne is waqt aap se iske mutaalliq kuchh puchha aur aap ne inkar kar diya to phir log hamein hamesha ke liye us se mahroom kar dengey. main to hargiz Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq kuchh nahi poochhoonga."
4448,"peer ke din musalman fajr ki Namaz padh rahe they aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padha rahe they ke achcha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nazar aaey. aap Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre ka parda utha kar sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekh rahe they. sahaba Namaz mein saf baandhey khadey huey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dekh kar hans padey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) peechhey hatney lagey taake saf mein aa jaaein. aap ne samjha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye tashrif lana chahtey hain. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, qareeb tha ke musalman us khushi ki wjah se jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh kar unhein hui thi ke wo apni Namaz todney hi ko they lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se ishara kya ke Namaz poori kar lo, phir aap hujre ke andar tashrif le gaey aur parda daal liya."
4449,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmaya karti thin, Allah ki bahut si ne'maton mein aik nemat mujh par ye bhi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat mere ghar mein aur meri baari ke din hui. aap us waqt mere seeney se tek lagaey huey they. aur ye ke Allah Taala ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke waqt mere aur aap ke thook ko aik sath jama kya tha ke Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ghar mein aaey to unke hath mein miswak thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh par tek lagaey huey they, maine dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us miswak ko dekh rahe hain. main samajh gaee ke aap miswak karna chahtey hain, isliye maine aap se poochha, ye miswak aap ke liye ley loon ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar ke ishara se asbaat mein jawab diya, maine wo miswak unse ley li. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey chabaa na sakey, maine puchha aap ke liye mein usey narm kar dun? aap ne sar ke ishaare se asbaat (positive) mein jawab diya. maine miswak narm kar di. aap ke samney aik bada piyala tha, chamdey ka ya lakdi ka (raawii hadis) umr ko is silsiley mein shak tha, iske andar pani tha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baar-baar apne hath uske andar dakhil kartey aur phir unhein apne chehrey par phertey aur farmatey ( لا إله إلا الله ). maut ke waqt shiddat hoti hai phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna hath utha kar kehney lagey ( في الرفيق الأعلى ( yahan tak ke aap rihlat farma gaey aur aap ka hath jhuk gaya."
4450,"marzul-maut main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) poochhtey rahtey they ke kal mera qiyam kahan hoga, kal mera qiyam kahan hoga? aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari ke muntazir they, phir paak beeviyon (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar qiyam ki ijazat de di aur aapki wafat unhiin ke ghar mein hui. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke aap ki wafat isi din hui jis din qaaeyde ke mutabiq mere yahan aap ke qiyam ki baari thi. rihlat ke waqt sar Mubarak mere seeney par tha aur mera thook aap ke thook ke sath mila tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) dakhil huey aur unke hath mein istemal ke qaabil miswak thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf dekha to maine kaha : Abdur-Rehmaan! ye miswak mujhey de do. unhon-ne miswak mujhey de di. maine usey achi tarah chabaayaa aur jhaad kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di, phir aap ne wo miswak ki, us waqt aap mere seeney se tek lagaey huey they."
4451,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat mere ghar mein, meri baari ke din hui. aap us waqt mere seeney se tek lagaey huey they. jab aap bimar padey to ham aap ki sihat ke liye duaein kya kartey they. us bimari mein bhi mein aap ke liye dua karne lagi lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they aur aap ka sar aasman ki taraf utha hua tha ( في الرفيق الأعلى في الرفيق الأعلى (aur Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) aaey to unke hath mein aik taaza tahnii thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf dekha to main samajh gaee ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) miswak karna chahtey hain. chunanche wo tahnii maine unse ley li. pahley maine usey chabaayaa, phir saaf karke aapko de di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se miswak ki, jis tarah pahley aap miswak kya kartey they us se bhi achi tarah se. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo miswak mujhey inayat farmai aur aap ka hath jhuk gaya, ya (raawii ne ye bayan kya ke) miswak aap ke hath se chhoot gaee. is tarah Allah Taala ne mere aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke thook ko us din jama kar diya jo aap ki duniya ki zindagi ka sabse aakhiri aur aakhirat ki zindagi ka sabse pahlaa din tha."
4452,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) apni qiyam gaah, Sunh se ghodey par aaey aur aa kar utrey , phir masjid ke andar gaey. kisi se aap ne koi baat nahi ki. iske baad aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre mein aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf gaey, laash Mubarak aik yamnii chadar se dhakii hui thi. aap ne chehra khola aur jhuk kar chehra Mubarak ko bosa diya aur roney lagey, phir kaha mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon Allah ki qism ! Allah Taala aap par 2 martaba maut taarii nahi karega. jo aik maut aap ke muqaddar mein thi, wo aap par taarii ho chuki hai."
4453,"abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) apni qiyam gaah, Sunh se ghodey par aaey aur aa kar utrey , phir masjid ke andar gaey. kisi se aap ne koi baat nahi ki. iske baad aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre mein aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf gaey, laash Mubarak aik yamnii chadar se dhakii hui thi. aap ne chehra khola aur jhuk kar chehra Mubarak ko bosa diya aur roney lagey, phir kaha mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon Allah ki qism ! Allah Taala aap par 2 martaba maut taarii nahi karega. jo aik maut aap ke muqaddar mein thi, wo aap par taarii ho chuki hai."
4454,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) logon se kuchh keh rahe they Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : umr ! baith jao, lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne baithney se inkar kya. itney mein log umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko chhod kar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aagey aur aap ne khutba masnoona ke baad farmaya : ammaa ba'd! tum mein jo bhi Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ibadat karta tha to usey malum hona chahiye ke aap ki wafat ho chuki hai aur jo Allah Taala ki ibadat karta tha to (uska ma'bood) Allah hamesha zinda rehney wala hai aur usko kabhi maut nahi aaeygi. Allah Taala ne khud farmaya hai (وما محمد إلا رسول قد خلت من قبله الرسل) ke '' Muhammad sirf rasool hain, unse pahley bhi rasool guzar chukey hain.'' irshad ( الشاكرين‏ ( tak. ibne-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya : Allah ki qism ! aisa mehsus hua ke jaisey pahley se logon ko malum hi nahi tha ke Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki hai aur jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski tilawat ki to sab ne unse ye aayat seekhii. ab ye haal tha ke jo bhi sunta tha wahi uski tilawat karne lag jata tha. (Zohri ne bayan kya ke) phir mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne khabar di ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! mujhey us waqt hosh aaya, jab maine Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko us aayat ki tilawat kartey suna, jis waqt maine unhein tilawat kartey suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee hai to main saktey mein aa gaya aur aisa mehsus hua ke mere paon mera bojh nahi utha paaengey aur main zameen par gir jaaunga."
4455,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapko bosa diya tha.
4456,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapko bosa diya tha.
4457,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapko bosa diya tha.
4458,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke marz mein ham aap ke munh mein dawaa dene lagey to aap ne ishara se dawaa deney se mana kya. ham ne samjha ke mareez ko dawaa peeney se (kuchh auqaat) jo na-gawari hoti hai ye bhi usi ka nateeja hai (is liye ham ne israar kya) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghar mein jitney aadmi hain sab ke munh mein mere samney dawaa dali jaey. sirf Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) us se alag hain ke wo tumharey sath us kaam mein Sharik nahi they. iski riwayat ibne-abii-zanaad ne bhi ki, unse Hisham ne, unse unke walid ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se."
4459,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke samney iska zikr aaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko koi ( khas ( wasiiyat ki thi? to unhon-ne batlaya kon kehta hai, main khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir thi, aap mere seeney se tek lagaey huey they, aap ne tasht mangwaayaa, phir aik taraf jhuk gaey aur aap ki wafat ho gaee. us waqt mujhey bhi kuchh malum nahi hua, phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko aap ne Kab wasii bana diya."
4460,"maine Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi ko wasii banaya tha. unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. maine puchha ke logon par wasiiyat karna kaisey farz hai ya wasiiyat karne ka kaisey hukm hai? unhon-ne bataya ke aap ne kitabullah ke mutabiq amal kartey rehney ki wasiiyat ki thi."
4461,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne na dirham chhodey they, na diinaar, na koi ghulam na baandii, siwa apne safaid khachchar ke jis par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sawar hua kartey they aur aap ka hathiyar aur kuchh wo zameen jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni zindagi mein mujaahidon aur musaafiron ke liye waqf kar rakhi thi."
4462,"shiddate-marz ke zamaney main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki be-chainii bahut badh gaee thi. Fatima zohra (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aah, abba jaan ko kitni be chainii hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke aaj ke baad tumharey abba jaan ki ye be-chainii nahi rahegii. phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee to Fatima (Raziallahu anha) kehti thin, haaye abba jaan! aap apne rab ke bulaawey par chaley gaey, haaye abba jaan! aap jannatul-firdaus main apne maqam par chaley gaey. ham Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ko aap ki wafat ki khabar sunatey hain. phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dafn kar diye gaey to aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha '' Anas! tumharey dil Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki laash par mitti dalney ke liye kis tarah aamada ho gaey they.''"
4463,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) haalate-sihat mein farmaya kartey they ke har Nabi ki Rooh qabz karne se pahley unhein jannat mein unki qiyam gaah dikhai gaee, phir ikhtiyar diya gaya. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar huey aur aap ka sar Mubarak meri raan par tha. us waqt aap par ghashii taarii ho gaee. jab hosh mein aaey to aap ne apni nazar ghar ki chhat ki taraf utha li aur farmaya ( اللهم الرفيق الأعلى ( ''aey Allah ! mujhey apni bargah mein anbiya aur siddeqeen se mila de. ''main usi waqt samajh gaee ke ab aap hamein pasand nahi kar saktey aur mujhey wo hadis yad aa gaee jo aap haalat sihat mein ham se bayan kya kartey they. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke aakhiri kalima jo zaban Mubarak se nikla wo yahi tha ke) اللهم الرفيق الأعلى ( ."
4464,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (nabi banaey janey ke baad) Makka mein das saal tak qiyam kya. jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil hoti rahi aur Madina mein bhi das saal tak aap ka qiyam raha.
4465,nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (nabi banaey janey ke baad) Makka mein das saal tak qiyam kya. jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil hoti rahi aur Madina mein bhi das saal tak aap ka qiyam rahaa.
4466,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to aap ki umr tiresath saal ki thi. ibne-Shahab ne kaha ke mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bhi isi tarah khabar di thi.
4467,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to aap ki zirah aik Yahudi ke yahan tees saa jau ke badley mein girwii rakhi hui thi.
4468,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko aik lashkar ka ameer banaya to kuchh sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki amaarat par aetraz kya. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey malum hua hai ke tum Usama (Raziallahu anhu) par aetraz kar rahe ho halanke wo mujhey sabse zyada azeez hai.
4469,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik lashkar rawaana farmaya aur iska ameer Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya. kuchh logon ne unki amaarat par aetraz kya. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko khitab kya aur farmaya ke agar aaj tum iski imaarat par aetraz kartey ho to tum us se pahley iske walid ki imaarat par isi tarah aetraz kar chukey ho aur Allah ki qism ! iske walid ( Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) amaarat ke bahut laaiq they aur mujhey sabse zyada azeez they aur ye (yani Usama (Raziallahu anhu)) bhi unke baad mujhey sabse zyada azeez hai.
4470,"tum ne Kab hijrat ki thi? unhon-ne bayan kya ke ham hijrat ke iraadey se Yaman chaley, abhi ham maqam Johfa mein pahunchey they ke aik sawar se hamari mulaqat hui. ham ne unse Madina ki khabar poochhi to unhon-ne bataya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ko panch din ho chukey hain maine puchha tum ne lailatul-Qadr ke barey mein koi hadis suni hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke haan, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke muazzan Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey khabar di hai ke lailatul-Qadr Ramazan ke aakhiri Ashrey ke saat (7) dinon mein (eik taaq raat ( hoti hai."
4471,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tum ne kitni jangein ladii thiin? unhon-ne bataya ke sattarah. maine puchha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kitney ghazwey kiye they? farmaya ke unnees.
4472,main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath pandarah jangon mein Sharik raha hun.
4473,wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sola jangon mein Sharik they.
